    # "And Hiroko, for her part, is sitting and watching calmly, albeit with a bewildered look on her face." with dissolve
    "Y Hiroko, por su parte, está observando con mucha calma, a pesar de la mirada desconcertada en su rostro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:728
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_afff5a6c_1:

    # "I'm sure her first time getting hypnotized is as confusing as it is exciting for her."
    "Estoy seguro de que su primera vez siendo hipnotizada le es tan confusa como emocionante."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:729
