# game/Kyou 6.rpy:787
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_e1b06e30:

    # ks frown "That's right, girls. Perfectly relaxed. Perfectly calm and willing to listen."
    ks frown "Eso es, chichas. Perfectamente relajadas. Perfectamente calmadas y listas para escuchar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:788
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_8fa799f7:

    # "There, both of them out like lights. And that can only mean one thing: That they were willing to be hypnotized."
    "Listo, luces fuera para ambas. Y eso solo puede significar una cosa: Estaban dispuestas a ser hipnotizadas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:789
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_2e5ea1f2:

    # "I breathe a small sigh of relief. I admit I kinda doubted myself for a little while there, but the evidence is sat before my eyes."
    "Suelto un leve suspiro de alivio. Admito que dudé un poco de mí por un momento, pero la evidencia yace frente a mis ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:790
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_022c1c10:

    # "And that relief gives way to a little anger after the shit they just put me through."
    "Y ese alivio da lugar a un poco de ira luego de la mierda por la que me hicieron pasar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:791
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_2f793c53:

    # "I mean, really? Rough me up and ransack my room? You can't just say this shit to someone out of the blue."
    "Es que, ¿en serio? ¿Atacarme y saquear mi habitación? No pueden venir a decirme esa mierda así como así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:792
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_07486909:

    # "So it's time to make them confess the real reason they're here. No more of these childish games."
    "Así que es hora de confesar la verdadera razón por la que están aquí. No más juegos infantiles."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:793
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_ec482666:

    # ks "So, girls, now that you're so calm and relaxed and deeply entranced, I think it's time for you both to be honest with me."
    ks "Entonces, chichas, ahora que están calmadas y relajadas y en un profundo trance, creo que es momento de que ambas sean honestas conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:794
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_8d6c82c8:

    # ks "When you came to me today, your true intention was to have me hypnotize you, wasn't it?"
    ks "Cuando vinieron a mí hoy, su verdadera intención era que las hipnotizara, ¿no es así? "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:801
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_495d81ea:

    # multi "No..." with dissolve
    multi "No…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:802
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_91642d52:

    # "Given the evidence I'm finding that REALLY hard to believe..."
    "Dada la evidencia, eso me parece MUY difícil de creer…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:809
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_1016d800:

    # ks frown "It's alright, girls. You can say what's in your hearts. There is no need to be anything but completely honest with me." with dissolve
    ks frown "Está bien, chicas. Pueden decir lo que hay en sus corazones. No hace falta ser nada menos que completamente honestas conmigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:810
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f3312816:

    # ks "So I'll ask you both again: Was your true intention today for me to hypnotize you?"
    ks "Así que volveré a preguntarles: ¿Su verdadera intención era que las hipnotizara?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:817
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_495d81ea_1:

    # multi "No..." with dissolve
    multi "No…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:825
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_304bfc1a:

    # "Ugh, even while hypnotized they're still somehow managing to be stubborn." with dissolve
    "Ay, incluso estando hipnotizadas, se las arreglan para ser obstinadas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:826
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f4e01be6:

    # "They seemed pretty furious with me just now, as if they really did believe that \"brainwashing\" bullshit."
    "Parecían bastante furiosas conmigo hace un momento, como si de verdad se creyeran esa mierda del \"lavado de cerebro\"."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:827
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_9edad778:

    # "But again, the facts are clear. I know I'm right about their true intentions."
    "Pero de nuevo, los hechos son claros. Sé que tengo razón en cuanto a sus verdaderas intenciones."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:828
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_6315342b:

    # "If they seriously believed that crap, they never would've let me put them under. Not in a million years."
    "Si en verdad creyeran esa porquería, nunca me habrían dejado ponerlas en trance. Ni en un millón de años."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:829
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_a88b4094:

    # "I just need to make them realize they can't hide their embarrassing truth from me any longer."
    "Solo tengo que hacerlas darse cuenta de que ya no me pueden ocultar su bochornosa verdad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:830
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_aee1c65b:

    # ks "But Nozomi, consider how easy it was to fall back into a nice relaxing trance under me. How natural and right it felt to do so."
    ks "Pero Nozomi, considera lo fácil que fue caer en un agradable y relajante trance ante mí. Lo natural y correcto que se sintió."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:831
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_70d363d8:

    # ks "You could have resisted, Nozomi, if you truly wanted to. It's a fact that you cannot hypnotize an unwilling subject."
    ks "Pudiste haber resistido, Nozomi, si en verdad hubieras querido. Es un hecho que no puedes hipnotizar a un sujeto indispuesto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:833
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_5974e0b5:

    # n "Not... n-not will- {w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    n "In… i-indis- {w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:835
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_956a8356:

    # ks irritated "You need to stop lying, Nozomi. You cannot argue with the simple fact that you allowed yourself to be hypnotized."
    ks irritated "Debes dejar de mentir, Nozomi. No puedes discutir el simple hecho de que te dejaste hipnotizar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:837
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_32bbca40:

    # ks frown "You were hypnotized. And ultimately that was your choice. Don't you agree, Nozomi?" with dissolve
    ks frown "Fuiste hipnotizada. Y ultimadamente, esa fue tu elección. ¿No estás de acuerdo, Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:839
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_8ccbf24e:

    # n "A-... Agree..." with dissolve
    n "De a-… cuerdo…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:841
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_8980cdc6:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. You cannot argue this simple logic." with dissolve
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. No puedes argumentar contra esta simple lógica." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:842
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_fb9a0992:

    # ks "This is the third time I have hypnotized you now, Nozomi. The third time you chose, so very willingly, to fall into a deep relaxing trance for me."
    ks "Esta es la tercera vez que te he hipnotizado, Nozomi. La tercera vez que elijes, tan dispuesta, caer en este profundo y relajado trance para mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:843
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_5f195c94:

    # ks "It's obvious then, that for all your angry protestations earlier, you actually love to be hypnotized but you are deeply ashamed of that fact."
    ks "Entonces es obvio que, a pesar de todas tus protestas de hace un momento, en realidad te encanta ser hipnotizada, pero eso te apena."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:845
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_a7265f4f:

    # ks "So you concocted an absurd story about me \"brainwashing\" Sayori and that she needed your help, when in reality you always knew she was fine."
    ks "Por lo que inventaste una absurda historia sobre mí \"lavándole el cerebro\" a Sayori y que necesitaba tu ayuda; cuando, en realidad, siempre supiste que estaba bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:847
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_c0911bee:

    # n "I... w-wha..." with dissolve
    n "In… ¿q-qué...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:849
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_b0ccd790:

    # ks "So you concocted an absurd story about me \"brainwashing\" Hiroko and that she needed your help, when in reality you always knew she was fine."
    ks "Por lo que inventaste una absurda historia sobre mí \"lavándole el cerebro\" a Hiroko y que necesitaba tu ayuda; cuando, en realidad, siempre supiste que estaba bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1066
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_bdff931f:

    # n "I... w-wha...?" with dissolve
    n "¿In… qu-qué...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1070
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_bdff931f_1:

    # n "I... w-wha...?" with dissolve
    n "¿In… qu-qué...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:852
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_0632c657:

    # "I'll just keep talking through what I think is going on with her and the truth will surface, I'm sure."
    "Solo seguiré hablando de lo que creo que está pasando y la verdad saldrá a la superficie, estoy seguro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:854
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_ba96d382:

    # ks "When you were hypnotized at the culture fest last year, you loved the experience so much that you wanted to be hypnotized again." with dissolve
    ks "Cuando fuiste hipnotizada en el festival cultural del año pasado, la experiencia te encantó tanto que querías ser hipnotizada otra vez." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:855
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_2cc94673:

    # ks "You didn't realize that I was hypnotizing you at first, because I wanted you to forget."
    ks "No te diste cuenta de que te estaba hipnotizando al principio porque quería que lo olvidaras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:856
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_24619fba:

    # ks "But the moment you discovered what had happened you were desperate for more."
    ks "Pero cuando descubriste lo que había pasado, estabas desesperada por más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:857
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_bbcbae5d:

    # ks "But you couldn't just ask to be hypnotized, Nozomi. You were too embarrassed to admit your desires."
    ks "Pero no podías simplemente pedir ser hipnotizada, Nozomi. Estabas demasiado avergonzada de admitir tus deseos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:858
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_6ea7e96a:

    # ks "That's why you needed a cover story. You could confront me over an imagined outrage and let yourself be \"tricked\" into going under for me."
    ks "Es por eso que necesitabas encubrirlo con una historia. Así podías enfrentarme por una indignación imaginaria para que te \"engañara\" y te pusiera en trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:860
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_976d66b9:

    # ks "All you really wanted was to be hypnotized again and you simply couldn't admit it to Hiroko or to me."
    ks "Lo único que realmente querías era ser hipnotizada otra vez y simplemente no pudiste admitírselo a Hiroko o a mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:862
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_63a65840:

    # ks "All you really wanted was to be hypnotized again and you simply couldn't admit it to Sayori or to me."
    ks "Lo único que realmente querías era ser hipnotizada otra vez y simplemente no pudiste admitírselo a Sayori o a mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:863
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_4f01e75d:

    # ks "And that's what's really going on with you. Isn't it, Nozomi?"
    ks "Y eso es lo que en verdad está pasando. ¿No es así, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:865
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f4dc6f6e:

    # n "U...uh..." with dissolve
    n "E-… eh…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:866
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_51f80b10:

    # ks "No more denial, Nozomi. I've laid out the facts clearly, and you must accept the truth of my words. Yes?"
    ks "Basta ya de negación, Nozomi. He expuesto los hechos claramente, y debes aceptar la verdad de mis palabras. ¿Sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:867
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_78604936:

    # n "Y-{w=1.0}...yes..." with dissolve
    n "S-{w=1.0}… sí…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:869
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_cd6ac7f2:

    # ks "That's right. It feels good to accept the truth, Nozomi." with dissolve
    ks "Eso es. Se siente tan bien aceptar la verdad, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:870
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f383c911:

    # "I next turn to look at the other girl sitting entranced on my bed."
    "Posteriormente volteo a ver a la otra chica, sentada en mi cama en trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:872
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_de8f3990:

    # ks "And Sayori, you must have been curious about hypnosis after hearing about it from Nozomi. Very curious."
    ks "Y Sayori, debes haber tenido curiosidad por ser hipnotizada, luego de oírlo de Nozomi. Mucha curiosidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:874
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_26649dfc:

    # s "Very curious..." with dissolve
    s "Curiosidad…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:876
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_85dc7ca7:

    # ks "So then, when you agreed to come here with Nozomi you knew you could be hypnotized. Did that thought excite you?" with dissolve
    ks "Entonces, cuando aceptaste venir con Nozomi, sabías que podrías ser hipnotizada. ¿Esa idea te emocionó?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:878
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_e0e88708:

    # s "... No?" with dissolve
    s "… ¿No?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:880
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_bdd85605:

    # "Bullshit." with dissolve
    "Pura mierda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:881
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_44badc4c:

    # ks frown "Sayori, it's obvious that you're not being honest with me."
    ks frown "Sayori, es evidente que no estás siendo honesta conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:882
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_4ec2afc6:

    # ks "Just like Nozomi, you were very eager, very willing, to fall into a trance for me."
    ks "Al igual que Nozomi, estabas ansiosa y muy dispuesta a caer en trance para mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:883
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_44a3d47a:

    # ks "So in reality, when Nozomi told you her plan you were very excited at the prospect of becoming hypnotized. You even skipped cram school to come here."
    ks "Por lo que, en realidad, cuando Nozomi te contó sus planes, te emocionó mucho la posibilidad de ser hipnotizada. Hasta te saltaste los cursos nocturnos para venir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:885
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_64ee79a4:

    # s "N... t-that's not..." with dissolve
    s "N-… e-so no…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:887
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_ef6d890f:

    # ks "And you went along with Nozomi's crazy story about Hiroko being \"brainwashed\"." with dissolve
    ks "Y le seguiste el juego a la loca historia de Nozomi sobre que a Hiroko le \"lavaron el cerebro\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:888
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_77d5b8c5:

    # ks "By doing that, you could come here and satisfy your curiosity without revealing your true intentions."
    ks "Haciendo eso, pudiste venir aquí y satisfacer tu curiosidad sin revelar tus verdaderas intenciones."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:889
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_ee5588f6:

    # ks "Isn't that right?"
    ks "¿No es eso cierto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:891
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_1d02fcd5:

    # s "T-that's..." with dissolve
    s "E- eso…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:892
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_e0c9c2fa:

    # ks "Just admit it, Sayori. To me, to Nozomi and to yourself. You're not fooling anyone."
    ks "Solo admítelo, Sayori. A mí, a Nozomi y a ti misma. No estás engañando a nadie."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:893
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_979c9e03:

    # ks "Are you?"
    ks "¿O sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:894
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_5b135898:

    # s "N-no...not fooling anyone..."
    s "E-engañando… a nadie…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:897
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_599a6954:

    # ks "And Hiroko, you must have been curious about hypnosis after hearing about it from Nozomi. Very curious."
    ks "Y Hiroko, debes haber tenido curiosidad por ser hipnotizada, luego de oírlo de Nozomi. Mucha curiosidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1118
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f49055af:

    # h sleeptalk_concerned "Y-yeah... very curious..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk_concerned "S-sí... curiosidad…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:901
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_85dc7ca7_1:

    # ks "So then, when you agreed to come here with Nozomi you knew you could be hypnotized. Did that thought excite you?" with dissolve
    ks "Entonces, cuando aceptaste venir con Nozomi, sabías que podrías ser hipnotizada. ¿Esa idea te emocionó?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:903
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_e40951be:

    # h "Eh? N-no..." with dissolve
    h "¿Eh? N-no…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:905
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_bdd85605_1:

    # "Bullshit." with dissolve
    "Pura mierda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:906
