    # ks "Yeah. Fair enough, I guess."
    ks "Sí. Comprendo, supongo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1173
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_97b98ecd:

    # "She crosses her legs as she reclines a little on the café chair, keeping her arms folded defensively."
    "Cruza las piernas y se reclina un poco en la silla de la cafetería, manteniendo sus brazos cruzados defensivamente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1177
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_66f30f42:

    # ks "I don't have it, by the way. If that's what you're wondering?"
    ks "No la tengo, por cierto. Por si te lo preguntabas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1176
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6b8d4193:

    # n "No?" with dissolve
    n "¿No?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1179
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f6e41f78:

    # "I hold my hands open to show her there's nothing hiding there, then lay them flat on the table."
    "Alzo mis manos abiertas para mostrarle que no hay nada oculto, luego coloco las palmas sobre la mesa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1180
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6860fb99:

    # ks sigh "No. I realize that penlight freaks you out, and I understand that."
    ks sigh "No. Me doy cuenta de que esa linterna te causa pánico, y eso lo entiendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1181
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c29baf13:

