    # n sigh "Oh, you know. I've only had one anxiety attack this morning." with dissolve
    n sigh "Oh, ya sabes. Tuve un solo ataque de ansiedad esta mañana." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1276
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_223ea4d7:

    # n "So... good, I guess?"
    n "Así que… bien, ¿supongo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1277
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_689ec14d:

    # s "\"I am so sorry you are going through this.\""
    s "\"Lamento que estés pasando por esto.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1278
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3aa49de1:

    # n "Thanks..."
    n "Gracias…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1279
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_311a1df0:

    # n side sad_side "..." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1281
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d6de36dd:

    # n sad_closed "I upset my brother yesterday." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Hice enojar a mi hermano ayer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1282
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_24701b67:

    # s "\"What?\""
    s "\"¿Qué?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1283
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6472bf2f:

    # n "You know he goes to our school, right?"
    n "Ya sabes que va a nuestra escuela, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1284
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4896664f:

    # s "\"Of course.\""
    s "\"Desde luego.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1285
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a7db0db1:

    # n sad_side "Obviously I wasn't coming to school, so I laid in a bit. And then I got up to use the bathroom." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Obviamente yo no iba a ir a la escuela, así que me recosté un rato. Y luego me levanté para ir al baño." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1287
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a98ff5de:

    # n front sleeptalk_concerned "And just as I come out of my room, the bathroom door opens and he's standing there." with dissolve
    n front sleeptalk_concerned "Y justo cuando salgo de mi habitación, la puerta del baño se abre y ahí está él." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1288
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf4760e5:

    # n "Then I just... I don't know, I just screamed at him."
    n "Y luego solo… No sé, le grité."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1289
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_051b1053:

    # s "\"...\""
    s "\"…\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1291
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cb168e12:

    # n concerned "I suppose I was still waking up, but seeing him in our school's uniform, and with his hair kinda unkempt as it was..." with dissolve
    n concerned "Supongo que todavía estaba despertando, pero al verlo con el uniforme de nuestra escuela y así de despeinado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1292
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_30d031c6:

    # n "For a second I thought it was Kyou standing there."
    n "Por un segundo pensé que era Kyou quien estaba ahí parado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1293
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f6414f40:

    # s "\"Nozomi... I am so sorry.\""
    s "\"Nozomi… lo lamento tanto.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1294
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90369dcf:

    # n "Yeah..."
    n "Seh…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1317
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e3d1f666:

    # s "\"Does your brother understand what you are going through?\""
    s "\"¿Tu hermano entiende por lo que estás pasando?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1297
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9976bd28:

    # n sigh "I don't think he does. Also, he's been having a hard time adjusting to high school and it's affected his self-esteem." with dissolve
    n sigh "No lo creo. Además, la ha pasado muy mal intentando ajustarse a la preparatoria, y eso ha afectado su autoestima." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1298
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7056b8bc:

    # n "Certainly isn't helpful having his big sister screaming at him like he's some kind of monster."
    n "Ciertamente no ayuda que su hermana mayor le grite que es alguna clase de monstruo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1299
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_39f6e5fe:

    # s "\"Please do not blame yourself for that. I'm sure he will come to understand, and your reaction seems perfectly natural to me.\""
    s "\"Por favor, no te culpes por eso. Estoy segura de que lo entenderá, y tu reacción me parece perfectamente natural.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1301
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5262023c:

    # n side smile "Heh, I'll try to keep that in mind. Thanks for listening to me whine, Sayori." with dissolve
    n side smile "Je, intentaré tener eso en mente. Gracias por escuchar mis lloriqueos, Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1302
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b0afa617:

    # s "\"I would hardly call it whining, but you're welcome.\""
    s "\"Yo no los llamaría lloriqueos, pero de nada.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1303
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_21132f25:

    # n "So anyway, how are you doing?"
    n "En fin, ¿cómo te va?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1304
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e98005f3:

    # s "\"Very well, actually. I might have some good news for you?\""
    s "\"Muy bien, de hecho. Puede que te tenga buenas noticias.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1305
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7b55ec4a:

    # n front surprised "Oh?" with dissolve
    n front surprised "¿Oh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1306
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5d964862:

    # s "\"It seems Kyou is about to quit the school to mitigate the damage he caused for himself by hurting you.\""
    s "\"Parece que Kyou abandonará la escuela para mitigar el daño que se causó a sí mismo por lastimarte.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1308
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8135ccb8:

    # n side frown "Wait, you talked to him?" with dissolve
    n side frown "Espera, ¿hablaste con él?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1309
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3b6bd2d9:

    # s "\"Oh no. Not directly anyway. I respect your warning about him. Hiroko has effectively become his mouthpiece though, it seems.\""
    s "\"Oh, no. Al menos no directamente. Respeto tu advertencia respecto a él. Pero perece que Hiroko se ha convertido en su portavoz.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1311
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d75306a5:

    # n front sigh "Yeah..." with dissolve
    n front sigh "Seh…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1312
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_078c0799:

    # s "\"Of all the people to take his side...\""
    s "\"De todas las personas que pudieron ponerse de su lado…\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1313
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fc943750:

    # n concerned "It's not her fault." with dissolve
    n concerned "No es su culpa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1314
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1a292ff6:

    # s "\"No? I am not sure why not?\""
    s "\"¿No? No estoy segura de eso. ¿Por qué no?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1315
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_228e3b68:

    # n "Well..."
    n "Pues…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1316
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_63fdf2d9:

    # n side sad_closed "*sigh* No, nevermind. I guess I'm still trying to get my head around her betrayal." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "*suspiro* No, olvídalo. Supongo que sigo intentando aceptar la traición." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1317
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2c821676:

    # s "\"Yes. I have a hard time understanding why people do what they do sometimes.\""
    s "\"Sí. A mí a veces me es difícil comprender por qué la gente hace lo que hace.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1318
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90369dcf_1:

    # n "Yeah..."
    n "Seh…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1319
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b9218f4e:

    # s "\"... Nozomi?\""
    s "\"¿Nozomi?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1320
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_30f09a2f:

    # n sad_side "Hm?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1321
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4b3ab850:

    # s "\"Are you in your room right now?\""
    s "\"¿Estás en tu habitación en este momento?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1323
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3f035f90:

    # n front surprised "Yeah, why?" with dissolve
    n front surprised "Sí, ¿por qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1324
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a77ee71:

    # s "\"Could you go up to the window?\""
    s "\"¿Podrías acercarte a la ventana?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1325
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_707f7ba7:

    # n "Uh, again, why?"
    n "Eh, de nuevo, ¿por qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1326
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_879d872c:

    # s "\"I thought I could teach you a relaxation technique. I sometimes use it to help manage my own stress.\""
    s "\"Pensaba enseñarte una técnica de relajación. A veces la uso para lidiar con mi propio estrés.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1327
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ee51a3a8:

    # s "\"At a time like this I think you may find it useful. Are you game?\""
    s "\"Creo que te puede ser útil en un momento como este. ¿Te parece bien?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1328
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b65671da:

    # n "Okay... Sure, I guess."
    n "De acuerdo… Claro, supongo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1337
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8722be5f:

    # n frown casual "Alright, I'm looking out the window. What now?" with dissolve
    n frown casual "Muy bien, estoy mirando por la ventana. ¿Ahora qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1344
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_72ad647f:

    # s "\"Just... I want you to take a deep breath and look at what is out there.\""
    s "\"Solo… Quiero que respires hondo y mires lo que hay afuera.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1345
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fcf3d74a:

    # s "\"Perhaps the neighbor's houses across the street. Or that sakura tree over by the park. It doesn't matter, just anything you find appealing right now.\""
    s "\"Quizá las casas de los vecinos que hay por la calle. O el árbol sakura que está en el parque. No importa. Lo que sea que encuentres atractivo. \""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1347
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0a431bcf:

    # n sigh "Honestly I'd just like to go outside again soon. It's only been a couple days and I'm already feeling myself go stir crazy being cooped up in here." with dissolve
    n sigh "Honestamente me gustaría salir pronto. Solo han pasado un par de días y ya siento que me estoy volviendo loca aquí encerrada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1348
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c37d62ed:

    # s "\"I sympathize. So did you find something?\""
    s "\"Simpatizo. Entonces, ¿encontraste algo?\" "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1350
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b90552c6:

    # n smile "The sakura tree, yes." with dissolve
    n smile "El árbol sakura, sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1370
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c8fac0b1:

    # s "\"I thought you might. I often enjoy staring at the cherry blossoms, myself. I find them very relaxing.\""
    s "\"Eso creí. Yo también disfruto de ver las flores del cerezo. Me parecen muy relajantes.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1358
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7259bd2c:

    # n "Mm, yes. I never noticed how well they catch the light before."
    n "Mm, sí. Nunca había notado lo bien que atrapan la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1359
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e9360688:

    # s "\"Right. And recall their scent. How it reminds us of spring time. A happier time.\""
    s "\"Cierto. Y recuerda su olor. Cómo te recuerda a la primavera. A tiempos más felices.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1360
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_64cdae32:

    # n "Gosh, yes."
    n "Dios, sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1363
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f2f5893d:

    # n surprised "Hey, isn't that...{w=0.4}{nw}" with dissolve
    n surprised "Oye, ¿qué esa no es…{w=0.4}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1387
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_819657f8:

    # s "\"Inhale deeply and imagine that scent filling your nostrils.\"" with dissolve
    s "\"Inhala profundo e imagina ese aroma llenando tus fosas nasales.\"" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1392
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_15dd3e23:

    # n "Mmm..."
    n "Mmm…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1368
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_58cc41dc:

    # s "\"Do you smell them, Nozomi?\""
    s "\"¿Las hueles, Nozomi?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1371
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_957e0bc9:

    # n smile "I do." with dissolve
    n smile "Sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1372
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b1fc0488:

    # s "\"Wonderful. Feeling more and more relaxed with each time you inhale deeply, and feeling all your pent-up tension drain away with each exhale.\""
    s "\"Maravilloso. Siéntete más y más relajada cada vez que inhalas profundo, y siente toda tu tensión contenida drenarse con cada exhalación.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1373
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_242d57c3:

    # s "\"Breathing in calm.\""
    s "\"Inhala calma.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1375
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dfdfe76a:

    # s "\"Breathing out stress.\""
    s "\"Exhala el estrés.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1378
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_069ec87d:

    # s "\"That feels so much better, does it not?\""
    s "\"Se siente mucho mejor, ¿no?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1379
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_adc20748:

    # n "Yeah... So much better."
    n "Sí… Mucho mejor."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1380
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_89656dac:

    # s "\"So much better. Each and every breath you take putting you in a deeper state of relaxation.\""
    s "\"Muchísimo mejor. Cada vez que respiras entras a un estado más profundo de relajación.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1382
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_04c68a2c:

    # s "\"But even as you relax so very deeply, you will find you can always keep your phone held to your ear, and are always able to stare ahead at the sakura tree.\""
    s "\"Pero por más profundamente relajada que estés, siempre podrás sostener tu teléfono en tu oreja, y siempre serás capaz mirar el árbol sakura.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1383
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ba41ce0b:

    # s "\"Breathing in...\""
    s "\"Inhala…\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1384
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_08377726:

    # s "\"Holding...\""
    s "\"Sostenlo…\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1390
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f2d32df4:

    # s "\"Breathing out, even more relaxed. Even more deep.\"" with dissolve
    s "\"Exhala, todavía más relajada. Todavía más profundo.\"" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1391
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2ec89ff1:

    # s "\"Can you still hear me, Nozomi?\""
    s "\"¿Aún puedes oírme, Nozomi?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1392
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_53c1cef0:

    # n "Yes."
    n "Sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1393
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_75e1d46b:

    # s "\"Very good. Breathe in...\""
    s "\"Muy bien. Inhala…\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1394
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b5283739:

    # s "\"Breathe out... Dropping deeper.\""
    s "\"Exhala… Cayendo más profundo.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1395
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fd6475a8:

    # s "\"Deeper. Keeping your phone held close to your ear at all times as you...\""
    s "\"Más profundo. Mantén tu teléfono muy cerca de tu oreja en todo momento y…\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1396
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e3535090:

    # s "\"Sleep.\""
    s "\"Duerme.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1403
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fa8eeae6:

    # ks casual smile "Not that I was there when it happened, but from that retelling, it sounds like you recalled it perfectly."
    ks casual smile "Yo no estuve ahí cuando pasó, pero con esa narración, me suena a que lo recuerdas a la perfección."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1434
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c3b0815a:

    # n "Sayori... n-no..." with dissolve
    n "Sayori… n-no…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1405
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_508277a1:

    # ks "Yes, Sayori. After putting you to sleep, she went through some mental conditioning with you that set you up for our meeting a little while ago."
    ks "Sí, Sayori. Luego de ponerte a dormir, te dio un poco de acondicionamiento mental, el cual te dejó lista para nuestra reunión de hace un rato."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1406
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c477967d:

    # ks "You did everything you were supposed to."
    ks "Hiciste todo lo que se suponía que hicieras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1407
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fa171186:

    # ks "But if you're wondering why I didn't just have you present yourself to me here instead of going through with that café thing, well..."
    ks "Pero si te preguntas por qué no simplemente te hice presentarte ante mí aquí en vez de hacer todo eso del café, pues…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1408
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b5877444:

    # ks "We weren't sure how effective the penlight would be from across the street and through a window."
    ks "No estábamos seguros de qué tan efectiva sería la linterna del otro lado de una calle y a través de una ventana."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1409
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c9ef5fd7:

    # ks "And I know how you feel about me right now, rightly or wrongly. So... we felt with the weaker light you might have resisted such a direct suggestion as that."
    ks "Y sé cómo te sientes respecto a mí ahora, para bien o para mal. Así que… sentimos que con una luz más débil podrías haberte resistido a una sugestión tan directa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1410
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_05e51524:

    # ks "We had to transition you slowly, you understand. Just to be sure."
    ks "Teníamos que hacer la transición lentamente contigo, ya sabes. Solo para estar seguros."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1411
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d05556ac:

    # n sleepy "Sayori... Oh my god, how could you?" with dissolve
    n sleepy "Sayori… Oh, por Dios, ¿cómo pudiste?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1444
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c9059fc6:

    # ss casual concerned_right "It had to be done, Nozomi. Kyou knows what is best for us." with dissolve
    ss casual concerned_right "Tenía que hacerse, Nozomi. Kyou sabe lo que es mejor para nosotras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1416
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_803c5b1a:

    # n "I told you to stay away from him. I told you."
    n "Te dije que te alejaras de él. Te lo dije."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1446
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f3c8151a:

    # ss "I did my best. It just turned out Kyou is better than me."
    ss "Hice lo mejor que pude. Pero resulta que Kyou es mejor que yo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1447
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b9335219:

    # ss laugh_right blush "He is better than all of us~" with dissolve
    ss laugh_right blush "Es mejor que todos nosotros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1449
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5afc6681:

    # hs casual happy blush "Yeah! Gotta hand it to him, we didn't stand a chance against Kyou~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    hs casual happy blush "¡Sí! Es un genio, no tuvimos oportunidad contra Kyou. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1450
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3106367e:

    # n "Hiroko. That was you outside my house, wasn't it?"
    n "Hiroko. Tú eras la que estaba afuera de mí casa, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1451
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3ec84b50:

    # hs laugh "Totes! I thought you were gonna freak out for sure when it looked like you saw me, but you just loved staring at that sakura tree too much~"
    hs laugh "¡Pero claro! Creí que te paniquearías cuando parecía que me viste, pero te encantaba demasiado mirar el árbol sakura."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1452
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_76dde87f:

    # hs "Made it super easy to keep Kyou's penlight in your eyes."
    hs "Fue superfácil mantener la linterna de Kyou en tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1428
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_09a92fc3:

    # ks "Which reminds me; I'm gonna need that back again, Hiroko."
    ks "Lo cual me recuerda; voy a necesitarla de vuelta, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1454
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f8bbd476:

    # hs happy_closed "Eheheh, 'kay 'kay. Here ya go."
    hs happy_closed "Jejeje, ta’ bien, ta’ bien. Ten."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1430
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_28074306:

    # "I can't resist allowing myself a wry grin as I take the penlight back from Hiroko and pocket it safely."
    "No puedo resistir dejar escapara una sonrisa, tomando la linterna de las manos de Hiroko y volviéndola a poner a salvo en mi bolsillo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1431
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c42d68a2:

    # ks smirk "I don't intend to make a habit of praising these two, Nozomi, but I have to admit; I never would've gotten you without the hard work and dedication of your friends."
    ks smirk "No quiero hacerme al hábito de elogiar a estas dos, Nozomi, pero he de admitir que nunca te habría atrapado sin el arduo trabajo y la dedicación de tus amigas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1432
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9332974e:

    # ks "They REALLY came through for me today."
    ks "DE VERDAD me hicieron un gran favor hoy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1458
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_97e968e9:

    # ss shocked "Hiroko, he... he praised us!"
    ss shocked "Hiroko, nos… ¡nos elogió!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1459
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb61918f:

    # hs cry_happy "He... Holy shit, he really did!"
    hs cry_happy "No… Ah, mierda, ¡sí lo hizo!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1460
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_49fa00db:

    # hs cry_joy "AAAAAAAAAAAA I'M SO HAPPY I COULD DIIIIEEEE!!" with shake
    hs cry_joy "¡¡AAAAAAAAAAAAH, ESTOY TAN FELIZ QUE PODRÍA MORIIIIIIIIR!!" with shake

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1461
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4e5db94e:

    # ss laugh_right "*squeal* Thank you so much, Kyou! I LIVE for your approval!"
    ss laugh_right "*chillido* ¡Muchísimas gracias, Kyou! ¡Yo VIVO por tu aprobación!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1463
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_982d4346:

    # n "... Why are you doing this, Kyou?" with dissolve
    n "… ¿Por qué estás haciendo esto, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1464
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_011e2f41:

    # ks neutral "Doing what?"
    ks neutral "¿Haciendo qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1441
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ac03709f:

    # n "Torturing me. Why am I not like they are yet?"
    n "Torturarme. ¿Por qué aún no soy como ellas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1446
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_688b6082:

    # ks frown "Because... I'm still conflicted about you, Nozomi."
    ks frown "Porque… Sigo en conflicto contigo, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1447
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_809a6f5c:

    # n "Conflicted?"
    n "¿En conflicto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1479
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_093bbe30:

    # ks neutral "I studied hypnosis for you. I watched you dropping deep for that hypnotist during the culture festival last year and I was inspired."
    ks neutral "Estudié hipnosis para ti. Te vi caer profundo para ese hipnotista durante el festival cultural y me sentí inspirado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1453
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bba3e2af:

    # ks "But this last week has made me question how I truly feel about you. And how I feel about myself."
    ks "Pero está semana me ha hecho cuestionarme qué es lo que verdaderamente siento por ti. Y cómo me siento conmigo mismo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1455
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_91e81676:

    # ks frown "After I spent this week brainwashing your friends into becoming my devoted groupies I had to re-examine my feelings for you."
    ks frown "Luego de pasar esta semana lavándoles el cerebro a tus amigas para convertirlas en mis fanáticas devotas, tuve que reexaminar mis sentimientos por ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1456
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_21264672:

    # ks "And what I realized is..."
    ks "Y me di cuenta de que…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1461
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4dbf3b24:

    # ks concerned "I didn't love you, Nozomi. For the longest time I really thought I did."
    ks concerned "No te amaba, Nozomi. Por mucho tiempo creí que te amaba."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1472
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_117ca29b:

    # ks "But as it turns out, I just didn't like the idea that something I wanted was unattainable."
    ks "Pero resulta que simplemente no me gustaba la idea de que algo que quería fuera inalcanzable."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1463
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b6b56fa5:

    # ks "I can have any girl I want now, if I put my mind to it. I still think you're pretty, and smart, and graceful, don't get me wrong."
    ks "Puedo tener a la chica que quiera ahora, ya que lo pienso. Aún creo que eres bonita, e inteligente, y llena de gracia, no me malentiendas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1464
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f08cecae:

    # ks "But when it comes down to it, you're just not that special anymore."
    ks "Pero al final del día, ya no eres tan especial."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1465
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3fdc7334:

    # "I let out a sigh, pausing for a moment before I continue."
    "Suelto un suspiro, haciendo una pausa antes de continuar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1466
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bfee0a0a:

    # ks neutral "Still, you're the only one that knows my secret who is in a position to do anything about it."
    ks neutral "Aunque eres la única que sabe mi secreto y que está en posición de hacer algo al respecto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1467
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_09304176:

    # ks "Not to mention you were going to cause trouble for me by pulling out of school and making me a scapegoat."
    ks "Sin mencionar que ibas a causarme problemas dejando la escuela y haciéndome un chivo expiatorio."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1468
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fd7c0f05:

    # ks "So I think you understand that I can't just let you be, can I?"
    ks "Por lo que creo que entiendes que no puedo solo dejarte ir, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1469
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8ef42928:

    # n "You could still undo this."
    n "Aún puedes deshacer esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1470
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_82f88b1f:

    # ks annoyed "What?"
    ks annoyed "¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1471
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ce264f72:

    # n "All of this. If your power over our minds is really so great you could erase all our memories, destroy the penlight and things can maybe go back to normal."
    n "Todo esto. Si tu poder sobre nuestras mentes de verdad es tan grande, podrías borrar nuestras memorias, destruir la linterna y tal vez todo pueda volver a la normalidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1472
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d98a57c4:

    # "That... I can't help but laugh at something so fucking ridiculous. Is she serious?"
    "Eso… No puedo evitar reírme de esa puta ridiculez. ¿Habla en serio?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1473
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2bd3b970:

    # ks "Why the hell would I EVER do that, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Por qué DEMONIOS haría eso, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1653
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_727f52f4:

    # n "Because maybe, deep down, there is still a conscience buried underneath all that entitlement you're carrying." with dissolve
    n "Porque tal vez, en el fondo, sigue habiendo algo de conciencia enterrada debajo de toda esa autojustificación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1475
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_98f32c6a:

    # n "You know what you're doing is evil. You... you're killing us from the inside, you must realize that."
    n "Sabes que lo que haces es malvado. Nos… nos estás matando por dentro, debes darte cuenta de eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1476
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a514021a:

    # n "And you're going to have to live with all of this. No one might be using a magic light to change you, but they won't have to."
    n "Y tendrás que vivir con todo esto. No estarán usando una luz mágica para cambiarte, pero nadie tendrá que hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1477
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_07579fa2:

    # n "You're changing yourself. And when this is all over, I don't think you'll like what you've become."
    n "Tú mismo te estás cambiando. Y cuando todo esto termine, no creo que te guste en lo que te habrás convertido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1478
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ecbc2b31:

    # "I scoff at her. It sounds like the vacuous moralizing of someone who knows she's doomed."
    "Me mofo de ella. Suena a una moralización vacía de alguien que sabe que está perdida."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1479
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e3dadca0:

    # "... I used to think the world of this woman, though. And I guess I owe it to her a little to consider what she said."
    "… Aunque solía creer que mi mundo entero era esta mujer. Y supongo que le debo un poco, así que bien podría considerar lo que dijo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1480
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9af54bc0:

    # n "So what will you do?"
    n "Y ¿qué harás?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1485
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2f3b6d6c:

    # ks frown "It's none of your concern, Nozomi. And as a matter of fact, you need to sleep now."
    ks frown "Eso no te incumbe, Nozomi. De hecho, ahora tienes que dormir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1487
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_03942dd7:

    # n sleep "..." with dissolve
    n sleep "…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1488
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c896ec19:

    # "She really thought I'd just throw all this away? That pisses me off."
    "¿De verdad pensó que echaría todo esto a la basura? Eso me enfurece."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1489
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_52e3a175:

    # ks "That's it, good girl. Dropping nice and deep for me. Loving how good it feels to drop deeper. Deeper."
    ks "Eso es, buena chica. Cae muy profundo para mí. Adorando lo bien que se siente caer más profundo. Más profundo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1490
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0ee6b48e:

    # ks "Finding it so easy to drop. So easy to listen to my voice and accept everything I tell you as your absolute, undeniable truth."
    ks "Te es tan fácil caer. Tan fácil escuchar mi voz y aceptar todo lo que te diga como la absoluta e innegable verdad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1492
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6bf82702:

    # ks "Because you are such a good listener, Nozomi. A very good and obedient and attentive listener."
    ks "Porque eres muy buena escuchando, Nozomi. Muy buena obedeciendo y escuchando atentamente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1493
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c77e5603:

    # ks "I'm right about all of it, aren't I?"
    ks "¿No es cierto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1494
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3b87dc83:

    # n sleeptalk "Right..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Cierto…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1496
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f8a60410:

    # "Now then, time to decide Nozomi's fate." with dissolve
    "Y ahora, es momento de decidir el destino de Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1751
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2e32d9ea:

    # "I meant what I said to her before, that she's not special." with dissolve
    "Lo que dije hace un momento era verdad; ella no es especial." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1502
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_28b09ea6:

    # "And when it comes down to it, she neglected and belittled me along with all the other girls in my class."
    "Y ya que estamos en eso, me hizo a un lado y me menospreció tanto como el resto de las chicas de mi clase."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1503
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7de185aa:

    # "My longing for her blinded me to that, but I can't deny that it's true."
    "Mi anhelo por ella me segó a eso, pero no puedo negar que es cierto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1504
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_77f62bdf:

    # "So she can be just another groupie for all I care."
    "Así que bien podría ser solo otra fanática, para lo que me importa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1505
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_18b8a8f0:

    # ks "And because you are such a good listener, you find it so very easy to accept that you adore everything about me."
    ks "Y ya que eres tan buena escuchando, te será muy fácil aceptar que adoras todo en mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1506
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cafc5031:

    # ks "As easy as breathing to accept that you cannot harbor a single negative thought about me."
    ks "Es tan fácil como respirar aceptar que no puedes concebir un solo pensamiento negativo sobre mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1507
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0e6ae655:

    # ks "In fact, whenever a negative thought about me pops into your head, you will immediately and automatically turn that negativity all the way around."
    ks "De hecho, cada vez que un pensamiento negativo sobre mí aparezca en tu cabeza, inmediata y automáticamente le darás una vuelta completa a esa negatividad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1508
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5dd20318:

    # ks "And more than that, you will multiply it by a factor of ten. That thought you had only makes you revere me ten times more."
    ks "Y, lo que es más, la multiplicarás por diez. Ese pensamiento que tuviste únicamente te hace venerarme diez veces más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1509
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_af01bc4d:

    # ks "Your number one concern in your life, always, is to win my approval and respect. Nothing else matters even as remotely as much to you."
    ks "Tu preocupación número uno en la vida, siempre, es ganarte mi aprobación y respeto. Nada más importa ni remotamente tanto para ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1510
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1837d900:

    # ks "You accept these words as your absolute truth, Nozomi. Whether fully awake or in a deep trance as you are now..."
    ks "Aceptas estas palabras como la absoluta verdad, Nozomi. Ya sea despierta o en un profundo trance como ahora…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1511
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cb0111a0:

    # ks "... This is who you are. Understand?"
    ks "… Esto es quien eres. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1512
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_140ef6f5:

    # n sleeptalk "I understand." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Comprendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1514
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c1e499b7:

    # ks "I thought you would, Nozomi. You are, after all, an extremely good and attentive listener." with dissolve
    ks "Eso pensé, Nozomi. Eres, después de todo, extremadamente buena escuchando atentamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1538
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2211bcd8:

    # ks "In a few moments it will be time to wake you up completely, embracing everything that you were told."
    ks "En unos momentos será hora de que despiertes por completo, abrazando todo lo que te he dicho."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1539
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_69c8a954:

    # ks "Once you do, you will find that can speak and move with complete freedom once again."
    ks "Y cuando lo hagas, notarás que, una vez más, puedes hablar y moverte con completa libertad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1540
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c1eb1bc3:

    # ks "Waking up on a count of five, Nozomi."
    ks "Despierta a la cuenta de cinco, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1541
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_261e1d24:

    # ks "One, two... Taking a deep breath, feeling energy slowly return to you."
    ks "Uno, dos… Respira profundo, siente la energía volver a ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1542
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_50eed1f9:

    # ks "Three, four... Beginning to blink. Feeling your head become clearer; thoughts returning."
    ks "Tres, cuatro… Comienzas a parpadear. Siente cómo tu cabeza se aclara; tus pensamientos regresan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1544
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_956ce66c:

    # ks "And five... wide awake, Nozomi."
    ks "Y cinco… despierta, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1545
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_afadbc11:

    # n sleepy "Mmn..." with dissolve
    n sleepy "Mmn…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1547
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3109e72f:

    # "I smirk as her eyelids flutter open, giving her a moment to register my face."
    "Le sonrío mientras sus ojos se abren, dándole un momento para reconocer mi rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1549
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3ed566b6:

    # "I can almost see her brain frantically working behind her eyes as they dart to and fro." with dissolve
    "Casi puedo ver su cerebro trabajando frenéticamente detrás de sus ojos que se mueven de lado a lado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1731
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ab543fe1:

    # "Her many apparent resentments over me fervently being processed in her mind as reasons to deepen her rapidly-growing feelings of reverence." with dissolve
    "Sus numerosos resentimientos hacia mí siendo fervientemente procesados en su mente como razones para profundizar sus crecientes sentimientos de veneración." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1552
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c1ed9367:

    # n blush "K... K-Kyou, ohmygosh, hi!" with dissolve
    n blush "K… K-Kyou, ohpordios, ¡hola!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1553
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_96b31a0c:

    # ks smirk "Hey again, Nozomi. Got anything to say to me?"
    ks smirk "Hola de nuevo, Nozomi. ¿Tienes algo qué decirme?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1736
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5ab3a95a:

    # n shocked "Y-y-you're..."
    n shocked "E-e-estás…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1555
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b07ca9b:

    # n happy "I'm... I'm kind of a HUGE fan of yours!" with dissolve
    n happy "Soy… ¡soy una ENORME admiradora tuya!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1751
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90f83133:

    # ks casual smirk "I knew you'd come around, Nozomi. But I can't say I feel the same way about you right now."
    ks casual smirk "Sabía que entrarías en razón, Nozomi. Pero no puedo decir que siento lo mismo por ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1557
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b4cc3087:

    # n side sad "You... you don't?" with dissolve
    n side sad "¿N-… no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1558
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_df8e3294:

    # ks frown "You've made a lot of trouble for me, running your mouth off about me making you uncomfortable."
    ks frown "Me has causado muchos problemas, dejando tu lengua suelta y diciéndoles a todos que te puse incómoda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1559
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5757ad67:

    # ks "Like, what the fuck is your problem?"
    ks "O sea, ¿cuál es tu puto problema?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1560
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0162fc0c:

    # n front surprised "Ah! I... I'm sorry!" with dissolve
    n front surprised "¡Ah! ¡Lo… lo siento!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1561
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_daf1beed:

    # "Maybe I've gotten a little used to how I've treated the others this week, talking to Nozomi like this..."
    "Tel vez me haya acostumbrado un poco a cómo he tratado a las otras esta semana, al hablarle a Nozomi así…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1562
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_78128c6e:

    # "But I can't help myself. After they've all belittled me for so long, that I now have the power to give some back?"
    "Pero no puedo evitarlo. Después de menospreciarme por tanto tiempo, ahora que tengo el poder de devolvérselo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1563
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6253198e:

    # "It's intoxicating..."
    "Es adictivo…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1564
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_12e496da:

    # ks angry "What am I supposed to do with an apology? Are you an imbecile?"
    ks angry "¿Qué se supone que haga con una disculpa? ¿Qué eres imbécil?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1565
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1059e939:

    # n concerned "I-I... y-you're right, that was imbecilic of me." with dissolve
    n concerned "Y-yo… t-tienes razón, eso fue imbécil de mi parte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1566
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ebc03dfa:

    # "Her eyes dart a little more as her mind seems to race in her head before she looks to me with determination."
    "Sus ojos revolotean un poco más y su mente parece acelerarse en su cabeza, luego me mira con determinación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1652
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0bcc421a:

    # n front2 frown casual "I'll fix it! I'll say what happened during our cleaning time together was a BIG misunderstanding and go back to school!" with dissolve
    n front2 frown casual "¡Lo arrelaré! ¡Diré que lo que pasó cuando estábamos limpiando juntos fue un GRAN malentendido y regresaré a la escuela!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1568
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8068ed36:

    # ks frown "Not good enough."
    ks frown "No es suficiente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1569
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_461cecb2:

    # n surprised "O-okay... I'll also apologize to you in front of everyone in class!" with dissolve
    n surprised "M-muy bien… ¡También me disculparé contigo en frente de toda la clase!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1570
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_824e8242:

    # n "I'll make sure everyone in school knows this was all my fault, you're completely blameless and I'm the only one causing trouble for everyone!"
    n "¡Me aseguraré de que todos en la escuela sepan que todo fue todo mi error, que estás completamente libre de culpa y que soy la única que les causa problemas a todos!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1571
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_de35770c:

    # ks "What else?"
    ks "¿Qué más?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1572
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_786f7045:

    # n shocked "And... er, and... I-I'll post about it on all my social media! E-e-everyone's going to know you're a really great guy, and, and I'm..." with dissolve
    n shocked "Y… em, y… ¡y lo publicaré en todas mis redes sociales! T-t-todo el mundo sabrá que eres un chico grandioso, y… y que yo soy…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1573
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_34def913:

    # n "I'm just a big hysterical idiot!"
    n "¡Que yo soy una idiota histérica!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1574
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3beb29cd:

    # ks "And?"
    ks "¿Y?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1575
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cba7b5af:

    # n concerned "A-and, er... uhhh..." with dissolve
    n concerned "Y-y, em... eeeh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1576
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_99f9aeb7:

    # ks "I'm waiting, Nozomi. What else?"
    ks "Estoy esperando, Nozomi. ¿Qué más?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1581
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_38462184:

    # "As she struggles to think of more ways to appease me, tears well in her eyes in frustration as she throws herself to the floor in front of me." with dissolve
    "Mientras se esfuerza por pensar en más maneras de apaciguarme, lágrimas brotan se sus ojos con frustración, y se arroja al suelo ante mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1584
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0eaa4874:

    # n "I-I-I don't know what else, Kyou!"
    n "¡N-n-no sé qué más, Kyou!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1585
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b3279ee6:

    # n "Tell me! Tell me what to do to make things right! I beg of you!"
    n "¡Dime! ¡Dime qué más hacer para enmendar las cosas! ¡Te lo ruego!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1588
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_06f826a7:

    # n "I'll... I-I'll do anything you wahahahaaannnt!"
    n "Haré… ¡haré todo lo que quieheheheeeraaas!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1587
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9a4539f7:

    # n "Just... p-please don't h-hate me, Kyou... I can't st... I can't stand it! I can't!"
    n "Pero… p-por favor, no me o-odies, Kyou… No puedo… ¡No puedo soportar eso! ¡No puedo!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1588
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a4db83aa:

    # "There. That's the response I wanted from my defeated opponent."
    "Ahí está. Esa es la respuesta que quería de mi oponente derrotada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1589
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a0c8b8c7:

    # "And this rush of power. To see her so utterly broken, grovelling at my feet for my forgiveness, when before she would barely even register my presence."
    "Y esta sensación de poder. Verla completamente rota, arrastrándose a mis pies en pos de mi perdón, cuando antes apenas se habría dado cuenta de mi presencia."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1590
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6ce581e3:

    # "Holy shit, it feels incredible."
    "Mierda, se siente increíble."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1593
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_52de2f89:

    # ks casual smirk "It's a start. Commit to everything you said, everything, and I MIGHT get around to forgiving you. Understand?"
    ks casual smirk "Es un comienzo. Comprométete a lo que dijiste, todo, y PUEDE que considere perdonarte. ¿Entendido?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1593
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c9a5a76a:

    # "She looks up at me from the floor; hope registering in her eyes through her glistening tears." with dissolve
    "Me mira desde el suelo; la esperanza se vislumbra en sus ojos a través de sus relucientes lágrimas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1594
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d4b04ce3:

    # n "Y-yes, Kyou. *sniffle* I-I won't disappoint you again, I swear!"
    n "S-sí, Kyou. *snif* ¡No volveré a decepcionarte, lo juro!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1597
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c727ce5e:

    # "Satisfied, I gesture for Nozomi to get up off the floor. She shakily gets back on her feet and starts to wipe her eyes behind her glasses."
    "Satisfecho, le indico con un gesto a Nozomi que se levante del suelo. Se pone de nuevo de pie temblando y empieza a frotar sus ojos por detrás de sus gafas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1630
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c062561b:

    # "I look around the room. All three women look back to me, giving me their complete and undivided attention." with dissolve
    "Observo la habitación. Las tres chicas me miran a mí, dándome su total e indivisa atención." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1635
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d3c640f8:

    # "Time I made a speech."
    "Hora de dar un discurso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1642
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a154c151:

    # ks casual smile "This was the week all our lives turned around. And we're not looking back."
    ks casual smile "Esta fue la semana en la que todas nuestras vidas cambiaron de rumbo. Y no miraremos atrás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1638
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_79b26f5e:

    # ks "Until now you all thought I was a loser creep, if you ever thought of me at all."
    ks "Hasta ahora, todas pensaban que era un perdedor y un bicho raro, eso si es que siquiera pensaban en mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1642
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d786cfe2:

    # "I leave them a moment to chew on that, letting their real feelings of shame seep out of their faces." with dissolve
    "Les doy un momento para masticar eso, dejando que sus sentimientos de vergüenza escapen por sus rostros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1643
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_87524209:

    # ks frown "Yeah, let that sink in. You blanked me, shouted at me, called me a creep, and spread all sorts of nasty gossip about me, I'm sure."
    ks frown "Sí, reflexiónenlo. Me rechazaron, me gritaron, me llamaron bicho raro, y esparcieron toda clase de rumores sucios sobre mí. Estoy seguro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1647
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_455c57da:

    # ks "For two and a half years, you girls made me an outcast and you didn't give a shit how much you hurt me." with dissolve
    ks "Por dos años y medio, ustedes, chicas, me hicieron un marginado y no les importó una mierda lo mucho que me hirieron." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1648
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_912b60f0:

    # ks "So none of you can deny that you all have a lot of atoning to do."
    ks "Así que ninguna de ustedes puede negar que tienen mucho que enmendar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1649
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1c75b93a:

    # "I let out a sigh as I look over their crestfallen faces."
    "Dejo salir un suspiro y miro esos rostros caídos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1650
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e8eee66d:

    # ks smile "But I can be forgiving. If none of you ignore or otherwise hurt me again, and Nozomi does everything she promised..."
    ks smile "Pero puedo ser indulgente. Si ninguna de ustedes vuelve a ignorarme o a hacerme daño, y Nozomi hace todo lo que prometió…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1651
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e934fa5f:

    # ks ".... Then I'll allow you three to worship me for the rest of your lives."
    ks "… Entonces les permitiré a las tres adorarme por el resto de sus vidas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1671
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11357c52:

    # "I watch with satisfied glee as all their faces almost immediately light up amidst a cacophony of excited squealing and giggling." with dissolve
    "Miro con regocijo cómo todos los rostros casi inmediatamente se iluminan y comienza una cacofonía de chirridos y risas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1656
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e19f1ce0:

    # h happy "I'm SO EXCITED! Like, what was I even doing with my life 'till now?" with vpunch
    h happy "¡Estoy TAN EMOCIONADA! O sea, ¿qué estaba haciendo con mi vida hasta ahora?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1657
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c4c0d587:

    # n loving "I think I can speak for all of us when I say how sorry we are for how we treated one of the world's leading lights." with dissolve
    n loving "Creo que puedo hablar por todas nosotras cuando digo cuánto sentimos haber tratado así a uno de los faros del mundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1658
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1d9540b8:

    # n "I can't even describe how thrilled I am to be putting things right!"
    n "¡Ni siquiera puedo describir la emoción que siento por arreglar las cosas!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1659
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7979d31a:

    # s casual laugh "I feel the same. You fill me with a sense of purpose I had not thought possible, Kyou." with dissolve
    s casual laugh "Me siento igual. Me llenas con una sensación de propósito que no creí que fuera posible, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1660
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3aecb636:

    # s "I would worship you until my dying breath, if you will allow it!"
    s "¡Te veneraré hasta mi último aliento, si me lo permites!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1661
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_42607f93:

    # ks smirk "Yeah. It's about time you all came to your senses."
    ks smirk "Sí. Ya era hora de que entraran en razón."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1665
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4b318571:

    # "I nod and check the time as I feel their adoring gazes on me." with dissolve
    "Asiento con la cabeza y reviso la hora, sintiendo sus miradas de adoración sobre mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1666
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1465acbc:

    # "It's getting late. They won't want to, and I sure don't want to, but I need to send them home before they're missed."
    "Se está haciendo tarde. Puede que no quieran, y yo definitivamente no quiero, pero tengo que enviarlas de vuelta a casa antes de que noten su ausencia."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1667
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_66b2295c:

    # ks "Anyway, it's time for you all to leave."
    ks "Como sea, es hora de que todas se vayan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1672
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b261e60c:

    # multi "Aww..." with dissolve
    multi "Auu…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1673
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5c1e66dc:

    # ks "I know. But clear your schedules tomorrow because I'm going to be calling on you again."
    ks "Lo sé. Pero hagan espacio en sus agendas mañana porque volveré a llamarlas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1677
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_42d21ce1:

    # s "I will dream of you until then~" with dissolve
    s "Soñaré contigo hasta entonces." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1678
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_975ec075:

    # h surprised "But tomorrow is..." with dissolve
    h surprised "Pero mañana es…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1679
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_833fd64e:

    # ks "What, Hiroko?"
    ks "¿Qué, Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1680
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2cf9a1b7:

    # h giggle "Eh, fuck it. I don't give a shit about that anymore!" with dissolve
    h giggle "Eh, al carajo. ¡Eso ya me importa una mierda!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1681
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8f78c6a0:

    # n "Bye for now, Kyou! I'll exonerate you on social media as soon as I get home~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}"
    n "¡Adiós por ahora, Kyou! Te exoneraré en redes sociales tan pronto como llegue a casa. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1684
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_21e05713:

    # "I let the three of them kiss me on their way out. I can still hear their girlish squealing about it as they left."
    "Dejo que las tres me besen al salir. Aún puedo oírlas parlotear sobre eso al partir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1687
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11022cfe:

    # "Holding my penlight up as I lounge on my bed, I reminisce back to that day this all began; nearly a year ago at the culture festival."
    "Sosteniendo mi linterna en mi cama, rememoro el día en que todo empezó; hace casi un año en el festival cultural."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1692
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7ff8e669:

    # "I'm barely up and showered before my doorbell rings."
    "Estoy recién levantado y duchado cuando suena el timbre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1700
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a6b9c904:

    # "I had my [hypno6]s show up early, so I had some time to prepare for Sayori's arrival."
    "Hice que mis [hypno6!t!l]s vinieran temprano para así tener tiempo de prepararnos para la llegada de Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1703
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_18dfae5b:

    # "The moment both of them are safely inside they revert to their robot-like states; their expressions falling blank, their arms stiff at their sides." with dissolve
    "En el instante en que se encuentran a salvo aquí dentro, regresan a sus estados robóticos; sus expresiones se quedan en blanco, con sus brazos rígidos a sus costados." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1704
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c4cab28e:

    # "After my session with her last night, Nozomi's behavioural programming should be nearly identical to Hiroko's."
    "Luego de la sesión que tuve con ella anoche, la programación del comportamiento de Nozomi debería ser idéntica a la de Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1705
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7cdc5495:

    # ks casual frown "Hiroko, sit down on the couch, over to your right. Nozomi, sit down on the left."
    ks casual frown "Hiroko, siéntate a la derecha del sofá. Nozomi, siéntate a la izquierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1710
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8e2d41a5:

    # "Both of them wordlessly take their positions on the couch as I continue to speak."
    "Ambas toman sus posiciones sin decir una palabra mientras sigo hablando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1715
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fbe2f493:

    # ks "When Sayori shows up, you are to smile and invite her to sit in the middle with you."
    ks "Cuando Sayori se aparezca, sonreirán y la invitarán a sentarse en medio de ustedes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1716
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cc214b4a:

    # ks "When I hold up my penlight, both of you will hold her by her shoulders and stop her from leaving the couch. Got it?"
    ks "Cuando tenga mi linterna en la mano, ambas la sujetarán de los hombros y evitarán que se levante del sofá. ¿Entendido?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1723
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8012ecba:

    # n "Got it."
    n "Entendido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1724
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c8e739c0:

    # h sad "Sayori won't be hurt, will she?" with dissolve
    h sad "Sayori no saldrá herida, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1718
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ded9bc43:

    # n concerned "Sayori won't be hurt, will she?" with dissolve
    n concerned "Sayori no saldrá herida, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1725
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_34c87f7f:

    # "That response makes me frown a little. I'm not intending to harm her friend, but I thought I'd programmed Hiroko better than that."
    "Esa respuesta me hace fruncir un poco el ceño. No tengo intenciones de dañar a su amiga, pero creí haber programado mejor a Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1720
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_95e7c879:

    # ks "Is that really any of your concern, [hypno6]?"
    ks "¿Es acaso eso de tu incumbencia, [hypno6!t!l]?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1721
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b47050ce:

    # n "Be that as it may, Kyou, Sayori is still my friend."
    n "Lo sea o no, Kyou, Sayori sigue siendo mi amiga."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1728
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bb39fc10:

    # ks "And Nozomi? Do you have an opinion on this?"
    ks "¿Y Nozomi? ¿Tienes alguna opinión al respecto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1723
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c7f050ba:

    # h "No, Kyou. I wasn't programmed to have an opinion."
    h "No, Kyou. No se me programó para tener una opinión."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1730
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ac8e2647:

    # ks "That's what I thought. Power down, Hiroko."
    ks "Eso pensé. Apagar ahora, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1733
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_59494b99:

    # "As I speak the words, I realise both of them drop back into trance. I should probably give them both separate trigger phrases soon." with dissolve
    "En cuanto digo esas palabras, me doy cuenta de que ambas regresan al trance. Tal vez debería darles claves separadas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1734
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_53def419:

    # ks "Hiroko, these instructions are for you, because you are the one with faulty code in your human mode programming."
    ks "Hiroko, estas instrucciones son para ti, porque es tu programación humana la que contiene código defectuoso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1729
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_032332c3:

    # ks "You must always acknowledge that you are a [hypno6]. You will always retain that knowledge in your core memory regardless of what state you're in."
    ks "Debes siempre saber que eres un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]. Siempre retendrás ese conocimiento en tu memoria central, sin importar en qué estado te encuentres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1730
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f6c54c5d:

    # ks "And a [hypno6] has no concerns of her own, besides what her programmer has given her. [hypno3]."
    ks "Y un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] no tiene preocupaciones propias, además de las que su programador le ha dado. [hypno3!]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1731
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_39b739f3:

    # n entranced_talk "[hypno2]." with dissolve
    n entranced_talk "[hypno2!t]." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1733
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9bd577e5:

    # ks "Good. Now let's try this again. Power up." with dissolve
    ks "Bien. Ahora intentemos de nuevo. Encender ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1736
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_59109087:

    # "After giving them a moment to come back to their senses, I ask again." with dissolve
    "Luego de darles un momento para volver en sí, pregunto nuevemante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1743
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6f01e8eb:

    # ks "Now Hiroko, are you worried about what we might do to Sayori?"
    ks "Ahora, Hiroko, ¿te preocupa lo que podamos hacerle a Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1744
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6fefdfeb:

    # h "No, Kyou."
    h "No, Kyou."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1739
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_958b7c0e:

    # ks "And why not?"
    ks "¿Y por qué no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1746
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_18536ef9:

    # h "Because I wasn't programmed to worry about that."
    h "Porque no se me programó para preocuparme por eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1741
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7733d89f:

    # "I nod in satisfaction. Hopefully it'll stick this time."
    "Asiento satisfecho con la cabeza. Espero que esta vez se quede así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1743
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a0cd093d:

    # "Just then the doorbell rings. That has to be Sayori."
    "Y entonces el timbre suena. Tiene que ser Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1744
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5b765766:

    # ks "Good. You know what to do."
    ks "Bien. Ya saben qué hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1748
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_01243186:

    # ks smile "Glad you could make it, Sayori." with longblink
    ks smile "Qué bueno que viniste, Sayori." with longblink

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1749
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f5e3d118:

    # s neutral_right "Yep. Let's get this over with." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Sip. Terminemos con esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1750
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5d171fb9:

    # multi "Come sit with us, Sayori~"
    multi "Ven a sentarte con nosotras, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1753
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2b6be906:

    # "Sayori shoots both of them a look, then gingerly sits down between the [hypno6]s before speaking again."
    "Sayori les arroja a ambas una mirada, para luego sentarse cautelosamente entre l[genero_ao]s [hypno6!t!l] y volver a hablar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1756
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c37dabb0:

    # s concerned "Nozomi? Hiroko? Are you both well?" with dissolve
    s concerned "¿Nozomi? ¿Hiroko? ¿Se encuentran bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1757
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_327cc275:

    # multi "I'm fine."
    multi "Estoy bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1759
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8ab1fc56:

    # "Their synchronized response unsettles Sayori, and I really wish I had time to make them act a little more sociable while in the presence of others. Oh well." with dissolve
    "Su respuesta sincronizada inquieta a Sayori. Ojalá hubiera tenido tiempo de hacerlas actuar un poco más sociables en presencia de otros. Pues ¿ya qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1760
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b080f0d7:

    # s "So... I am still at a complete loss as to what has been happening these last few days."
    s "Bien... Sigo sin estar al tanto de qué es lo que ha estado pasando estos últimos días."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1761
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_64299dcd:

    # s concerned "The two of you have suddenly both regarded me with a level of distance that would have me thinking we are complete strangers." with dissolve
    s concerned "Las dos se han estado dirigiendo a mí con un grado de distanciamiento que me haría pensar que somos completas extrañas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1762
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_918c9f2a:

    # s frown_right "Yet you appear to hang on Kyou's every word. I haven't been able to stop thinking why that is." with dissolve
    s frown_right "No obstante, parecen atender cada palabra de lo que Kyou dice. No he podido dejar de preguntarme el porqué." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1763
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1070ed64:

    # s "I have a theory or two but, well, you did say you would go over this."
    s "Tengo una hipótesis o dos, pero, bueno, ya dijiste que lo explicarías todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1764
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1bbc6095:

    # s "And since neither of my closest friends have been willing to tell me anything, I'll listen to what you have to say."
    s "Y dado que ninguna de mis más cercanas amigas se ha mostrado dispuesta a contarme nada, escucharé lo que tengas que decir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1765
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6905ddbc:

    # "I could end this right now. All I'll have to do is pull the penlight from my pocket and my [hypno6]s will restrain her long enough for me to work my magic."
    "Podría acabar con esto justo ahora. Lo único que tengo que hacer es sacar la linterna de mi bolsillo, y mis [hypno6!t!l] la retendrán por tiempo suficiente para hacer mi magia."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1766
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dbcdcd40:

    # "But maybe it'll be more entertaining to drag this out longer."
    "Pero puede que sea entretenido alargar esto un poco."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1769
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0f1af4a5:

    # ks "Alright, so..."
    ks "Muy bien, pues…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1770
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_44ede826:

    # "I probably should've prepared something if I was going to do this. Guess I'll just wing it."
    "Probablemente debí preparar algo si iba a hacer esto. Supongo que improvisaré."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1771
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cc0236d6:

    # ks "After Nozomi flipped out on me the other day I realized I needed to do something, so I swung by her clubroom after school and asked if we could talk."
    ks "Después del disgusto que Nozomi tuvo conmigo el otro día, me di cuenta de que tenía que hacer algo, así que pasé por su club y le pregunté si podíamos hablar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1772
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_44f7e9fd:

    # ks "And we did. We talked it out for a while, and she agreed she overreacted and wanted to start over with a clean slate."
    ks "Y eso hicimos. Lo discutimos y concluimos que sí estaba exagerando y quiso hacer borrón y cuenta nueva."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1773
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1f8bba11:

    # "Sayori's frown looks like it deepened as she listens to me."
    "El ceño de Sayori parece fruncirse más mientras me escucha."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1774
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fa26a267:

    # s "Did she now..."
    s "¿De verdad?..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1775
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_51919dc8:

    # "With a chuckle I turn to look at Nozomi."
    "Riendo levemente, volteo a ver a Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1776
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ad2f0305:

    # ks "Nozo, back me up on this."
    ks "Nozo, ayúdame con esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1781
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_533ad5df:

    # "With a shrug, I casually pull my penlight out into view..."
    "Encogiéndome de hombros, pongo casualmente mi linterna a la vista…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1791
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_870d3ef1:

    # "And right on cue Sayori suddenly finds herself restrained on the couch by her seated companions." with dissolve
    "Y con esa señal, Sayori súbitamente se encuentra restringida en el sofá por sus acompañantes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1796
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_61b9c025:

    # s panicked "What... G-get off of me!" with dissolve
    s panicked "¿Qué?... ¡S-suéltenme!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1804
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_84ef3060:

    # "Ignoring Sayori's protests, I begin to sweep the light beam over Sayori's shocked eyes, which snap to look my way as they're illuminated in the penlight's glow." with dissolve
    "Haciendo caso omiso a sus protestas, comienzo a deslizar el haz de luz por sus conmocionados ojos, los cuales miran en mi dirección iluminados por el destello de la linterna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1806
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a3fddff:

    # ks neutral "Sayori, listen to me. I'm about to explain everything."
    ks neutral "Sayori, escúchame. Voy a explicarlo todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1808
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c03db3bf:

    # s "Nozomi, Hiroko, please. Come to your senses!"
    s "Nozomi, Hiroko, por favor. ¡Entren en razón!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1810
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5773c215:

    # ks "Relax, Sayori. No one here means you any harm; we just need to make sure you pay attention."
    ks "Relájate, Sayori. Nadie busca hacerte daño; solo debemos asegurarnos de que prestes atención."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1812
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_230634f8:

    # "Sayori grunts and struggles as I continue to pass the light across her eyes."
    "Sayori gruñe y forcejea mientras continúo pasando la luz por sus ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1829
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_da1732aa:

    # "Just like the others when I showed them, she is finding the light irresistible despite her obvious distress."
    "Tal como con las otras cuando se la mostré, la luz le es irresistible a pesar de su evidente desesperación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1814
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_43b47124:

    # ks "And all I'm asking is that you watch as the light passes your eyes. Left to right..."
    ks "Y lo único que te pido es que observes la luz que pasa por tus ojos. De izquierda a derecha…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1816
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_657ef04a:

    # ks "Right to left..."
    ks "De derecha a izquierda…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1818
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0e86488e:

    # ks "All I'm asking, as you find yourself concentrating on this light, is that you let yourself relax. After all, it's perfectly safe to relax under the light."
    ks "Lo único que te pido es que te concentres en esta luz, que te relajes. Después de todo, es perfectamente seguro relajarte ante la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1820
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c8cec20c:

    # s surprised_right "Is this how... with the others..." with dissolve
    s surprised_right "¿Así es como… las otras…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1822
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c37e50fd:

    # ks "It's alright, Sayori. Just relax and let go. There's no need to think."
    ks "Está bien, Sayori. Solo relájate y déjate llevar. No hace falta pensar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1824
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8483492e:

    # ks "Letting your eyelids close, then open again as the light passes right to left..."
    ks "Deja que tus párpados se cierren y se vuelvan a abrir mientras la luz pasa de derecha a izquierda…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1826
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e9adbf46:

    # ks "Left to right..."
    ks "De izquierda a derecha…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1828
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_caedcd41:

    # ks "Feeling your eyelids become heavier with every blink. Harder to keep open, just as your thoughts begin to cease."
    ks "Siente cómo tus párpados se ponen pesados cada vez que pestañeas. Se vuelve más difícil abrirlos y tus pensamientos comienzan a cesar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1831
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_eda5cb8a:

    # ks "Feeling all those thoughts in your head drift away as you relax, deeper and deeper." with dissolve
    ks "Siente cómo todos esos pensamientos se van, y tú te relajas, más y más profundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1833
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11dbac7f:

    # ks "Feeling so nice not to have to think for a while. Feeling so wonderful to let your eyelids droop, becoming sleepy under the light even as you focus on it for me."
    ks "Se siente tan bien no tener que pensar por un rato. Se siente tan maravilloso dejar que tus párpados caigan. Estar bajo esta luz te da tanto sueño, aunque te concentres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1835
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_36b21f67:

    # s sleepy "Kyou... y-you..." with dissolve
    s sleepy "Kyou… t-tú…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1836
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5a2d409a:

    # ks "Emptying your thoughts, Sayori. Letting yourself feel so relaxed as you go deeper and deeper."
    ks "Vacía tus pensamientos, Sayori. Siéntete completamente relajada al caer más y más profundo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1838
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e4de480a:

    # ks "Going so deep. Feeling so good. So empty. So sleepy."
    ks "Muy profundo. Te sientes tan bien, tan relajada que cada vez te de más sueño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1840
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d032b9e8:

    # ks "You're doing so well, Sayori. Let your eyes open a little, just once more as you keep watching the light."
    ks "Lo estás haciendo muy bien, Sayori. Abre tus ojos un poquito, solo una vez más y sigue observando la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1842
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2c46bcb2:

    # ks "That's right. Now sleep."
    ks "Eso es. Ahora duerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1844
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7e14e41d:

    # "I watch with satisfaction as Sayori's head droops slightly while she sinks into her entranced sleep." with dissolve
    "Veo con satisfacción a Sayori dejar caer su cabeza ligeramente, durmiendo en un profundo trance." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1845
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_acf95124:

    # "The [hypno6]s still hold her tightly by the shoulders, even though Sayori's struggles gave out ages ago."
    "L[genero_ao]s [hypno6!t!l] la siguen sosteniendo con fuerza de los hombros, aunque la lucha de Sayori haya cesado hace eras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1846
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_264994df:

    # ks "Going deeper, Sayori. Going so deep, feeling so relaxed, so empty of thought."
    ks "Más profundo, Sayori. Caes tan profundo, te sientes tan relajada que desaparecen todos tus pensamientos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1847
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0e9a7f37:

    # ks "And knowing how good it feels makes you want to go deeper. More relaxed. More empty."
    ks "Y saber lo bien que se siente te hace querer ir más profundo. Estar más relajada. Más vacía."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1848
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_faff163f:

    # ks "But even as you go so deep, Sayori, even as your mind becomes so empty, you can still hear my voice and respond to my words. Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "Pero por más profundo que vayas, Sayori, por más vacía que esté tu mente, siempre podrás oír mi voz y responder a mis palabras. ¿Comprendes, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1849
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_553aaf3e:

    # s sleeptalk "I understand..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Comprendo…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1851
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a35933bc:

    # "After the stress of handling Nozomi's induction, I'm really appreciative that Sayori made this so easy for me." with dissolve
    "Después del estrés que fue manejar la inducción de Nozomi, en verdad aprecio que Sayori me lo haya puesto tan fácil." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1852
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8e854925:

    # "And with the last of Nozomi's clique under my influence I should be able to keep any rumours about us from spreading out of control."
    "Y con el último miembro de la pandilla de Nozomi bajo mi influencia, debería ser capaz de evitar que los rumores sobre nosotros se esparzan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1853
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf232fcc:

    # "All the while having three subjects to play with. I'm looking forward to seeing how far their minds will go to adapt to the realities I'll implant in their heads."
    "Y todo mientras tengo a tres sujetos con los que jugar. Y ansío ver cuán lejos pueden llegar sus mentes para adaptarse a las realidades que implante en sus cabezas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1854
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2893f246:

    # "... But I'm getting ahead of myself. First I need to make sure Sayori joins us proper."
    "... Pero me estoy adelantando. Primero necesito asegurarme de que Sayori se nos una como se debe."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1858
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_16efefdc:

    # "With her friends now robots, I think to instead mold this one's mind in a different direction."
    "Con sus amigas siendo ahora robots, pienso en moldear la mente de esta en una dirección diferente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1862
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cd03fe21:

    # "I mean, I don't want her to feel left out. Not that she'll be \"feeling\" anything by the time she leaves here tonight."
    "Por supuesto, no quiero que se sienta excluida. No es que vaya a \"sentir\" nada para cuando termine con ella esta noche, claro está."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1863
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4d003c6b:

    # ks "And while you listen, Sayori, it's very important that you acknowledge my words are your reality."
    ks "Y mientras escuchas, Sayori, es muy importante que reconozcas mis palabras como tu realidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1864
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2fdefbf2:

    # ks "If I say something is true for you, then it must absolutely be true. Understand?"
    ks "Si digo que algo es verdad para ti, entonces es la verdad absoluta. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1865
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_575268fe:

    # s sleeptalk "I... understand." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Com-… prendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1867
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e79b0000:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. It feels good to acknowledge my words as your reality." with dissolve
    ks "Eso es, Sayori. Se siente tan bien reconocer mis palabras como tu realidad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1868
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e340d577:

    # ks "So when I- {w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks "Por lo que cuando te- {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1871
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e06fd606:

    # "What the?! Someone's at the door. And they're pounding on it instead of using the bell like a normal person."
    "¡¿Pero qué?! Hay alguien en la puerta. Y la están golpeando en lugar de usar el timbre como una persona normal."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1872
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d47a5ae1:

    # "Who the hell could that be?"
    "¿Quién diablos podrá ser?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1873
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b3588fae:

    # "Cold callers? At the weekend?"
    "¿Un vendedor? ¿En fin de semana?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1874
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_217f22fb:

    # "Ugh. I'll just keep my voice down and hope they take the hint. I can't be distracted right now."
    "Aj. Solo voy a bajar la voz y esperaré que entienda la indirecta. Ahora no puedo distraerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1875
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_51d127a9:

    # ks "So Sayori, when I say that- {w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "Por lo que, Sayori, cuando te digo que-{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1877
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d6c5d512:

    # "Oh for fuck's sake. So NOW they've discovered the door bell."
    "Ay, carajo. AHORA sí descubrió el timbre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1878
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f4f4ac10:

    # "All this noise they're making had better not wake Sayori or there's gonna be a murder."
    "Más vale que todo este ruido no haya despertado a Sayori o alguien será asesinado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1879
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1880
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_97d7b598:

    # "Alright, sounds like they're gone. Let's try this again."
    "Muy bien, parece que se fue. Intentemos de nuevo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1881
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_367bf4a2:

    # ks "Sayori- {w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks "Sayori-{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1883
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6a323813:

    # "GODDAMNIT! WHY AREN'T THEY LEAVING?" with vpunch
    "¡MALDITA SEA! ¿QUÉ NO SE VA A IR?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1884
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7fe3c24d:

    # s sleeptalk "Mmn..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Mmn…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1886
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b09451c:

    # "I can't answer the door with Sayori and the [hypno6]s like this. And I can't wake her now or she'll know what happened." with dissolve
    "No puedo abrir la puerta con Sayori y l[genero_ao]s [hypno6!t!l] así. Y no puedo despertarla ahora o sabrá lo que pasó." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1889
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_10907478:

    # "... What the!? I think Sayori's cell just went off?"
    "… ¿¡Pero qué!? ¿El teléfono de Sayori acaba de sonar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1890
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf0874e3:

    # "But..."
    "Pero…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1891
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6f8be6b8:

    # s sleepy "Urrgh..." with dissolve
    s sleepy "Ayyy…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1892
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5e196bd9:

    # ks angry "Why the FUCK is it so loud?!"
    ks angry "¡¿Por qué CARAJOS hay tanto ruido?!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1893
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7d4f24d2:

    # "Sayori's eyelids flicker open as her phone vibrates furiously in her pants pocket."
    "Los ojos de Sayori se abren mientras su teléfono vibra furiosamente en su bolsillo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1894
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1af11e80:

    # ks "AGH! Hiroko, turn that fucking phone off!"
    ks "¡AJ! ¡Hiroko, apaga ese puto teléfono!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1897
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ee93f925:

    # multi "Sayori! SAYORI!"
    multi "¡Sayori! ¡SAYORI!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1901
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1e73d0e3:

    # s "... Dad?"
    s "… ¿Papá?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1902
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_714d5e57:

    # s panicked_right "DAD! DAD HELP, I'M IN HERE!" with vpunch
    s panicked_right "¡PAPÁ! ¡AYÚDAME, ESTOY AQUÍ!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1904
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0ada47b2:

    # "Fuck. Fuck. Fuck."
    "Mierda. Mierda. Mierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1905
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_75fe47ce:

    # "What do I do? What do I do?"
    "¿Qué hago? ¿Qué hago?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1906
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_39c1da75:

    # multi "Boy, if you don't open this door you're going to be in a whole new world of trouble."
    multi "Muchacho, si no abres esta puerta estarás en un mundo de problemas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1907
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_367823d9:

    # "My head starts to swim. I can feel my breath shortening."
    "Mi cabeza empieza a dar vueltas. Siento que me falta el aliento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1909
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9c87b882:

    # "And just then I notice Sayori looking straight at me as she starts to speak gently." with dissolve
    "Y entonces noto a Sayori mirándome directamente y empieza a hablar con gentileza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1910
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d0471c33:

    # "She's... grinning?"
    "Está… ¿sonriendo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1911
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_99cf8adf:

    # s "{size=16}I think now would be a good time to mention my father's a cop.{/size}"
    s "{size=16}Creo que ahora sería un buen momento para mencionar que mi papá es policía.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1912
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e640afad:

    # ks angry "SON OF A BITCH!" with vpunch
    ks angry "¡HIJA DE PUTA!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1913
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2b94721a:

    # "And now she mentions it, I can hear this guy on the other side of the door talking to someone else. It sounds like he's calling in backup."
    "Y ahora que lo menciona, puedo oír a ese sujeto del otro lado de la pueta hablando con alguien más. Suena a que está pidiendo refuerzos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1914
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ea1a35fb:

    # s frown_right "You were warned, Kyou. Things will only get worse for you from here on." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Se te advirtió, Kyou. Las cosas solo se pondrán peores para ti de ahora en adelante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1916
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8aff0e31:

    # "My attentions wildly shift from the door, which is again being pounded on..."
    "Mi atención va y viene salvajemente de la puerta, la cual sigue siendo golpeada..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1917
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_92dfbb68:

    # "... and Sayori; flanked by my two useless [hypno6]s as they keep her pointlessly restrained on the couch."
    "… y Sayori; flanqueada por mis dos inútiles [hypno6]s que siguen sujetándola en vano en el sofá."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1918
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f5eaef52:

    # "I pocket my penlight for all the good it will do right now as my mind races."
    "Meto mi linterna a mi bolsillo, pues no me servirá de nada, sintiéndome cada vez más nervioso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1935
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cd70a45e:

    # "I'll just... I'll just say everyone's got it all wrong. Sayori wasn't harmed; I didn't lay a finger on her, or her friends. Everyone's fine."
    "Solo… solo diré que todos están en un error. Sayori no salió herida; no le puse un dedo encima, ni a sus amigas. Todos están bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1920
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c54ee34b:

    # "What could I seriously be done for?"
    "¿Qué más se le puede hacer?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1922
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_17658202:

    # multi "FOR FUCK'S SAKE OPEN THIS DOOR!" with vpunch
    multi "¡CON UN CARAJO, ABRAN ESTA PUERTA!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1923
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_92b871ba:

    # s "I think you had better do what daddy says."
    s "Creo que será mejor que hagas lo que papi dice."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1926
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2fa9219b:

    # nvl_narrator "Sayori's father burst into my house as I finally allowed him in. Some uniformed officers followed shortly after."
    nvl_narrator "El padre de Sayori irrumpe en mi casa en cuanto finalmente lo dejo entrar. Seguido poco después de algunos oficiales uniformados."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1927
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_31fd5bfd:

    # nvl_narrator "My words did nothing to sway them from arresting me. Especially when it turned out Sayori had another trick up her sleeve."
    nvl_narrator "Mis palabras no hicieron nada para persuadirlos de no arrestarme. Sobre todo porque resultó que Sayori tenía otro as bajo la manga."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1928
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_50dba267:

    # nvl_narrator "Apparently her cellphone had been recording the whole time she was in my house, and captured my attempt to hypnotize her."
    nvl_narrator "Aparentemente su teléfono estuvo grabando todo el tiempo que estuvo en mi casa y capturó mi intento de hipnotizarla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1931
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_586a71e6:

    # nvl clear
    # nvl_narrator "As I await trial I heard that Hiroko and Nozomi have been undergoing hypnotherapy to undo the programming I did on them."
    nvl clear
    nvl_narrator "Esperando el juicio, escuché que Hiroko y Nozomi han estado recibiendo hipnoterapia para deshacer la programación que les di."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1933
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c0cda299:

    # nvl_narrator "They are supposedly making slow progress and it is unknown if they will ever make a full recovery."
    nvl_narrator "Supuestamente están progresando lentamente y no se sabe si algún día se recuperarán por completo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1934
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b198f961:

    # nvl_narrator "Although I'm sure if they just let me use the penlight on them again I could fix them in a flash."
    nvl_narrator "Aunque estoy seguro de que, si me dejaran usar la linterna en ellas una vez más, podría arreglarlas en un santiamén."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1936
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4eb55d87:

    # nvl clear
    # nvl_narrator "Speaking of the penlight... it's apparently under lock and key in an evidence vault."
    nvl clear
    nvl_narrator "Hablando de la linterna… aparentemente está bajo llave en una bóveda de evidencia."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1938
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c95f51ec:

    # nvl_narrator "No one really knows what to do with it. Although if word gets out to a wider audience I'm sure there'd be a lot of interest."
    nvl_narrator "Nadie sabe qué hacer con ella. Aunque, si se corriera la voz, estoy seguro de que habría mucho interés."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1940
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7da52d46:

    # nvl clear
    # nvl_narrator "Spending time in confinement has meant I've had a lot of time alone with my thoughts."
    nvl clear
    nvl_narrator "Pasar tiempo en confinamiento me ha dado mucho tiempo a solas con mis pensamientos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1942
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0566a84e:

    # nvl_narrator "It's forced me to confront what I did to those girls. Just... why did I go through with all of that?"
    nvl_narrator "Me ha obligado a enfrentar lo que les hice a esas chicas. Yo… ¿por qué hice todo eso?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1943
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_de95ccdf:

    # nvl_narrator "I started out on a journey to win Nozomi's affection, yet in the end all I did was twist her mind like a soft pretzel just out of a sense of morbid curiosity."
    nvl_narrator "Comencé este viaje para ganarme el afecto de Nozomi, y al final, lo único que hice fue retorcer su mente como un pretzel por un mero sentido de morbosa curiosidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1945
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1d6669df:

    # nvl clear
    # nvl_narrator "And all the excuses I made to myself to justify it just don't seem to cut it anymore."
    nvl clear
    nvl_narrator "Y las excusas que me hice a mí mismo para justificarlo ya no parecen servir de nada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1947
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0be49428:

    # nvl_narrator "So all that I have left now is the realization that this is the kind of guy I am."
    nvl_narrator "Lo único que me queda es darme cuenta de que esta es la clase de sujeto que soy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1948
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5ca9903a:

    # nvl_narrator "I hurt people."
    nvl_narrator "Le hago daño a la gente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1956
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e855973f:

    # "I arrive at Nozomi's place bright and early, and she is there to greet me at the door."
    "Llego a casa de Nozomi muy en la mañana, y ella está ahí para recibirme en la puerta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1957
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1b1d8b63:

    # n "Welcome, Kyou. It is good to see you again."
    n "Bienvenido, Kyou. Es bueno volver a verte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1958
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ae0016e0:

    # "I notice the flat manner in which the [hypno6] greets me immediately, which instantly tells me one thing: We're currently alone in this house."
    "Noto la llana manera en la que [el] [hypno6!t!l] inmediatamente me saluda, lo cual al instante me dice una cosa: En este momento estamos solos en la casa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1959
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf303fbf:

    # "Suits me just fine."
    "Me viene genial."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1960
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_52a098ab:

    # ks casual "Show me to your room, [hypno6]."
    ks casual "Muéstrame tu habitación, [hypno6!t!l]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1973
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5ff6fde6:

    # "I can only assume this is how she is now when she's alone, so her [hypno6] programming seems to be holding up well. That's good."
    "Solo puedo asumir que así es como actúa ahora cuando está sol[genero_ao], por lo que está reteniendo su programación de [hypno6!t!l] bastante bien. Qué bueno."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1975
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6bff25d3:

    # "I can only assume this is how my [hypno6] is now when left to its own devices, so its [hypno6] programming seems to be holding up well. That's good."
    "Solo puedo asumir que así es como actúa mi [hypno6!t!l] al estar sol[genero_ao], por lo que está reteniendo su programación de [hypno6!t!l] bastante bien. Qué bueno."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1976
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_550e4000:

    # "Looking over Nozomi's stiffened form with satisfaction, I address her calmly."
    "Viendo con satisfacción a la tiesa Nozomi, me dirijo a ella con calma."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1988
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_afb181cc:

    # ks casual frown "Tell me what's going on with the Akemi family today, [hypno6]."
    ks casual frown "Dime qué sucede hoy con la familia Akemi, [hypno6!t!l]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1978
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d374cee9:

    # n "Yes, Kyou. Ichiro is out with his friends this morning, Yoshio is at work and Atsuko is doing some grocery shopping. She'll be back soon."
    n "Sí, Kyou. Ichiro salió con sus amigos esta mañana, Yoshio está en el trabajo y Atsuko se encuentra comprando víveres. Volverá pronto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1979
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ec4774fb:

    # ks "And do any of them suspect that you know what you really are?"
    ks "¿Y alguno de ellos sospecha lo que realmente eres?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1980
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_842436fa:

    # n "No, Kyou. None of the Akemi family have indicated that they know I have attained awareness of my true nature."
    n "No, Kyou. Nadie en la familia Akemi ha indicado saber que he obtenido consciencia de mi verdadera naturaleza."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1981
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_43269e18:

    # ks "Wonderful. Keeping your awareness hidden is your top priority while you're with the Akemi family."
    ks "Maravilloso. Mantener esa consciencia en secreto es tu prioridad principal mientras estés con la familia Akemi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1982
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d5fc5dac:

    # ks "If they realize you've learned you're not their daughter they'll certainly have you shipped away to be re-formatted."
    ks "Si descubre que aprendiste que no eres su hija, te enviarán con certeza a ser reformateada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1983
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_93856cb2:

    # n "I understand, Kyou."
    n "Entiendo, Kyou."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1984
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a5a7200f:

    # "That I've been able to completely dissociate Nozomi from her family after barely two days is wild."
    "Qué haya sido capaz de disociar por completo a Nozomi de su familia en tan solo dos días en una locura."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1991
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8e4a7dc6:

    # "Okay, so I still sometimes slip when trying to think of her as nothing but a [hypno6]. Like I have some programming on my own mind to do, heh."
    "Muy bien, aún tengo problemas intentando pensar en ella como nada más que un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]. Creo que tengo programación que hacer en mi mente, je."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1992
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6bcac8a8:

    # "Anyway, I'm looking forward to spending more time tinkering with Nozomi's code, if only I can deal with Sayori today."
    "En fin, no puedo esperar a pasar más tiempo jugueteando con el código de Nozomi, si es que puedo lidiar con Sayori hoy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1993
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d3a2b4d5:

    # ks "By the way, you told the Akemis I'd be here, didn't you?"
    ks "Por cierto, les dijiste a los Akemi que estaría aquí, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1994
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_77bb2508:

    # n "Yes, Kyou. I told Yoshio and Atsuko that you and Sayori would be visiting for an impromptu study group, as you instructed."
    n "Sí, Kyou. Les dije a Yoshio y a Atsuko que tú y Sayori me visitarían para un grupo de estudio improvisado, tal como instruiste."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1995
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8b9605b3:

    # "Alright. If I'm lucky there won't be any nasty surprises. If I'm not, I'll have to explain to Nozomi's mom what I'm doing in the middle of an induction."
    "Muy bien. Si tengo suerte, no habrá sorpresas desagradables. Si no, tendré que explicarle a la mamá de Nozomi lo que estoy haciendo a media inducción."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1997
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f899a064:

    # "I hear the doorbell sound from downstairs. That has to be Sayori."
    "Oigo el timbre sonar en el piso de abajo. Tiene que ser Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1998
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_471e7161:

    # ks frown "Get the door, [hypno6], and lead Sayori back here."
    ks frown "Ve a la puerta, [hypno6!t!l], y trae a Sayori hasta acá."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1999
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6380986f:

    # n "Yes, Kyou."
    n "Sí, Kyou."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2004
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3666bce4:

    # s "So."
    s "Entonces."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2005
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b9794a66:

    # s concerned "How... are you, Nozomi?" with dissolve
    s concerned "¿Cómo… estás, Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2006
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b0ecd037:

    # n side smile_side "I'm fine, Sayori." with dissolve
    n side smile_side "Estoy bien, Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2008
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_87ef230e:

    # "Sayori frowns at her friend's muted response as I nervously clear my throat." with dissolve
    "Sayori le frunce el ceño a la lacónica respuesta de su amiga y se aclara con ansiedad la garganta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2009
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7ff67d19:

    # ks smile "And how are you, Sayori?"
    ks smile "¿Y cómo estás tú, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2010
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_52a713fd:

    # s frown_right "Oh I am just peachy. Is Hiroko not joining us?" with dissolve
    s frown_right "Oh, estoy de maravilla. ¿Hiroko no nos acompañará?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2011
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_be19a171:

    # "Not needing her for this, I brought Hiroko to my house and left her to do some monotonous tasks as a test of her programming."
    "Al no necesitarla para esto, llevé a Hiroko a mi casa y la dejé haciendo algunas tareas monótonas como una prueba para su programación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2012
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b3638d3c:

    # ks "Ah, no. She couldn't tear herself away from her tennis practice."
    ks "Ah, no. No pudo abandonar su práctica de tenis."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2013
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c0b4d052:

    # s "Hmm. Alright then. Now, I believe the two of you are going to enlighten me on what I have been out of the loop on."
    s "Mmm. Bien, entonces. Ahora, me parece que ustedes dos planean iluminarme con lo que me he perdido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2014
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8c032866:

    # ks neutral "Alright, so..."
    ks neutral "Muy bien, pues…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2015
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_44ede826_1:

    # "I probably should've prepared something if I was going to do this. Guess I'll just wing it."
    "Probablemente debí preparar algo si iba a hacer esto. Supongo que improvisaré."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2016
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_999640fa:

    # ks "After Nozomi flipped out on me the other day I realized I needed to clear the air, so I swung by her clubroom after school and asked if we could talk."
    ks "Después del disgusto que Nozomi tuvo conmigo el otro día, me di cuenta de que tenía que hacer algo, así que pasé por su club y le pregunté si podíamos hablar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2017
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a94dfeed:

    # ks "And... uh, we did. We talked it out for a while, and in the end she accepted that she overreacted and wanted to start over with a clean slate."
    ks "Y… em, eso hicimos. Lo discutimos y concluimos que sí estaba exagerando, y quiso hacer borrón y cuenta nueva."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2018
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1f8bba11_1:

    # "Sayori's frown looks like it deepened as she listens to me."
    "El ceño de Sayori parece fruncirse más mientras me escucha."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2019
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2df9123a:

    # s frown "Did she now..." with dissolve
    s frown "¿De verdad?..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2021
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8e8aae1b:

    # "With a chuckle I turn to look at Nozomi." with dissolve
    "Riendo levemente, volteo a ver a Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2022
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c7b628e6:

    # ks smile "Nozomi, back me up on this."
    ks smile "Nozomi, ayúdame con esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2026
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f1fcbf33:

    # n smile_side "It's all true, Sayori. I accept that I overreacted, and I want to start over with a clean slate." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Todo es verdad, Sayori. Acepto que exageré, y quiero hacer un borrón y cuenta nueva." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2027
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c66b727d:

    # s "And... you could not have simply told me this at any time before now? I'm sorry, Nozomi, but I don't understand why we needed to do this here."
    s "Y… ¿no pudieron simplemente haberme dicho eso cuando fuera? Perdóname, Nozomi, pero no entiendo por qué tenemos que hacer esto aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2028
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f6df19ef:

    # s "You all made it seem much more complicated than what you are now telling me."
    s "Lo hicieron parecer mucho más complicado que lo que me están diciendo ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2029
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2701d565:

    # ks "Yeah, well... there was a complication."
    ks "Sí, bueno… sí hubo una complicación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2030
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0702cbd3:

    # s "Which was?"
    s "¿La cual fue?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2033
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f500901e:

    # ks "The penlight that got Nozomi so worked-up in the first place."
    ks "La linterna que hizo que Nozomi se angustiara tanto en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2034
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8348baed:

    # "Sayori's skeptical gaze turns to the penlight I hold up before her."
    "La mirada escéptica de Sayori se dirige a la linterna que sostengo ante ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2035
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c2889026:

    # s frown_right "And what would be so complicated about it? You shone it in her face as some kind of prank, yes?" with dissolve
    s frown_right "¿Y qué tendría eso de complicado? La encendiste en su rostro a modo de alguna clase de broma, ¿cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2037
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7c507000:

    # ks "Right. Well, I guess to understand you need to see where Nozomi was coming from initially."
    ks "Es correcto. Pues, supongo que para entender tienes que verlo desde el punto de vista de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2038
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ba47b37d:

    # "As I'm about to continue, Sayori holds up a hand to shush me."
    "Estoy a punto de continuar cuando Sayori alza una mano para callarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2039
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6209b155:

    # s "Actually, Kyou, I would like to hear more from Nozomi herself."
    s "De hecho, Kyou, me gustaría oírlo de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2041
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_276d8b36:

    # "She then turns her attention to her friend, who simply smiles at her." with dissolve
    "Luego dirige su atención a su amiga quien simplemente le sonríe." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2042
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_59c020a7:

    # s "I can understand the forgiveness, Nozomi. It did seem to be over a misunderstanding caused by a little mischief."
    s "Puedo entender el perdón, Nozomi. Parece haber sido un malentendido causado por una travesura."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2043
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b0562950:

    # s "But what of yours and Hiroko's sudden quietude and... compliance?"
    s "Pero ¿qué hay de ese súbito sosiego tuyo y de Hiroko y su… complacencia?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2044
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2d928d58:

    # n surprised_side "I'm not sure what you mean, Sayori?" with dissolve
    n surprised_side "No estoy segura de a qué te refieres, Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2045
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_94ab8c45:

    # s "I mean, how do we go from not wanting to speak to Kyou on Monday, being scared of him by Tuesday..."
    s "Lo que quiero decir es: ¿Cómo es que pasamos de no querer hablar con Kyou el lunes, tenerle miedo el martes…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2046
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7381dd78:

    # s "Angrily confronting him by Thursday, to having him home and hanging on his every word by Saturday?"
    s "Enfrentarlo iracundamente el jueves, a invitarlo a casa y atender cada palabra de lo que dice el sábado?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2047
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_53eec164:

    # s "That is an odd progression is it not?"
    s "Es una progresión extraña, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2048
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1f5ea2be:

    # n "Um, w-well..."
    n "Em, p-pues…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2050
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ff3e1f69:

    # "Nozomi blinks slowly and raises a hand to rub her head." with dissolve
    "Nozomi parpadea lentamente y alza una mano para rascarse la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2051
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ce773a7e:

    # n "Actually, could you talk to Kyou about this? I'm feeling a little tired trying to process what you just said."
    n "De hecho, ¿podrías hablar de eso con Kyou? Me siento un poco cansada procesando lo que acabas de decir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2052
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0b64a7b8:

    # s "Tired? Nozomi, it is mid-morning. Are you getting enough sleep?"
    s "¿Cansada? Nozomi, estamos en plena mañana. ¿Estás durmiendo lo suficiente?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2053
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d59bbee1:

    # n laugh "Ahaha, that's kinda funny coming from you. But yes, I think so." with dissolve
    n laugh "Jajaja, eso es gracioso viniendo de ti. Pero sí, eso creo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2054
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5d8587aa:

    # ks "Look, Sayori."
    ks "Mira, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2057
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_aa9a5c2b:

    # "While Sayori was distracted I took the opportunity to turn on my penlight and align it with her eyesight."
    "Mientras Sayori estaba distraída, aproveché la oportunidad para encender mi linterna y alinearla a la altura de sus ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2061
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_10f9c7fd:

    # "Her head turned slightly to face me as I spoke up, and her eyes almost immediately find themselves looking into the beam of light that crosses over them." with dissolve
    "Su cabeza giró ligeramente para verme mientras hablo, y sus ojos casi de forma inmediata se dirigen al haz de luz que pasa sobre ellos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2062
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a3fddff_1:

    # ks neutral "Sayori, listen to me. I'm about to explain everything."
    ks neutral "Sayori, escúchame. Voy a explicarlo todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2064
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_de381faa:

    # s "Kyou, if you think re-enacting your prank is going to help- {w=0.8}{nw}"
    s "Kyou, si crees que repetir tu broma ayudará- {w=0.8}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2066
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_63dc01d5:

    # ks "No, Sayori, you're wrong. This will make everything clear to you, you'll see."
    ks "No, Sayori, te equivocas. Esto lo aclarará todo, ya verás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2068
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_19d95d0a:

    # "Sayori frowns once more, but I can tell she's already distracted by the patterns the light has started to form in her eyes as I pass the beam across them once more."
    "Sayori frunce el ceño una vez más, pero puedo notar que ya está distraída con los patrones de luz que han empezado a formarse ante sus ojos mientras vuelvo a pasar el haz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2069
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_aa846a25:

    # ks "All you need to do is listen, watch my light, and concentrate on what you see."
    ks "Lo único que tienes que hacer es escuchar, observar la luz y concentrarte en lo que ves."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2071
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_85b8b49a:

    # ks "And as you concentrate on this light, you will find it appropriate to let yourself relax. After all, it's perfectly safe to relax under the light."
    ks "Y al concentrarte en la luz, puedes empezar a relajarte. Después de todo, es perfectamente seguro relajarte bajo la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2073
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_838cfc02:

    # s concerned_right "Wait... Is this how... with the others..." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Espera… ¿Así es como… las otras…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2076
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c37e50fd_1:

    # ks "It's alright, Sayori. Just relax and let go. There's no need to think."
    ks "Está bien, Sayori. Solo relájate y déjate llevar. No hace falta pensar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2078
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8483492e_1:

    # ks "Letting your eyelids close, then open again as the light passes right to left..."
    ks "Deja que tus párpados se cierren y se vuelvan a abrir mientras la luz pasa de derecha a izquierda…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2080
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e9adbf46_1:

    # ks "Left to right..."
    ks "De izquierda a derecha…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2082
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_caedcd41_1:

    # ks "Feeling your eyelids become heavier with every blink. Harder to keep open, just as your thoughts begin to cease."
    ks "Siente cómo tus párpados se ponen pesados cada vez que pestañeas. Se vuelve más difícil abrirlos y tus pensamientos comienzan a cesar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2085
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_eda5cb8a_1:

    # ks "Feeling all those thoughts in your head drift away as you relax, deeper and deeper." with dissolve
    ks "Siente cómo todos esos pensamientos se van, y tú te relajas, más y más profundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2087
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11dbac7f_1:

    # ks "Feeling so nice not to have to think for a while. Feeling so wonderful to let your eyelids droop, becoming sleepy under the light even as you focus on it for me."
    ks "Se siente tan bien no tener que pensar por un rato. Se siente tan maravilloso dejar que tus párpados caigan. Estar bajo está luz te da tanto sueño, aunque te concentres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2089
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_36b21f67_1:

    # s sleepy "Kyou... y-you..." with dissolve
    s sleepy "Kyou… t-tú…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2090
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5a2d409a_1:

    # ks "Emptying your thoughts, Sayori. Letting yourself feel so relaxed as you go deeper and deeper."
    ks "Vacía tus pensamientos, Sayori. Siéntete completamente relajada al caer más y más profundo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2091
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_09abd83e:

    # "As Sayori's head starts to droop I lean in towards Nozomi and whisper:"
    "Cuando la cabeza de Sayori comienza a caer, me acerco a Nozomi y susurro:"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2092
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_79bd7e98:

    # ks "{size=16}Hold her for me, so she doesn't fall.{/size}"
    ks "{size=16}Sostenla por mí, para que no se caiga.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2095
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8c53359b:

    # "Waiting a moment for Nozomi to grip Sayori firmly, I then continue."
    "Espero a que Nozomi sujete firmemente a Sayori, luego continúo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2099
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e4de480a_1:

    # ks "Going so deep. Feeling so good. So empty. So sleepy."
    ks "Muy profundo. Te sientes tan bien, tan relajada que cada vez te de más sueño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2101
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d032b9e8_1:

    # ks "You're doing so well, Sayori. Let your eyes open a little, just once more as you keep watching the light."
    ks "Lo estás haciendo muy bien, Sayori. Abre tus ojos un poquito, solo una vez más y sigue observando la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2103
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2c46bcb2_1:

    # ks "That's right. Now sleep."
    ks "Eso es. Ahora duerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2105
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9d80d18d:

    # "I look on as Sayori's head droops slightly while she sinks into her entranced sleep." with dissolve
    "Veo con satisfacción a Sayori dejar caer su cabeza ligeramente, durmiendo en un profundo trance." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2112
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_264994df_1:

    # ks "Going deeper, Sayori. Going so deep, feeling so relaxed, so empty of thought."
    ks "Más profundo, Sayori. Caes tan profundo, te sientes tan relajada que desaparecen todos tus pensamientos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2113
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0e9a7f37_1:

    # ks "And knowing how good it feels makes you want to go deeper. More relaxed. More empty."
    ks "Y saber lo bien que se siente te hace querer ir más profundo. Estar más relajada. Más vacía."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2114
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_faff163f_1:

    # ks "But even as you go so deep, Sayori, even as your mind becomes so empty, you can still hear my voice and respond to my words. Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "Pero por más profundo que vayas, Sayori, por más vacía que esté tu mente, siempre podrás oír mi voz y responder a mis palabras. ¿Comprendes, Sayori? "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2115
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_553aaf3e_1:

    # s sleeptalk "I understand..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Comprendo…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2117
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a35933bc_1:

    # "After the stress of handling Nozomi's induction, I'm really appreciative that Sayori made this so easy for me." with dissolve
    "Después del estrés que fue manejar la inducción de Nozomi, en verdad aprecio que Sayori me lo haya puesto tan fácil." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2118
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8e854925_1:

    # "And with the last of Nozomi's clique under my influence I should be able to keep any rumours about us from spreading out of control."
    "Y con el último miembro de la pandilla de Nozomi bajo mi influencia, debería ser capaz de evitar que los rumores sobre nosotros se esparzan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2119
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf232fcc_1:

    # "All the while having three subjects to play with. I'm looking forward to seeing how far their minds will go to adapt to the realities I'll implant in their heads."
    "Y todo mientras tengo a tres sujetos con los que jugar. Y ansío ver cuán lejos pueden llegar sus mentes para adaptarse a las realidades que implante en sus cabezas. "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2120
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2893f246_1:

    # "... But I'm getting ahead of myself. First I need to make sure Sayori joins us proper."
    "… Pero me estoy adelantando. Primero necesito asegurarme de que Sayori se nos una como se debe."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2123
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_80223f28:

    # "... That sounded like the door opening downstairs. Nozomi's mom must be home."
    "… Creo que escuché la puerta abrirse ahí abajo. La mamá de Nozomi debe estar en casa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2124
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4d003c6b_1:

    # ks "And while you listen, Sayori, it's very important that you acknowledge my words are your reality."
    ks "Y mientras escuchas, Sayori, es muy importante que reconozcas mis palabras como tu realidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2125
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2fdefbf2_1:

    # ks "If I say something is true for you, then it must absolutely be true. Understand?"
    ks "Si digo que algo es verdad para ti, entonces es la verdad absoluta. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2126
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_575268fe_1:

    # s sleeptalk "I... understand." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Com-… prendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2128
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_691f4973:

    # ks "And what is true for you is that although you are still very deeply asleep, you will still be able to stand upright, on your own two feet, while remaining so deep as you are." with dissolve
    ks "Y la verdad es que, aunque sigas profundamente dormida, seguirás siendo capaz de mantenerte de pie, aunque sigas así de profundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2129
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_793adaed:

    # "Leaving it a moment to sink in, I then whisper to Nozomi to let her go."
    "Le doy un momento para asimilar eso, luego le susurro a Nozomi que la suelte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2132
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cab74d7f:

    # ks "{size=16}Now go downstairs and greet Atsuko. Keep her from coming in here as long as you can.{/size}"
    ks "{size=16}Ahora baja y recibe a Atsuko. Evita que suba tanto tiempo como puedas.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2925
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ad13a939:

    # "I don't know how much longer I can stay here before Nozomi's mother disturbs us."
    "No sé cuánto tiempo pueda seguir aquí antes de que la madre de Nozomi nos moleste."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2136
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a379171e:

    # "Hopefully Nozomi will buy me enough time to plant the seeds in Sayori's head that I need to."
    "Con algo de suerte Nozomi me ganará tiempo suficiente para plantar las semillas que necesito en la cabeza de Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2137
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_23e4af24:

    # "Now which seeds should those be..."
    "¿Pero qué semillas serán?…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2141
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_16efefdc_1:

    # "With her friends now robots, I think to instead mold this one's mind in a different direction."
    "Con sus amigas siendo ahora robots, pienso en moldear la mente de esta en una dirección diferente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2145
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_db74a91d:

    # "I guess I'm not much for change. Besides, having three robotized girls would be good for comparison, given their differing human personalities."
    "Supongo que no quiero cambiar mucho. Además, tener a tres chicas robotizadas sería bueno para comparar, dadas sus diferentes personalidades humanas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2146
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2df98355:

    # ks "And as you accept this reality, that you can stand straight and listen to me while still being deeply asleep, you may find it even easier to accept the reality of my words."
    ks "Y al aceptar esa realidad, que puedes mantenerte de pie y escucharme mientras sigues profundamente dormida, te será más fácil aceptar la realidad de mis palabras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2147
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11a942fb:

    # ks "The reality that you are a [hypno6], and not a flesh and blood human."
    ks "La realidad de que eres un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], y no una humana de carne y hueso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2148
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5cde4a61:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "I... what?" with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Soy… ¿qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2150
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_035385d2:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. A [hypno6], built from the ground up to look and behave indistinguishably from a real human being." with dissolve
    ks "Así es, Sayori. Un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], construid[genero_ao] de pies a cabeza para verse y comportarse indistinguiblemente como una humana." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2151
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_540fe055:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "That's... impossible." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Es… imposible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2153
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ea2a6d61:

    # ks "Remember, Sayori, my words are your reality. So if I say it, then it's more than possible." with dissolve
    ks "Recuerda, Sayori, mis palabras son tu realidad. Por lo que, si lo digo, es más que posible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2154
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b1f5de0b:

    # ks "It's real. Because after all, it's your reality that you are a [hypno6]."
    ks "Es real. Porque, después de todo, es tu realidad que seas un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2161
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7cb05797:

    # ks "That is your truth, Sayori. Your reality, and the more you think about what I have said, the more real my words become."
    ks "Esa es tu verdad, Sayori. Tu realidad, y entre más piensas en lo que dije, más reales se vuelven mis palabras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2162
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1e97f5c3:

    # ks "The more you think about your reality, the more you realize you are not having thoughts at all."
    ks "Entre más piensas en tu realidad, más te das cuenta de que ni siquiera tienes pensamientos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2163
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2e5017c0:

    # ks "You are merely processing instructions from the programs you are running."
    ks "Simplemente estás procesando instrucciones de los programas que estás corriendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2170
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f0b08ff6:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori; I am your programmer. And while you are in this deeply relaxed state I can alter any facet of your code that I please."
    ks "Así es, Sayori; yo soy tu programado. Y mientras te encuentras en este estado de profunda relajación, puedo alterar cualquier faceta de tu código como me pazca."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2171
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_195610ca:

    # ks "You will process all that I have just said to you, Sayori."
    ks "Procesarás todo lo que acabo de decirte, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2172
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ca5934c6:

    # ks "And once you have done so fully, and have accepted everything as your complete reality you will say \"[hypno2]\"."
    ks "Una vez lo hayas hecho y hayas aceptado todo como tu realidad absoluta, dirás \"[hypno2!t!l]\"."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2173
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2b2fcfbb:

    # "Spending a few anxious moments in silence, I wonder how Nozomi is doing with her mother."
    "Paso unos inquietantes momentos de silencio, preguntándome cómo le va a Nozomi con su madre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2174
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3829e2ba:

    # "There doesn't seem to be any commotion outside, but I know I'm on borrowed time here."
    "No parece haber nada de conmoción ahí afuera, pero sé que tengo el tiempo medido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2175
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_18c294a6:

    # s sleeptalk "[hypno2]." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "[hypno2!t]." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2177
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_67de40f0:

    # ks "Very good, [hypno6]. Your acceptance causes your spine to tingle with a pleasurable jolt of electricity that feels wonderful to your robotic brain." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien, [hypno6!t!l]. Tu aceptación hace que tu espina sienta una descarga eléctrica de placer que hace que tu cerebro robótico se sienta de maravilla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2178
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1896a770:

    # ks "It always feels this good to obey my instructions, Sayori. No matter whether you're deep asleep as you are now, or fully wide awake and alert."
    ks "Siempre se siente muy bien obedecer mis instrucciones, Sayori. No importa si estás profundamente dormida como ahora, o despierta y alerta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2185
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_553aaf3e_2:

    # s sleeptalk "I understand..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Entiendo…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2187
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2a7b4745:

    # "I think I can hear voices. I need to wrap this up now and hope I've done enough." with dissolve
    "Creo que puedo oír voces. Tengo que ocultar esto y esperar haber hecho suficiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2188
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8affb323:

    # ks "Now Sayori, I will count to three, and on three you will awaken feeling calm and refreshed and fully accepting of these truths I have told you."
    ks "Ahora, Sayori, contaré hasta tres, y a las tres despertarás sintiéndote fresca y calmada, y aceptando completamente las verdades que te conté."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2189
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_79d5eb0a:

    # ks "Fully accepting that you are a [hypno6] under my command. Understand?"
    ks "Aceptando por completo que eres un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] bajo mis órdenes. ¿Entendido?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2190
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0af51841:

    # s sleeptalk "Yes..." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Sí…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2192
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4514b15b:

    # ks "Good. One, beginning to stir." with dissolve
    ks "Bien. Uno, comienzas a moverte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2193
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6b4ea685:

    # ks "Two, testing the corners of your eyelids, feeling them lighten."
    ks "Dos, tus párpados comienzan a abrirse, sintiéndose más y más ligeros."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2195
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_defe8aeb:

    # ks "And three, awake and refreshed, Sayori."
    ks "Y tres, fresca y despierta, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2197
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fafb6ddd:

    # s "Mmn..." with dissolve
    s "Mmn…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2202
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3a50487e:

    # "Almost immediately after, the bedroom door opens as who I can only assume is Nozomi's mom strolls in, followed behind by her anxious-looking daughter." with dissolve
    "Casi inmediatamente después, la puerta de la habitación es abierta por quien solo puedo asumir que es la mamá de Nozomi, seguida por su angustiada hija." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2203
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2a2d5390:

    # nm "Oh, don't be silly! I'm just going to say hi, and then you can get back to..."
    nm "¡Ay, no seas tontilla! Solo voy a saludar y luego pueden regresar a…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2204
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8457be91:

    # "She smiles as our eyes meet."
    "Sonríe en cuanto nuestras miradas se cruzan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2205
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1d824454:

    # nm "You must be Kyou."
    nm "Tú debes ser Kyou."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2206
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9fe1a9b0:

    # ks smile "Ah, that's me. It's nice to meet you, Mrs. Akemi."
    ks smile "Ah, ese soy yo. Gusto en conocerla, Sra. Akemi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2207
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9c55b29f:

    # nm laugh "Ah, Atsuko is fine. And it's nice to meet you as well, Kyou." with dissolve
    nm laugh "Ay, llámame Atsuko. Y gusto en conocerte también, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2209
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_92fbe6b5:

    # "As we talk, I notice Sayori rubbing her temple in confusion." with dissolve
    "Mientras hablamos, noto a Sayori frotando confundida su sien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2210
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3b7632d2:

    # "I can only assume she's trying to adjust to her new reality in the midst of being disoriented by the sudden appearance of Nozomi's mother."
    "Asumo que intenta ajustarse a su nueva realidad, a la vez que está desorientada por la repentina aparición de la madre de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2211
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6333868f:

    # nm surprised_side "Oh, but Sayori! How are you, hun?" with dissolve
    nm surprised_side "¡Oh, pero, Sayori! ¿Cómo estás tú, cielo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2212
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_64b583ba:

    # s concerned "I am... I-I'm good, Atsuko. Thank you for asking." with dissolve
    s concerned "Estoy… B-bien, Atsuko. Gracias por preguntar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2213
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_173f8c8b:

    # "I can tell Atsuko isn't entirely convinced by her answer, but I get the impression this is a normal state of affairs between these two."
    "Me doy cuenta de que Atsuko no está convencida por completo por su respuesta, pero tengo la impresión de que eso es algo normal entre estas dos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2215
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_48a62b72:

    # nm smile_side "Of course." with dissolve
    nm smile_side "Por supuesto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2216
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8db6f73d:

    # "I really don't want her interacting with an unpredictable Sayori any more than she needs to."
    "De verdad no quiero que interactúe con una impredecible Sayori más de lo necesario."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2217
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9aa6d87d:

    # ks "Anyway, Sayori and I need to be going."
    ks "Como sea, Sayori y yo nos tenemos que ir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2218
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2a9d507e:

    # nm surprised "Already?" with dissolve
    nm surprised "¿Tan pronto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2219
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_03a43e69:

    # ks "Yeah. Sorry about the short visit."
    ks "Sí. Lamento que la visita fuera corta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2220
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2e555089:

    # nm "Well... could I speak to you before you go?"
    nm "Pues… ¿podría hablar contigo antes de que te vayas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2221
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_34f8a23b:

    # "No. I'd rather get Sayori out of here in case she says something I'll regret in her post-hypnotic stupor."
    "No. Preferiría sacar a Sayori de aquí en caso de que diga algo de lo que me arrepienta en estupor posthipnótico."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2222
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_512b9b3f:

    # ks "Of course."
    ks "Por supuesto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2227
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1342af86:

    # "I follow her outside as I wonder what she could possibly want to talk about."
    "Salgo junto a ella de la habitación y me pregunto de qué querrá hablar conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2228
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b307ff64:

    # nm "It's just... I was so surprised. Did you know that this is the first time Nozomi has ever invited a boy over?"
    nm "Es que… estaba tan sorprendida. ¿Sabías que esta es la primera vez que Nozomi trae a un chico a la casa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2229
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5c29d79b:

    # ks casual surprised "I, er... I didn't, no."
    ks casual surprised "Yo, em… no sabía, no."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2230
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7d8cf204:

    # nm surprised "I almost didn't believe it when she told me about you. She's never showed much interest in boys before." with dissolve
    nm surprised "Casi no pude creerlo cuando me habló de ti. Nunca había mostrado interés en chicos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2231
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5484e3f5:

    # "I let out a nervous chuckle as I rub the back of my neck."
    "Dejo salir una risita nerviosa frotando la parte de atrás de mi cuello."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2232
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_67a15cdf:

    # ks smile "And, uh... what has Nozomi been telling you about me, Mrs- I mean, Atsuko?"
    ks smile "Y, eh… ¿qué le ha contado de mí, Sra- digo, Atsuko?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2233
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a90e4d4b:

    # nm smile "Oh, very little to tell the truth. Mostly she was just very insistent that you be allowed to visit, so I had to read between the lines a little." with dissolve
    nm smile "Oh, muy poco, a decir verdad. Más que nada estuvo muy insistente en que te permitiera visitarnos, por lo que tuve que leer entre líneas un poco." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2234
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_73f954f6:

    # nm "Until yesterday I was actually starting to think she might be... you know?"
    nm "Hasta ayer, estaba empezando a pensar que ella podría ser… ya sabes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2235
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0e9a29bd:

    # nm laugh "Ahaha, not that there'd be anything wrong with that! We're a modern family, after all." with dissolve
    nm laugh "¡Jajaja, no es que eso tenga algo de malo! Somos una familia moderna, después de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2236
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e96a412c:

    # nm smile "But I've been telling her she needed some more people in her life, so I'm grateful if she's taken it to heart." with dissolve
    nm smile "Pero le he estado diciendo que necesitaba un poco más de gente en su vida, y estoy agradecida de que se lo haya tomado de corazón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2237
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e3fc5fab:

    # ks neutral "Wait, you're telling me she doesn't have many friends?"
    ks neutral "Espere, ¿me está diciendo que no tiene muchos amigos?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2238
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b4c64cc8:

    # nm surprised "Does that surprise you, Kyou? I suppose it might; I'm sure she seems very outgoing and friendly on the outside." with dissolve
    nm surprised "¿Eso te sorprende, Kyou? Me imagino por qué; estoy segura de que parece muy extrovertida y amiguera en el exterior." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2239
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4f1d4f20:

    # nm "But there are only a few people she genuinely trusts enough to bring any closer than that."
    nm "Pero hay muy pocas personas en las que genuinamente confía lo suficiente para dejar que se acerquen más que eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2240
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_768c027f:

    # nm laugh "So you can't imagine how excited I've been to meet you, Kyou. You must be someone very special if you're connecting with her~" with dissolve
    nm laugh "Así que no puedes imaginar lo emocionada que he estado de conocerte, Kyou. Debes ser alguien muy especial si estás conectando con ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2241
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_713b11dc:

    # nm "But I know, I know, you have places to be and you're having to listen to this old woman's natter. I won't keep you any longer today."
    nm "Pero ya sé, ya sé, tienes lugares adónde ir y aquí te tengo escuchando el parloteo de está doña."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2242
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b623036d:

    # nm smile "Just... be kind to her, won't you?" with dissolve
    nm smile "Solo... sé amable con ella, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2243
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_afe7297f:

    # ks smile "Huh? O-of course."
    ks smile "¿Eh? P-por supuesto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2244
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b148e612:

    # nm "Good! I hope to see you again, Kyou. You're welcome in this house anytime."
    nm "¡Bien! Espero volver a verte, Kyou. Eres bienvenido en esta casa cuando sea."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2248
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_42bb3a6f:

    # "That... was awkward."
    "Eso fue… incómodo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2249
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11ce065f:

    # s neutral_right "Do we absolutely need to go to your home, Kyou? I have cram school to get to." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "¿Es imperativo que vayamos a tu casa, Kyou? Tengo que ir a mis cursos nocturnos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2250
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7610bdcf:

    # ks casual frown "Yes, we do. What makes you think you can question me, [hypno6]?"
    ks casual frown "Sí, sí lo es. ¿Qué te hace pensar que puedes cuestionarme, [hypno6!t!l]?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2251
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_709ac71c:

    # s concerned_right "I just... of course I do not \"think\" at all as I have discovered, but processing all of this is a shock to my system, Kyou." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Es que… desde luego que yo no \"pienso\", por lo que he descubierto, pero procesar todo esto es un choque fuerte para mi sistema, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2252
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ef6214bd:

    # "I learned some things about Nozomi that I didn't expect."
    "Aprendí algunas cosas sobre Nozomi que no me esparaba."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2253
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c2c6d447:

    # s "Having to accept that I am... you know."
    s "El tener que aceptar que soy… ya sabes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2254
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6a97b14b:

    # "I thought I knew everything there was to know about her."
    "Creí que sabía todo lo que había que saber de ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2255
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b705e5df:

    # s "It is so outlandish, yet somehow I accept it completely."
    s "Es tan estrafalario, y aun así lo acepto por completo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2256
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dce44c05:

    # "How could someone like Nozomi have barely any friends in her life?"
    "¿Cómo puede alguien como Nozomi tener pocos amigos en la vida?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2257
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_631dee4b:

    # s "This must obviously be a part of my programming. And processing that only leads me further into my acceptance of who... no, what I am."
    s "Esto obviamente debe ser parte de mi programación. Y procesarlo solo me lleva a aceptar más a profundidad quién… no, qué soy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2258
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9deeb3ea:

    # "Not to mention what else her mom said to me..."
    "Sin mencionar la otra cosa que me dijo su madre…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2259
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_128e73da:

    # "\"Just... be kind to her, won't you?\""
    "\"Solo... sé amable con ella, ¿sí?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2260
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4231037e:

    # s sleep "So I apologize for questioning your authority, Kyou. You are my programmer after all." with dissolve
    s sleep "Así que me disculpo por cuestionar tu autoridad, Kyou. Eres mi programador, después de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2261
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8e1ce8c2:

    # "I've quieted this voice I've had in my head since I started all this. It hurts my project if I ever have to think of Nozomi and her friends as people."
    "He estado callando esta voz en mi cabeza desde que empecé con todo esto. Mi proyecto se verá dañado si pienso en Nozomi y sus amigas como gente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2262
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8c7fc91f:

    # "But that woman brought that voice right back."
    "Pero esa mujer trajo la voz de vuelta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2267
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0e3e1a0f:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. I'll need to alter your code to get rid of that disobedient human streak in you that caused you to question me in the first place."
    ks "Es correcto, Sayori. Tengo que alterar tu código para deshacerme de esa desobediencia humana que te hizo cuestionarme en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2268
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b628d537:

    # "I need to quiet that voice again."
    "Tengo que callar esa voz otra vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2269
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b2eb4a08:

    # ks "And that's why we're going to my house. I need to do a lot of work on your buggy programming."
    ks "Y es por eso que iremos a mi casa. Tengo mucho trabajo que hacer en tu defectuosa programación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2270
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_495e6482:

    # "I just need to continue immersing myself thinking that these girls aren't human. As if I were doing a little programming on my own mind."
    "Solo tengo que seguir sumergiéndome en el pensamiento de que estas chicas no son humanas. Como si estuviera programando un poco en mi propia mente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2271
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d128a2e7:

    # s neutral_right "I understand." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Entiendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2272
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2b79361c:

    # "I just have to never think of them as human again. I can do that, right?"
    "Todo lo que tengo que hacer es nunca volver a pensar en ellas como humanas. Puedo hacer eso, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2275
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2ee7f1d9:

    # "That turned out to be a productive day of programming."
    "Ese fue un día de programación muy productivo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2278
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11022cfe_1:

    # "Holding my penlight up as I lounge on my bed, I reminisce back to that day this all began; nearly a year ago at the culture festival."
    "Sosteniendo mi linterna en la cama, rememoro el día en que todo empezó; hace casi un año en el festival cultural."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2282
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7ff8e669_1:

    # "I'm barely up and showered before my doorbell rings."
    "Estoy recién levantado y duchado cuando suena el timbre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2286
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9e2fac70:

    # "With a grin, I get the door and find a sweetly-smiling Nozomi there to greet me."
    "Con una sonrisa, abro la puerta y me encuentro a Nozomi saludándome con una dulce expresión en su rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2287
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3eac50b8:

    # "I gotta admit, after she's blanked me for so long, being able to make her come on command is more than a little pleasing."
    "Debo admitir que, después de ser rechazado por ella por tanto tiempo, poder hacerla venir con una orden es más que placentero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2288
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b0c887b1:

    # n "Good morning, Kyou~ May I come in?"
    n "Buenos días, Kyou. ¿Puedo pasar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2289
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e0feb795:

    # "Still grinning, I swing the door fully open and step aside."
    "Sin dejar de sonreír, abro la puerta por completo y me hago a un lado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2290
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fbe5afe8:

    # ks casual smile "By all means. {w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks casual smile "Adelante. {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2296
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_604757d5:

    # "Wh- what the?! {w=0.5}{nw}"
    "¡¿P-pero qué?! {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2301
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_71ea0a28:

    # ks casual sigh "Urrgh..."
    ks casual sigh "Ayyy…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2302
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6fb41186:

    # ks "What... what just happened?"
    ks "¿Qué… qué acaba de pasar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2305
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6cc1b1fc:

    # n "We figured out you hypnotized us, so we decided to confront you about it."
    n "Descubrimos que nos hipnotizaste, así que decidimos enfrentarte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3099
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6564f31e:

    # s "N-Nozomi! Don't tell him anything." with dissolve
    s "¡N-Nozomi! No le digas nada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2308
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3314037f:

    # n "Sorry. I couldn't help myself." with dissolve
    n "Perdón. No pude evitarlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3103
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7fb2e456:

    # "I feel a groan escape my lips as I try to climb off the floor where I find myself, only to feel a weight push sharply into my spine." with dissolve
    "Siento un gruñido escapar de mis labios al intentar levantarme del suelo, para luego sentir un peso presionar bruscamente contra mi columna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3105
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90cb867c:

    # k "A- OWW!" with dissolve
    k "¡A- AUU!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3107
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_05e0636e:

    # h "Don't fuckin' move!" with dissolve
    h "¡Quietecito, cabrón!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2313
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_022357ad:

    # "I struggle, but Hiroko's got me pinned pretty good while I feel a slender set of fingers skim through my pockets." with dissolve
    "Forcejeo, pero Hiroko me tiene muy bien apretado. De pronto siento unos delgados dedos hurgar entre mis bolsillos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3110
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_23b371c0:

    # s "Hmm. I do not know if this means anything, but he had on him his phone and this... looks like a penlight."
    s "Mmm. No sé si esto signifique algo, pero llevaba consigo su teléfono y esto… parece una linterna tipo pluma."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2317
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_75598e6e:

    # n side frown_side "Maybe he used an app on his phone to do it?" with dissolve
    n side frown_side "¿Tal vez lo hizo con una aplicación de su teléfono?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2318
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6bfa75cc:

    # s casual_folded "... He hypnotized the three of us with an app? That is what you're saying?" with dissolve
    s casual_folded "… ¿Nos hipnotizó a las tres con una aplicación? ¿Eso estás diciendo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3116
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7b82a8aa:

    # n sad_side "... Hmm, well I read about it in a comic once."
    n sad_side "... Mmm, pues lo leí una vez en un cómic."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2320
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b0e5ecc6:

    # n sad_closed blush "... Actually, nevermind. That does seem far-fetched." with dissolve
    n sad_closed blush "… ¿Sabes qué?, olvídalo. Eso parece muy descabellado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3120
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cb20c090:

    # h "Just fucking ask him!" with dissolve
    h "¡Solo pregúntenselo, carajo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2322
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_80fc14db:

    # "I grimace as I feel the full weight of this little punk on my back." with vpunch
    "Hago una mueca al sentir todo el peso de esta mocosa en mi espalda." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2352
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fc2c3ae5:

    # "If only I wasn't such a pathetic specimen of a man, I would've thrown her across the room by now." with dissolve
    "Si no fuera un espécimen tan patético de hombre, ya la habría hecho volar al otro lado de la habitación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2325
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_13db1885:

    # h "How'd you do it, dude?"
    h "¿Cómo lo hiciste, viejo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3126
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_df1e6973:

    # k "Agh... y-you're saying I hypnotized you all somehow? Don't be ridiculous!" with dissolve
    k "Ay... ¿d-dicen que las hipnoticé de alguna manera? ¡No digan ridiculeces!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3127
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3a920412:

    # s frown_right "We know, Kyou. Nozomi figured it out."
    s frown_right "Lo sabemos, Kyou. Nozomi lo descifró."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3129
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dafd2e81:

    # k "What?" with dissolve
    k "¿Qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2329
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_56bbc925:

    # "I thought that's what I heard the first time, but... that's impossible."
    "Eso creí escuchar la primera vez, pero... es imposible."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2330
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9280d60e:

    # "They should've forgotten everything."
    "Deberían haberlo olvidado todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2331
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf0015ea:

    # h "DON'T play dumb with us!" with vpunch
    h "¡NO te hagas el tonto con nosotras!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3134
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_915ce3cd:

    # k "Ugh... w-what makes you even think I could do that?"
    k "Ay… ¿qu-qué les hace creer que siquiera podría hacer eso?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2333
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_de5e79cd:

    # n frown "Well, we- {w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    n frown "Pues, nos-{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3139
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf7b394e:

    # n surprised "Mmpth!"
    n surprised "¡Mmnf!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2336
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0e8ba4a0:

    # "Nozomi's answer is abruptly cut off as Sayori claps her hand around Nozomi's lips."
    "La respuesta de Nozomi es cortada abruptamente por la mano de Sayori puesta en sus labios."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2337
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4150aebc:

    # "For a brief moment I wonder if she remembers doing exactly the same thing to her just a couple days ago."
    "Por un breve momento me pregunto si recuerda haberle hecho exactamente lo mismo hace solo un par de días."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3143
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b5396714:

    # s "You really can't help yourself, can you." with dissolve
    s "De verdad no puedes evitarlo, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3145
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d90820d9:

    # s "Anyway, you needn't concern yourself with that, Kyou. What should concern you is whether or not you answer our questions to our satisfaction." with dissolve
    s "En fin, que eso no te preocupe, Kyou. Lo que sí debe preocuparte es si tus respuestas a nuestras preguntas nos satisfacen o no." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3147
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fe58662a:

    # k "And... and why should I? You come into my home and you assault me! I should be asking you to leave!" with dissolve
    k "¿Y… y por qué debería? ¡Entraron a mi casa y me atacaron! ¡Debería estarles pidiendo que se vayan!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3149
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f60eda43:

    # h "We ain't leaving 'till you tell us how you did this shit to us!" with dissolve
    h "¡No nos iremos hasta que nos digas cómo nos hiciste esta mierda!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2342
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ba055846:

    # s "And when we can ensure you are never able to do so again."
    s "Y cómo podemos asegurarnos de que nunca seas capaz de volverlo a hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3152
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4c9962c4:

    # "I scoff at them. How are they gonna do that? By killing me?" with dissolve
    "Me mofo de ellas. ¿Cómo piensan hacer eso? ¿Matándome?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2346
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e2fc18de:

    # "Just then, Nozomi pulls Sayori's hand away from her mouth as they exchange looks." with dissolve
    "Entonces, Nozomi retira la mano de Sayori de su boca e intercambian miradas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2347
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_13e94e2f:

    # n frown "I guess it's not safe for me to be around him right now, so I'm going to check his room." with dissolve
    n frown "Supongo que no es seguro que yo esté junto a él. Mejor iré a revisar su habitación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3156
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bb4164a3:

    # k "Huh, why? What are you going to do?" with dissolve
    k "¿Eh, por qué? ¿Qué vas a hacer?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2349
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c6274b1b:

    # n smile "I'm going to examine your room for clues about how you hypnotized us all." with dissolve
    n smile "Examinaré tu habitación en busca de pistas de cómo nos hipnotizaste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2351
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c32d73b5:

    # n front irritated "Urrrgh..." with dissolve
    n front irritated "Ayyy…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3162
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_795c4bc7:

    # "And with that Nozomi scurries away from me, out of my reach." with dissolve
    "Y dicho eso, Nozomi se escabulle lejos de mi alcance." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3163
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_05d8f72b:

    # s "Well then, Kyou, are you ready to talk?"
    s "¿Y bien, Kyou? ¿Listo para hablar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2357
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a25ab37c:

    # "Dammit, what am I supposed to do?"
    "Maldición, ¿qué se supone que haga?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2358
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6cc69e0e:

    # "Am I really gonna just lie here? Let myself get restrained by a little girl like a fucking wimp?"
    "¿Solo voy a quedarme aquí tirado? ¿Me dejaré restringir por una niñita como un jodido debilucho?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2359
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ae900dc3:

    # "Sure, I'm no alpha male, but I could take Hiroko on if I wanted to."
    "Claro, no soy un macho alfa, pero podría acabar con Hiroko si quisiera."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2360
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d6580434:

    # "Hell, Sayori won't be hard to knock down either. I could take them both on."
    "Diablos, Sayori tampoco sería difícil de derribar. Podría ganarles a ambas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2361
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_74521790:

    # "Then I'd grab my penlight back and put them under before they can do anything about it."
    "Y luego volver a tomar mi linterna y ponerlas en trance antes de que puedan hacer nada al respecto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3170
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9bb99cbf:

    # k "A-AGH!" with vpunch
    k "¡A-AAY!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2363
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b73bb3e:

    # "Bitch behind me is twisting my arm."
    "La perra que tengo detrás me está torciendo el brazo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3173
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8687c11c:

    # h "Fuckin' spill, you piece of shit!" with dissolve
    h "¡Escupe la puta sopa, pedazo de mierda!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3175
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c17337bc:

    # "That's it, I'm gonna..." with dissolve
    "Se acabó, voy a…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3181
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b316c44a:

    # k "A-ALRIGHT! Just let go of me, will you?"
    k "¡E-ESTÁ BIEN! Solo suéltame, ¿quieres?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3183
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_621a0a3f:

    # h "Ain't happening. Tell us what you did!" with dissolve
    h "Eso no pasará. ¡Dinos lo que hiciste!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2370
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_85c1bd11:

    # "Reason wins out, I guess. I'll talk a bit while I try to figure out what went wrong."
    "Más vale razonar, supongo. Hablaré un poco mientras intento averiguar qué salió mal."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3186
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_922543cb:

    # k "O-okay, so..." with dissolve
    k "M-muy bien, pues…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2372
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a5faf85a:

    # "Did they shake off their mental conditioning somehow? Is that how they found out?"
    "¿Lograron quitarse su acondicionamiento mental? ¿Así fue cómo lo descubrieron? "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3188
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a4b82f01:

    # k "When me and Nozomi were cleaning the classroom by ourselves. That's when I hypnotized her."
    k "Cuando Nozomi y yo estábamos limpiando el salón a solas. Ahí fue cuando la hipnoticé."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2374
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fbed90e9:

    # "But then... No, it seems Nozomi is still responsive to the commands I sent her last night."
    "Pero entonces… No, parece que Nozomi sigue respondiendo a las órdenes que le envié anoche."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2375
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3ed9b4a1:

    # s "And how did you accomplish that, Kyou?"
    s "¿Y cómo lograste eso, Kyou?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2376
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a0a02f24:

    # "So then..."
    "Entonces…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3192
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_07b2cd0f:

    # k "I just, like, got her to stare at my finger and encouraged her to go into a trance for me."
    k "Yo solo, pues, la hice mirar mis dedos y conseguí ponerla en estado de trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2378
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_497d0562:

    # "Okay, I can figure out how they found out later. What's important is that if Nozomi hasn't shaken off the mental conditioning that I gave her..."
    "Muy bien, puedo averiguar cómo lo descubrieron después. Lo que importa es que Nozomi no se ha quitado el acondicionamiento que le di…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2379
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3d030eb4:

    # "... Then I'm gonna bet these two haven't either."
    "… Entonces apuesto a que estas dos tampoco."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2380
