    # "I gotta say, even with what I've been able to do with them these past few days, I wasn't convinced that would work."
    "He de decir que, aun con todo lo que he sido capaz de hacer con ellas estos últimos días, no estaba convencido de que funcionaría."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2427
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1d5bf47e:

    # "But as I grin and pick myself up off the floor, watching the two of them as they stand in front of me with such distant expressions..."
    "Pero al sonreír y levantarme del suelo, viéndolas a las dos de pie ante mí con las miradas perdidas…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2428
