    # ks frown "Nozomi, I think that's enough! It's about time you listen- {w=0.8}{nw}"
    ks frown "¡Nozomi, creo que ya es suficiente! Ahora tienes que escuchar- {w=0.8}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2483
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d908bbe8:

    # n "DON'T LEAVE ME ALONE WITH HIM!" with shake
    n "¡NO ME DEJEN SOLA CON ÉL!" with shake

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2486
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a9fb6d48:

    # h "W-wha?!" with dissolve
    h "¡¿Qu- qué?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2487
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cdbf8b23:

    # s "Nozomi. What is..."
    s "Nozomi. ¿Qué está…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2488
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb6e33a2:

    # "Shit."
    "Mierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2489
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c2ac4cec:

    # n angry "NOW! STOP HIM!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡AHORA! ¡DETÉNGANLO!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2490
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1fd0159f:

    # ks angry "Wait, NO! I SAID LISTEN AND-{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks angry "¡Esperen, NO! ¡TIENEN QUE ESCUCHAR Y-{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2492
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_28a7d324:

    # h casual_armup furious "SHUT THE FUCK UP!{w=0.8}{nw}" with shake
    h casual_armup furious "¡CIERRA LA PUTA BOCA!{w=0.8}{nw}" with shake

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2497
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e54ed573:

    # "Oh... oh man, I feel like I've been kicked in every conceivable part of the human body."
    "Oh… oh, Dios, siento que he sido pateado en cada parte concebible del cuerpo humano."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2498
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_66772809:

    # "Everything hurts..."
    "Me duele todo…"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2512
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_09ec4b84:

    # "And when the dust settles I find myself once again on the floor with three girls towering above me."
    "Y cuando se dispersa el polvo, me doy cuenta de que estoy una vez más en el suelo, con las tres chicas encima de mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2513
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4dd23a30:

    # "They're... crying in a huddle?"
    "Están… ¿están llorando abrazadas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2514
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90029674:

    # s "I never felt anything like it, Nozomi. He, h-he was saying something to us and it all started to feel like a dream."
    s "Nunca había sentido algo así, Nozomi. Nos, n-nos estaba diciendo algo y todo se empezó a sentir como un sueño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2515
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ee67465d:

    # h "Yeah, right? That was s-so fuckin' scary! I couldn't do ANYTHING!"
    h "Es cierto. ¡Qué puto m-miedo! ¡No pude hacer NADA!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2516
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_82a69147:

    # n "I-I know, but it's okay. We're going to be okay!"
    n "L-lo sé, pero está bien. ¡Vamos a estar bien! "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2517
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1913b6f5:

    # "They look so pathetic. They didn't even get hurt; I'm the one lying bruised on the floor."
    "Se ven tan patéticas. Ni siquiera salieron heridas; yo soy el que está magullado en el suelo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2518
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b428c15f:

    # "And while they're huddled like that I don't know if they've realized I've come to."
    "Y estando así abrazadas, no sé si se dieron cuenta de que me reincorporé."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2519
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_33873b17:

    # "They might have come out of their tranced states now, but I bet even now I can drop them back with a few careful words..."
    "Habrán salido de su estado de trance de momento, pero apuesto a que incluso ahora puedo hacerlas caer con unas cuantas palabras..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2520
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_55c42e39:

    # k "Mm.. mmpth?"
    k "Mm... ¿mmnf?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2521
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4c04cdea:

    # "Wait, my lips aren't moving."
    "Espera, mis labios no se mueven."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2525
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_088fb977:

    # "And as I struggle to work my mouth I notice the girls have turned their attention to me." with dissolve
    "Y luchando por hacer mi boca funcionar, noto que las chicas han vuelto su atención hacia mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2526
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3230b218:

    # n "W-we'll make sure he can't hurt us anymore."
    n "N-nos aseguraremos de que no pueda volver a hacernos daño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2527
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6d506333:

    # "It's coming back to me now, about the fight we just had. Involving a three girl pile-on and a shitload of duct tape that they must have swiped from the kitchen."
    "Ya me estoy acordando. Lo que sucedió en la pelea. Recuerdo algo que involucra a tres chicas apiladas y mucha cinta adhesiva seguro sacaron de la cocina."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2528
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f5ddbeee:

    # "How much of the fucking stuff did they use on me? Shit."
    "¿Cuánto de está mierda usaron en mí? Carajo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2533
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fae118d1:

    # "I can barely move down here, and it's all I can do to try sitting up on the floor as the girls break off their embrace to watch me carefully like I'm some caged animal."
    "Apenas me puedo mover aquí abajo, y lucho por sentarme en el suelo mientras las chicas se sueltan para mirarme cuidadosamente cual animal enjaulado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2536
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f24a3267:

    # "Wiping her eyes with one hand, Nozomi crouches down beside me. And that's when I notice what's in her other hand..."
    "Limpiando sus ojos con una mano, Nozomi se agacha junto a mí. Y entonces me doy cuenta de lo que lleva en la otra mano..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2581
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8b4f4684:

    # n "What's with that look, Kyou? It's just a harmless penlight isn't it?"
    n "¿A qué viene esa mirada, Kyou? Es una pluma linterna inofensiva, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2546
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e23a5acb:

    # n "Anyone would think it was dangerous, the way you're flinching at it."
    n "Cualquiera creería que es peligrosa por la forma en la que te estremece."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2548
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_04b72b90:

    # "Goddammit. I gotta figure a way out of this fast."
    "Maldita sea. Debo pensar cómo salir de aquí rápido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2584
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ec851c4c:

    # h "What're we gonna do about him?"
    h "¿Qué harás con él?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2550
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f70cfc02:

    # s "We could destroy that penlight, but..."
    s "Podríamos destruir esa linterna, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2551
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_13bc2801:

    # n "But you'll probably make a new one, won't you, Kyou?"
    n "Pero probablemente harás una nueva, ¿no es así, Kyou?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2552
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_32186e67:

    # "I shoot her a glare. To think I trusted her and her tears just now... I thought she was better than that."
    "Le arrojo una mirada. Y pensar que confié en ella y en sus lágrimas... Creí que era mejor que eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2553
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d01ee62d:

    # "But yeah. I mean, of COURSE I'd make a new one!"
    "Pero sí. ¡Por SUPUESTO que haría una nueva!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2554
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0b046481:

    # "Even if they destroy it and the schematics I left on my computer I know the gist of what I did before."
    "Aunque destruyeran los esquemas que dejé en mi computadora, sé los pasos que seguí para llegar a ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2555
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9bae6277:

    # "I could try again..."
    "Podría intentarlo de nuevo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2591
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_37e9a420:

    # h "Shit. Just looking at him's makin' me feel he's in my head again."
    h "Coño. Tan solo mirarlo me hace sentir que está en mi cabeza."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2593
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d5955c44:

    # h "Nozo, make him stop, you gotta make him stop." with dissolve
    h "Nozo, haz que pare, tienes que hacer que pare." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2594
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_48615961:

    # n "There's a way, but... are we going to be okay with it?"
    n "Hay una forma, pero... ¿estamos dispuestas a ello?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2559
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dee18041:

    # s concerned "You mean..." with dissolve
    s concerned "Te refieres a..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2560
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8a5d1d4d:

    # "No, come on, there's gotta be a way out of this tape. If I can just..."
    "No, vamos, tiene que haber una forma de liberarme de esta cinta. Si tan solo pudiera..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2598
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a7c80a73:

    # h "Shit, how else are we 'sposed to stop him?"
    h "Puta madre, ¿de qué otra forma lo vamos a detener?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2600
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_65cc370a:

    # h "No one else's gonna believe any of this shit if we tell 'em. S-so what, we just run and hope he never pulls this shit again?" with dissolve
    h "Nadie nos creerá un carajo. ¿Y qué? ¿Vamos a correr y esperar que nunca vuelva a hacer esta mierda?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2563
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_919925dd:

    # h "We just gonna live in fear of this dude the rest of our lives? 'Cuz I ain't having it!"
    h "¿Vamos a vivir con miedo de este tipo por el resto de nuestras vidas? ¡Porque yo no pienso hacer eso!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2603
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_03607377:

    # h "I don't wanna live like that! It ain't fair!"
    h "¡No quiero vivir así! ¡No es justo!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2605
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d37b24dc:

    # s "I... don't disagree. He has presented us with a unique and frightening quandary." with dissolve
    s "Yo... no discrepo. Nos está presentando una aterradora incertidumbre como ninguna otra." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2567
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_48b26bc1:

    # "Ugh, just listening to these three debate what to do with me like this. It's humiliating."
    "Aj, el solo escuchar a estas tres debatir qué hacer conmigo. Es humillante."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2568
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_574823ed:

    # "But I think I felt something give. Just a little more, maybe..."
    "Pero creo que estoy por romper algo. Solo un poco más, tal vez..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2569
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a5d82957:

    # s concerned "But is it even an option for us? You seem to think you can do this, Nozomi." with dissolve
    s concerned "¿Pero es siquiera una opción para nosotras? Pareces creer poder hacer esto, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2570
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6863bedf:

    # s "It can be done?"
    s "¿Es posible?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2611
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_aa533b65:

    # n "I don't know. But it shouldn't have been possible for him to do what he did to us, so..." with dissolve
    n "No lo sé. Pero lo que nos hizo no debería ser posible, así que…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2575
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_959e28ed:

    # n frown "I think it's worth it to try." with dissolve
    n frown "Creo que vale la pena intentarlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2615
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_facb2534:

    # "Shit, no! Get that away from me!" with dissolve
    "¡Mierda, no! ¡Aléjate de mí!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2578
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_383f3606:

    # k "M-MMTH!"
    k "¡M-MMF!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2580
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_47058074:

    # n "Don't worry, Kyou. You know I won't hurt you."
    n "No te preocupes, Kyou. Sabes que no te haré daño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2620
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_316b2950:

    # "No! Bitch, you are NOT taking this away from me!"
    "¡No! ¡NO me vas a quitar esto, perra!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2584
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_59e06d73:

    # "Like you even know how to use that thing in your hand..."
    "Como si supieras usar lo que tienes en las manos..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2586
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4a8ca47e:

    # n "Far from it, Kyou. I mean, for you to go through with all of this? I think... I think you're in a lot of pain."
    n "Todo lo contrario, Kyou. Digo, mira por lo que estás pasando. Creo... creo que estás sufriendo mucho. "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2588
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b5358df4:

    # k "Mmpth."
    k "Mmpt."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2589
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4aab8476:

    # "You think waving that light in my face is all it takes, and now you're pitying me? Fuck you. Just fuck you."
    "¿Crees que sacudirme esa luz en la cara es todo lo que hay que hacer? ¿Y ahora me compadeces? Jódete. Vete a la mierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2628
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_77ea3bb4:

    # n "And maybe I can help, Kyou. Just as long as you keep staring up at this light as you have been."
    n "Y tal vez pueda ayudarte, Kyou. Solo sígueme y no dejes de mirar esta luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2594
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_77dd5ea0:

    # "... Wait, why AM I staring at the light?"
    "... Espera, ¿por qué ESTOY mirando la luz?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2633
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b94885ee:

    # n "It's okay if you didn't notice. We both know how irresistible this light is by now, don't we?"
    n "Está bien si no te diste cuenta. A estas alturas ambos sabemos lo irresistible que es la luz, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2598
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5ad0858c:

    # "And her voice... she doesn't even sound angry. Just sort of... wistful."
    "Y su voz... ni siquiera suena enojada. Más bien... melancólica."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2599
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_41a4970b:

    # n "So it's only natural if you're unable to look away; seeing those patterns form in your eyes as you continue to stare so diligently."
    n "Por lo que es natural que no puedas desviar la mirada; viendo esos patrones formarse en tus ojos, mirándolos con deleite."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2601
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ceb3c4df:

    # "It's almost... nice..."
    "Es casi... agradable..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2602
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0b80a4f8:

    # n "That's right, Kyou. We all know how much you like to stare."
    n "Eso es, Kyou. Todos sabemos lo mucho que te gusta mirar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2604
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ee000cc0:

    # "... Wait, what's going on?"
    "... Espera, ¿qué está pasando?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2605
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_23c8c7fe:

    # n "And it's fine. Stare as much as you like."
    n "Y está bien. Mira tanto como quieras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2607
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b23fd26:

    # n "It's such a normal thing to do under the circumstances, right? We've all done it."
    n "Es normal hacerlo en estas circunstancias, ¿cierto? Todos lo hemos hecho."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2609
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bb12b7b9:

    # "Right. I was staring at that light. Just staring normally..."
    "Cierto. Estaba mirando la luz. Eso es... normal..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2610
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8b103b2b:

    # n "So don't worry, Kyou. Stare all you want. Relax all you want..."
    n "Así que no te preocupes, Kyou. Mira tanto como quieras. Relájate tanto como quieras..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2615
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_87319ceb:

    # n "Drift all you want... That's it."
    n "Déjate llevar tanto como quieras... Eso es."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2619
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9c9b79c8:

    # n "Just letting yourself drop into a nice, calm state for us. Letting your eyes close as they are."
    n "Déjate caer a un agradable y calmado estado. Deja que tus ojos se cierren."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2623
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_77713c4d:

    # n "That's right, Kyou. It's going to be okay."
    n "Eso es, Kyou. Todo va a estar bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2627
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2601dc29:

    # n "So you can let those eyes close for me now."
    n "Puedes dejar que esos ojos se cierren."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2630
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90143046:

    # n "I'll take care of everything..."
    n "Yo me encargaré de todo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2635
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_df0e3c99:

    # "As another school day draws to a close, I gather my things and ponder."
    "Otro día de escuela llega a su fin, y yo guardo mis cosas reflexionando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2643
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_902812cb:

    # h "Fuckin' finally. Now I'm gonna blow off tennis club and punch the walls in my room." with dissolve
    h "Carajo, por fin. Ahora voy a escaparme del club de tenis y golpear las paredes de mi habitación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2644
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_38993b6c:

    # s concerned "I am so sorry about yesterday. It wasn't your fault." with dissolve
    s concerned "Lamento lo de ayer. No fue tu culpa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2645
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cff5baf3:

    # h neutral_side "I can't stop thinking about it, y'know? That shit really got in my head." with dissolve
    h neutral_side "No puedo dejar de pensar en eso, ¿sabes? Esa mierda está metida en mi cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2646
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4686da7f:

    # "What on earth was I doing these last few months?"
    "¿Qué rayos estuve haciendo los últimos meses?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2647
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d97b4ea6:

    # h sad_side "I'll never forgive that motherfucker." with dissolve
    h sad_side "Nunca perdonaré a ese hijo de puta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2648
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b76f5911:

    # s uniform_folded "I can only encourage you to keep going. You have a lot of potential, anyone can see that." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "Solo puedo alentarte a seguir adelante. Tienes mucho potencial, eso todos pueden verlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2649
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_60af7f35:

    # h "Yeah... I mean, what else am I 'sposed to do?"
    h "Sí... digo, ¿qué más se supone que haga?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2653
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_00be5a05:

    # n "Is everything okay?" with dissolve
    n "¿Todo en orden?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2655
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_53c9550f:

    # h "Nah." with dissolve
    h "Nah." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2658
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_68e06012:

    # n sad_side "I'm so sorry, Hiroko. I got you mixed up in all of this." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Lo lamento tanto, Hiroko. Terminé involucrándote en todo esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2659
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_03f65644:

    # h "No, it ain't your fault. There's only one person whose fault this is and he's..."
    h "No, no es tu culpa. Solo hay una persona a quien culpar y es..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2660
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d55a7882:

    # "I guess I'd better head home..."
    "Supongo que mejor ya me voy a casa..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2661
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d6af05fb:

    # h sleep "Just tell me it ain't happening again." with dissolve
    h sleep "Solo dime que no volverá a pasar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2662
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e791c729:

    # n frown_side "It won't. We destroyed it and everything about it that we could find. Please try not to worry." with dissolve
    n frown_side "No volverá a pasar. La destruimos y todo lo que pudimos encontrar relacionado a ella. Por favor, trata de no preocuparte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2664
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6359eea1:

    # h angry "{size=16}Fuck, here he comes.{/size}" with dissolve
    h angry "{size=16}Mierda, ahí viene. {/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2666
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_09214f0b:

    # ks neutral "Hm?" with dissolve
    ks neutral "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2667
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_21ed6af1:

    # "As I walk towards the door, three girls look to me and... was that pink-haired girl talking about me?"
    "Mientras camino a la puerta, tres chicas voltean a verme y... ¿la pelirrosa estaba hablando de mí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2668
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ff263de2:

    # n surprised "A-ah, it's nothing. She's just having a bad day, that's all." with dissolve
    n surprised "A-ah, no es nada. Solo está teniendo un mal día, eso es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2669
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7ba23ccf:

    # h irritated "Yeah... Just a bad day." with dissolve
    h irritated "Sí… solo un mal día." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2670
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_84d20e40:

    # "I look over the three of them, and... wait, are these girls in my class?"
    "Las miro a las tres y... espera, ¿estas chicas están en mi clase?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2672
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ab56a9ef:

    # "They must be but, wow, how do I not know them by now? Especially this pink-haired girl. She really stands out." with dissolve
    "Tienen que, pero, guau, ¿cómo es que aún no las conozco? Sobre todo a la pelirrosa. En serio destaca." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2673
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_70f5b278:

    # "I think our brown-haired class rep called her Hiyoko? I wonder what they were talking about."
    "Creo que nuestra representante de clase castaña la llamó... ¿Hiyoko? Me pregunto de qué estaba hablando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2674
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_db476b2d:

    # s "Is he... is he just going to stand there, do you think?"
    s "¿Creen que… creen que solo se quede ahí parado?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2675
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d6f7de33:

    # "Maybe she just transferred here and I missed it?"
    "¿Tal vez la acaban de transferir y no me enteré?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2676
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_17ced8a2:

    # h angry "Wh-what're you staring at?" with dissolve
    h angry "¿Qu- qué estás mirando?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2677
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_250edb9a:

    # ks surprised "H-huh? Oh..."
    ks surprised "¿E-eh? Oh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2678
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_726fbbf0:

    # "Shit, I'm bothering them. Maybe I'm being creepy again."
    "Mierda. Las estoy molestando. Tal vez estoy siendo espeluznante otra vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2679
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a6e4738a:

    # "I should just excuse myself and leave."
    "Será mejor que me excuse y me vaya."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2680
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9d76d6b8:

    # ks sigh "Sorry. I'll get out of your hair."
    ks sigh "Lo siento. Las dejaré solas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2681
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_42001e78:

    # "As I turn to head out the door, I hear the pink-haired girl suck in a breath."
    "Me doy la vuelta para caminar hacia la puerta y escucho a la pelirrosa tomar aire."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2682
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_77a92e66:

    # h "Y-yeah... go on, get outta here."
    h "S-sí... eso, largo de aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2685
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cfe073e9:

    # n "Uh, Kyou? Do you have a moment?"
    n "Eh, ¿Kyou? ¿Tienes un momento?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2686
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6dffe5c4:

    # ks surprised "Huh?"
    ks surprised "¿Eh?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2688
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9a86f7ea:

    # "Just as I'm heading out I realize our class rep is wanting me for something."
    "En cuanto estoy por salir, descubro que nuestra representante me quiere para algo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2689
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0a016ec8:

    # "Wish I knew what her name was."
    "Ojalá supiera su nombre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2690
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_926c3f4f:

    # "I guess I could ask, but something tells me I really shouldn't bother her."
    "Supongo que podría preguntar, pero algo me dice que en serio no debería molestarla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2691
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_35fc5768:

    # n "It's just... well, how was your weekend?"
    n "Es solo que... bueno, ¿cómo estuvo tu fin de semana?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2692
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_014b4731:

    # ks frown "My... weekend?"
    ks frown "Mi... ¿fin de semana?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2693
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8af423c8:

    # "Ugh, what do I tell her? I have no... Oh wait, I remember now."
    "Ay, ¿qué le digo? No me... Oh, espera, ya recuerdo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2694
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4b8814ee:

    # ks smile "It was a perfectly normal and uneventful weekend."
    ks smile "Fue un fin de semana perfectamente normal y sin eventos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2696
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_df9f8f6d:

    # "As lame as that answer was, it seems to satisfy her." with dissolve
    "Por tonta que sea esa respuesta, parece satisfacerla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2697
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a68bde4e:

    # n "That's great. Sorry, I won't hold you up any longer; have a nice evening."
    n "Eso es grandioso. Lo siento, ya no te retendré; ten una buena tarde."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2698
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3aef7306:

    # ks "Yeah, you too uhh..."
    ks "Sí, igual tú, emm..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2700
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_59ee01a0:

    # "I trail off as she walks away. Shit, how do I not know this girl's name?"
    "Me detengo en cuanto se va. Mierda, ¿cómo es que no sé el nombre de esa chica?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2702
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a8b889b1:

    # "Oh well. As long as I don't bother her, it's fine."
    "OH, bueno. Siempre y cuando no la moleste, está bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2759
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_efd361b7:

    # "No. I can't bear to see her like this any longer."
    "No, ya no puedo soportar verla así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2760
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e703129e:

    # ks smile "Nozomi, I promise. Once you listen and obey, I'll let you say whatever you want."
    ks smile "Nozomi, te lo prometo. Solo debes escuchar y obedecer, y te dejaré decir lo que quieras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2761
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e9ce1bc6:

    # n "K-Kyou, please."
    n "K-Kyou, por favor."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2762
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7e28a579:

    # "Resting my hands on the shoulders of the other girls, I smile as I continue to speak."
    "Poniendo mis manos en los hombros de las otras, sonrío y sigo hablando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2763
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7f4e72a1:

    # ks "Let's say it together, girls. \"Listen and obey\"."
    ks "Todas juntas, chicas. \"Escuchar y obedecer\"."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2767
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2770
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf3d2cc2:

    # n surprised "L-listen and..." with dissolve
    n surprised "E-escuchar y..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2771
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a2926825:

    # ks "That's right, girls. Feeling so good, so comfortable, so right about falling deeper for me."
    ks "Eso es, chicas. Se siente tan bien, tan cómodo, tan correcto caer profundo para mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2772
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_316a5814:

    # ks "So let's say it again, girls: \"Listen and obey\"."
    ks "Díganlo una vez más, chicas: \"Escuchar y obedecer\"."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2777
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd_1:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2781
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1e57a05c:

    # "My smile widens as I notice Nozomi absent-mindedly following suit with the others. Any chance she may have had of resisting already lost in her own vacant whisper." with dissolve
    "Mi sonrisa crece al oír que Nozomi al unísono con las otras sin pensar. Cualquier oportunidad que haya tenido de resistir se ha perdido en sus propios susurros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2782
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d3d13f34:

    # ks "Allowing yourselves to remember fully how perfectly natural it is for you to be in this deep, obedient state of trance."
    ks "Recuerden lo perfectamente natural que es estar en este profundo y obediente estado de trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2783
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_526c8d52:

    # ks "All your conscious thoughts, cares, and worries effortlessly drifting far away, girls, as you repeat for me one more time: Listen and obey."
    ks "Todos sus pensamientos conscientes, angustias y preocupaciones se van, chicas, al repetir una vez más para mí: Escuchar y obedecer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2787
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd_2:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2791
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7b616991:

    # "As they all intone blankly, I breathe out a sigh that I've been holding for a while." with dissolve
    "Escuchándolas entonar inexpresivamente, dejo salir un suspiro que estuve sosteniendo por un rato." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2792
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_126fb8a8:

    # "The pain in my bruised back and arms reminding me how close I came to losing it all."
    "El dolor en mis magullados brazos y espalda me recuerda lo cerca que estuve de perderlo todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2793
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_79a053c2:

    # "I'll have to make sure they'll never get a chance to stop me again."
    "Tengo que asegurarme de que nunca vuelvan a tener oportunidad de detenerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2794
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1b56cd48:

    # ks "Good girls. Your minds becoming so blank, so free of thought, and that's perfectly okay. They won't need to stay blank for long."
    ks "Buenas chicas. Sus mentes están tan vacías, tan libres de pensamiento, y eso está perfectamente bien. No tendrán que estar en blanco por mucho tiempo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2795
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f1fdf003:

    # ks "In a moment, I will tell you of some new thoughts for your minds to accept as if they were your own."
    ks "En un momento les daré algunos pensamientos nuevos que aceptarán como si fueran propios."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2796
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ff8b9dc8:

    # ks "And you will find it so easy, so automatic, to accept them as your own thoughts, because of how free of thought you are now."
    ks "Y será tan fácil y tan automático aceptarlos como sus propios pensamientos, gracias a lo libres de pensamiento que están ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2797
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d1f4ee62:

    # "I pause a moment to look over each of them carefully as they as they stare vacantly back at me. They look every bit as blank as I describe."
    "Hago una pausa para observar cuidadosamente a cada una con sus miradas perdidas. Parecen estar en blanco, tal como describo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2798
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_db5c8ef3:

    # "What I have in mind should work. After everything, there's no reason why it wouldn't."
    "Lo que tengo en mente debería funcionar. Después de todo, no tendría por qué no."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2799
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b0c0b55e:

    # ks "So here is your first thought, girls... you fully accept and cherish the fact that I hypnotized you into my service as my personal spies."
    ks "Estos son sus primeros pensamientos, chicas... aceptarán y apreciarán el hecho de que las hipnoticé para servirme como mis espías personales."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2800
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_952aafa9:

    # ks "Any objections you might have had to this in the past are mere disagreements that you have completely moved on from."
    ks "Cualquier objeción que hayan tenido en el pasado son meros desacuerdos que ya han superado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2802
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b02971f9:

    # "I mean, why am I leaving so much to chance now? Controlling them so covertly like I have been?"
    "Digo, ¿por qué estoy dejando tanto en manos de la suerte? ¿Controlarlas tan en cubierto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2803
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b1f84bba:

    # ks "So now your first priority, always, is to gather information while under the guise of being ordinary high school students."
    ks "Por lo que ahora, su primera prioridad, siempre, es recopilar información bajo la fachada de ser estudiantes de preparatoria ordinarias."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2806
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_93831884:

    # "This past week's shown me just how deep a level of access I've attained to their minds. To their realities."
    "Esta semana me ha mostrado cuánto acceso tengo a sus mentes. A sus realidades."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2807
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_427f79ce:

    # ks "When you learn something new, your first thought is always \"How will this information benefit Kyou Koyama?\""
    ks "Cuando aprendan algo nuevo, lo primero que piensen siempre será \"¿Cómo puede esta información beneficiar a Kyou Koayama?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2808
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8fc3bdb0:

    # "So why not shape their realities such that they won't even think to stop me? Even ENJOY helping me in my goals?"
    "¿Por qué no reformar sus realidades de tal forma que ni siquiera piensen en detenerme? ¿Que incluso DISFRUTEN ayudarme a cumplir mis metas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2809
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90254b98:

    # ks "And nothing brings you more pleasure than sharing your information with me."
    ks "Y nada les trae más placer que compartir su información conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2815
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_087419cd:

    # ks "Do you understand, girls?"
    ks "¿Comprenden, chicas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2819
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_94eb954e:

    # multi "Yes..." with dissolve
    multi "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2823
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b2c7901:

    # ks "Good. Now, in a few moments I'm going to tap you on your nose, and when you feel the tap, count slowly to three in your head and return to wakefulness." with dissolve
    ks "Bien. Y ahora, en unos momentos, voy a tocar sus narices, y cuando sientan mi dedo, contarán lentamente hasta tres en su cabeza y volverán a despertar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2824
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_613f36b7:

    # ks "Returning to wakefulness and fully accepting everything you were told."
    ks "Despertarán una vez más aceptando completamente todo lo que les dije."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2826
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_21735481:

    # "I leave a moment for my words to sink in, then gingerly tap my fingertip against the bridge of Nozomi's nose."
    "Espero un momento para dejarlas asimilar mis palabras, luego pongo cautelosamente la yema de mi dedo en la punta de la nariz de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2827
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1265bec2:

    # "Let's see how she responds to this..."
    "Veamos cómo responde a eso..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2828
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d1f12924:

    # n neutral "..." with dissolve
    n neutral "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2829
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7402a596:

    # ks "Welcome back, Nozomi."
    ks "Bienvenida de vuelta, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2831
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a5296671:

    # "I can see the focus return to Nozomi's eyes as she comes to, smiling as she registers my voice."
    "Puedo ver el foco regresar a los ojos de Nozomi mientras vuelve en sí, sonriendo al reconocer mi voz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2832
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2d5647b9:

    # n smile "Ah, thanks. I'm still feeling a little disoriented~" with dissolve
    n smile "Ah, gracias. Aún me siento un poco desorientada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2833
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5aa14420:

    # "I smile back, encouraged. Although I'm confident I have nothing to worry about, I should still test her response before I wake the others."
    "Animado, le devuelvo la sonrisa. Aunque confío en que no tengo nada de qué preocuparme, debería probar su respuesta antes de despertar a las otras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2834
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d0637aad:

    # ks "I hope you're feeling better after your little freakout just now."
    ks "Espero que te sientas mejor luego de tu pánico de hace un momento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2835
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5c6d416e:

    # "Nozomi giggles quietly."
    "Nozomi se ríe silenciosamente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2836
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_af9e7512:

    # n happy "Of course~ Looking back, I feel kinda silly making so much fuss." with dissolve
    n happy "Por supuesto. En retrospectiva, me siento un poco tonta por armar tanto alboroto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2837
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2101067d:

    # n smile "So I want to assure you, I'm completely happy with our working relationship." with dissolve
    n smile "Así que quiero asegurarte que estoy completamente feliz con nuestra relación de trabajo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2838
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_586261a4:

    # "Her gaze turns to her two friends, still standing entranced in the middle of the room."
    "Vuelve su mirada a sus dos amigas que siguen en trance en medio de la habitación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2839
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_64211e38:

    # n pout_left "Aren't you going to wake them up?" with dissolve
    n pout_left "¿No las vas a despertar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2840
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_65d5577a:

    # ks "In a minute. I just wanted to make sure you were on board with all this first."
    ks "En un minuto. Primero quería asegurarme de contar contigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2841
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6b925503:

    # ks "I mean, what I'm asking you to do, going behind people's backs and informing on them for me..."
    ks "Digo, lo que te estoy pidiendo, ir detrás de la gente y reunir información para mí..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2842
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a4c31481:

    # ks "It's a big ask."
    ks "Es una gran petición."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2843
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_65f9db1b:

    # "Nozomi gives a determined nod."
    "Nozomi asiente determinada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2844
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_510a2e13:

    # n frown "I understand, but I want to do this for you, Kyou. It feels right." with dissolve
    n frown "Lo entiendo, pero quiero hacerlo por ti, Kyou. Siento que es lo correcto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2845
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bec28973:

    # n "And I know my friends will want to do their part, too."
    n "Y sé que mis amigas también querrán hacer su parte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2846
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e508d994:

    # "I look into her eyes, her face, anywhere she might exhibit a tell that she might be trying to pull the wool over my eyes."
    "Observo sus ojos, su rostro, cualquier parte que pueda dar algún vestigio de estarme tomando el pelo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2847
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4296c4e9:

    # "But there's none that I can see."
    "Pero no veo nada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2849
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a36356d:

    # "Satisfied, I turn to one of the others and bring my finger up to tap the tip of their nose..."
    "Satisfecho, me acerco a una de las otras y alzo mi dedo para tocar la punta de su nariz..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2858
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0cc8be34:

    # "Never in my wildest dreams did I imagine that watching Nozomi up on that stage would lead to her and her friends becoming my devoted fangirls."
    "Ni en mis más salvajes sueños habría imaginado que ver a Nozomi en ese escenario la llevaría a ella y a sus amigas a convertirse en mis devotas fanáticas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2860
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ae813362:

    # "Never in my wildest dreams did I imagine that watching Nozomi up on that stage would lead to me discovering that she and her friends were actually [hypno6]s."
    "Ni en mis más salvajes sueños habría imaginado que ver a Nozomi en ese escenario me llevaría a descubrir que ella y sus amigas eran de hecho [hypno6!t!l]s."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2861
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3e9f18d7:

    # "Let alone that I'd be able to hack them for my own study."
    "Ni mucho menos que podría hackearlas para mis estudios."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2862
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_70609347:

    # "Man, for the first time in years... life is actually good."
    "Cielos, por primera vez en años... la vida es buena."

# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-07-28 19:33

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1583
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_57d9c77c:

    # "As she struggles to think of more ways to appease me, tears well in her eyes in frustration as she throws herself to the floor out of sheer desperation."
    "Mientras se esfuerza por pensar en más maneras de apaciguarme, lágrimas brotan se sus ojos con frustración y se arroja al suelo envuelta en la desesperación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1710
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_175e1760:

    # "After our intense session last night, Nozomi's behavioural programming should be even more airtight than Hiroko's."
    "Después de nuestra intensa sesión de anoche, la programación del comportamiento de Nozomi debería estar incluso mejor que la de Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1727
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6e8cdfa4:

    # h sleeptalk_concerned "Sorry, Kyou, it's just that Sayori's still my friend." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk_concerned "Lo siento, Kyou, es que Sayori sigue siendo mi amiga." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1729
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bb9e80fd:

    # n "No, Kyou. I wasn't programmed to have an opinion on this matter."
    n "No, Kyou. No fui programada para tener una opinión de este asunto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1736
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3c2280a9:

    # ks "And a [hypno6] has no concerns of [p_their] own, besides what [p_their] programmer has given her. [hypno3]."
    ks "Y un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] no tiene preocupaciones propias, solo las que le ha dado su programador. [hypno3!t]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1737
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_41207cb8:

    # h entranced_talk "[hypno2]." with dissolve
    h entranced_talk "[hypno2!t]." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1969
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7e7ac089:

    # "Nozomi nods and the [hypno6] turns to lead me to [p_their] assigned bedroom, maintaining [p_their] neutral detached demeanor and walking with precise, measured steps."
    "Nozomi asiente, y [el] [hypno6!t!l] se da la vuelta para dirigirme a su habitación asignada, manteniendo su conducta neutral y dando pasos precisos y mesurados."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1983
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1c4befd4:

    # "Looking over Nozomi's stiffened form with satisfaction, I then spare a look at [p_their] room."
    "Después de observar satisfecho a Nozomi en su rígido estado, le echo un vistazo a su habitación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1984
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_29c3e24e:

    # ks casual angry "The fuck?! This place is a mess."
    ks casual angry "¡¿Qué mierda?! Este lugar es un desastre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1985
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dce6306c:

    # "... Honestly, with how put-together Nozomi seemed while posing as a human, this is a serious look behind the curtain."
    "... Honestamente, con lo organizada que Nozomi parecía ser al hacerse pasar por humana, me sorprende hallar esto tras bambalinas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1986
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_20902d0f:

    # ks sigh "No girl should be living like this..."
    ks sigh "Ninguna chica debería vivir así..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1987
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_edafefb0:

    # "Ugh, no. I can't let myself get distracted. Sayori's gonna be on her way here as I speak. I can fix Nozomi's human code later."
    "Aj, no. No puedo distraerme. Sayori debe estar en camino mientras hablo. Después arreglo el código humano de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1991
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c118233c:

    # ks "And do any of them suspect that you've been re-programmed?"
    ks "¿Y alguno de ellos sospecha que has sido reprogramad[genero_ao]?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1992
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5d9164c8:

    # n "No, Kyou. None of the Akemi family have indicated that they know my programming has been altered."
    n "No, Kyou. Nadie en la familia Akemi ha indicado saber que mi programación ha sido alterada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1994
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0bca3e14:

    # ks "Wonderful. Keeping your code changes hidden is your top priority while you're with the Akemi family."
    ks "Maravilloso. Mantener los cambios en tu código ocultos es tu prioridad principal mientras estés con la familia Akemi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1995
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a4581f87:

    # ks "If they realize you're no longer programmed to be their daughter, they'll surely have you shipped away to be re-formatted."
    ks "Si descubren que ya no estás programad[genero_ao] para ser su hija, seguramente te enviarán lejos a ser reformateada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1997
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c375b0f2:

    # n "I understand, Kyou. My humanity is the lie I tell the world."
    n "Entiendo, Kyou. Mi humanidad es la mentira que le cuento al mundo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1998
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_acc73740:

    # ks "Yeah... That's right."
    ks "Sí... Es correcto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2000
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e5c8b483:

    # "No, I mean... dissociate the [hypno6] from [p_their] designated \"family\" with a few programming tweaks..."
    "No, más bien... disociar [al] [hypno6!t!l] de su \"familia\" designada con unos cuantos retoques en su programación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2007
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0942f5c7:

    # "Shit. I haven't slipped in my thinking for a while. Looks like I still have a little programming to do on my own mind."
    "Mierda. Llevo un rato haciéndome nudos en la cabeza. Parece que aún tengo algo de programación pendiente en mi propia mente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2008
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7cd095a6:

    # "The \"girl\" that stands before me is NOTHING but a [hypno6]. C'mon, Kyou."
    "La \"chica\" que está frente a mí no es NADA más que un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]. Vamos, Kyou."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2010
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f65448b4:

    # "And on that note, I'm looking forward to spending more time tinkering with Nozomi's code. If only I can deal with Sayori today."
    "Y hablando de eso, estoy impaciente por pasar más tiempo haciéndole retoques al código de Nozomi. Eso si es que puedo lidiar con Sayori hoy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2041
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6cd44e4a:

    # "Nozomi smiles as [p_they] registers my words, interpreting them as the direct command I intended them to be."
    "Nozomi sonríe al escuchar mis palabras, interpretándolas como una orden directa, tal como es mi intención."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2122
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_55001b2e:

    # "The [hypno6] keeps Sayori gripped in [p_their] arms, hugging her around her chest to keep her upright."
    "[el!c] [hypno6!t!l] sujeta a Sayori en sus brazos, abrazándola del pecho para mantenerla erguida."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2166
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bb79aec1:

    # ks "A [hypno6] made of wires, gears and circuits. A [hypno6] that runs programs and processes instructions, with no capacity to think for [p_them]self."
    ks "Un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] hech[genero_ao] de cables, engranes y circuitos. Un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] que corre programas y procesa instrucciones, incapaz de pensar por su cuenta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2176
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_698a3f50:

    # ks "Because after all, you are a [hypno6], Sayori. A [hypno6] that processes instructions from [p_their] programmer. Just as you are doing now."
    ks "Porque, después de todo, eres un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], Sayori. Un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] que procesa instrucciones de su programador. Justo como ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2183
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a33ca6b:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. I am your programmer. And while you are in this deeply relaxed state I can alter any facet of your code that I please."
    ks "Es correcto, Sayori. Yo soy tu programador. Y mientras estés en este estado de profunda relajación, puedo alterar cualquier faceta de tu código como me plazca."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2192
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_44dc3f6b:

    # ks "So you will find yourself always wanting to obey my instructions, just as any [hypno6] should for [p_their] programmer. Understand, Sayori?"
    ks "Por lo que siempre querrás obedecer mis instrucciones, como cualquier otr[genero_ao] [hypno6!t!l] que obedece a su programador. ¿Entiendes, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2219
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_19b44a81:

    # "She smiles as our eyes meet." with dissolve
    "Sonríe en cuanto nuestras miradas se cruzan." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2229
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8c70bfdc:

    # "Even on her better days, of which this is certainly not, Sayori looks ready to drop dead from exhaustion."
    "Hasta en sus mejores días, y este no es uno de ellos, Sayori parece estar a punto de morir de agotamiento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2268
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7e797a4f:

    # s concerned "Having to accept that I am... you know." with dissolve
    s concerned "Tener que aceptar que soy... ya sabes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2269
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_333465ba:

    # "I thought someone like her would be popular. She's kind, and beautiful. Everyone must want to know her as much as I do."
    "Creí que alguien como ella sería popular. Es amable y hermosa. Todos deben querer conocerla tanto como yo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2271
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ff124b6c:

    # s surprised_right "It is so outlandish, yet somehow I accept it completely." with dissolve
    s surprised_right "Es tan estrafalario, y sin embargo lo acepto completamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2273
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3795119e:

    # s sleeptalk "This must obviously be a part of my programming. And processing that only leads me further into my acceptance of who... no, WHAT I am." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Esto obviamente debe ser parte de mi programación. Y procesarlo solo me lleva a aceptar más a profundidad quién… no, QUÉ soy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2286
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e60f45d8:

    # "These girls are NOT human. I've been over this. Nozomi and her clique are all [hypno6]s."
    "Estas chicas NO son humanas. Creí haberlo dejado claro. Nozomi y su pandilla son todas [hypno6!t!l]s."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2289
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ee908b94:

    # "All of them. There's no need for me to think of them as human again."
    "Todas lo son. Ya no necesito volver a pensar en ellas como humanas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2337
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_40e5918d:

    # n sad_closed blush "... A-actually, nevermind. That does seem far-fetched." with dissolve
    n sad_closed blush "... ¿S-sabes, qué?, olvídalo. Eso suena muy descabellado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2873
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_69d3a777:

    # "Yeah. I know boys shouldn't hit girls but, fuck it. I'm done playing nice."
    "Sí. Sé que los chicos no deben golpear a las chicas, pero a la mierda. Se acabó el señor amable."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2874
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2bebb28c:

    # "I'm not going to let these fucking bitches take everything from me."
    "No pienso dejar que estas jodidas perras me lo arrebaten todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3693
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dc7700bc:

    # h "I {nw}" with dissolve
    h "Te {nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2876
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b6be861f:

    # extend "SAID- {w=0.5}{nw}" with vpunch
    extend "DIJE- {w=0.5}{nw}" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2878
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_37d75286:

    # "Hiroko screams into my ear, but a moment later her scream reaches a different pitch as I throw my head rearward, hitting her nose with the back of my skull." with vpunch
    "Hiroko me grita al oído, pero un momento después su grito alcanza un tono diferente, pues arrojo mi cabeza hacia atrás golpeando su nariz con mi cráneo." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3704
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0a5c8c69:

    # "I wince at her fucking volume, but all too quickly she pulls away and her screams are muffled as she claps her hands over her face in anguish."
    "Su puto volumen me hace retorcerme, pero rápidamente me suelta y sus gritos son ahogados por sus manos, las cuales se llevó a la cara angustiada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2886
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_00d1192a:

    # "And in a flash, {nw}" with dissolve
    "Y en un santiamén me pongo con{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2887
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9d45e2ea:

    # extend "I haul myself forcefully back to my feet, which serves to flip Hiroko onto her back as she lets out another howl." with vpunch
    extend " fuerza de pie, lo cual hace a Hiroko caer de espaldas dejando escapar otro aullido." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2888
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b377c9f:

    # "Just as I rise to my full height, I find myself locking eyes with the other one."
    "Una vez estoy completamente erguido, miro a los ojos a la otra."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2889
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_eca83716:

    # "Her tired eyes are uncharacteristically wide as her sleep-deprived mind tries to take in what is happening in front of her."
    "Sus ojos cansados están inusualmente abiertos y su mente privada de sueño intenta asimilar lo que sucede ante ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2890
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_37ecfd86:

    # "That's too bad. As by the time she raises her arms to defend herself I'm already there to shove her full in the chest."
    "Qué lástima. Para cuando logra levantar los brazos para defenderse ya la estoy tacleando de lleno en el pecho."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2896
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_279aa633:

    # s "A-aahh! {w=0.5}{nw}"
    s "¡A-aaah! {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2897
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d4a68cab:

    # extend "" with vpunch
    extend "" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2898
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_445513c0:

    # "And down she goes, stumbling backwards to crash to the floor between the table and the couch while the phone and penlight she was holding spill out of her hands."
    "Y directo al piso. Se estrella de espaldas contra el trozo de suelo entre la mesa y el sofá, a la vez que el teléfono y la linterna que sostenía caen de sus manos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2901
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9d8806ae:

    # "The adrenaline running hot in me, I seize my chance as I scoop my penlight up from the floor..."
    "Con la adrenalina corriendo por mis venas, aprovecho la oportunidad para recoger mi linterna del suelo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2905
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fa39cf3a:

    # "... Just as I turn to find a furious Hiroko yapping at my heels."
    "... Y justo entonces me doy la vuelta para encontrarme a una furiosa Hiroko ladrándome."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2909
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3f72fbbc:

    # h "Y-you {w=0.1}{nw}"
    h "¡J-jodido {w=0.1}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2910
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c59fc500:

    # extend "FUCKIN'..." with vpunch
    extend "HIJO DE..." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2911
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8d60965c:

    # "Hiroko lunges, but I'm ready for her, as I reach out and grab her arm before her punch can connect."
    "Hiroko lanza una estocada, pero estoy listo para ella. Alzo una mano y atrapo su brazo antes de que su golpe conecte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2913
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d71932e9:

    # "She grunts and strains as we tussle, while she seems to blink back the pain in her eyes." with dissolve
    "Gruñe y forcejea mientras parece aguantarse el dolor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2914
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_493e9b16:

    # "That headbutt just now really smarted her, I can tell."
    "El cabezazo de hace un momento no le hizo mucha gracia, por lo que veo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2915
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3f81fc06:

    # "And it gives me ample time to hold my penlight in my other hand properly, as I switch it on..."
    "Y eso me da tiempo suficiente para sujetar bien la linterna en mi otra mano, encenderla..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2916
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_33a09d39:

    # s "Hiroko! Don't let him shine the light in your eyes!"
    s "¡Hiroko! ¡Que no te encienda la luz en los ojos!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2917
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7f4117a2:

    # h angry_side "WHAT?" with dissolve
    h angry_side "¿QUÉ?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2918
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b7a87ff7:

    # "Fine. So Sayori figured it out. Big woop."
    "Muy bien. Conque Sayori lo descifró. Un hurra por ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3743
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c1943976:

    # ks casual angry "A-agh!" with vpunch
    ks casual angry "¡A-ay!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2923
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_13981a37:

    # "Hiroko clenches her eyes shut just as I sweep my light over her face."
    "Hiroko cierra los ojos justo cuando paso la luz por su rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2924
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8f422e17:

    # ks "Open your eyes you little bitch... {w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "Abre los ojos, pequeña perra... {w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2925
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a500c8a5:

    # extend "OW, FUCK!" with vpunch
    extend "¡AU, MIERDA!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2926
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e9e2e5b9:

    # "While I tug her left and right, she manages to close in a little and land a kick to my shin with those sneakers of hers."
    "Mientras la jaloneo, logra acercarse un poco y darme una patada en la barbilla con su zapatilla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2927
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6de1f41c:

    # "It takes me by surprise but, nah come on, that didn't hurt much."
    "Me toma por sorpresa, pero nah, vamos, no dolió mucho."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2929
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6fd9f33f:

    # "And as she flails to try and block my right hand from bearing the light down on her, I simply shine it across her face again."
    "Y cuando sacude la mano para intentar bloquear el disparo de luz de mi mano derecha, simplemente la paso por su rostro una vez más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2934
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b12d72e3:

    # s "KYOU!"
    s "¡KYOU!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2935
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6929ed97:

    # "That's when I find Sayori upon me again, her arms locking with mine as she tries to knock me off balance." with vpunch
    "Y en ese momento Sayori vuelve a abalanzarse contra mí, encerrando mis brazos en los suyos, intentando hacerme perder el equilibrio." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2936
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f4f8856b:

    # s irritated "U-ugh, stop this madness!" with vpunch
    s irritated "¡A-aj, detén esta locura!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2937
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_af285a3d:

    # "But after her initial impact, one thing is laughably obvious."
    "Pero después de su impacto inicial, es tan obvio que da risa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2942
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1aabed82:

    # ks "GET OFF OF ME!" with shake
    ks "¡QUÍTATE SE ENCIMA!" with shake

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2943
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8d7af2b3:

    # "She has no body strength whatsoever. A quick elbow is enough to put that zombie girl back on the floor."
    "No tiene ni una pizca de fuerza corporal. Un codazo rápido es suficiente para mandar a esa chica zombi de regreso al suelo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2944
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6f31fe9f:

    # h shocked_side "S-SAYORI!" with vpunch
    h shocked_side "¡S-SAYORI!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2945
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_00a0821c:

    # "And yeah, maybe she hit her head against the coffee table on the way down."
    "Y sí, puede que se haya golpeado la cabeza con la mesa de centro durante la caída."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2947
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bcda5d46:

    # "I'm not gonna think about that. All I know is the little thug before me was shocked enough to open her eyes again."
    "No voy a pensar en eso. Todo lo que sé es que la buscapleitos que tengo delante está tan impactada que volvió a abrir los ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2948
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cbc7b1bb:

    # h pain "A-aah, {w=0.2}shit what {nw}" with dissolve
    h pain "¡A-ay, {w=0.2}mierda, ¿qué {nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2949
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4d5a104e:

    # extend "WAS that?!" with vpunch
    extend "FUE eso?!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2950
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4dd9dff4:

    # "There. A little victory, as even that glimpse of the light is enough to distract her from the fight."
    "Ahí está. Una pequeña victoria, pues hasta un pequeño vistazo de la luz es suficiente para distraerla de la pelea."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2951
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f0a921a1:

    # "And it allows me to take a breath and clear some of the red mist from my own eyes."
    "Y eso me permite respirar y dispersar un poco de la neblina roja que tengo el los ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2952
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4691f9bf:

    # "I need to think like a hypnotist. And these girls continue to be my subjects."
    "Debo pensar como hipnotista. Y estas chicas siguen siendo mis sujetos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2953
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_007948f0:

    # ks frown "H-hey now, let's all of us take a step back and relax, shall we?"
    ks frown "E-está bien, todos demos un paso atrás y relajémonos, ¿les parece?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2954
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_822660fb:

    # h "F-Fuck you!"
    h "¡C-come mierda!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2955
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8ba7678a:

    # "Hiroko might protest, but that sounded weak as hell."
    "Hiroko podrá protestar, pero eso sonó extremadamente débil."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2957
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_319b2fee:

    # "And as I flash my penlight menacingly over her closed eyes, I can feel how much easier it's becoming to keep her at bay."
    "Y sosteniendo amenazadoramente la luz de mi linterna en sobre sus ojos cerrados, puedo sentir lo fácil que se está volviendo acorralarla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2958
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4dc3b064:

    # ks "You'll find all of this so much easier if you'll just listen and obey."
    ks "Verán que todo es mucho más fácil si deciden escuchar y obedecer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2959
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9ae80e7b:

    # "That's it. The phrase I instilled in these bitch's heads."
    "Eso es. La frase que instalé en las cabezas de estas perras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2975
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e221f8c0:

    # "And of course Kyou's able to catch her eye with it before she can turn her attention back to the fight." with dissolve
    "Y, por supuesto, Kyou es capaz de atrapar su ojo con la linterna antes de que vuelva su atención a la pelea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2976
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c26243a9:

    # "That glimpse, along with Kyou repeating his \"listen and obey\" mantra, means it's pretty much over for Hiroko as Kyou feels the fight drain out of her."
    "Es destello, sumado a que Kyou sigue repitiendo su mantra de \"escuchar y obedecer\" marcan el fin del juego para Hiroko, y Kyou siente su lucha mermarse."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2979
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_65de7ffc:

    # "As Kyou compells her to open her eyes again, she starts to pull them back without thinking and gets another flash of the light for her trouble."
    "En cuanto Kyou le exige que vuelva a abrir los ojos, ella lo hace sin pensar y recibo otro disparo de luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2984
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_91db9c5f:

    # "Sayori gets up again and desperately tries to pull Kyou away from her friend..."
    "Sayori vuelve a levantarse y desesperadamente intenta alejar a Kyou de su amiga..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2987
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c339c8e6:

    # "But Hiroko's by now lost in trance at Kyou's command, as Sayori feels her own grip on her mind faltering on account of hearing the mantra same as her friend." with dissolve
    "Pero Hiroko, a estas alturas, ya está perdida en trance bajo las órdenes de Kyou, y Sayori siente el control de su mente flaquear ante el sonido del mismo mantra que se llevó a su amiga." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2991
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_209a5de4:

    # "Without Hiroko to distract him, Kyou is easily able to hold Sayori at bay and finish off her own descent into trance." with dissolve
    "Sin Hiroko distrayéndolo, Kyou puede mantener a Sayori a raya con facilidad y finalizar su descenso al trance." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2994
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a5eba15c:

    # "The two girls now stand helpless while Kyou catches his breath as his anger over this situation returns, now that the danger has passed." with dissolve
    "Las dos chicas se quedan indefensas de pie mientras que Kyou recupera el aliento y su ira ante la situación regresa, habiendo pasado el peligro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2996
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2971db96:

    # "Only just then he hears the door close behind him, prompting a thought to enter his head that had been forgotten about amidst all the adrenaline."
    "Y en ese momento escucha la puerta cerrarse detrás de él, haciendo de inmediato que vuelva a su cabeza lo que olvidado con toda la adrenalina."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2997
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4048609d:

    # "... Where's Nozomi?"
    "... ¿Dónde está Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2998
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f3b9f7b5:

    # "Kyou rushes to the window where he sees Nozomi dashing off in a fright with her phone to her ear. Fuck."
    "Kyou se abalanza a la ventana para ver a Nozomi corriendo despavorida con su teléfono en la oreja. Mierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2999
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_53cef39f:

    # "He can't very well run out there and grab her in broad daylight, so he grabs his own phone and tries to send her a text message."
    "No puede salir allá afuera y agarrarla en plena luz del día, por lo que toma su teléfono e intenta enviarle un mensaje de texto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3000
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ac9d6f68:

    # "All Nozomi has to do is read the message... Just one look at her phone screen and surely she'll be helplessly walking right back into his clutches."
    "Solo hace falta que Nozomi lea el mensaje... Tan solo una mirada a la pantalla de su teléfono y caminará de vuelta a sus garras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3001
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ea5103fb:

    # "Only she's all too aware of the stakes as she keeps the phone to her ear, pleading with whoever's on the line to help her."
    "Excepto que ya está más que consciente de lo que está en juego y mantiene su teléfono en la oreja, suplicándole a quien sea que esté en la línea que la ayude."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3002
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_54b8c2aa:

    # "At this point it's clear Nozomi isn't going to simply abandon her friends even if she's clearly terrified and out of her depth."
    "A este punto queda claro que Nozomi no piensa abandonar a sus amigas, por más que esté aterrada y no haya nada que pueda hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3003
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b48c193a:

    # "She's stopped at a safe distance from Kyou's house and turns back to face it, while she stays on the line to the police or whoever."
    "Se detuvo a una distancia segura de la casa de Kyou y se da la vuelta para mirarlo, manteniéndose en la línea de la policía o quien sea."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3004
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_35f9ae74:

    # "Kyou might be recalling that the compulsion to read her messages right away was only given to Nozomi's friends and not her, and kicks himself over yet another oversight."
    "Puede que Kyou recuerde que el impulso de leer sus mensajes de inmediato solo se le dio a las amigas de Nozomi y no a ella, y se enoja consigo mismo por ese otro descuido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3005
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_db760954:

    # "And so, seething at Nozomi having gotten away for now, Kyou's anger gives way to necessity: He needs to prepare for the inevitable attention she's about to bring him."
    "Y así, con la sangre hirviendo, ya que Nozomi escapó por ahora; la ira de Kyou da lugar a la necesidad: Necesita prepararse para la inevitable atención que está por traerle."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3006
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb407df2:

    # "Turning back from the window, Kyou now addresses his hypnotized captives."
    "Alejándose de la ventana, Kyou se dirige ahora a sus cautivas hipnotizadas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3007
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a545b5c8:

    # "Kyou deepens their trances a bit before having them forget any notion that they were here to stop him and convincing them that they're at his house of their own free will."
    "Kyou profundiza sus trances un poco más y las hace olvidar toda noción de haber venido aquí para detenerlo, y las convence de que están en su casa por su propia voluntad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3008
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a7f915b8:

    # "They were all just chilling at his house when Nozomi decided to get weird! Kyou did nothing wrong, it was all a big misunderstanding, right girls? Right."
    "¡Todos estaban pasando el rato y de pronto Nozomi decidió ponerse rara! Kyou no hizo nada malo, todo fue un gran malentendido, ¿cierto, chicas? Cierto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3009
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_152251fb:

    # "And they're all having such a great time hanging out with Kyou. So great that they should show how good a time by laughing."
    "Y todas se la estaban pasando tan bien con Kyou. Tanto, que debería demostrar lo grandioso que fue con unas risas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3012
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_09c17486:

    # "The two of them start to laugh helplessly, as Kyou impresses on them that they're laughing out their free will while they're at it." with dissolve
    "Las dos comienzan a reír desamparadas y, mientras tanto, Kyou les impone que estaban riendo por voluntad propia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3013
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_44512706:

    # "Satisfied, he then cracks open the window to make sure their laughter is heard by Nozomi from across the street to send her a message."
    "Satisfecho, abre la ventana y se asegura de que sus risas sean escuchadas por Nozomi desde el otro lado de la calle para enviarle un mensaje."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3014
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0a06c0b3:

    # "\"They're mine, and you're next!\""
    "\"¡Ya son mías, y sigues tú!\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3016
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0c29bc91:

    # "Following that little moment of maniacal villainy, there'll probably be a time skip."
    "Seguido de ese pequeño momento de villanía maniática, probablemente habrá un salto de tiempo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3017
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_61c1a8d3:

    # "As expected, the authorities might arrive at Kyou's only for Hiroko and Sayori to insist nothing is wrong, so it comes to nothing."
    "Como era de esperarse, las autoridades llegaron a casa de Kyou solo para que Hiroko y Sayori insistieran que todo estaba bien, por lo que no ocurre nada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3018
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_049f6848:

    # "If Kyou was hoping Nozomi would eventually read the message he left her, he's left waiting as she never returns."
    "Si Kyou esperaba que Nozomi eventualmente leyera el mensaje que le dejo, se queda esperando, pues nunca regresa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3019
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9800ce3c:

    # "Not to his house certainly, but not to school either. Kyou never sees her again."
    "Ciertamente no a su casa, pero tampoco a la escuela. Kyou nunca la vuelve a ver."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3020
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cd4f4d1e:

    # "But Kyou's got bigger things on his mind, as his newfound powerlust continues without her."
    "Pero Kyou tiene asuntos más grandes en mente, y su recién adquirido deseo de poder continúa sin ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3021
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7b2b0d76:

    # "Using his penlight and her former friends, it's a simple matter for him to take over the school and beyond, ruling from the shadows."
    "Usando su linterna y a las examigas de la chica, es para él un juego de niños apoderarse de la escuela y más, gobernando desde las sombras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3022
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f32f92ae:

    # "Although much like before, his pursuit of power leaves him empty inside as he starts to wonder what it's all for."
    "Aunque, al igual que antes, su búsqueda de poder lo deja vacío por dentro y comienza a preguntarse de qué sirve todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3023
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_87456502:

    # "No one loves you, Kyou."
    "Nadie ama a Kyou."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3024
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b559ed8:

    # "*** THE END ***"
    "*** FIN ***"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3151
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cf7ce0c2:

    # "I have no idea what's going to happen today."
    "No tengo idea de qué pasará hoy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3152
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f259a057:

    # "Nozomi texted me to say she'll be here a little earlier than the others. I think she wants to say a few things to me first."
    "Nozomi me envió un mensaje diciendo que vendría más temprano que las otras. Creo que quiere decirme algunas cosas primero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3154
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_406d9f5c:

    # "That must be her."
    "Esa debe ser ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3162
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_81648746:

    # n "{size=16}Hey, Sir...{/size}" with dissolve
    n "{size=16}Hola, Señor...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3163
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_65dea0ff:

    # "I notice right away that my conditioning the other day has held up; She's still quiet as a mouse in this house."
    "Noto de inmediato que mi acondicionamiento del otro día aún sigue en pie; sigue callada como un ratón al entrar a esta casa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3165
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_30ea6683:

    # n "Hey." with dissolve
    n "Hola." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3166
