# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3358
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0b8a4850:

    # n "Maybe Kyou was at fault, but that penlight really shouldn't have affected me the way it did."
    n "Tal vez sea culpa de Kyou, pero esa linterna no debería haberme afectado así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3361
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a71993f1:

    # n front sigh "Hypnosis isn't as dangerous as that, I promise. It's supposed to be fun and safe; neither of us could've known that it would affect me so severely." with dissolve
    n front sigh "La hipnosis no es así de peligrosa, lo prometo. Se supone que sea divertida y segura; ninguno de los dos pudo saber que me afectaría tan severamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3362
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e8c05335:

    # "Still quivering with rage, Hiroko replies with a low growl."
    "Aún temblando de fura, Hiroko responde con un gruñido."

