translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_08673e4f:

    # "Not wanting to test her, I pull my penlight out from my pocket, where it's been lying untouched for the past couple of days."
    "No queriendo ponerla a prueba, saco la linterna de mi bolsillo, donde ha permanecido intacta el último par de días."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3371
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3eee1c63:

    # "And she immediately snatches it out of my hand!" with vpunch
    "¡E inmediatamente me la arrebata de la mano!" with vpunch

