# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3385
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ed10a66c_1:

    # s "To think that your secret little science project would cause so much trouble."
    s "Y pensar que tu proyectito de ciencias secreto causaría tantos problemas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3386
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_05ade129_1:

    # s frown_right "There is a hidden genius in you, Kyou. Now if only you could start using it for good..." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Hay un genio oculto en ti, Kyou. ¿Podrías empezar a usarlo para el bien?..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3387
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_801a41c4:

    # "I let out a nervous chuckle."
    "Dejo escapar una pequeña risa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3388
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_02532f3b:

    # s "If that penlight is doing what it seems to be doing, then it needs to go. It's too dangerous to keep around."
    s "Si esa linterna hace lo que dices que hace, tiene que irse. Es demasiado peligroso que siga por ahí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3390
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b2274a77_1:

    # n front frown casual_folded "Yes, I agree." with dissolve
    n front frown casual_folded "Sí, estoy de acuerdo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3391
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5d153426_1:

    # ks surprised "What?! I worked so hard on this. I realise it's dangerous, but do I really have to ditch it right now?"
    ks surprised "¡¿Qué?! Trabajé muy duro en esto. Me doy cuenta de que es peligrosa, pero ¿en serio debo deshacerme de ella?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3392
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b57cbacc_1:

    # ks "I mean, don't we want to know why it does what it does? There could be a research project in this. Or- {w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "Digo, ¿no queremos saber por qué hace lo que hace? Podría hacerse un proyecto de investigación sobre esto. O- {w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3394
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d8f81029:

    # h angry "NOPE!" with vpunch
    h angry "¡NOP!" with vpunch

