    # "An awkward silence hangs in the room for a few moments, interrupted only by the sound of Hiroko slipping my penlight into her bag."
    "Un silencio incómodo se prolonga en la habitación por unos momentos, interrumpido por el sonido de Hiroko metiendo mi linterna a su mochila."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3403
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_149f7129_1:

    # s frown "You ARE going to destroy that thing, aren't you?" with dissolve
    s frown "SÍ vas a destruir esa cosa, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

