    # n "Well, anyway, I think we should give the hypnosis a rest. At least for now."
    n "Pues, en fin, creo que deberíamos darle a la hipnosis un descanso. Al menos por ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3408
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_31c4be24_1:

    # ks concerned "Yeah..." with dissolve
    ks concerned "Sí..." with dissolve

