translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_46e85bc1:

    # n "I mean, when we started this it was meant to be fun, and I guess a little bit kinky if I'm being honest."
    n "Digo, cuando empezamos, se suponía que fuera divertido, y supongo que picante, si soy honesta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3410
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d5cf1a23:

    # ks "But it'll be fine now, won't it? We'll just do it without the penlight, like last time."
    ks "Pero estará bien ahora, ¿no? Simplemente lo haremos sin la linterna, como la última vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3411
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8ee15131:

    # n "Maybe. It's just that talking to my friends brought me to my senses a little bit."
    n "Tal vez. Es solo que hablar con mis amigas me hizo entrar un poco en razón."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3412
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fbb4243f_1:

    # "I simply nod. I can't say I'm happy about all this, but she's right; we need to take a step back."
    "Simplemente asiento con la cabeza. No puedo decir que estoy feliz con todo esto, pero tiene razón; hay que dar un paso atrás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3414
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_400caa09:

    # h sad_side dress_arm "Can't you just be done with this forever, Nozo? I don't wanna see you getting hurt again." with dissolve
    h sad_side dress_arm "¿No puedes solo terminar con esto para siempre, Nozo? No quiero volver a verte lastimada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3415
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8d7ac5a9:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "Hiroko, I know you're worried, but I promise nothing will happen like that ever again." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Hiroko, sé que estás preocupada, pero te prometo que nada así volverá a pasar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3416
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_05373b8c:

    # n "I know people do this kind of thing all the time and only have happy memories of their experiences."
    n "Sé que la gente hace esta clase de cosas todo el tiempo y solo tengo recuerdos felices de estas experiencias."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3417
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3c255993:

    # n "And this desire I have? It's not going to go away; it's a part of who I am."
    n "¿Y este deseo que tengo? Nunca se irá; es parte de quien soy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3418
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9d278753:

    # n "I know I wasn't careful enough and Kyou and I rushed into things, but we've learned from that."
    n "Sé que no tuve suficiente cuidado y que Kyou apresuró las cosas, pero hemos aprendido de eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3419
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_363c4748:

    # n sleep "So please don't worry about me, Hiroko." with dissolve
    n sleep "Así que, por favor, no te preocupes por mí, Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3420
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_17168829:

    # n "But... but I know that has to sound so weird and stupid to you both, and it's why I never told you about this part of myself until now."
    n "Pero... pero sé que debe sonar raro y estúpido para ambas, y es por eso que nunca les hablé de esta parte de mí hasta ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3421
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c6e1fdfa:

    # s sleep "We really should have suspected something at last year's culture festival." with dissolve
    s sleep "Debimos sospechar algo en el festival cultural del año pasado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3422
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a24f0879:

    # s "Looking back, it seems obvious now given how eager you were to volunteer for Satoshi's hypnotic stage show."
    s "En retrospectiva, perece tan obvio dado lo ansiosa que estabas de ser voluntario en el espectáculo de hipnosis de Satoshi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3423
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b7b1751b:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "I'm so sorry for making you both worry, and for getting you mixed up in my nonsense. I was selfish chasing my desires so recklessly." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Lamento haberlas preocupado a ambas, y por haberlas involucrado en esta locura. Fui egoísta al perseguir mis deseos tan imprudentemente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3425
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8b569a78_1:

    # n cry "You're both having to work so hard for your futures and I'm just... j-just bringing you down with this stupid crap." with dissolve
