# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4731
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b335a11d:

    # "I watch as she innocently looks into the light as I pass it across her face."
    "La veo observar inocentemente la luz mientras la paso por su rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4733
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cd2cf1c0:

    # ks "Finding it so easy, so natural, to let yourself sink into the couch. To allow my light to sweep over your face."
    ks "Es tan fácil, tan natural simplemente hundirte en el sofá. Permitir que mi luz se deslice por tu rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4735
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3e4f1af0:

    # ks neutral "Very good. Just letting the light take you down. Letting your eyelids become heavy. Knowing deep down how sleepy it makes you to watch the light."
    ks neutral "Muy bien. Deja que la luz te lleve. Deja que tus párpados se pongan pesados. Sabiendo en el fondo cuánto sueño te da observar la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4737
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9da1b970:

    # ks "Very natural, very right it is, to stare and sink further."
    ks "Es muy natural, muy correcto mirar y dejarte llevar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4739
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9d58e6d7:

    # ks "And if you need to relax even deeper, letting those tired, heavy eyelids close... that's okay."
    ks "Y si necesitas relajarte más profundamente dejando que esos pesados párpados se cierren... puedes hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4742
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_16e1cfef:

    # ks "Letting them close..." with dissolve
    ks "Deja que se cierren..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4744
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_511debc7:

    # ks "Dropping so quickly, [alt_name]. So deeply."
    ks "Y caerás muy rápido, [alt_name]. Muy profundo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4746
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ce573a4d:

    # ks "And sleep."
    ks "Y duerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4748
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2e1bae4a:

    # ks "Feeling so good as your conscious mind falls deep asleep, [alt_name]." with dissolve
    ks "Se siente muy bien dejar que tu mente consciente se quede profundamente dormida, [alt_name]." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4749
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6c4b9c89:

    # "I take a moment to pause, as I collect myself for what I'm about to do..."
    "Hago una pequeña pausa, armándome de valor para lo que estoy a punto de hacer..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4750
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_68cbad21:

    # ks "Now, [alt_name], as you remain so deeply asleep, I want you to remember that this is not who you truly are."
    ks "Y ahora, [alt_name], que estás profundamente dormida, quiero que recuerdes que esta no es quien eres en realidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4751
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_95622ee6:

    # ks "You need to become Sayori again, while still remaining in this deep, completely relaxed state of trance."
    ks "Conviértete en Sayori una vez más, permaneciendo en este profundo y completamente relajado estado de trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4752
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2d11e6d7:

    # ks "You can do that can't you... Sayori?"
    ks "Puedes hacer eso, ¿verdad... Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4754
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_73735ab1:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "I-I... yes..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "S-... sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4756
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_87e94a28:

    # "I breathe a little sigh. So far so good." with dissolve
    "Suelto un leve suspiro. De momento todo va bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4757
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7c6fe0ef:

    # ks "That's... that's great, Sayori. I knew you could do it."
    ks "G-... grandioso, Sayori. Sabía que podrías hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6661
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cfe37577:

    # ks "And now that you are, once again, Sayori I want you to do something else for me."
    ks "Y ahora que eres nuevamente Sayori, quiero que hagas algo por mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4759
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cb78b6d6:

    # ks "This time, I need you to accept that [alt_name] no longer exists as a part of you."
    ks "Esta vez quiero que aceptes que [alt_name] ya no forma parte de ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4760
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9ac4ed39_1:

    # ks "[alt_name] is no more, and the words \"become [alt_name]\" will no longer have any special effect on you if you hear me or anyone else say it."
    ks "[alt_name] ya no existe, y las palabras \"Conviértete en [alt_name]\" ya no tienen ningún efecto especial en ti al escucharme a mí o a quien sea decirlas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4761
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ae3b8afe_1:

    # ks "Also... you will no longer be compelled to blank your mind completely when you try to sleep at night. What you do when you try to sleep is entirely up to you again."
    ks "Además... ya no estarás obligada a vaciar por completo tu mente al intentar dormir por las noches. Lo que hagas al intentar dormir, una vez más, depende enteramente de ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4762
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ebce5f4e:

    # ks "In fact, anything I may have suggested to you in trance will immediately and effortlessly fade from your mind."
    ks "De hecho, cualquier sugestión que pudiera haberte dado mientras estabas en trance se desvanecerá al instante de tu mente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4763
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_976d3e97:

    # ks "None of the suggestions I made previously will influence your behaviour or thinking in any way."
    ks "Ninguna de las sugestiones que creé previamente influirá de ninguna manera en tu comportamiento o tu pensamiento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4764
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6cbdd3cd_1:

    # ks "Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "Comprendes, ¿Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4765
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2c76e08e_1:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Yes..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4767
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e99d8bce:

    # ks "That's great, Sayori. Completely free of my suggestions, just feeling so good. So relaxed... so ready to accept new suggestions..." with dissolve
    ks "Grandioso, Sayori. Completamente libre de mis sugestiones, te sientes muy bien. Muy relajada... y lista para aceptar nuevas sugestiones..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4768
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_47f35b67:

    # ks "So if I were to now suggest to you that every time you met me in the past week was a figment of your imagination, you would have no trouble accepting it as the truth."
    ks "Por lo que, si te dijera que cada ocasión en la que estuviste conmigo esta semana fue un porducto de tu imaginación, no tendrías problemas acepándolo como verdad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4769
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ca99e760:

    # ks "And as figments of your imagination, you should find it so very easy to simply... forget, Sayori."
    ks "Y como productos de tu imaginación que son, debería ser muy fácil simplemente... olvidarlos, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4770
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3d523337:

    # ks "Simply allow these figments to leave your mind completely."
    ks "Simplemente dejar que abandonen tu mente por completo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4771
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2703da93:

    # ks "We never met at any time outside of our normal school routines, so it makes no sense for you to recall such things... isn't that right, Sayori?"
    ks "Nunca nos vimos fuera de nuestras rutinas escolares de siempre, por lo que no tiene sentido que recuerdes esas cosas... ¿no es cierto, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4772
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ced25502:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Right..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Cierto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5857
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3d81d054:

    # ks "Absolutely right. And there's one more thing you need to do. One more thing that will be completely natural and correct for you to do." with dissolve
    ks "Absolutamente cierto. Y hay una cosa más que necesito que hagas. Una cosa más que será completamente natural y correcta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4775
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d27a82f5:

    # ks "The moment you wake, you will get up off the couch, leave my house and go straight back to your home."
    ks "En cuanto despiertes, te levantarás del sofá, saldrás de mi casa y te irás directo de regreso a la tuya."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4776
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2bdae08d:

    # ks "You will remember nothing of our meeting, or that you were ever here."
    ks "No recordarás nada de nuestras reuniones, o que estuviste aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4777
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_006e29b3:

    # ks "Is that understood, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Entendido, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4778
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_06707d7a:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Understood..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Entendido..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4780
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4de3af3b:

    # ks "Very good, Sayori. You really are a wonderful hypnotic subject. Taking these suggestions so well. So fully." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien, Sayori. Eres un maravilloso sujeto hipnótico. Al absorber tan bien y tan plenamente estas sugestiones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4781
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4be2d562:

    # ks "Now we will wake you up on a count of three. I'm going to count up, and on three you will become fully awake and instantly acting on what you were told."
    ks "Ahora vamos a despertarte a la cuenta de tres. Voy a contar y a las tres estarás completamente despierta, y al instante actuarás como se te indicó."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4782
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c3a3f916:

    # ks "Counting up now... one... two..."
    ks "Ahora, comenzaré a contar... uno... dos..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4783
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d315ab35:

    # "I let a moment linger as I look her over."
    "Dejo que el momento se prolongue mientras la observo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4784
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_741cacf1:

    # "I really wish we could've been friends, Sayori."
    "En serio desearía que pudiéramos haber sido amigos, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4786
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_fe2bf186:

    # ks "Three."
    ks "Tres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5976
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e1554201_1:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5981
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e1554201:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4795
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ab16ccf6:

    # "And just like that, Sayori wordlessly stands and quietly exits the house, leaving me alone with my thoughts..."
    "Y así sin más, Sayori se pone de pie sin decir una palabra y abandona silenciosamente la casa, dejándome a solas on mis pensamientos..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4798
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_fb90956b:

    # "... And my penlight."
    "... Y mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4799
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8a191fc8:

    # "This is... it was too important to give this up. Possibly even important in more ways than I know right now."
    "Esto es... esto era demasiado importante para dejarlo ir. Posiblemente de formas de las que yo ni siquiera sé."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4800
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2976d595:

    # "I hope there was a part of Sayori that understood."
    "Espero que una parte de Sayori lo haya entendido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4807
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_1f62191e:

    # "I barely had any sleep last night."
    "Apenas pude dormir anoche."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4808
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_008cef54:

    # "As it is, I'm feeling like a kid on Christmas morning."
    "Pero, aun así, me siento como niño en la mañana de navidad. "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4809
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_6daff279:

    # "That Nozomi and my girlfriend are coming over to my house to hang out and talk about my hobby? I'm still amazed this is happening."
    "Que Nozomi y mi novia vengan de visita a pasar tiempo conmigo y hablar de mi pasatiempo... Sigo asombrado de que esté pasando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4810
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_302737a2:

    # "But I gotta get used to this. I can't freak out and get nervous; this is a totally normal thing. I gotta be cool. I gotta stay calm."
    "Pero tengo que acostumbrarme a esto. No puedo entrar en pánico ahora; esto es algo completamente normal. Debo estar sereno. Debo estar calmado. "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4811
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_7c886959:

    # "... I gotta shower before they get here. Shit."
    "... Debo ducharme antes de que lleguen. Mierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4816
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_76d96ff3:

    # "It's not long after I'm showered and changed that the doorbell rings."
    "No mucho después de haberme duchado y cambiado, suena el timbre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4823
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_09c1affa:

    # "And opening the door brings the welcome sight of Sayori, together with Nozomi, as I let them both inside."
    "Y abrir la puerta revela la bienvenida imagen de Sayori junto con Nozomi, y las dejo a ambas entrar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4824
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_5f4e7686:

    # ks casual smile "Hey, thanks for coming, you two."
    ks casual smile "¿Qué tal? Gracias a ambas por venir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4825
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_bcd2ea46:

    # s alert_laugh "Of course! It's so refreshing to be able to take some quality time away from those idiotic textbooks." with dissolve
    s alert_laugh "¡Desde luego! Es muy refrescante poder pasar algo de tiempo de calidad lejos de esos estúpidos libros de texto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4827
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a07b3272:

    # n side smile_side "Oh, that reminds me, Sayori. Do you have long before you need to leave? I remember you usually have cram school today." with dissolve
    n side smile_side "Oh, eso me recuerda, Sayori. ¿Cuánto tiempo te puedes quedar? Me acordé de que por lo general tienes cursos nocturnos hoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4828
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_7cb2a0e8:

    # "Sayori snorts."
    "Sayori resopla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4829
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c9344007:

    # s casual_folded alert_irritated "Practically every day, yes. I won't be attending this time, though." with dissolve
    s casual_folded alert_irritated "Prácticamente todos los días, sí. Pero no asistiré por esta ocasión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6217
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_6e1cdbae:

    # n sad_side "No? I thought your parents would have a few things to say about that." with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿No? ¿No crees que tus padres tendrán un par de cosas que decir al respecto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4831
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_58453f1c:

    # s alert_annoyed "Oh, they did." with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed "Oh, ya las dijeron." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4832
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_7c9f944c:

    # "Sayori leaves a pause as Nozomi looks to her."
    "Sayori hace una pausa y Nozomi la mira."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6220
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_20c01b72:

    # s casual_handup "I may have said a few things back." with dissolve
    s casual_handup "Puede que yo haya respondido un par de cosas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4834
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_95ed544a:

    # n surprised_side "What?" with dissolve
    n surprised_side "¿Qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4835
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c3bedf0a:

    # "Sayori just chuckles at our faces and shakes her head."
    "Sayori simplemente se ríe en nuestras caras y sacude la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4836
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_edb94fea:

    # s alert_smile_right casual "Do not worry yourselves. I don't intend to make a habit of it, but I wanted just this one weekend to be free of all that rubbish." with dissolve
    s alert_smile_right casual "No se preocupen. No tengo intención de volverlo un hábito, pero quería tener al menos este fin de semana libre de todas esas tonerías." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6842
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c1cbef13:

    # "And with that, she claps her hands together, as if to signal the end of this topic."
    "Y dicho eso, junta sus manos, como si intentara anunciar el cierre de este tema."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4838
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_2ccb506d:

    # s casual_folded alert_laugh "Now let's do what we came here for~" with dissolve
    s casual_folded alert_laugh "Ahora hagamos lo que vinimos a hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4840
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_3b3d6742:

    # n smile_side "Well... alright. And I admit I've been looking forward to today, Sayori." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Pues... muy bien. Y admito que he estado impaciente por lo de hoy, Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4841
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_7885acae:

    # n laugh "We hardly ever get to hang out like this~" with dissolve
    n laugh "Muy rara vez podemos pasar tiempo juntas así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4842
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a5f6e057:

    # s alert_smile "Well, that is something we need to fix, as much as my time allows." with dissolve
    s alert_smile "Bueno, eso es algo que debemos arreglar, tanto como el tiempo nos permita." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4846
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_2734dd1b:

    # n "And Kyou, I must admit I'm really curious about this culture fest show you're putting on." with dissolve
    n "Y, Kyou, he de admitir que siento mucha curiosidad por tu acto para el festival cultural." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4847
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_cc96b6ea:

    # ks "Y- you are?"
    ks "¿E-en serio?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6235
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f98ea690:

    # n front2 chuckle "I mean, I don't think you've done anything for the festival on your own steam before..." with dissolve
    n front2 chuckle "Bueno, creo que nunca has hecho nada para el festival por tu propia cuenta..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6236
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_012d5934:

    # n smile "So for you to go all out like this, it makes me think this is something very special." with dissolve
    n smile "Por lo que verte ponerle tanto entusiasmo me hace pensar que es algo muy especial." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4850
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_af05b430:

    # n laugh blush "S- So I'm excited to be working with you for it~" with dissolve
    n laugh blush "A-así que estoy muy emocionada de trabajar contigo para hacerlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4852
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f41b0487:

    # "Damn, she's gonna make me blush if she keeps on like that." with dissolve
    "Diablos, va a hacer que me sonroje si sigue así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4853
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a3f3a812:

    # ks smile blush "Y- yeah, I'm looking forward to it as well. So should we get started?"
    ks smile blush "S-sí, yo también estoy impaciente. Entonces ¿comenzamos?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4854
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_4ea671ee:

    # s alert_happy "We should!" with dissolve
    s alert_happy "¡Comenzamos!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4862
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_c8c7ed12:

    # "And with that, the pair of them get seated on my living room couch." with dissolve
    "Y con eso, el par se sienta en el sofá de mi sala." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4867
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a41b8ffb:

    # n "So... I'm sorry, but I have to ask..."
    n "Y... perdón, pero tengo que preguntar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6257
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_339108f9:

    # n side smile "What made you take up hypnosis, Kyou?" with dissolve
    n side smile "¿Qué te despertó tu interés por la hipnosis, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4871
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_12f3d08d:

    # ks surprised noblush "Huh?" with dissolve
    ks surprised noblush "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6263
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_51503480:

    # n "Well I mean, I don't know you very well but I always thought you were more into technology and such." with dissolve
    n "Pues, es que, no te conozco muy bien, pero siempre pensé que eras más de tecnología y eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6264
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_94e96a96:

    # n neutral "Was I wrong about that?" with dissolve
    n neutral "¿Estaba equivocada?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4874
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_543a8ee7:

    # ks neutral "Uh, well, I'm pretty big on gadgets and things, so not really."
    ks neutral "Eh, pues, sí me encantan los artilugios y esas cosas, así que no."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4875
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_a4a59c4f:

    # n surprised "Oh! So then, what got you into hypnosis?" with dissolve
    n surprised "¡Oh! Entonces, ¿qué te introdujo a la hipnosis?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4876
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_bcc42e49:

    # n smile "Was it always something you were into, or is this a more recent thing?" with dissolve
    n smile "¿Es algo en lo que siempre estuviste interesado, o es más bien reciente?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4877
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_df75bf74:

    # "Goddamn, she's asking me and I kinda want to tell her..."
    "Maldita sea, me lo está preguntando y me gustaría decirle..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4878
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_f48b16c2:

    # "But now that she asks, should I really tell them both that it's all because of her?"
    "Pero ahora que pregunta, ¿debería decirles a ambas que lo hice por ella?"

