# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1239
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5e512fa4:

    # "As I snap my fingers I smile delightedly as Nozomi's eyes quickly glaze over."
    "Chasqueo los dedos y sonrío con deleite al ver que los ojos de Nozomi rápidamente se ponen vidriosos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1241
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7c011f44:

    # ks smile "Very good, Nozomi. We look just like any other young couple on a date, don't we?"
    ks smile "Muy bien, Nozomi. Lucimos como una pareja teniendo una cita como cualquier otra."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1242
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1357b526:

    # ks "So long as we don't raise our voices or make any rash movements we'll be beneath anyone's notice."
    ks "Siempre y cuando no alcemos la voz ni hagamos ningún movimiento brusco, nadie nos notará."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-12-02 22:44

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6085
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d21d6e7e:

    # "I wake up bright and early the next morning."
    "Despierto muy temprano a la mañana siguiente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6086
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_2f2470c1:

    # "Akiko called me after she was done with student council last night, and asked if I wanted to meet for breakfast..."
    "Akiko me llamó anoche después de sus asuntos con el consejo estudiantil y me propuso reunirnos para desayunar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6090
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_706f0ee0:

    # "I'm a little nervous about it. I don't really know what she's expecting to get out of this."
    "Estoy un poco nervioso. No estoy seguro de qué espera obtener de esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6091
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_27d766a1:

    # "And my head's still doing all sorts of loops, trying to process everything that's happened this week."
    "Y mi cabeza sigue dando vueltas y vueltas, intentando procesar todo lo que ha pasado esta semana."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6092
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_4ae07311:

    # "Ugh, why did I tell Akiko I was studying hypnosis, and WHY did I tell her I hypnotized my classmates..."
    "Ay, ¿por qué le dije a Akiko que estaba estudiando hipnosis, y POR QUÉ le dije que hipnoticé a mis compañeras…?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6093
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_446d2170:

    # "She's going to find out that I didn't tell the whole story. That I left out the part about my penlight."
    "Se dará cuenta de que no le conté la historia completa. Que omití lo de mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6094
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_aad4d91a:

    # "That what I did to them was more than what anyone could expect from hypnosis..."
    "Que lo que le hice fue más de lo que cualquiera podría esperar de la hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6096
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_00ac3ca0:

    # a "Kyou! Over here!" with dissolve
    a "¡Kyou! ¡Por aquí!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6097
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_f1aebc44:

    # "B-but that's enough. I can't dwell on that right now."
    "P-pero ya es suficiente. No puedo preocuparme por eso ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6098
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_3dfddcc8:

    # ks casual smile "A-Akiko!"
    ks casual smile "¡A-Akiko!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6099
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_03a490a1:

    # "I need to focus."
    "Debo concentrarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6100
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ec34aa8c:

    # ks "How are you?"
    ks "¿Cómo estás?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6101
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_cf43c638:

    # a casual_down happy "I'm good, thanks." with dissolve
    a casual_down happy "Yo, muy bien, gracias." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6102
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_84cbee35:

    # a laugh_wink "I could eat, though~" with dissolve
    a laugh_wink "Pero me vendría bien algo de comer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6106
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_23a721d5:

    # "She's not wasting any time."
    "No pierde el tiempo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7058
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c1914bac:

    # a "If I get these pancakes down me now, they'll have just enough time to settle before kendo practice." with dissolve
    a "Si me como estos panqueques ahora, tendrán justo el tiempo suficiente para acomodarse antes de la práctica de kendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:11372
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_0ce3cd5c:

    # ks casual confused "You're still doing kendo?"
    ks casual confused "¿Aún practicas kendo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6113
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_83e52e0c:

    # a happy "Yup! I have no time in school, but I belong to a weekend kendo club. I can train most weeks." with dissolve
    a happy "¡Sipi! No tengo tiempo en la escuela, pero voy a un club de kendo los fines de semana. Puedo entrenar casi todas las semanas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6114
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_7f7c21c8:

    # ks sigh "So that's why we're up this early in the morning."
    ks sigh "Conque por eso vinimos tan temprano en la mañana."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6115
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_0816cf29:

    # a casual smirk "Not a morning person, Kyou? That's too bad." with dissolve
    a casual smirk "¿No eres muy mañanero, Kyou? Qué lástima." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6116
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e25b075a:

    # ks sigh "Eh, whatever. I like to lay-in after a school week but it's fine."
    ks sigh "Meh, cómo sea. Me gusta recostarme luego de una semana de escuela. Pero está bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6117
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_1d9e34a1:

    # a sad_side "Especially after the one you just had, huh." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Sobre todo luego de la que acabas de tener, ¿eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6118
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_00af7257:

    # ks "Yeah..."
    ks "Seh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6119
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_0b7a5314:

    # "I then smile to her as I add:"
    "Luego le sonrío y añado:"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6120
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_16e11252:

    # ks smile "At least my weekend's looking up."
    ks smile "Al menos mi fin de semana luce más brillante."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6122
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_71cc7506:

    # "Akiko giggles as she breaks off a piece of pancake with her fork and takes a bite." with dissolve
    "Akiko se ríe, cortando un trozo de panqueque con su tenedor, y luego toma un bocado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6123
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_f06b0163:

    # "She's definitely a lot cuter out of uniform, I have to say."
    "Está mucho más linda sin uniforme, debo decir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6124
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_3136772b:

    # a laugh_wink "S-so anyway, let's talk about brains!" with dissolve
    a laugh_wink "P-pues bien, ¡ahora hablemos de sesos!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6125
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ff47c86c:

    # "... Even if she's just as weird."
    "... Aunque siga igual de rara."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6127
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_8b8e2916:

    # ks "R-right... You said you're into psychology, didn't you?" with dissolve
    ks "C-claro... Dijiste que te gustaba la psicología, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6128
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_028b1893:

    # a casual_down smile "Yup! I like picking people's brains apart and finding out what they're about..." with dissolve
    a casual_down smile "¡Sipi! Me gusta desmantelar los cerebros de la gente y averiguar cómo funcionan..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6129
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_07ad7120:

    # ks "Picking people's brains apart?"
    ks "¿Desmantelar los cerebros de la gente?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6130
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_3bbca04b:

    # "She shrugs."
    "Se encoge de hombros."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6131
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_a40c3bd1:

    # a happy "Maybe that's a funny way to put it, I don't know. I've just always been interested in people and why they are the way they are~" with dissolve
    a happy "Tal vez sea un modo muy raro de decirlo, no sé. Es que siempre me ha interesado la gente y el porqué son como son." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6132
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c30aa6db:

    # ks smirk "So is this why we're here? You're going to try taking me apart and finding out how I work?"
    ks smirk "¿Y por eso estamos aquí? ¿Vas a desmantelarme y averiguar cómo funciono?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6133
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_4cc842f2:

    # a smirk "Oh no, you got me~" with dissolve
    a smirk "Oh, no, me atrapaste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6134
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_90e94e36:

    # a laugh_wink "But what's a conversation if you're not learning about each other?" with dissolve
    a laugh_wink "Pero ¿qué es una conversación si no aprendes nada del otro?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6135
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_38823d42:

    # ks neutral "... Smalltalk?"
    ks neutral "... ¿Parloteo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6136
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_f8d4e021:

    # a casual frown_side "Exactly." with dissolve
    a casual frown_side "Exacto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6137
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_1f8f952e:

    # "Her lips crinkle disdainfully before she regains her focus."
    "Sus labios se arrugan con desdén, y luego recupera su enfoque."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6138
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_442ca236:

    # a smile "So anyway, I've never met someone who knows hypnosis before." with dissolve
    a smile "Pero, en fin, nunca había conocido a alguien que supiera de hipnosis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6139
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_1f403501:

    # ks smile "Oh... uh, really?"
    ks smile "Oh... em, ¿en serio?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6140
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ee4ed951:

    # a neutral_side "I... guess there was that guy at the culture festival last year. The one who put on that hypnosis show?" with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Pues... supongo que estaba ese chico del festival cultural del año pasado. ¿El que hizo un acto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6141
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_5be06ab0:

    # ks neutral "You didn't talk to him?"
    ks neutral "¿No hablaste con él?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6142
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_da09492f:

    # a casual_down neutral "I helped him organize a little but besides that? Not really." with dissolve
    a casual_down neutral "Lo ayudé un poco a organizar, pero fuera de eso, la verdad es que no." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6143
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_492ab2a9:

    # ks "Huh. Why not?"
    ks "Oh. ¿Por qué no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6144
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_2805aae3:

    # "Another shrug."
    "De nuevo se encoge de hombros."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6145
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ff84883e:

    # a sleep "It felt so ridiculous to me. Getting people up in front of everyone and encouraging them to make dummies of themselves seems so cheap." with dissolve
    a sleep "Me pareció muy ridículo. Traer a gente al escenario y ponerlas a hacer el tonto delante de todos suena muy mezquino." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6146
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c2061153:

    # a smile "I'm interested in REAL hypnosis. The kind of thing that can make a difference to someone's life." with dissolve
    a smile "A mí me interesa la hipnosis de VERDAD. La que puede hacer una diferencia en la vida de alguien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6147
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e04ca84a:

    # ks "Stage hypnosis is real, you know."
    ks "La hipnosis escénica es de verdad, ¿sabes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6149
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_941d21c3:

    # "Akiko's eyes widen incredulously." with dissolve
