    a sad_side "Sí. Aunque no haya salido tan bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6161
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d0fdc977:

    # a neutral "So what did you do to hypnotize your classmates? How did it work?" with dissolve
    a neutral "¿Y qué hiciste para hipnotizar a tus compañeras?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6162
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_70f2b133:

    # ks "A-ah, well..."
    ks "A-ah, pues..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6163
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_fb43a144:

    # "Shit. Of course she'd want to know more about that. What am I supposed to tell her? More of the truth?"
    "Mierda. Por supuesto que iba a querer saber más. ¿Qué se supone que le diga? ¿Más de la verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6164
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c58f6df5:

    # a happy "Tell me if I'm being too nosy, but I'm just having a lot of trouble picturing it." with dissolve
    a happy "Dime si estoy siendo muy preguntona, pero es que me es muy difícil imaginármelo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6165
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e618c01c:

    # "I mean... Again, she's heard all those rumours so I need to tell her something. Just not everything."
    "Bueno... Una vez más, ya escuchó todos esos rumores, así que tengo que decirle algo. Simplemente no todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6167
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_18c13dab:

    # ks neutral "O-okay, well I basically got them to focus on a light while I encouraged a hypnotic trance state by talking to them." with dissolve
    ks neutral "B-bueno, pues básicamente hice que se concentraran en una linterna mientras las guiaba al trance hipnótico con mis palabras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6168
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_7d938e6f:

    # ks "And it worked. They listened, they looked up at the light and they seemed comfortable about being hypnotized."
    ks "Y funcionó. Escucharon, miraron la luz y parecían estar cómodas mientras las hipnotizaba."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6169
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_3bdb8b89:

    # a casual surprised "And then what happened?" with dissolve
    a casual surprised "¿Y luego qué pasó?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6170
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_1e87ed48:

    # "I notice her leaning in slightly, her pancakes cooling in front of her as she ignores them for the sake of hearing me speak."
    "Noto que se inclina ligeramente hacia a mí, ignorando sus panqueques que se enfrían ante ella, con tal de escucharme hablar. "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6171
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_7f0d1e4e:

    # "Her attention feels a little awkward, but I can't back out now."
    "Su atención es un poco incómoda, pero no puedo echarme para atrás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6173
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_a1504709:

    # ks sigh "Well... I basically gave them some simple suggestions to follow, and I guess they didn't take to them very well." with dissolve
    ks sigh "Pues... básicamente les di algunas sugestiones simples, y supongo que no se las tomaron muy bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7144
