translate spanish Day6_Redemption_8b4dd1d2:

    # "Akiko takes a moment to eat as she thinks over what I said."
    "Akiko se toma un momento para comer, reflexionando lo que dije."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6191
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_871eddba:

    # "I can just see that curious mind of hers trying to work things out."
    "Puedo ver su mente curiosa intentando procesarlo todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6192
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_111c5c12:

    # "Maybe she's trying to guess which of my classmates I hit on? I didn't name names but she no doubt has some idea..."
