    # a sad "So... you tried to use hypnosis to ask people out and it blew up in your face." with dissolve
    a sad "Así que... intentaste usar hipnosis para conseguirte una cita y te salió el tiro por la culata." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6194
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_fce3c643:

    # "Ah. Figures she'd come to that conclusion."
