    # "Obviously I only did that to Nozomi, but this seems a bad time to correct her."
    "Obviamente eso solo lo hice con Nozomi, pero parece un mal momento para corregirla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6196
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_769cb5b0:

    # a sigh "And if people really think hypnosis is like the cartoons, it's not hard to see how they convinced themselves you were forcing them to date you or something." with dissolve
    a sigh "Y si la gente en serio cree que la hipnosis es como en las caricaturas, no es difícil ver por qué pensaron que las estabas obligando a salir contigo o algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6197
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_eb16a226:

    # a neutral "*sigh* Stupid. Brains don't work like that." with dissolve
    a neutral "*suspiro* Qué estupidez. Los cerebros no funcionan así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6198
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_9825f662:

    # ks "They really don't."
    ks "Claro que no."

