translate spanish Day6_Redemption_5ccda6c3:

    # ks "But it's too late now. I tried to apologize, but they won't even look my way, so... s-so..." with dissolve
    ks "Pero ya es muy tarde. Intenté disculparme, pero ya ni siquiera quieren mirarme, a-... a-así que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6216
