    # ks surprised "Oh, well..."
    ks surprised "Oh, bueno..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6229
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_6358a113:

    # "Okay, then. I'll just tell her what she wants to know."
    "Pues bien. Creo que simplemente le diré lo que quiere saber."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6230
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_5362cffe:

    # ks neutral "So the idea is, hypnosis is about entering a state of focused attention. So I was using the light as a way of directing their attention to where I wanted it."
    ks neutral "La cosa es que la hipnosis se trata de entrar a un estado de atención concentrada. Así que uso la luz para dirigir la atención de alguien adonde la quiero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6231
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ab44440e:

    # ks "And while they're focusing on that, giving all their conscious thought to the light, I'm speaking to them, and my words find their way into their subconscious."
    ks "Y mientras se concentra en eso, poniendo todos sus pensamientos conscientes en la linterna, yo le hablo, y mis palabras logran entrar a su subconsciente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6232
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_84857db3:

    # a casual neutral "Their subconscious?" with dissolve
    a casual neutral "¿Su subconsciente?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6233
