    # "I smile as Akiko starts to lean in again, as if she'd already banished our unpleasant interlude from her mind."
    "Sonrío mientras Akiko comienza a inclinarse de nuevo, como si nuestro desagradable interludio ya se hubiera desvanecido de su mente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6234
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_5257db8a:

    # ks smile "Y-yeah! Their subconscious starts to take it in, and you can use it to suggest they're getting sleepy and hypnotized, and after that..."
    ks smile "¡S-sí! Su subconsciente comienza a absorberlo, y puedes usar eso para sugestionar que siente sueño y que está siendo hipnotizado, y después..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6235
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e1910876:

    # ks "Well, after that the real fun begins."
    ks "Bueno, después de eso comienza la diversión."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6236
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_3a3d7aa1:

    # a smirk "That's when you ask them to be your girlfriend." with dissolve
    a smirk "Ahí es cuando le pides que sea tu novia." with dissolve

