    # a neutral_side "What do they do to stop people smoking? Do they just tell their subconscious to quit?" with dissolve
    a neutral_side "¿Qué hacen para que la gente ya no fume? ¿Simplemente le dicen a su subconsciente que lo deje?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6245
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_b21e979b:

    # ks "I think it's more like... trying to ascribe a negative feeling to picking up a cigarette. Telling them to feel a really bad taste in their mouths... stuff like that."
    ks "Creo que más bien... intentan atribuir sentimientos negativos al cigarro. Decirles que sienten un terrible sabor de boca… cosas así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6246
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d7aa6e06:

    # a surprised "And that really works?" with dissolve
    a surprised "¿Y en serio funciona?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6247
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d1ead4ea:

    # ks "Of course! Maybe not for everybody, but some people find it really useful."
    ks "¡Por supuesto! Tal vez no para todos, pero es muy útil para muchas personas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6249
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_b727d4f0:

    # "She smiles in understanding, cutting up another piece of her pancake which has surely gotten cold by now." with dissolve
    "Sonríe con entendimiento, cortando otro trozo de su panqueque, el cual, a estas alturas, ya está frío." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6250
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c5c4636c:

