    # "Akiko takes a breath and sighs as she pulls the glasses from her face before rubbing her eyes." with dissolve
    "Akiko toma aire y suspira, quitándose los anteojos para frotarse los ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6426
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ce9c9939:

    # a sigh "Something tells me that didn't go like you wanted." with dissolve
    a sigh "Algo me dice que no salió como querías." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6427
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_5cd2403b:

    # ks neutral "You're right. I'm not sure what went wrong."
    ks neutral "Es correcto. No estoy seguro de qué salió mal."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6429
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_78f6cac8:

    # "My mind's racing as I sit beside her, while she slips her glasses back on and looks to me." with dissolve
    "La cabeza me da vueltas y me siento junto a ella, mientras vuelve a ponerse las gafas para mirarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6430
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_af5ee6df:

    # "What to do..."
    "¿Qué hago...?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6431
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_4899ae6a:

    # ks "Okay, can you tell me what was going through your head during all that?"
    ks "De acuerdo, ¿podrías decirme qué es lo que ocurría en tu cabeza?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6432
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d4ebb39d:

    # a sleep "Uh, sure. Let me think..." with dissolve
    a sleep "Eh, claro. Déjame pensar..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6433
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_257f0327:

    # a sigh "Well... I could feel my eyes were getting tired and a little dry, because I was staring at that picture for so long." with dissolve
    a sigh "Bueno... Mis ojos empezaban a sentirse cansados y un poco secos, porque miré la pintura por mucho tiempo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6434
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_b25c23d5:

    # a neutral "And I think you were saying I'm supposed to picture the alphabet in my head?" with dissolve
    a neutral "Y ¿creo que dijiste que debía visualizar las letras en mi cabeza?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6435
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_009b0b7b:

    # ks "Uhh..."
    ks "Eeeh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6436
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e7ec6b3a:

    # "I quickly bring up my phone and flick through my script."
    "Rápidamente alzo mi teléfono y hojeo el guion."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6437
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_03667bd9:

    # ks "Yeah, that's right."
    ks "Oh, sí, así fue."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6438
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_cd8b91ff:

    # a casual surprised "You wrote it down? Can I see?" with dissolve
    a casual surprised "¿Lo anotaste? ¿Puedo ver?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6439
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e4eda572:

    # "I look at her as she makes a move for my phone, and she takes my passivity as permission to pull it from my fingers as she looks at the screen."
    "La miro acercarse a mi teléfono, e interpreta mi pasividad como permiso para tomarlo de mis dedos, clavando sus ojos en la pantalla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6440
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_09fcefe4:

    # a neutral "Hmm... yeah, so I couldn't picture the letters at all. It was annoying me so I stopped trying and just kept saying the letters." with dissolve
    a neutral "Mmm... sí, no pude ver las letras. Y eso me molestaba, así que dejé de intentarlo, y simplemente continué diciéndolas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6441
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_1f9ba2e0:

    # ks frown "Oh... really?"
    ks frown "Oh... ¿en serio?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6442
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_b0a21ac7:

    # a smile "Yup! And I wasn't very interested in that tree either. I still looked at it, though." with dissolve
    a smile "¡Sipi! Y tampoco estaba muy interesada en el árbol. Pero sí lo estaba mirando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6444
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_42de415a:

    # "Akiko then taps her finger on a part of the text she's reading off my phone." with dissolve
    "Entonces Akiko pone su dedos en una parte del texto que está leyendo en mi teléfono." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6445
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_8505b703:

    # a "And... see here, when you started talking about relaxing and getting sleepy, that felt nice to listen to."
    a "Y... esto de aquí, cuando empezaste a hablar de relajación y de sueño, fue agradable de escuchar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6446
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_00698a7e:

    # a sad "But I don't know. I didn't really want to sleep on your couch just because you told me to." with dissolve
    a sad "Pero no sé. Creo que no quería dormirme en tu sofá solo porque me lo dijiste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6447
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_46cba7e5:

    # "She hands me my phone back and lets out another sigh."
    "Me devuelve el teléfono y suelta un suspiro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6448
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_3efb1e4d:

    # a casual_down sigh "It was interesting, don't get me wrong, but I don't really understand how it's supposed to work. Sorry." with dissolve
    a casual_down sigh "Fue interesante, no me malinterpretes, pero no entendí realmente cómo se supone que funcione. Lo siento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6449
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_4efe6ad6:

    # "I sigh in return, defeated."
    "Yo suspiro también, abatido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6450
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c301a496:

    # ks sigh "Yeah, it's not your fault. Thanks for letting me try it."
    ks sigh "Sí. No es tu culpa. Gracias por dejarme intentarlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6455
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_2b5e65f5:

    # "Akiko smiles as she stretches up from the couch."
    "Akiko sonríe, levantándose del sofá."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6456
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_26a05e1e:

    # a "Maybe I just can't be hypnotized~"
    a "Tal vez yo no puedo ser hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6603
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_7873d4ea:

    # ks casual sigh "Ah, th-that's not it. I just..."
    ks casual sigh "Ah, n-no es eso. Es que yo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6458
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c872b464:

    # "I'm just not that good a hypnotist after all."
    "No soy tan buen hipnotista, después de todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6459
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e3a6666c:

    # "Not without my penlight."
    "No sin mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6606
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_5014066c:

    # a casual laugh_wink "Well hey, at least I can say the rumours about you were greatly exaggerated!" with dissolve
    a casual laugh_wink "¡Pero oye, al menos puedo decir que los rumores sobre ti son una gran exageración!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6461
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_53f0d3f8:

    # ks surprised "Huh?!"
    ks surprised "¡¿Eh?!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6462
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_fa75a580:

    # a sad "Uh, about you hypnotizing girls to sleep with you?" with dissolve
    a sad "Em, ¿de que hipnotizas chicas para que duerman contigo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6463
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_736a9dce:

    # ks sigh "Oh, right. Yeah."
    ks sigh "Oh, claro. Seh."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6464
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_eedae265:

    # "Damn. She's trying to encourage me, but that's just a kick to the gut."
    "Demonios. Intenta animarme, pero eso fue una patada en el estómago."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6465
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_0200146e:

    # a smirk "I was only a little worried about that, just so you know." with dissolve
    a smirk "Eso me preocupaba solo un poquito, para que lo sepas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6467
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_4eb3343c:

    # a happy "Anyway, I should get ready for kendo practice now, so I'll see you at school?" with dissolve
    a happy "En fin, ya debería irme a la práctica de kendo, así que, ¿nos vemos en la escuela?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6470
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_9a0a19c5:

    # "All that study of hypnosis I did. The effort I put into applying what I learned into writing these hypnosis scripts..."
    "Todo lo que estudié sobre hipnosis. Todo el empeño que puse en aplicar lo que aprendí en escribir estos guiones de hipnosis..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6471
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_21e8c87d:

    # "Talking in front of a mirror to get my hypnotic patter right. All to help prepare for times like this."
    "Hablar frente al espejo para desarrollar mi ritmo hipnótico. Todo en espera de un momento como este."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6472
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d6f7804b:

    # "But when it came down to it..."
    "Pero a la hora de la verdad..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6475
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_71c2267f:

    # "Was this the only thing that mattered?"
    "¿Era esto lo único que importaba?"

