# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4461
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_64348c32:

    # "So then, steeling myself, I lean in towards her as I keep one hand on her legs as I announce my intentions..."
    "Entonces, armándome de valor, me inclino hacia ella, sin quitar la mano de sus piernas, anunciando mis intenciones..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4462
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fbb2396e:

    # ks smirk "Let's get you moved into a more comfortable position."
    ks smirk "Hay que ponerte en una posición más cómoda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4465
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3b485ae5:

    # n "K-Kyou?!"
    n "¡¿K-Kyou?!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4466
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f4f5198a:

    # ks casual smirk "It's not like you can move yourself, all tied up as you are."
    ks casual smirk "Claro, no puedes moverte sola si estás atada así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4467
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9f8a772c:

    # "Nozomi squeaks as her struggles only serve to keep the illusion of her bondage, leaving her helpless to my carefully re-arranging her on the floor of her bedroom."
    "Con un chillido, Nozomi forcejea, lo cual no hace más que reforzar la ilusión de las ataduras, dejándola indefensa y fácil de reacomodar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4469
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a89cdd01:

    # "... Like so."
    "... Así está mejor."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4470
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_86f8f148:

    # n "Ahh! Kyou, this isn't comfortable at all!"
    n "¡Aah! ¡Kyou, esto no es cómodo!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4471
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_302f60b0:

    # "And for her part, Nozomi still doesn't seem all that upset about her current situation if that's all she has to whine about."
    "Y por su parte, aún parece que Nozomi no está tan molesta por su situación actual, si esa es su única queja."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4473
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6630890c:

    # k "You're in a more comfortable position for ME, Nozomi." with dissolve
    k "Estás en una posición más cómoda para MÍ, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4474
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fef32fa8:

    # k "Why should I care if you're comfortable? You're being punished."
    k "¿Por qué debería importarme si tú estás cómoda? Estás siendo castigada..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4476
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_405b3a96:

    # n "Nnnrgh..." with dissolve
    n "Nnnñgh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4477
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ab2c81b3:

    # "Nozomi replies with a grunt as her body tenses and strains."
    "Nozomi responde con un gruñido, tensando su cuerpo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4479
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2479be3e:

    # "Those hypnotically-suggested ropes may have shifted position a little after I moved her, but as far as she's concerned they're still as inescapable as before." with dissolve
    "Puede que esas cuerdas hipnóticas se hayan movido un poco cuando la cambié de posición, pero en cuanto a ella concierne, siguen siendo igual de inescapables." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4481
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a5dab0cc:

    # k "Now where were we..." with dissolve
    k "Muy bien, en dónde estábamos..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4484
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_44a5037a:

    # "And without further warning, I run the fingertips of my free hand skittishly down the exposed soles of her feet." with dissolve
    "Y sin advertencia, paso un poco temeroso las yemas los dedos de mi otra mano por las plantas de sus pies." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4486
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7c53eeb4:

    # "And without further warning, I swipe my free hand down to swat her backside over her skirt."
    "Y sin advertencia, le doy una palmada con mi otra mano a su retaguarda por encima de su falda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4493
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2e40b510:

    # k "Aw, look at that. Seems my rival's the ticklish type."
    k "Oh, mira nada más. Parece que mi rival es cosquilluda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4497
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_76456844:

    # "Although my taunt buoys her a little, as her moment of weakness gives way to a determined growl while her body tenses defiantly." with dissolve
    "Aunque mi burla la mantiene un poco a flote, pues su pequeño momento de debilidad da lugar a una mirada determinada y la hace tensar su cuerpo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4498
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e475891a:

    # "That determination, I note, still doesn't extend to her actually kicking her feet away or making any move to defend herself."
    "Esa determinación, sin embargo, puedo notar que no es suficiente para alejar sus pies de mi mano o hacer algo para defenderse."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4500
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6e61d2b5:

    # k "You're not gonna try and kick me?"
    k "¿No intentarás patearme?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4503
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e0fa0d30:

    # k "Aw man, that doesn't sound like someone who's ready to give up. We need to do something about that, don't we?"
    k "Oh, vaya, esas no son las palabras de alguien que esté lista para rendirse. Hay que hacer algo al respecto, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5043
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9b21a817:

    # extend "M-MmMMPTH!"
    extend "¡M-MmMMFF!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4508
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c040ab72:

    # "I purposefully wait for her protesting reply before I tease my fingertips gently down the length of her soles once more."
    "Espero apropósito a que proteste antes de deslizar las puntas de mis dedos por sus suelas una vez más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4509
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3ae26238:

    # "She puffs haughtily through her nose as she struggles not to give me the satisfaction of hearing her laugh again."
    "Resopla altivamente por la nariz en una lucha por no darme la satisfacción de oír nuevamente su risa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4510
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b61c0f99:

    # "But I'm still barely stroking her skin here. How does she think she's going to hold out if I tickle her properly?"
    "Pero apenas estoy acariciando su piel. ¿Cuánto cree que resistirá si le hago cosquillas como se debe?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4512
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a79e2763:

    # k "What's the matter, Nozomi? Anything I can do to cheer you up?" with dissolve
    k "¿Qué sucede, Nozomi? ¿Hay algo que pueda hacer para animarte?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4514
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cd76a002:

    # "Without waiting for an answer, I drag my fingers a little more forcefully towards her heels while she snorts at the floor." with dissolve
    "Sin esperar su respuesta, arrastro mis dedos un poco más fuerte hacia sus talones, haciéndola resollar en el suelo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4515
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_71526974:

    # n "Nnngh!"
    n "¡Nnngh!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4517
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f69a339d:

    # k "You know, you'd feel a lot better if you just admitted I beat you." with dissolve
    k "¿Sabes?, te sentirás mucho mejor si tan solo admites que te vencí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4518
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5e290769:

    # n "{cps=10}NNNN... N- {w=1.0}{nw}{/cps}"
    n "{cps=10}NNNN... N- {w=1.0}{nw}{/cps}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4521
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8695bb33:

    # extend "SNNRRRRRK~"
    extend "SNNJJJJJK"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4522
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cd679514:

    # "This time I trace down the full length of each foot with a spidering motion as I up the intensity."
    "Esta vez revoloteo mis dedos de arriba abajo por ambos pies, con mayor intensidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4523
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_113aa80e:

    # "Now that she's started to crack, I decide that's enough playing around."
    "Ahora que está empezando a romperte, creo ya fueron suficientes juegos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4524
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_833fa1e6:

    # "I want to make her laugh."
    "Quiero hacerla reír."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4525
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6c82614c:

    # k "Right? I knew you'd see the funny side."
    k "¿Ves? Sabía que le verías el lado divertido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4526
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c871186a:

    # n "{cps=10}Shshsh... sh-shut {nw}{/cps}"
    n "{cps=10}Cjcjcj... c-cá{nw}{/cps}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4529
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_59c2ab12:

    # extend "AAHAHAHAHAHHAAAP!" with vpunch
    extend "LLAAJAJAJAJAJAAATEEE!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4532
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_239a147f:

    # k "Man, that's a cute laugh, Nozomi. I could listen to it all day." with dissolve
    k "Vaya, qué risa tan linda, Nozomi. Podría escucharla todo el día." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4535
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9708ed69:

    # n "Heeh... h-heeeeh~" with dissolve
    n "Jee... j-jeeee." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4537
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6bbe523d:

    # "I can't help but laugh a little with her as her breath catches, while she fights to control the giggles bubbling up inside her." with dissolve
    "No puedo evitar reírme un poco con ella mientras recupera el aliento, luchando por controlar las carcajadas que burbujean desde su interior." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4540
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_030eff20:

    # "The moment I ramp up again..." with dissolve
    "En cuanto vuelvo a atacar..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4545
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5cdeb24c:

    # n "Ahahahaha~ St-stohohohohop!"
    n "¡Ajajajaja D-detejejejejente!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4549
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a446a521:

    # k "If you're asking me to stop then does that mean you accept your defeat?" with dissolve
    k "Si me pides que me detenga, ¿significa que aceptas tu derrota?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4556
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c4d5ffc0:

    # k "Then I guess I'm gonna hear your cute laugh some more, huh. That's too bad."
    k "Entonces supongo que escucharé tu linda risa un rato más, ¿eh? Qué lástima."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4557
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d1c461c6:

    # n "AHAHAHAHA! HAHA! HAHAHAHAHA!" with shake
    n "¡AJAJAJAJA! ¡JAJA! ¡JAJAJAJAJA!" with shake

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4560
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6f97f2ed:

    # n "Ehehehehe... eheh... e-ehehehehehee!" with dissolve
    n "¡Jejejejeje... jeje... e-ejejejejejee!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4561
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6c4967c0:

    # k "Just tell me what I wanna hear, Nozomi. It's all you've got to do."
    k "Solo dime lo que quiero oír, Nozomi. Eso es todo lo que tienes que hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4565
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d5bc1465:

    # n "Nyayahahahaha! Haaah!" with dissolve
    n "¡Niajajajajaja! ¡Jaa!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4567
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_805a2eb9:

    # n "Pthh-okay! Hahahaha!"
    n "¡Pfft-está bien! ¡Jajajaja!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4570
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4e9dac61:

    # "Grinning widely, I withdraw my fingers just a little from her tortured feet." with dissolve
    "Sonriendo de oreja a oreja, alejo mis dedos solo un poco de sus torturados pies." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4572
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7a392ff8:

    # k "Alright, Nozo. I'm waiting." with dissolve
    k "Muy bien, Nozo. Estoy esperando." with dissolve

