    # k "So you're giving up?"
    k "¿Entonces te rindes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4581
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_db69c5ae:

    # n "Haaah... y-yeah..." with dissolve
    n "Jaaa... s-sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4582
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c5f5a2f7:

    # k "I won fair and square, right?"
    k "Gané justa y limpiamente, ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4583
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9618780f:

    # n "*sigh* Right... Fair and square."
    n "*suspiro* Cierto... Limpia y justamente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4585
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_297b96b9:

    # k "I won, you lost. Say it." with dissolve
    k "Yo gané, tú perdiste. Dilo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4586
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_66fefbe2:

    # n "... You won, I lost."
    n "... Tú ganaste, yo perdí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4587
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_faa3ec77:

    # k "And you proclaim me king of the settlers."
    k "Y me proclamas rey de los colonos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4591
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d3c1a912:

    # "I can't resist giving her toes another sly teasing." with dissolve
    "No me puedo resistir a darles a sus dedos otro toque furtivo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4592
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3679aa89:

    # n "E-eep! I-I proclaim you king of the settlers now please stop!"
    n "¡A-ay! ¡T-te proclamo rey de los colonos, ahora por favor para!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4603
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_79762239:

    # k "O-oh, come on, that wasn't even hard." with dissolve
    k "O-oh, vamos, eso no estuvo tan fuerte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4608
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_24c2ef8e:

    # k "And what WAS the point? Oh yeah..." with dissolve
    k "¿Y cuál SÍ es el punto? Ah, sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4614
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6510f65c:

    # k "The point is you're not accepting your position, Miss Akemi." with dissolve
    k "El punto es que no está aceptando su posición, Señorita Akemi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4616
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ed573a67:

    # "Nozomi growls as she wriggles under my grasp." with dissolve
    "Nozomi gruñe, meneándose bajo mi agarre." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4619
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d2f139d5:

    # k "See, that right there? That's bad." with dissolve
    k "¿Ves? De eso hablo. Eso está mal." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4620
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9634139f:

    # n "{cps=15}K-Kyou I'm... nng, I'm warning y-... {w=0.5}{nw}{/cps}"
    n "{cps=15}K-Kyou Te... nng, Te lo advier-... {w=0.5}{nw}{/cps}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4623
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5065f773:

    # extend "AHH!" with vpunch
    extend "¡AAH!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4627
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_197d6cc2:

    # k "But... but, Nozomi, you're the one who can make this stop."
    k "Pero... pero, Nozomi, tú eres quien puede hacer que esto pare."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4629
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_727798f7:

    # "I'm glad she can't see my face from here. I must be blushing pretty hard." with dissolve
    "Me alegra que no pueda ver mi rostro desde aquí. De seguro estoy muy sonrojado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4637
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2b666176:

    # n frown "Ugh, what are you even doing back there?!"
    n frown "Aj, ¡¿qué estás haciendo ahí atrás?!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4639
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c542880b:

    # k "This? This is more about what you're NOT doing!" with dissolve
    k "¿Esto? ¡Esto se trata más bien de lo que tú NO estás haciendo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4644
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_42056b9a:

    # "My palm cracks down on her vulnerable backside and she winces audibly. She definitely felt that one." with dissolve
    "Mi palma se estrella con su vulnerable retaguarda y ella se estremece. Ese definitivamente sí lo sintió." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4645
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_55e459be:

    # n "Tststststs..."
    n "Tststststs..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4646
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_847c34df:

    # k "Tell me I won."
    k "Dime que gané."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4657
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a648a603:

    # "I don't know if I'm settling into character or what, but her stubbornness is getting tiresome." with dissolve
    "No sé si me estoy metiendo en personaje o algo, pero su terquedad me está cansando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4658
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c9264cb4:

    # n concerned "Oh my god, Ky- {w=0.5}{nw}"
    n concerned "Oh, por Dios, Ky- {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4664
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d0d93063:

    # "So I withdraw my hold on her for a moment so I can rub my hands, which I'm thinking would also leave her a chance to pull away from me if she wanted." with dissolve
    "Así que suelto mi agarre un momento para poder frotarme las manos, lo cual creo que también le daría una oportunidad de alejarse si quisiera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4665
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bd1b7161:

    # "But although she groans and writhes beside me, her body and mind remain so resolutely disciplined to keep her mental bondage in place throughout."
    "Pero por más que gruña y se retuerza junto a mí, su cuerpo y mente permanecen firmemente determinados en mantener su restricción mental en su lugar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4666
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_85ef3803:

    # k "Now I think you have something to say to me, don't you."
    k "Me parece que tienes algo que decirme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4668
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fbcf1888:

    # "I can see her bite her lip as her rear tenses up again, like she's weighing up her options." with dissolve
    "Puedo verla morderse el labio mientras que su trasero se tensa de nuevo, como si estuviera valorando sus opciones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4670
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d6a9a445:

    # "And while she's doing that, I return my hand gently to her rump and give it a little stroke." with dissolve
    "Y mientras hace eso, llevo mi mano con gentileza de vuelta a su rabadilla y le doy un golpecito." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4675
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_caa9ef1c:

    # k "Fair and square?" with dissolve
    k "¿Justa y limpiamente?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4677
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_65fa01ea:

    # k "And you proclaim me king of the settlers?"
    k "¿Y me proclamas rey de los colonos?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4682
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d65dc202:

    # "I give her butt another, albeit more playful, smack." with dissolve
    "Le doy a su trasero otro coscorrón, un poco más juguetón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4683
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c19caf1a:

    # n surprised "E-eep! I-I proclaim you king of the settlers now please stop!"
    n surprised "¡A-ay! ¡T-te proclamo rey de los colonos, ahora por favor para!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4690
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6a544b6b:

    # "Just then we're interrupted by an obnoxious knocking on Nozomi's door." with dissolve
    "Y entonces nos interrumpen unos desagradables golpes en la puerta de Nozomi." with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-04-04 21:09

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2712
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e2d46c25:

    # "I get up to leave, but as I start to head out I notice three girls look to me and... was that pink-haired girl talking about me?"
    "Me pongo de pie para retirarme, pero cuando estoy por salir, noto a tres chicas mirándome y... ¿esa chica de cabello rosado estaba hablando de mí?"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-04-17 23:57

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2608
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_70343fb0:

    # s "But is it even an option for us? It seems you believe this is possible, Nozomi."
    s "¿Pero es siquiera una opción para nosotras? Pareces creer que es posible, Nozomi."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-04-25 19:45

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4820
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_20af6ea3:

    # "When morning comes, I find myself walking at a brisk pace."
    "Llega la mañana, y yo camino con paso apresurado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4821
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_91fee47e:

    # "Nozomi texted me again last night, insisting I stop by late in the morning."
    "Nozomi me mandó otro mensaje anoche, insistiendo en que llegara tarde por la mañana."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4823
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_24aa5c17:

    # "So here I am. Rolling up at this unfamiliar street at ten o'clock, and all of a sudden I stop dead in my tracks."
    "Así que heme aquí. Pasando por esta calle desconocida a las diez en punto, y mis pies se detienen de repente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4824
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fc7c2333:

    # "There's that feeling again. What if this really isn't her house?"
    "De nuevo esa sensación. ¿Qué tal si esta no es realmente su casa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4825
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4619ca0e:

    # "I don't want to knock on some stranger's door and get into that kind of situation..."
    "No quiero llamar a la puerta de algún extraño y terminar en esa clase de situación..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4826
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a6e97c50:

    # "But I don't want to back out either."
    "Pero tampoco me quiero echar para atrás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4827
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c06f7f70:

    # "Dammit. If Nozomi wasn't being so shifty I'd never be doubting her like this..."
    "Maldita sea. Si Nozomi no estuviera actuando tan sospechoso, no estaría dudando así de ella..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4829
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_143f6c1f:

    # n "Kyou? That... is you, isn't it?" with dissolve
    n "¿Kyou? Ese... eres tú, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4830
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_484910c8:

    # "Just then I realize the door in the distance has pulled open, revealing a familiar figure squinting at me from inside."
    "Entonces me doy cuenta de que la puerta a la distancia se ha abierto, revelando un rostro familiar que me mira desde adentro con los ojos entrecerrados."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4831
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2722a999:

    # ks casual surprised "N-Nozomi..."
    ks casual surprised "N-Nozomi..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4832
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7f09a767:

    # "So she really did mean for us to meet. That's reassuring, at least."
    "O sea que sí pretendía que nos reuniéramos. Eso es reconfortante, al menos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4833
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_098d2d6c:

    # n irritated "... Are you just going to stand there or do you want to come in?" with dissolve
    n irritated "... ¿Te vas a quedar ahí parado o quieres entrar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4838
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_da39d978:

    # "Stepping inside the spacious-looking house, I pop my shoes off while Nozomi watches me anxiously."
    "Tras adentrarme a la casa de aspecto espacioso, me quito los zapatos mientras Nozomi me mira nerviosa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4841
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_06ff5e88:

    # "In the meantime we're joined by someone else, who I can only assume is Nozomi's mother." with dissolve
    "En eso, se nos une alguien más, quien solo puedo asumir que es la madre de Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4843
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a9dfe501:

    # nm laugh "Welcome, Kyou! Nozomi told me we'd be having company today~" with dissolve
    nm laugh "¡Bienvenido, Kyou! Nozomi me dijo que tendríamos compañía hoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4844
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0cd1a8fc:

    # "This looks to be someone who doesn't get anxious a lot."
    "Parece alguien que no se pone nerviosa muy seguido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4845
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_af147211:

    # ks casual smile "N-nice to meet you..."
    ks casual smile "G-gusto en conocerla..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4846
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3564d9ca:

    # "Mrs. Akemi? I'm about to say, before she happily introduces herself."
    "¿Sra. Akemi?, estoy por decir, pero entonces ella se presenta felizmente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4848
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0137788f:

    # nm smile "Atsuko. It's a pleasure~" with dissolve
    nm smile "Atsuko. Es un placer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4849
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_685a6c4e:

    # nm smile_side "I believe you've met my daughter." with dissolve
    nm smile_side "Me parece que conoces a mi hija." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4851
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_24bb000c:

    # "Nozomi rolls her eyes." with dissolve
    "Nozomi rueda los ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4852
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4144add7:

    # n "Yes, mom. Kyou's a classmate of mine."
    n "Sí, mamá. Kyou es mi compañero de clase."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4853
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_855be797:

    # nm laugh "And that's wonderful~ It's nice to see who else you spend time with, Nozomi." with dissolve
    nm laugh "Maravilloso. Me alegra ver con qué otras personas convives, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4854
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4b0ea7b3:

    # nm smile "Anyway, make yourself at home, dear." with dissolve
    nm smile "En fin, siéntete como en casa, cariño." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4855
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dd47942a:

    # "Atsuko smiles, and I smile politely back."
    "Atsuko sonríe, y yo le devuelvo cortezmente la sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4856
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bbea1ad1:

    # ks "Thanks."
    ks "Gracias."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4858
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_35f0f1a8:

    # "It feels weird, to think out of the two of them that she seems happier to see me here than her daughter." with dissolve
    "Es extraño pensar que, de las dos, ella parezca más feliz de verme aquí que su hija." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4859
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_93ef9979:

    # "I guess it's awkward that I'm meeting Nozomi like this, but still..."
    "Supongo que es algo incómodo reunirme así con Nozomi, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4860
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_70180625:

    # n smile_side "S-so like I was telling you mom, Kyou's here to help me with a... um, class project." with dissolve
    n smile_side "P-pues, como te decía, mamá, Kyou vino a ayudarme con un... em, proyecto escolar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4861
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_91eb3769:

    # "Stealing my penlight is a \"class project\", huh?"
    "Robarme mi linterna es un \"proyecto escolar\", ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5273
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7dc12ec0:

    # nm happy "Oh, of course. Don't let me keep you!" with dissolve
    nm happy "Oh, por supuesto. No dejen que los detenga!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4864
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cbdcaba4:

    # "And with that, Nozomi ushers me upstairs."
    "Y con eso, Nozomi me dirige hacia las escaleras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4868
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b109b159:

    # "Leading me to..."
    "Llevándome a..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5360
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e3541af3:

    # ks casual confused "This is your room?"
    ks casual confused "¿Esta es tu habitación?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4872
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b7fe04fb:

    # "Nozomi lets out a little snort as she pulls the door closed behind her."
    "Nozomi suelta un pequeño resoplido, cerrando la puerta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4873
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_47314fc4:

    # n "Yeah, yeah, don't judge me."
    n "Sí, sí, no me juzgues."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4874
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a5fd9cfe:

    # "My eyes can't help but give her place a thorough looking over..."
    "Mis ojos no pueden evitar examinar a detalle el lugar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4875
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ab801f94:

    # ks sigh "There's stuff everywhere."
    ks sigh "Hay cosas por todos lados."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4876
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fcfe2f96:

    # "Like, where to begin? If it's not clothes dumped on the floor, it's piles of cardboard boxes... board games?"
    "O sea, ¿por dónde empezar? Si no es ropa desparramada en el suelo, son pilas de cajas de cartón… ¿juegos de mesa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4922
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4dc826d8:

    # n front2 annoyed_left "Yeah... I know." with dissolve
    n front2 annoyed_left "Sí, ya sé." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4924
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_051d05aa:

    # "Wow, there's a TON of board games here. From simple card games to some really obscure-looking advanced stuff." with dissolve
    "Guau, aquí hay MUCHÍSIMOS juegos de mesa. Desde simples juegos de cartas hasta algunos que lucen de lo más recóndito y avanzado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4883
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_931ef2e4:

    # n pout "A-Anyway, I've had more important things to worry about, like..." with dissolve
    n pout "E-en fin, he tenido cosas más importantes de las que preocuparme, como..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4884
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0f2243fd:

    # "I knew she hosts board game nights, but I had no idea she was this serious about it."
    "Sé que organiza noches de juegos de mesa, pero no tenía idea de que se lo tomara tan en serio."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4886
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_75092d3c:

    # n concerned "Er, Kyou?" with dissolve
    n concerned "Em, ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4887
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ec343bae:

    # "Oh, right. While I was busy examining her messed-up room, Nozomi had sat down on her bed."
    "Oh, claro. Mientras estaba ocupado examinando su desastre de habitación, Nozomi se había sentado en su cama."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4932
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d32c015a:

    # ks frown "Oh... y-yeah. More important things."
    ks frown "S-sí... Cosas más importantes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4890
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_42560d6e:

    # "I got so caught up in the experience of being in Nozomi's place that I forgot for a moment why I'm even here."
    "Estaba tan absorto en la experiencia de estar en la habitación de Nozomi, que olvidé por un momento por qué estoy aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4891
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a3c86dae:

    # n "So... we need to talk about what happened, don't we?"
    n "Pues... tenemos que hablar de lo que pasó, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4892
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4af52b01:

    # ks sigh "Yeah. Yeah, we do."
    ks sigh "Sí. Sí, es cierto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4893
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d7fa5b8e:

    # "As I agree, Nozomi picks her phone up from where it laid on her bed, then taps her thumb on the screen a few times."
    "Mientras me expresó de acuerdo, Nozomi toma su teléfono de donde yacía en la cama, luego toca la pantalla con su pulgar un par de veces."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4894
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2f5d2d92:

    # ks frown "So where is it?"
    ks frown "¿Y dónde está?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4895
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0e0bc94f:

    # n frown "I'll... I-I'll get to that, Kyou. But first..." with dissolve
    n frown "A... a eso voy, Kyou. Pero primero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4896
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7713d4a7:

    # "She falls silent as her eyes linger on her phone. I'm about to ask what she's looking at until I hear my own voice come out of her phone's speakers."
    "Se queda en silencio con los ojos fijos en su teléfono. Estoy a punto de preguntar qué está mirando cuando escucho mi propia voz salir de las bocinas del dispositivo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4898
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2cf702e4:

    # t "{b}You recognise this light, Nozomi. So you know how natural it is to want to look into it.{/b}"
    t "{b}Reconoces esta luz, Nozomi. Así que, sabes que es muy natural querer mirarla.{/b}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4899
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_16aede80:

    # n irritated "First I wanted to talk about what you said to me while I was hypnotized the other day." with dissolve
    n irritated "Primero quería hablarte de lo que me dijiste mientras estaba hipnotizada el otro día." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4900
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6a829a50:

    # n "Because, well..."
    n "Porque, pues..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4902
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d490bca4:

    # "Nozomi frowns as she presses her thumb on the screen again, silencing the audio for a moment." with dissolve
    "Nozomi frunce el ceño mientras vuelve a tocar la pantalla, silenciando el audio por un momento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4903
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e272b89e:

    # n "Something stood out..."
    n "Algo llamó mi atención..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4904
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_39fbda0a:

    # t "{b}So from now on, Nozomi, whenever we are alone in this house and I say \"[hypno3]\"...{/b}"
    t "{b}Así que, de ahora en adelante, Nozomi, siempre que estemos solos en esta casa y yo diga \"[hypno3!t]\"...{/b}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4905
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_07e3b073:

    # n neutral "Ah, right here." with dissolve
    n neutral "Ah, justo ahí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4906
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_19c5db73:

    # t "{b}You will find yourself compelled to become exactly what you believe a zombie to be.{/b}"
    t "{b}Vas a convertirte exactamente en lo que creas que un zombi es.{/b}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4907
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_028fff9f:

    # "Nozomi taps her thumb and the crappy-sounding speech on her phone falls silent once more."
    "Nozomi presiona con su pulgar y el sonido mierdero de su celular es silenciado una vez más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4908
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a50b9945:

    # ks sigh "Man, you ever thought about getting a decent phone? That thing sounds like it's had it."
    ks sigh "Caray, ¿has pensado en conseguirte un teléfono decente? Esa cosa suena a que ya no da para más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4909
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3638857a:

    # n surprised "Wh-what? No..." with dissolve
    n surprised "¿Qu-qué? No..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4911
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d14ed12e:

    # "Nozomi shakes her head and scoffs at me as she sets her cheapass phone down on her lap." with dissolve
    "Nozomi sacude la cabeza y se mofa, colocando su baratija de teléfono en su regazo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4912
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0cb6fce4:

    # n "Nevermind that, what do you think of this thing you said to me?"
    n "Olvídate de eso, ¿qué opinas de esto que me dijiste?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4913
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_331b3157:

    # ks neutral "O-oh, when I was explaining how your zombie trigger was supposed to work?"
    ks neutral "O-oh, ¿cuándo te expliqué cómo debía funcionar tu ancla de zombi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4914
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_90369dcf:

    # n "Yeah..."
    n "Sí..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4916
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f503b379:

    # "She sighs." with dissolve
    "Ella suspira." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4917
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e6e8b50a:

    # n "I mean, that's the thing. You didn't really explain it, you just left it to my subconscious to figure out."
    n "Es que esa es la cosa. Realmente no lo explicaste, dejaste que mi subconsciente lo descifrara."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4918
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_871e7d3a:

    # n neutral "\"You will find yourself compelled to become exactly what you believe a zombie to be.\"" with dissolve
    n neutral "\"Vas a convertirte exactamente en lo que creas que un zombi es.\"" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4919
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_86b6e1f4:

    # n angry "That's so open-ended!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡Eso es muy ambiguo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4920
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_be134a8b:

    # ks frown "Y-yeah, but..."
    ks frown "S-sí, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4922
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9851a677:

    # "I had my reasons for doing it that way." with dissolve
    "Tuve mis motivos para hacerlo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4923
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a6c1a8c1:

    # ks "You weren't sure about the whole thing so I thought, well... you should decide how you want to be a zombie in front of me."
    ks "No estabas muy convencida, así que pensé, bueno... que tú debías decidir cómo querías ser un zombi frente a mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4924
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ec685e8f:

    # n angry "But that's not what you said! You told me to be a zombie just like I think they are!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡Pero eso no es lo que dijiste! ¡Me dijiste que fuera un zombi tal cual creyera que son!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4925
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7600c867:

    # n "And zombies are scary! They... they're creatures of the night that shamble around and eat the flesh off your bones while ranting about brains!"
    n "¡Y los zombis dan miedo! Son... ¡son criaturas de la noche que se arrastran y arrancan carne de los huesos mientras gruñen por cerebros!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4926
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_af484e97:

    # n irritated "They're mindless, e-evil monsters and when you said the magic word, that's what I was supposed to be!" with dissolve
    n irritated "¡Son monstruos m-malignos e irracionales, y cuando dijiste la palabra mágica, eso es lo que se suponía que fuera!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4927
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4b9754cf:

    # n angry "So that's what I was, Kyou! You... y-you MADE me into that!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡Y eso fui, Kyou! Tú... ¡m-me CONVERTISTE en eso!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4928
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5159199e:

    # ks surprised "But..."
    ks surprised "Pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4930
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_55e2c4a8:

    # "I can't deny what happened two days ago in my living room. I saw it all." with dissolve
    "No puedo negar lo que paso hace dos días en la sala de mi casa. Lo vi todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4931
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_74e5f149:

    # "Nozomi was a shambling, slurring mess that wanted to eat me alive. I didn't imagine that."
    "Nozomi estaba arrastrándose y balbuceando sin parar, intentando comerme vivo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4932
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_da78fda5:

    # "And yet..."
    "Y sin embargo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4933
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4b1c2529:

    # ks "I didn't make you into that, Nozomi. It's impossible!"
    ks "Yo no ten convertí en eso, Nozomi. ¡Es imposible!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4934
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b97779c2:

    # n annoyed "I have a stinging pain in my right foot telling me it's not." with dissolve
    n annoyed "Tengo un dolor punzante en el pie diciéndome que es posible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4935
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e6eea93d:

    # ks sigh "No, I mean... it can't have been hypnosis! Or, o-or there was more than that going on!"
    ks sigh "No, quiero decir... ¡no pudo haber sido hipnosis! O... ¡ha-había algo más sucediendo!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4937
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0e5f28a0:

    # "Yeah. I gotta get away from the emotion of what went down and focus on the facts." with dissolve
    "Sí. Tengo que alejarme de la emociones generadas por lo que ocurrió y concentrarme a los hechos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4938
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_81ae9f9c:

    # ks neutral "Hypnosis can only guide a person into a focused, receptive state. It can't make you do literally anything you're told."
    ks neutral "La hipnosis solo puede guiar a alguien a un receptivo estado de concentración. No puede obligarte a hacer literalmente lo que sea que te digan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4939
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e47b65ef:

    # ks "So maybe I screwed up, but you should've only followed that command as much as you were comfortable with. As much as you were safe with."
    ks "Así que, tal vez metí la pata, pero tú solo debías seguir esa orden en tanto estuvieras cómoda haciendo. En tanto estuvieras a salvo haciéndolo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4940
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fbe7120f:

    # ks "Because, Nozomi, you're always in control no matter how deeply hypnotized you get. No matter how convincing I might be."
    ks "Porque, Nozomi, tú siempre tienes el control sin importar cuán profundamente hipnotizada estés. Sim importar lo convincente que sea."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4942
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a33ca971:

    # "Nozomi sighs loudly as she crosses her arms tightly in front of her." with dissolve
    "Nozomi suspira con fuerza y se cruza firmemente de brazos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4943
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4da5b538:

    # n "I know what you're talking about, Kyou. It's the hidden observer theory."
    n "Sé de qué estás hablando, Kyou. Es la teoría del observador oculto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4944
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_703e5e1a:

    # n annoyed_left "The idea that there's a separate consciousness that sits apart from a person's mind while they're hypnotized." with dissolve
    n annoyed_left "La idea de que hay una consciencia que se queda por separado de la mente de la persona mientras está hipnotizada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4945
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ae4f77ef:

    # n "No matter how much a hypnotist dissociates a hypnotized person from reality, that part of them should always hold an objective view of their reality."
    n "Sin importar cuánto disocie el hipnotista a la persona de su realidad, esa parte de ella mantendrá siempre una visión objetiva."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4946
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cd69515b:

    # n frown "So if it needs to, it can intervene." with dissolve
    n frown "De modo que, si hace falta, puede intervenir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4947
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_21d6e564:

    # n "It's why a deeply hypnotized person will still wake up if you left them alone for a while and they had to fulfill a basic need."
    n "Es por eso que una persona profundamente hipnotizada despertará si la dejas a solas por un rato y debe satisfacer alguna necesidad básica."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4948
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_712421be:

    # ks smirk "And I guess it's why hypnotists aren't ruling the world with their armies of brainwashed servants."
    ks smirk "Y supongo que es por eso que los hipnotistas no están dominando el mundo lavando cerebros y creando ejércitos de sirvientes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4949
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bb5bc772:

    # n pout_left "... Uh, sure." with dissolve
    n pout_left "... Eh, claro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4950
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7be1bcf6:

    # n neutral "But that's exactly the point, Kyou. There was no \"hidden observer\" to tell me I didn't seriously want to eat your brains or whatever." with dissolve
    n neutral "Pero ese es exactamente el punto, Kyou. No hubo ningún \"observador oculto\" que me dijera que en verdad no quería comerme tu cerebro o lo que sea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4951
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1d5761a3:

    # n irritated "Gosh, never mind this hidden observer stuff. Why didn't I feel ANYTHING when I hit my head or stepped on my glasses?" with dissolve
    n irritated "Dios, ya ni hablemos de lo del observador. ¿Por qué no sentí NADA cuando me golpeé la cabeza o pisé mis anteojos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4952
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a1d688e6:

    # n frown "Why couldn't I stop myself? Why didn't I acknowledge the reality of the situation no matter what happened to me?" with dissolve
    n frown "¿Por qué no podía detenerme? ¿Por qué no me di cuenta de la situación sin importar lo que me ocurriera?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4954
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c07b8827:

    # "Nozomi grips the sleeves of her sweater as she sighs harshly through her nose." with dissolve
    "Nozomi aprieta las mangas de su suéter, suspirando duramente por la nariz." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4955
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_aaf903f4:

    # n "It kept me up all night thinking about it."
    n "Estuve despierta toda la noche pensando en eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4956
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f877837e:

    # n concerned "And the more I thought about it, the more I was convinced that it could've only been caused by one thing." with dissolve
    n concerned "Y entre más lo pensaba, más convencida estaba de que solo pudo causarlo una cosa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4957
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_19efb262:

    # ks neutral "What's that?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4959
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e98f3ab3:

    # "Nozomi scoffs at me. Like I was supposed to know what she's talking about." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se mofa. Como si yo tuviera que saber de qué habla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4960
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d46b7e89:

    # n "The only thing that I can't figure out at all."
    n "La única cosa que no logro entender."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4962
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_14329e83:

    # "As her statement hangs in the air, her expression softens." with dissolve
    "Con esa declaración en el aire, su expresión se suaviza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4963
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_454ac30f:

    # "Her hand then slides with some reluctance towards her pillow, reaching underneath it before pulling back holding a familiar object..."
    "Luego su mano se desliza con cierta renuencia por debajo de su almohada, sacando de ahí un objeto familiar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4966
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6c70857d:

    # n concerned "I'm talking about this, Kyou." with dissolve
    n concerned "Hablo de esto, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4969
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_723694fa:

    # "AUTHOR'S NOTE - This marks the end of this storyline for the time being."
    "NOTA DE LA AUTORA – Esto marca el final de esta línea de momento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4970
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_22403a29:

    # "The whole script is still being worked on, so things may change further from what's currently been presented."
    "Aún se está trabajando en la historia, por lo que las cosas podrían cambiar con respecto a lo que hay actualmente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4971
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1a4e15f1:

    # "Still, I hope you enjoyed what's been written so far, and that you'll look forward to the next update~"
    "Aun así, espero que hayan disfrutado lo que hay escrito hasta ahora, y esperen con ansias la próxima actualización."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4972
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a00cf8c4:

    # "TO BE CONTINUED..."
    "CONTINUARÁ..."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 6.rpy:4842
    old "Nozomi's Mom"
    new "Mamá de Nozomi"

    # game/Kyou 6.rpy:4897
    old "Nozomi's Phone"
    new "Teléfono de Nozomi"
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-05-25 08:08

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4865
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_722894ea:

    # n smile_side "S-so like I was telling you mom, Kyou's here to help me with a... um, class project. And we have a lot of ground to cover, you know?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "P-pues, como te decía, mamá, Kyou vino a ayudarme con un... em, proyecto escolar. Y tenemos mucho qué trabajar, ¿sabes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4866
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f9de0fa7:

    # nm happy "Oh, of course. Don't let me stop you!" with dissolve
    nm happy "Oh, por supuesto. ¡No los entretengo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4867
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e9756534:

    # "Taking my penlight to play with is a \"class project\", huh?"
    "Llevarse mi linterna para jugar es un \"proyecto escolar\", ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4868
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ddb76eea:

    # nm laugh "Just promise me you'll behave yourselves while I go food shopping~" with dissolve
    nm laugh "Solo prométanme que se comportarán mientras voy a comprar víveres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4869
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_15a4e51f:

    # n frown_side blush "O-of COURSE we'll behave ourselves!" with dissolve
    n frown_side blush "¡P-por SUPUESTO que nos comportaremos!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4871
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1faaa5f1:

    # "Nozomi scoffs as her mother chuckles to herself and makes ready to leave." with dissolve
    "Nozomi frunce el ceño mientras su madre se ríe y se prepara para salir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4872
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8393b19d:

    # n frown "Let's go, Kyou." with dissolve
    n frown "Vamos, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4884
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ed6a404f:

    # "My eyes can't help but give her room a thorough looking over..."
    "Mis ojos no pueden evitar examinar la alcoba a detalle..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4893
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f8abbe80:

    # "It's not what I expected from a girl's bedroom, that's for sure."
    "No es lo que esperaba de la habitación de una chica, eso está claro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4901
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_425c88bd:

    # "I got so caught up in the experience of being in Nozomi's bedroom that I forgot for a moment why I'm even here."
    "Estaba tan absorto en la experiencia de estar en la alcoba de Nozomi, que olvidé por un momento por qué estoy aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4902
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c1c28f8b:

    # "But to get to the point, Nozomi pulls open her desk drawer and, with some seeming reluctance, takes out a familiar object..."
    "Pero yendo al grano, Nozomi abre el cajón de su escritorio y, con aparente renuencia, saca un objeto familiar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4907
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_23aa2ab5:

    # "That's it all right. My penlight doesn't look any different to all the others of its kind, but she couldn't have found a copy of that exact model so quickly."
    "Definitivamente es la mía. Mi linterna no se ve diferente a otras de su tipo, pero no pudo haber encontrado una copia de exactamente el mismo modelo tan rápido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4908
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3d304aea:

    # "... That I even considered she could be deceiving me sure is a depressing thing to think about."
    "... Que haya siquiera considerado que pueda estarme engañando es algo muy deprimente cuando lo pienso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4910
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_12994b90:

    # n side sad "You... said you made this, right?" with dissolve
    n side sad "Dijiste... que tú la hiciste, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4912
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2beb07ca:

    # "I frown at her and nod."
    "Frunciendo el ceño, le asiento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4948
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e33e011b:

    # ks frown "Yeah. Well, it's an off-the-shelf medical penlight that I modified a little."
    ks frown "Sí. Bueno, es una pluma linterna médica comercial que modifiqué un poco."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4914
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b78df8df:

    # n sad_closed "Right. So, uhh..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Claro. Y, eeh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4915
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_84ef5286:

    # "I might still be annoyed about what she pulled the other day, but I can't deny I'm also really interested to hear what she did with my penlight while she's had it."
    "Puede que aún esté molesto por lo que hizo el otro día, pero no negaré que también estoy muy interesado en lo que hizo con mi linterna mientras la tuvo consigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4916
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dfa106a6:

    # ks neutral "What is it?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4918
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4ffa3a75:

    # "Nozomi looks anxiously at the penlight in her hand as she begins to answer." with dissolve
    "Nozomi mira nerviosa la linterna que tiene en su mano mientras comienza su respuesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4919
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a377414a:

    # n front concerned "Okay, so... when I got back home, I was starting to feel silly for making such a big deal about this thing." with dissolve
    n front concerned "Bien, pues... cuando volví a casa, me sentí un poco tonta por hacer tanto escándalo por esta cosa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4920
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4e175c27:

    # n neutral "But after dinner, I locked myself in this room and... I switched it on." with dissolve
    n neutral "Pero después de cenar, me encerré en esta habitación y... la encendí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5450
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ec068c1a:

    # n neutral_left "And I... w-well..." with dissolve
    n neutral_left "Y entonces... e-este..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4922
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_747a73e4:

    # ks frown "You tried shining the light in your own eyes."
    ks frown "Probaste apuntar la luz a tus propios ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4955
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6f15c9b2:

    # n front2 sleep "Mhm..." with dissolve
    n front2 sleep "Mjm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4924
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_994fc193:

    # "I mean, what else was she going to do with it?"
    "Bueno, ¿qué otra cosa iba a hacer con ella?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4925
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_64e32041:

    # "Just then, Nozomi falls back onto her bed and holds the penlight up in front of her before pointing the end towards her face."
    "En ese momento, Nozomi se recuesta en su cama y sujeta la linterna en el aire, para luego dirigirla hacia su rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4926
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_808d1c3c:

    # n frown "I laid down and held it at arm's length, like this. I was trying to shine it back and forth over my face, just like you did." with dissolve
    n frown "Me acosté y la sostuve a un brazo de distancia, así. Intenté moverla de lado a lado sobre mi rostro, como hiciste tú." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4927
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_42773e9c:

    # n neutral "But as soon as the light hit my eyes, I felt instantly drawn to it. Just like before." with dissolve
    n neutral "Pero en cuanto la luz golpeó mis ojos, me sentí instantáneamente atraída a ella. Igual que antes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4928
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dcf9f0d6:

    # n sleep "After that... it was almost automatic." with dissolve
    n sleep "Después de eso... fue casi automático." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4929
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0d62917e:

    # n sleeptalk "I kept moving the light over my eyes, feeling kinda relaxed about the whole thing." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Seguí deslizando la luz por mis ojos, empezaba a sentirme relajada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4930
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9cd47394:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "So I kept doing it, and I think at some point a light must have switched off in my own head." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Así que continué haciéndolo, y creo que en algún momento las luces se apagaron dentro de mi cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4931
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3954a649:

    # n concerned "Because the next thing I remember, I was crying out after I dropped the penlight on my face." with dissolve
    n concerned "Porque lo siguiente que recuerdo es pegar un grito cuando la linterna me cayó en la cara." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5420
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_04184e3f:

    # ks casual confused "You... dropped it on your face?"
    ks casual confused "¿Se... te cayó en la cara?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4933
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c767500d:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned blush "T-that's what I said." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned blush "E-eso dije." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4934
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_27f2f5c2:

    # n pout_left "A-anyway, after that I put your penlight in my desk drawer and I didn't dare use it again." with dissolve
    n pout_left "E-en fin, después de eso puse tu linterna en el cajón de mi escritorio y no me atreví a usarla otra vez." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4935
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e5aa1072:

    # n pout "I mean... I proved what I wanted to prove, anyway." with dissolve
    n pout "Digo... de todas formas ya probé lo que quería probar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4936
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_aa6819bf:

    # ks neutral "And what was that?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4938
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2123f5c1:

    # "She sits back up and faces me, crossing her legs as she brings the penlight in her hand down to rest uncomfortably in her lap." with dissolve
    "Vuelve a sentarse para mirarme, cruzando las piernas y dejando la linterna incómodamente posada en su regazo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4939
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0ee59194:

    # n "I managed to deeply hypnotize myself with barely any effort at all. Without you or anyone else guiding me. Just this penlight."
    n "Logré hipnotizarme profundamente sin apenas ningún esfuerzo. Sin ti ni nadie que me guiara. Solo la linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4988
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b3cc87da:

    # n "But what would have happened if I heard someone talking while I was spacing out like that?"
    n "Pero ¿qué habría pasado si hubiera oído a alguien hablar mientras estaba en ese trance?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4941
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8cfc2ff0:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "Might I have taken their words into my subconscious and acted on them?" with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "¿Habría absorbido sus palabras en mi subconsciente y actuado conforme a ellas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4942
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_77d7e00d:

    # n surprised "Or what if I left the tv on? I could've woken up and gone right outside to buy some of that limited edition french toast flavour ice cream they've been pushing lately!" with dissolve
    n surprised "¿Y si hubiera dejado la tele encendida? ¡Podría haber despertado e ido directo a comprar una de esas tostadas francesas sabor helado edición limitada de los anuncios!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4943
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b954c722:

    # ks "Y-yeah... that would've been awful."
    ks "S-seh... eso habría estado feo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4944
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a562fa2e:

    # n shocked "W-what would've happened if I didn't drop the penlight on my face? I could've been stuck in a trance until someone broke into my room and woke me up!" with dissolve
    n shocked "¿Qu-qué tal si no hubiera soltado la linterna en mi cara? ¡Podría haberme quedado atrapada en un trance hasta que alguien irrumpiera en mi habitación y me despertara!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4945
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5701877f:

    # ks sigh "Oh come on, Nozomi, you know that's..."
    ks sigh "Ay, vamos, Nozomi, sabes que eso es..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4947
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ab187d26:

    # "Nozomi frowns at me and at the same time I stop what I'm saying." with dissolve
    "Nozomi me frunce el ceño a la vez que interrumpo lo que estoy diciendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4948
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4573dee3:

    # n "Impossible. Except we know it's not. Not after what's been happening to me."
    n "Imposible. Excepto que no lo es. No después de lo que me ha estado pasando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5000
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_27e748d7:

    # n "The night of the dead changed everything."
    n "La noche de los muertos lo cambió todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5498
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d274f202:

    # ks confused "Is that what we're calling it now?"
    ks confused "¿Así la llamamos ahora?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4951
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fa365bdf:

    # n side neutral_side "Call it whatever you want, but you know I'm not just fantasizing about how dangerous hypnosis is." with dissolve
    n side neutral_side "Llámala como quieras, pero sabes que no estoy fantaseando sobre lo peligrosa que es la hipnosis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4955
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_df113f75:

    # n front surprised "This light really IS the reason your hypnosis worked so well on me!" with dissolve
    n front surprised "¡Esta linterna realmente ES la razón por la que tu hipnosis funcionó tan bien en mí!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4956
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a93245f1:

    # n shocked "It's the reason I stayed like a zombie no matter how much pain I was in. It HAS to be!" with dissolve
    n shocked "Es la razón por la que me quedé como zombi sin importar cuánto dolor sintiera. ¡TIENE que serlo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4958
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_09340a90:

    # "If it wasn't for the other night, I would've thought Nozomi was just letting her imagination get the better of her."
    "De no ser por la otra noche, habría pensado que Nozomi se está dejando llevar por su imaginación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4959
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_66f3e8dc:

    # "But I have to believe that Nozomi really is experiencing a deep form of hypnotic suggestibility that I hadn't thought possible."
    "Pero he de creer que Nozomi sí está experimentando algún profundo tipo de sugestibilidad hipnótica que nunca creí posible."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4961
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bcef399e:

    # "And that my penlight was what brought it about."
    "Y que mi linterna fue la que la provocó."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-05-27 07:12

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4963
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f10f1e7a:

    # "*** AUTHOR'S NOTE - The dialogue past this is gonna be extremely rough and ready."
    "*** NOTA DE LA AUTORA – El diálogo a partir de ahora será extremadamente burdo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4964
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fa8e3d57:

    # "I hate to do it, although it's a more effective a writing technique than agonizing over every single line; I can edit everything later. Here we go! ***"
    "Detesto hacerlo, pero es una técnica de escritura más efectiva que agonizar por cada detallito; puedo editar todo luego. ¡Aquí vamos! ***"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4965
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a044a07f:

    # ks sigh "Well... if you really thought it was that dangerous why did you take it and use it on yourself?"
    ks sigh "Bueno... si en serio pensabas que era tan peligrosa, ¿por qué la tomaste y la usaste en ti mismsa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4966
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_82ab485d:

    # n frown "Because I had to know for sure. And I took it because I didn't think I could trust you!" with dissolve
    n frown "Porque tenía que estar segura. ¡Y la tomé porque no creí que pudiera confiar en ti!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4967
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d94a1986:

    # n side sad_side "You made this thing. You must have known what it was capable of, right?" with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Tú hiciste esta cosa. Debes saber de qué es capaz, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4968
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e96448b6:

    # ks "I made it to help catch people's attention, I didn't think it'd work as well as this!"
    ks "La hice para atraer más fácilmente la atención de la gente, ¡no pensé que funcionaría tan bien!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4969
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ef40731f:

    # n sad_closed "Yeah... After I thought about it some more, I had to wonder how much you really knew." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Sí... Tras pensarlo un poco más, me empecé a preguntar qué tanto sabías." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4970
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5b2e9e80:

    # n "And I realized if you really knew what this thing was capable of, a lot of things would be different."
    n "Y me di cuenta de que, si supieras realmente de lo que esto es capaz, muchas cosas habrían sido diferentes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4971
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_84028d0d:

    # n sad "You wouldn't have let me leave with your penlight if you knew how powerful it was, no matter how many ultimatums I gave." with dissolve
    n sad "No me habrías dejado irme con tu linterna si hubieras sabido lo poderosa que es, sin importar cuántos ultimátums te diera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4972
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f3dc69d6:

    # n "So I'm sorry, Kyou. I was scared, but I should've been more honest about my feelings and what my intentions were."
    n "Así que, lo siento, Kyou. Tenía miedo, pero pude a ver sido más honesta sobre mis sentimientos y cuáles eran mis intenciones."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4973
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_91f2c4e8:

    # "I nod. I'm not really that mad at her anymore, now that I've heard her out."
    "Asiento con la cabeza. Ya ni siquiera estoy tan molesto con ella, ahora que pude escucharla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4974
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f73ae047:

    # "Still, all this does beg the question..."
    "Sin embargo, esto nos deja una pregunta..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4975
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2854f132:

    # ks neutral "What do we do now?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué hacemos ahora?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4976
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f9b03655:

    # n front concerned "Well, I was thinking..." with dissolve
    n front concerned "Bueno, estaba pensando..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4979
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2898dfeb:

    # "Just then, there's an obnoxious knocking on the bedroom door." with dissolve
    "De pronto, suenan unos desagradables golpes en la puerta de la habitación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4980
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c8ff96c9:

    # nm "Nozomi? Kyou? Is it safe to come in?"
    nm "¿Nozomi? ¿Kyou? ¿Es seguro entrar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4981
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7b163477:

    # "Just then, Nozomi hurriedly stuffs the penlight back in her desk drawer and slams it shut."
    "En ese momento, Nozomi se apresura a ocultar la linterna de regreso en su cajón y lo cierra de un azote."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4982
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b1bbfd6a:

    # n side frown_side "U-uh, just a moment!" with dissolve
    n side frown_side "¡E-eh, un momento!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4985
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bb5aa5a6:

    # "Nozomi quickly hops off the bed and hurries to the door, but not before sparing me a glance and holding a finger to her lips."
    "Nozomi salta rápidamente de la cama y corre hasta la puerta, pero no sin antes echarme una mirada y poner un dedo frente a sus labios."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4988
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c2c225ce:

    # n smile_side "Okay, come in!" with dissolve
    n smile_side "¡Muy bien, pasa!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4993
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_23b47cac:

    # "The invitation barely leaves Nozomi's mouth before the door swings open and a smiling Atsuko strolls inside." with dissolve
    "La invitación apenas escapa de la boca de Nozomi cuando la puerta se abre, dando paso a una sonriente Atsuko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4994
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a4128e37:

    # nm "Sorry for barging in on you two. Hope I wasn't interrupting anything~"
    nm "Perdón por invadirlos así. Espero no estar interrumpiendo nada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4998
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7db8a8a2:

    # "Nozomi sighs." with dissolve
    "Nozomi suspira." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4999
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7a38498a:

    # n "No, mom. Me and Kyou were just talking."
    n "No, mamá. Kyou y yo solo estábamos hablando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5082
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f31aab5e:

    # ks casual sigh "Y-yeah. About the project."
    ks casual sigh "S-sí. Del proyecto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5001
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9ff4a8a6:

    # nm neutral_side "All going well, I hope?" with dissolve
    nm neutral_side "¿Todo va bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5003
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_342116b6:

    # ks neutral "Uhh... good. Yeah, good." with dissolve
    ks neutral "Eeh... bien. Sí, bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5004
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c7140b47:

    # n neutral_side "We were just going over some things, mom." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Solo estábamos repasando algunas cosas, mamá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5006
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f9005e24:

    # "Atsuko giggles mischievously." with dissolve
    "Atsuko se ríe con picardía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5007
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a3c0665d:

    # nm "Alright~ But do take a break some time, okay? I got some snacks for the fridge."
    nm "Muy bien. Pero tómense algún descanso, ¿sí? Tengo bocadillos en el refrigerador."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5008
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_33975a94:

    # n smile_side "Thanks, mom. We'll be down for lunch in an hour." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Gracias, mamá. Bajaremos a almorzar en una hora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5009
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_699d88ba:

    # nm smile "Wonderful! Well then, I'll leave you to it~" with dissolve
    nm smile "¡Maravilloso! Muy bien, yo me retiro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5012
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1c67e300:

    # "Atsuko closes the door behind her as she leaves us to it."
    "Atsuko cierra la puerta, dejándonos solos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5013
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0951c275:

    # ks smile "Your mom seems nice."
    ks smile "Tu mamá parece agradable."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5015
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7db8a8a2_1:

    # "Nozomi sighs." with dissolve
    "Nozomi suspira." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5016
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a840592c:

    # n sad "She is, even if she smothers me and Ichiro a bit." with dissolve
    n sad "Lo es, a pesar de que nos sofoque un poco a Ichiro y a mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5017
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_057fb5d8:

    # ks neutral "Ichiro?"
    ks neutral "¿Ichiro?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5018
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0e74354f:

    # n smile "Oh, didn't I tell you? He's my little brother." with dissolve
    n smile "Oh, ¿no te conté? Es mi hermanito." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5019
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d950d6d5:

    # "It had been a curiosity at the back of my mind, about what Nozomi's family is like."
    "Sí tenía un poco de curiosidad de saber cómo es la familia de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5020
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f60e5a06:

    # n front smile "You might have even met him in passing. He's a first year at our school." with dissolve
    n front smile "Puede que incluso lo hayas visto por ahí. Está en primer año en nuestra escuela." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5021
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4244cfe3:

    # n chuckle "Anyway..." with dissolve
    n chuckle "Como sea..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5563
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0d4e0124:

    # "Nozomi pulls her desk drawer open and takes my penlight back out of there..." with dissolve
    "Nozomi abre el cajón de su escritorio y vuelve a sacar mi linterna..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5025
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ab07e7cf:

    # "... and then hands it to me."
    "... y luego me la entrega."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5117
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3e8b3d53:

    # n front2 smile "Thanks for letting me borrow this. But I think it's better if you had it back." with dissolve
    n front2 smile "Gracias por prestármela. Pero creo que es mejor devolvértela." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5028
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8f912347:

    # "I take it from her, although it feels a bit weird now, after what we've been talking about before her mom stepped in."
    "La tomo de su mano, aunque ahora se siente algo extraño, después de lo que estuvimos discutiendo antes de que entrara su mamá."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5029
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fb44b871:

    # n side neutral_side "At least now if something happens, there'll be someone nearby who can help." with dissolve
    n side neutral_side "Al menos ahora, si algo pasa, habrá alguien cerca que pueda ayudar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5030
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_725d9fbf:

    # ks surprised "Huh? But aren't you worried your mom will find out about your secret?"
    ks surprised "¿Eh? Pero ¿no te preocupa que tu mamá descubra tu secreto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5031
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fc6b07a1:

    # "Nozomi nods."
    "Nozomi asiente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5032
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_75bb177a:

    # n neutral "I am. But I've given this a lot of thought, and if we're going to keep doing hypnosis together then I have to think about my own safety." with dissolve
    n neutral "Sí. Pero ya lo pensé bastante, y si vamos a seguir haciendo hipnosis juntos, tengo que pensar en mi propia seguridad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5033
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_18cdc38c:

    # "Her own safety?"
    "¿Su propia seguridad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5034
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ef9ef81f:

    # ks frown "What, so you still don't trust me?"
    ks frown "¿Qué, entonces aún no confías en mí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5035
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_98c9742c:

    # n front annoyed_left "It doesn't matter if I trust you, Kyou. We've seen what your penlight can do to me, even if you didn't mean it to." with dissolve
    n front annoyed_left "No importa si confío en ti, Kyou. Ya vimos lo que tu linterna puede hacerme, por más que no fuera tu intención." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5036
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f4ecfc68:

    # n neutral "We know it's dangerous, and knowing what I do now, it's made everything I've done with you so far really scary..." with dissolve
    n neutral "Sabemos que es peligrosa, y sabiendo lo que sé ahora, todo lo que he hecho contigo ahora es muy aterrador..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5586
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1ea2fa89:

    # n front frown blush "But I also won't deny it's given me the best experience of hypnosis in my entire life." with dissolve
    n front frown blush "Pero no negaré que también me ha dado la mejor experiencia de hipnosis de toda mi vida." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5587
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e3c662da:

    # ks confused "S-so, what are you saying?"
    ks confused "E-entonces, ¿qué es lo que dices?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5039
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d0c4b03a:

    # n sleeptalk "I'm saying... I want us to try doing more things with your penlight. It's dangerous, but we know to be more careful now." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Digo... que quiero que intentemos hacer más cosas con tu linterna. Es peligrosa, pero ahora sabemos que hay que ser cuidadosos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5040
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_017dcd36:

    # n frown "And I feel there are so many unanswered questions about it." with dissolve
    n frown "Y siento que guarda tantas preguntas sin respuesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5041
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6d4e6550:

    # n side neutral "Like is it just me who's affected by your penlight so extremely, or will it do the same for others?" with dissolve
    n side neutral "Como ¿soy solo yo la que es afectada a tal extremo por tu linterna, o les hará lo mismo a otros?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5042
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_05ce5ef4:

    # n sad_side "But more importantly... can we use it to achieve a state of hypnosis and induce suggestions that doesn't end up hurting me? O-or anyone?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Pero más importante... ¿podemos usarla para alcanzar un estado de hipnosis e inducir sugestiones que no me hieran? ¿A-a mí o nadie?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5043
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e6198b2f:

    # n sad_closed "Because I really want to believe we can." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Porque en serio quiero creer que sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5044
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_da8975bb:

    # n sad "But what do you think, Kyou? You've made something... amazing." with dissolve
    n sad "Pero ¿tú qué opinas, Kyou? Hiciste algo... asombroso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5045
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_41cbb1d8:

    # "Looking down at my penlight, I start to feel a little sense of pride."
    "Dándole un vistazo a mi linterna, empiezo a sentir una ligera sensación de orgullo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5046
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2ef9964f:

    # n front smile "Do you want to find out more about it with me?" with dissolve
    n front smile "¿Quieres aprender más sobre ella conmigo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5047
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1f6d20bc:

    # "And as I look to her, I'm feeling a rush of excitement."
    "Y al mirarla a ella, siento una descarga de emoción."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5049
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_68bd3703:

    # ks smile blush "Yeah. Of course that's what I want."
    ks smile blush "Sí. Claro que eso quiero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5050
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_63934b3d:

    # "We smile at each other in silence for a moment."
    "Nos sonreímos el uno al otro en silencio por un momento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5051
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fdec83e2:

    # "It's been an awkward few days between us, but right now it feels like we're starting to understand each other."
    "Los últimos días han sido bastante incómodos para nosotros, pero ahora mismo parece que estamos empezando a entendernos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5053
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ae895163:

    # "Nozomi's eyes start to wander from me to the penlight now in my hands." with dissolve
    "Los ojos de Nozomi pasan de mí a mi linterna, la cual se encuentra ahora en mi mano." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5054
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_db15327f:

    # n "Okay then, so... let's review what we DO know."
    n "Muy bien, pues... repasemos lo que SÍ sabemos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5055
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cbd376a6:

    # ks frown noblush "Right. So, this is an off-the-shelf medical penlight that I bought from the internet."
    ks frown noblush "Claro. Pues, esta es una pluma linterna médica comercial que compré en internet."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5056
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d5f15339:

    # ks "It was pretty cheap, which was important since I was gonna take it apart and maybe break it."
    ks "Fue muy barata, lo cual era importante, ya que iba a desmantelarla y tal vez romperla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5057
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2fea05d0:

    # n frown "So that also means there's nothing special about the light itself, I guess?" with dissolve
    n frown "Eso también significa que la luz en sí no tiene nada de especial, supongo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5058
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_63649aea:

    # ks neutral "Yeah. The intensity and beam width are pretty standard."
    ks neutral "Sí. La intensidad y el tamaño del haz son bastante estándar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5059
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1a2f7527:

    # n side neutral_side "Okay. So what's special about the pattern you put on it?" with dissolve
    n side neutral_side "Muy bien. ¿Y qué tiene de especial el patrón que le pusiste?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5060
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7d39c6c1:

    # ks frown "I... It's a little complicated, I guess. I don't think it looks like anything in particular."
    ks frown "Eh... es un poco complicado, supongo. No creo que se parezca a nada en particular."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5061
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_90cb3bae:

    # n neutral "And that's why you thought it'd catch the eye so well? Because it doesn't look like anything?" with dissolve
    n neutral "¿Y por eso creías que atraería la mirada tan bien? ¿Porque no es parecido a nada?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5062
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9d70bab8:

    # ks neutral "Yeah. I have no idea why it worked on you as well as it does, though."
    ks neutral "Sí. Pero no tengo idea de por qué funcionó así de bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5063
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e25da122:

    # n sad "Could there be a way to make it work... less well? Like turning down the intensity of the beam, maybe?" with dissolve
    n sad "¿Habrá alguna forma de hacerla funcionar... menos bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5619
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b62c348c:

    # ks neutral "No. Like I said, it's a basic penlight. It just switches on and off, that's all."
    ks neutral "No. Como dije, es una linterna básica. Simplemente se enciende y apaga, eso es todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5065
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e14de6e7:

    # n neutral_side "Hmm..." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5066
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8134fcfd:

    # n neutral "What about if you put that pattern onto a different model of penlight? One that you CAN adjust or has a weaker beam to start with?" with dissolve
    n neutral "¿Qué tal si pusieras el patrón en un modelo diferente de linterna? ¿Una que SÍ puedas ajustar o que ya directamente tenga un rayo más débil?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5067
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ef836d81:

    # ks sigh "I could try but it'll take ages. I'd have to buy it online again, then I gotta take it apart and try to make the same pattern as this one."
    ks sigh "Podría intentarlo, pero tomará siglos. Tendría que volver a comprarla en línea, luego desmantelarla e intentar hacer un patrón igual a este."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5068
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7ec7ece0:

    # ks "It'll be a lot of work, probably."
    ks "Será mucho trabajo, probablemente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5069
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ee8c0390:

    # n sad_side "And just as we're going into exam season... I suppose it's asking too much of you to try that right now." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Y justo cuando estamos entrando en exámenes... Supongo que intentarlo ahora mismo sería pedirte demasiado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5070
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_00af7257:

    # ks "Yeah..."
    ks "Seh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5071
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_48600f07:

    # n smile "Okay. Well, let's forget about that angle for now." with dissolve
    n smile "De acuerdo. Pues, olvidémonos de ese ángulo por ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5072
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b14d3cdc:

    # n front smile "If we can't do anything about the light then we need to focus on what you do with it." with dissolve
    n front smile "Si no podemos hacer nada en cuanto a la luz, debemos concentrarnos en qué haces con ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5073
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4c46f296:

    # ks neutral "It's not like I even do much. I just shine it back and forth over your eyes and do a standard induction while you watch."
    ks neutral "Tampoco es que haga mucho. Solo la muevo de lado a lado en tus ojos y hago una inducción estandar mientras la miras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5074
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_00cf269d:

    # n pout_left "Okay, I guess there's not much you can change about that either. Go a little slower, maybe?" with dissolve
    n pout_left "Muy bien, supongo que tampoco hay mucho que puedas cambiar ahí. ¿Ir un poco más lento, tal vez?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5191
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_086342d1:

    # n front2 neutral "But besides that, there's what you say to hypnotize me, and what you say while I'm under. Because you really could work on how you phrase your suggestions." with dissolve
    n front2 neutral "Pero aparte de eso, está lo que dices para hipnotizarme, y lo que dices mientras estoy en trance. Porque en serio podrías trabajar en cómo redactas tus sugestiones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5076
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8b73d848:

    # n frown "And speaking of suggestions, maybe next time you could make it clear to my subconscious not to do anything that'll endanger me?" with dissolve
    n frown "Y hablando de sugestiones, ¿tal vez a la próxima podrías dejarle en claro a mi subconsciente que no haga nada que me ponga en peligro?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5077
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e9a78247:

    # ks sigh "Yeah. Yeah, I could..."
    ks sigh "Sí. Sí, podría..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5195
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6386ade6:

    # n front sigh "And you could impress a lighter trance instead of trying to make me go deep. Maybe that'd be safer?" with dissolve
    n front sigh "Y podrías inducir un trance más ligero, en lugar de intentar llevarme profundo. ¿Tal vez eso sea más seguro?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5080
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4889c0d4:

    # "Honestly, with the way she's unloading on me, it sounds like she's already thought this stuff through."
    "Honestamente, con todo lo que está descargando sobre mí, suena a que ya lo pensó bastante."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5696
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c479bdcb:

    # ks confused "Alright, then. So how exactly do you want me to do this? I tell your subconscious not to be so dumb this time, and then what?"
    ks confused "Pues muy bien. Entonces ¿cómo quieres que haga esto, exactamente? Le digo a tu subconsciente que no sea tonto esta vez, ¿y luego qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5082
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d7cd9b05:

    # n side sad_side "Okay, so I was thinking we could try some more memory play. Like, if you ask me any question, suggest I'll have no idea what the answer is." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Bien, pues pensé que podríamos hacer algo más con la memoria. Como, si me haces una pregunta, no tendré idea de cuál es la respuesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5083
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f674a0a2:

    # n sad "That should be safe. And I think you could really test how effective it's been on me by asking me simpler and simpler questions." with dissolve
    n sad "Eso debería ser seguro. Y creo que podrías probar qué tan efectivo fue haciéndome preguntas más y más simples." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5085
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_df095947:

    # ks smirk "Like what's the number between three and five?"
    ks smirk "¿Como qué número va entre el tres y el cinco?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5087
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_afd92fac:

    # ks smirk "Like what your name is?"
    ks smirk "¿Como cuál es tu nombre?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5089
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5c5c1925:

    # "Nozomi rolls her eyes at me." with dissolve
    "Nozomi me rueda los ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5090
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_799bbd53:

    # n "Yes. Like that."
    n "Sí. Por ejemplo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5093
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e15484dd:

    # "It sounds like a plan, so I hold up the penlight in front of her."
    "Parece un buen plan, así que sostengo la linterna frente a ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5214
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6645bd9b:

    # "And in response, Nozomi lays back on her bed."
    "Y en respuesta, Nozomi se recuesta en su cama."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5102
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7afe0be1:

    # n "So, you know what you're doing?"
    n "Entonces, ¿sabes lo que haces?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5217
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_692b5dd5:

    # ks casual frown "Try to put you in a lighter trance than before, tell your subconscious to watch itself and say you can't answer questions. Got it."
    ks casual frown "Intento ponerte en un trance más ligero que antes, le digo a tu subconsciente que tenga cuidado y decir que no puedes responder preguntas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5106
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_894f483b:

    # "Nozomi sucks in a breath to steel herself, then nods." with dissolve
    "Nozomi toma aire para armarse de valor, luego asiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5107
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f5683e41:

    # n "Alright, I'm ready when you are."
    n "Muy bien, lista cuando tú lo estés."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5108
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fd27889f:

    # "I proceed to induce a trance state in her, slowly sweeping the penlight across her eyes several times until her eyes seem to glaze over."
    "Procedo a inducirle un estado de trance, lentamente deslizando la linterna por sus ojos varias veces hasta que parecen desenfocarse."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5110
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b41303c1:

    # "Instead of telling her to sleep, I merely impress the idea that she's hypnotized now while she appears dazed and I start to do what we agreed." with dissolve
    "En vez de decirle que duerma, simplemente la hago a la idea de que está hipnotizada mientras parece aturdida y comienzo a hacer lo que acordamos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5111
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b1db7128:

    # ks neutral "While you're in this nice, relaxed state of trance, consciousness fading, you'll find that your subconscious is still listening attentively to my voice."
    ks neutral "Mientras estés en este agradable y relajado estado de trance, y tu consciencia se desvanece, tu subconsciente seguirá escuchando mi voz con atención."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5112
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2dd2d88a:

    # ks "And what I want you to know is that, no matter what you find suggested to you, whether now or any other time, if you feel the suggestion will cause you harm..."
    ks "Y lo que quiero que sepas es que, sin importar qué sugestión te dé, ya sea ahora o en otro momento, si sientes que la sugestión va a lastimarte..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5113
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9e9259f9:

    # ks "... you will ignore the suggestion and proceed as if it was never suggested in the first place. Understand, Nozomi?"
    ks "... ignorarás la sugestión y procederás como si nunca la hubiera dicho en primer lugar. ¿Comprendes, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5114
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_45195164:

    # n sleepy "I understand..." with dissolve
    n sleepy "Comprendo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5116
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b8252c9c:

    # "Is this better than the other times we've done this? She still seems pretty out of it after a few sweeps of the light." with dissolve
    "¿Es esto mejor que las otras veces? Yo aún la veo bastante perdida luego de unos pocos deslices de la luz." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5117
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e520ffb7:

    # "Well, let's carry on..."
    "Bueno, continuemos..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5118
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_890e94e2:

    # ks "Very good, Nozomi. And with that in mind, I want to suggest something else."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Y con eso en mente, hay algo más que quiero decirte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5119
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cc487a92:

    # ks "While we're together in this room and you're asked a question, you'll find yourself instantly forgetting the answer."
    ks "Mientras estemos juntos en esta habitación e intentes contestar una pregunta, olvidarás instantáneamente la respuesta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5120
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9c3c4366:

    # ks "It doesn't matter what the question is, you'll always seem to find the answer just completely drops away from your conscious mind."
    ks "Da igual qué pregunta sea, notarás que la respuesta simplemente se esfuma de tu mente consciente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5121
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fd021f79:

    # ks "But there's no need to worry, because you'll consciously remember again as soon as I leave the room. Okay, Nozomi?"
    ks "Pero no hay por qué preocuparse, porque volverás a recordar conscientemente tan pronto como yo salga de la habitación. ¿Muy bien, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5122
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d0c71635:

    # n sleepy "Okay..." with dissolve
    n sleepy "Bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5124
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f7158285:

    # ks smile "That's great, Nozomi. Your subconscious remembering everything I told you as you wake up on three." with dissolve
    ks smile "Grandioso, Nozomi. Tu subconsciente recordará todo lo que te dije cuando despiertes a la cuenta de tres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5125
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2a6a8f5c:

    # ks "One, two... three."
    ks "Uno, dos... tres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5126
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cbcf53d4:

    # n surprised "A-ahhh..." with dissolve
    n surprised "A-aaah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5127
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0a09782b:

    # "I smile as she breathes and the life seems to immediately return to her eyes, looking at me now, not through me as before."
    "Sonrío y, con un respiro, la vida parece regresar de inmediato a sus ojos que ahora me miran a mí, y no a través de mí como antes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5128
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d2f84b4c:

    # "I can't help it, watching her wake up from her trances is still cute."
    "No puedo evitarlo, verla despertar de sus trances sigue siendo adorable."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5129
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9c934117:

    # n smile blush "That felt... nice. You did what we agreed, right?" with dissolve
    n smile blush "Eso se sintió... bien. Hiciste lo que acordamos, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5130
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a09166f2:

    # ks "Yeah. I tried not to take you as deep as the other times, although you still seemed pretty out of it."
    ks "Sí. Intenté no llevarte tan profundo como las otras veces, aunque aun así lucías bastante perdida."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5131
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_979740f1:

    # "Nozomi sits up on the bed and crosses her legs, running a hand through her hair."
    "Nozomi se siente an la cama y cruza las piernas, pasando una mano por su cabello."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5132
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_590a60a3:

    # n side smile_side "Yeah. It still felt pretty intense to me." with dissolve
    n side smile_side "Sí. Igual se sintió muy intenso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5284
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5d9e4ad7:

    # ks casual smile "Do you remember anything about it?"
    ks casual smile "¿Recuerdas algo del trance?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5134
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2889c693:

    # n "Um..."
