# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5266
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7f88ba27:

    # n angry "God... damn it, Kyou!" with dissolve
    n angry "Con un... ¡demonio, Kyou!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5267
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fd6dc910:

    # ks sigh "Yeah, I know you didn't want your mom finding out but you knew it was a risk and telling her was the only way to calm her down."
    ks sigh "Sí, ya sé que no querías que tu mamá se enterara, pero sabías que era un riesgo y decirle la verdad era la única manera de calmarla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5268
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_523d3b45:

    # n side frown "Yeah, I didn't like to see her worry like that. But you didn't have to say we were doing some sort of culture festival thing together!" with dissolve
    n side frown "Sí, no me gustó verla así de preocupada. ¡Pero no tenías que decirle que estábamos haciendo algo para el festival cultural juntos!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5269
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_939d656f:

    # ks frown "Did you have any better ideas? Besides, we don't have to do anything, just say we had to cancel or something."
    ks frown "¿Tenías alguna mejor idea? Además, no tenemos que hacer nada, solo dile que tuvimos que cancelarlo o algo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5270
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9d6544f4:

    # n front irritated "Oh, I intend to!" with dissolve
    n front irritated "¡Oh, créeme, lo haré!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5271
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_16a7585e:

    # n pout_left blush "Gosh, if everyone saw us partnered up to do a hypnosis show of all things and I'm never going to live this down." with dissolve
    n pout_left blush "Dios, si todos nos vieran juntarnos para dar un espectáculo, y nada menos que uno de hipnosis, y nunca saldré de esta ciudad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5274
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cd82ba5b:

    # n annoyed "If I knew this was going to happen I never would've talked to you in the first place." with dissolve
    n annoyed "De haber sabido que esto iba a pasar nunca te habría hablado en primer lugar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5275
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a4afffcd:

    # ks "Oh, that's right. You're embarrassed of me, aren't you."
    ks "Oh, cierto. Te avergüenzas de mí, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5276
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_859d25fb:

    # n irritated "Rrrrgh! I'm not..." with dissolve
    n irritated "¡Grrrr! No..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5279
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4fc3e4e4:

    # "Nozomi holds a hand to her temple as she flops back down on her bed, then sighs."
    "Nozomi coloca una mano en su sien dejándose caer en su cama."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5282
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b2bd828d:

    # n sigh noblush "Okay, I'm sorry. I'm just feeling a bit overwhelmed, that's all." with dissolve
    n sigh noblush "De acuerdo, lo siento. Es que me siento un tanto abrumada, es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5856
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e29f87fb:

    # ks casual sigh "Yeah. So anyway, you want to talk about what just happened?"
    ks casual sigh "Sí. Pues, en fin, ¿quieres hablar de lo que acaba de pasar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5285
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b914d518:

    # "Nozomi nods." with dissolve
    "Nozomi asiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5286
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_72006be0:

    # n "It seems I was every bit as affected as before, didn't it?"
    n "Parece que fue igual de efectivo que antes, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5287
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fb7dd5cf:

    # ks "You didn't seem so out of it when I put you under, but yeah."
    ks "No te veías tan perdida cuando te puse en trance, pero sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5288
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4fbd4542:

    # ks "I thought things would change when your mom walked in, but you still couldn't help yourself."
    ks "Creí que las cosas cambiarían cuando tu mamá entró, pero aun así no podías evitarlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5289
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3bb2b30a:

    # n side sad_closed "Yeah. I couldn't figure out how to answer even the simplest questions. That was an odd feeling to have in front of mom." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Sí. No tenía idea de cómo contestar ni las más simples preguntas. Se sintió muy extraño delante de mamá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5290
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f90c4cdc:

    # ks frown "But I told your subconscious to ignore any harmful suggestions, I swear."
    ks frown "Pero le dije a tu subconsciente que ignorara toda sugestión dañina, lo juro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5291
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cb481726:

    # n frown "Well, I mean, it was humiliating but I don't think I was in any danger so I can't say I'm surprised that didn't help me." with dissolve
    n frown "Bueno, pues, fue humillante, pero no creo que haya estado en ningún peligro, así que no me sorprende que eso no me haya ayudado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5292
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2693a122:

    # ks neutral "Yeah, I guess. So how do we make sure that part works? Put you under again and suggest you jump out of a window or something?"
    ks neutral "Sí, supongo. Entonces ¿cómo nos aseguramos de que esa parte funciona? ¿Te pongo en trance y te digo que saltes por la ventana o algo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5492
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_62cb3de3:

    # n front2 angry "Absolutely not! Don't be stupid!" with dissolve
    n front2 angry "¡De ninguna manera! ¡No seas estúpido!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5294
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0e5b2edb:

    # ks sigh "Okay, yeah. Sorry. But that means we're still flying blind over whether your subconscious really has a limit to this stuff."
    ks sigh "Muy bien, sí. Perdón. Pero eso quiere decir que aún no podemos saber si tu subconsciente tiene algún límite para esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5295
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2089c0c8:

    # n side sad_side "So did we really learn anything from this?" with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Entonces ¿aprendimos algo de esto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5296
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_758e2968:

    # ks smile "Maybe not. But wasn't it fun to do this again? And no one got hurt this time."
    ks smile "Tal vez no. Pero ¿no fue divertido hacerlo de nuevo? Y nadie salió herido esta vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5297
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dd4f1ad9:

    # n front pout_left blush "I mean, I could've done without mom knowing about this..." with dissolve
    n front pout_left blush "Bueno, habría preferido que mamá no lo supiera..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5298
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fbee420c:

    # "She's embarrassed about that of course, but there's opportunity here."
    "Eso le da vergüenza, por supuesto, pero aquí hay una oportunidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5299
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_27b990fa:

    # ks "But she didn't mind at all, did she?"
    ks "Pero no le molestó, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5300
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_db6a49e8:

    # n pout "Well, no..." with dissolve
    n pout "Pues, no..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5301
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7c47bbda:

    # ks "And are you sure you don't want to do a show for the culture fest?"
    ks "¿Y estás segura de que no quieres armar un espectáculo para el festival cultural?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5302
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9c07ec9d:

    # ks "If you think about it, it'd make our experiments a lot easier if we could say we're doing it as part of an official project"
    ks "Si lo piensas, será mucho más fácil hacer nuestros experimentos si podemos decir que lo hacemos como parte de un proyecto oficial."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5304
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e917e289:

    # n side sad_closed "But still, what's everyone at school going to think?" with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Aun así, ¿qué pensarán todos en la escuela?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5305
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b3105330:

    # ks sigh "Look, tell them whatever you want, I don't care. But seriously, think about it."
    ks sigh "Mira, diles lo que quieras, me da igual. Pero en serio, piénsalo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5306
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a78a10af:

    # n sad_side "Yeah..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5308
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_46da4622:

    # "Soon after Atsuko called us down for lunch and some awkward conversation was had."
    "Poco después Atsuko nos llamó para almorzar y algo de charla un tanto incómoda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5309
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2e7415e5:

    # "Atsuko seemed excited about our partnership, but we honestly didn't have much to say about it; just that we were brainstorming ideas."
    "Atsuko parece emocionada por nuestra asociación, pero honestamente no teníamos mucho que decir al respecto; solo que estábamos teniendo una lluvia de ideas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5311
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_785a4ccd:

    # "I didn't stay long after lunch. Nozomi said she had to get some things ready for tomorrow, but she told me she'd think about what I said."
    "No me quedé mucho después de la comida. Nozomi dijo que debía preparar algunas cosas para mañana, pero prometió que pensaría en lo que dije."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5312
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5ca8478a:

    # "So when I get back home I crash on the couch and do some thinking of my own."
    "Cuando llego a casa me arrojo al sofá y yo también me pongo a pensar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5313
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_05b1325a:

    # "All things considered, today went pretty well."
    "A pesar de todo, hoy fue un buen día."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5314
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3c625a33:

    # "I'm feeling better about myself, Nozomi's talking to me again and we seem to be working things out."
    "Me siento mejor conmigo mismo, Nozomi me habla otra vez y parece nos estamos entendiendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5315
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_00a4cd99:

    # "But most importantly..."
    "Pero lo más importante..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5318
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ea46eca7:

    # "I got my penlight back."
    "Recuperé mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5525
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1c6cc2b7:

    # "*** AUTHOR'S NOTE - And that's all I have time for, but at least we have a drafted script that takes us to the end of this day's scenes! ***"
    "*** NOTA DE LA AUTORA – ¡Y eso es todo lo que tengo por ahora, pero al menos hemos redactado un guion que nos lleva al final de las escenas de este dia! ***"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5526
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_245fcbf8:

    # "*** I have some ideas for how to continue this storyline, but as ever I'm interested in your thoughts if your feel like sharing~ ***"
    "*** Tengo algunas ideas de cómo continuar esta historia, pero como siempre, me interesa saber lo que piensan si desean compartirlo. ***"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7236
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_07e9e229:

    # a neutral noblush "Such as making them cluck like chickens, or..." with dissolve
    a neutral noblush "Como hacer que cacaree como gallina, o..." with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-06-21 08:56

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5218
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f6541718:

    # "And what's more, I know I can't just say that and expect Atsuko to believe it. Especially when you're in no state to back me up."
    "Es más, sé que no puedo simplemente decir eso y esperar que Atsuko se lo crea. Sobre todo cuando no estás en condiciones de apoyarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5219
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fca44595:

    # "I'll need to hypnotize you in front of her, just to prove that's all this is."
    "Tendré que hipnotizarte delante de ella, solo para probar que de eso se trata todo esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5221
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_530d93d0:

    # ks smile "Uh, I'm going to help her out, okay, Atsuko?" with dissolve
    ks smile "Em, voy a ayudarla, ¿de acuerdo, Atsuko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5222
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1d4b6241:

    # nm surprised "Huh?" with dissolve
    nm surprised "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5223
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_00d285ea:

    # "Hopefully I won't need the penlight for this. I'm sure neither of us want her asking questions about that thing."
    "Espero no necesitar la linterna para esto. Estoy seguro de que ninguno de los dos quiere que nos empiece a preguntar por esa cosa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5224
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1ae125f1:

    # "But from what I've read about hypnosis I think I can pull this off without it."
    "Pero por lo que leí sobre hipnosis, creo que puedo lograrlo sin ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5226
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_beccf003:

    # "All I gotta do is go up to Nozomi, gently hold her shoulder and look confident. Like I know what I'm doing." with dissolve
    "Solo tengo que acercarme a Nozomi, tomarla suavemente del hombro y mostrar confianza. Como si supiera lo que estoy haciendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5231
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3f2d411e:

    # "She looks like she'd rather spontaneaously burst into flames than endure another moment of this in front of her mom." with dissolve
    "Tiene cara de que preferiría arder en llamas de manera espontánea a soportar un momento más de esto en frente de su mamá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5233
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_35d3f3ad:

    # "Nevertheless, Nozomi turns her eyes to look at mine." with dissolve
    "No obstante, Nozomi me mira directo a los ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5241
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_981e5d4e:

    # "I have to keep the relief from showing on my face as Nozomi slumps back into trance. So I was right that it would work!"
    "Tratando de evitar que el alivio se me note en toda la cara, veo a Nozomi caer de vuelta en trance. ¡Tenía razón; sí funcionó!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5242
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6f0a905f:

    # "With Nozomi being under hypnotic suggestion already, I knew she was already in a state of half trance still."
    "Teniendo a Nozomi bajo una sugestión hipnótica, sabía que ya estaba en un estado de semi-trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5244
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cd625ee4:

    # "So with that in mind I figured it would't be too hard to induce her back into a full trance, even as embarrassed as she must be right now."
    "Así que, con eso en mente, imaginé que no sería difícil inducirla de nuevo a un trance completo, por más apenada que se encuentre ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5285
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_be37852f:

    # n pout_left blush "Gosh, if everyone saw us partnered up to do a hypnosis show of all things I'm never going to live it down." with dissolve
    n pout_left blush "Dios, si todos nos vieran juntarnos para dar un espectáculo, y nada menos que uno de hipnosis, nunca nadie lo va a olvidar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5301
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ac527d40:

    # ks "Yeah. I tried to give you a lighter trance this time, but you still seemed to go pretty deep anyway."
    ks "Sí. Intenté darte un trance más ligero esta vez, pero creo que fuiste bastante profundo de todos modos."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-07-18 09:57

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4998
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d5204197:

    # n concerned "I just... I just don't understand how you made something like this." with dissolve
    n concerned "Es que... es que no entiendo cómo hiciste algo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4999
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e64a59bd:

    # "It begs the question, though:"
    "Pero eso me deja con la pregunta:"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5002
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c628e025:

    # ks sigh "If you really suspected it was so dangerous why did you take it to use on yourself?"
    ks sigh "Si en verdad sospechabas que era tan peligrosa, ¿por qué la tomaste para usarla en ti misma?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5003
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_89721f3b:

    # n frown "Because I could hardly believe what had happened. I needed proof." with dissolve
    n frown "Porque no podía creer lo que había pasado. Necesitaba pruebas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5004
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_82a9156c:

    # n irritated "And I couldn't trust your opinion. I thought you had to be hiding something from me." with dissolve
    n irritated "Y no podía confiar en tu opinión. Pensé que tenías que estar ocultándome algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5005
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0539e234:

    # ks frown "You don't trust me?"
    ks frown "¿No confías en mí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5006
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e8ba2fad:

    # n side sad_side "I didn't..." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "No confiaba..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5007
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_06398373:

    # "She sighs."
    "Suspira."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5008
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8dbeed62:

    # n sad_closed "You have to understand. I hardly know you, and you show up and just casually mention hypnosis like you wouldn't think it'd pique my interest." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Debes comprender. Apenas te conozco, y tú te apareces y casualmente mencionas la hipnosis así nada más como si no creyeras que captaría mi interés." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5009
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ef3b437d:

    # n sad_side "And more than that, you have this strange light that affects me as much as this and it's just..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Y además, tienes esta extraña luz que me afecta tanto y..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5010
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d02f6207:

    # n sad "You made it yourself! You HAD to know what it was capable of!" with dissolve
    n sad "¡La hiciste tú mismo! ¡TENÍAS que saber de lo que era capaz!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5013
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5786099d:

    # ks sigh "I made it to help catch people's attention, I didn't think it'd work as well as this!"
    ks sigh "¡La hice para atraer más fácilmente la atención, no creí que funcionaría así de bien!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5040
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_06854706:

    # n "And I realized if you actually knew what this thing could do, a lot of things would be different." with dissolve
    n "Y me di cuenta de que, si en serio hubieras sabido lo que esta cosa podía hacer, muchas cosas serían diferentes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5017
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_eadcf61c:

    # n front sleeptalk_concerned "So I'm sorry, Kyou. I was scared, but I should've been more honest about my feelings and what my intentions were." with dissolve
    n front sleeptalk_concerned "Así que, lo siento, Kyou. Tenía miedo, pero debí ser más honesta con lo que sentía y cuáles eran mis intenciones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5019
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b9bbd39f:

    # "But still, it does leave us in a weird place..."
    "Sin embargo, esto nos deja en una posición extraña..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5055
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9fef45db:

    # n "U-uh..."
    n "E-eh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5030
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_89742dd4:

    # "Just then, Nozomi looks to me while putting a finger to her lips, then hurriedly stuffs the penlight back in her desk drawer and slams it shut."
    "En ese momento, Nozomi me mira con un dedo en sus labios, luego se apresura a ocultar la linterna de regreso en su cajón y lo cierra de un azote."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5035
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e2c5e38b:

    # n smile_side "Sure, come in!" with dissolve
    n smile_side "¡Claro, pasa!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5064
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9a13cd4d:

    # "Nozomi smiles faintly." with dissolve
    "Nozomi sonríe tenuemente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5067
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4fb71351:

    # n "She is, although she can be a bit much sometimes."
    n "Lo es, aunque a veces sea un poco exagerada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5068
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_06acd751:

    # ks neutral "Yeah?"
    ks neutral "¿Ah, sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5069
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5fbf25fa:

    # n sad_side "I mean, you saw her just now. She couldn't wait to get involved with us!" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Bueno, la acabas de ver. ¡No podía esperar para involucrarse con nosotros!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5070
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_565c4eb3:

    # n front pout "I get why she still smothers Ichiro so much, but I'm eighteen years old! I'm not a kid anymore!" with dissolve
    n front pout "Entiendo por qué aún sofoca tanto a Ichiro, ¡pero yo tengo dieciocho! ¡Ya no soy una niña!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5072
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1d770ef5:

    # "I'm sure that's a name I haven't heard before."
    "Creo que ese nombre no lo he escuchado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5073
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e729531a:

    # n smile "Oh, right. He's my little brother." with dissolve
    n smile "Oh, cierto. Es mi hermanito." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5074
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_05bd4e75:

    # "Nozomi smiles again; more brightly this time."
    "Nozomi vuelve a sonreír; más vívidamente esta vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5075
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a5ea0f26:

    # n side smile "You might have met him, actually. He's a first year at our school." with dissolve
    n side smile "Puede que ya lo hayas conocido, de hecho. Está en primer año en nuestra escuela." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5076
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6ad64af7:

    # ks smile "Oh, huh."
    ks smile "Oh, vaya."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5077
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9de60d22:

    # "I don't really know what to say to that, but she's quick to move on."
    "No sé qué responder a eso, pero ella rápidamente cambia de tema."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5078
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4357d50c:

    # n front chuckle "Anyway..." with dissolve
    n front chuckle "En fin..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5120
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c23b37aa:

    # n neutral_right "And there's something else I decided." with dissolve
    n neutral_right "Y hay una cosa más que he decidido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5087
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0c462413:

    # ks smile "What's that?"
    ks smile "¿Qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5088
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_03365fdf:

    # n sleep "I want to change rule number three." with dissolve
    n sleep "Quiero cambiar la regla número tres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5571
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2670a5f9:

    # ks confused "Huh?"
    ks confused "¿Eh?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5090
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e3a71406:

    # "Rule number three? Then she means..."
    "¿Regla número tres? Se refiera a..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5498
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_754ed35e:

    # n neutral "Now that we know what your penlight can do, I don't think we should try any hypnosis at your place anymore." with dissolve
    n neutral "Ahora que sabemos lo que tu linterna puede hacer, no creo que debamos intentar más hipnosis en tu casa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5092
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_33836f76:

    # ks "Then..."
    ks "Entonces..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5127
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4667af28:

    # n neutral_left "We'll do it here instead." with dissolve
    n neutral_left "Lo haremos aquí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5576
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cdd1a394:

    # ks "Huh? But aren't you worried your mom will find out about your secret?"
    ks "¿Eh? ¿Pero no te preocupa que tu mamá descubra tu secreto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5097
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ca4546c4:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "I am. But I've given this a lot of thought, and if we're going to keep doing hypnosis together then I have to think about my own safety." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Sí. Pero lo he estado pensando mucho, y si vamos a seguir practicando hipnosis juntos, debo pensar en mi propia seguridad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5099
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_18474cba:

    # n "Knowing there's someone else in the house who can help if things go wrong... i-it just seems like the smart thing to do."
    n "Saber que hay alguien más en la casa que puede ayudar si las cosas salen mal... parece la decisión más inteligente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5101
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e2aa76c5:

    # "Nozomi sighs irritatedly."
    "Nozomi suspira con irritación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5102
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bcaa8803:

    # n front annoyed_left "Look, it doesn't matter if I trust you or not. We've seen what your penlight can do to me, even if you didn't mean it to." with dissolve
    n front annoyed_left "Mira, no importa si confío en ti o no. Ya hemos visto lo que tu linterna puede hacerme, incluso si no es tu intención." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5113
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_15b187b8:

    # n front smile "So what do you think? Want to find out more about it with me?" with dissolve
    n front smile "Entonces ¿qué opinas? ¿Quieres aprender más sobre ella conmigo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5121
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fc4c1c77:

    # n "Okay then, so first... I think it'd be a good idea to review what we DO know about this thing."
    n "Pues muy bien, para empezar... creo que sería buena idea repasar lo que SÍ sabemos de esta cosa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5122
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d322a253:

    # "I nod in agreement as I turn my penlight over in my hand."
    "Asiento con la cabeza, dándole vueltas a la linterna en mi mano."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5123
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b97092ba:

    # ks neutral noblush "Right. So like I said, this is an off-the-shelf medical penlight that I bought from the internet."
    ks neutral noblush "Claro. Pues, como dije, esta es una pluma linterna médica comercial que compré en internet."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5130
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c25c4a7f:

    # ks neutral "Yeah. I figured it'd engage a person's natural curiosity so they're more inclined to focus on it and facilitate them going into a hypnotic state."
    ks neutral "Sí. Me imaginé que captaría la curiosidad natural de una persona para inclinarla más a concentrarse en ella y facilitarle entrar al trance hipnótico."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5131
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7d69653c:

    # ks "I have no idea why it works on you as well as it does, though."
    ks "Aunque no tengo idea de por qué funcionó tan bien en ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5133
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0e9443cb:

    # "Nozomi strokes her chin thoughtfully." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se frota la barbilla pensando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5134
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_85918618:

    # n "I wonder if there could there be a way to make it work... less well?"
    n "Me pregunto si habrá alguna manera de hacerla funcionar... ¿menos bien?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5617
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c2b39f9f:

    # ks confused "What do you mean?"
    ks confused "¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5136
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2f6f6e59:

    # n pout_left "Like... could you turn down the intensity of the beam, maybe?" with dissolve
    n pout_left "Por ejemplo, ¿podrías bajar la intensidad de la luz, tal vez?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5138
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1a3feb84:

    # n neutral "Hmm..." with dissolve
    n neutral "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5173
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8d401a1f:

    # n front2 frown "What about if you put that pattern onto a different model of penlight? One that you CAN adjust or has a weaker beam to start with?" with dissolve
    n front2 frown "¿Qué tal si pones ese patrón en un modelo diferente de pluma linterna? ¿Uno que SÍ se pueda ajustar o que tenga un haz más débil para empezar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5140
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_42cb8c79:

    # "I let out a little groan."
    "Dejo salir un ligero gruñido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5141
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_af00d694:

    # ks sigh "I could try but it'll take ages."
    ks sigh "Podría intentarlo, pero tomaría siglos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5142
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_94f9116d:

    # ks "I'll probably have to buy it online again so that'll be a couple days, then I gotta take it apart and try to make it emit the same pattern as this one."
    ks "Probablemente tendría que comprarla en línea otra vez, eso sería ya un par de días, luego debo desmantelarla e intentar hacerla emitir el mismo patrón que esta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5143
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f716405e:

    # n side sad_side "Right... And then it might not even work at all." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Cierto... Y luego puede que ni siquiera funcione." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5144
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c3237b0c:

    # ks frown "Yeah. I mean, the patterning's gotta be important, but we don't know if it's the only reason it works this way."
    ks frown "Sí. Digo, el patrón seguro es importante, pero no sabemos si es la única razón por la que funciona así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5145
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bd2b2073:

    # ks "Maybe the light intensity and width are exactly what they need to be so we can't deviate."
    ks "Tal vez la intensidad y el ancho de la luz son exactamente como deben ser y no nos podemos desviar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5146
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_09c8c7fb:

    # ks "Or maybe there's something else that's special about this particular light that we don't know about."
    ks "O tal vez haya algo especial en esta linterna en particular que desconocemos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5147
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_751ce7b6:

    # "Nozomi nods with a sigh."
    "Nozomi asiente con un suspiro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5148
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_be7c34b9:

    # n sad_closed "Yeah. Not to mention exam season is almost on top of us, so I suppose it's asking too much of you to experiment with this stuff right now." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Sí. Sin mencionar que tenemos la temporada de exámenes casi encima, así que supongo que experimentar con esto ahora mismo sería pedirte demasiado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5149
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_63e8fedd:

    # ks sigh "Yeah..."
    ks sigh "Seh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5150
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0415e471:

    # "We both fall silent for a moment..."
    "Ambos nos quedamos en silencio por unos intantes..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5152
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4efa52e5:

    # "Then, with a small shrug, Nozomi smiles encouragingly at me as she speaks up again." with dissolve
    "Luego, encogiéndose de hombros, Nozomi me ofrece una sonrisa alentadora al volver a hablar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5153
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cf6ce42b:

    # n "Okay. Well, let's forget about that angle for now."
    n "De acuerdo. Pues, olvidémonos de ese ángulo por ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5167
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_085466f4:

    # ks smirk "Like \"What's the number between three and five?\""
    ks smirk "Como \"¿Qué número va entre el tres y el cinco?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5169
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f479dd43:

    # ks smirk "Like \"What's your name?\""
    ks smirk "Como \"¿Cuál es tu nombre?\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5171
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a0ef2fb9:

    # "Nozomi scoffs at me." with dissolve
    "Nozomi resopla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5181
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c4866f61:

    # ks frown "Try to put you in a lighter trance than before, tell your subconscious to watch itself and say you can't answer questions. Got it."
    ks frown "Intento ponerte en un trance más ligero que antes, le indico a tu subconsciente que se cuide y digo que no puedes contestar preguntas. Lo tengo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5185
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6568b9fc:

    # "Okay. So a lighter trance than last time..."
    "Muy bien. Entonces un trance más ligero que el de la última vez..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5186
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2ad85e35:

    # "I'm not totally sure how to do that when Nozomi's so easy to hypnotize, but I guess I shouldn't impress so much about how sleepy she's getting."
    "No estoy del todo seguro de cómo hacer eso cuando Nozomi es tan fácil de hipnotizar, pero supongo que no debería enfocarme tanto en que tenga sueño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5187
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a3407b7a:

    # "I'll just have to wing it."
    "Tendré que improvisar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5191
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b767d8ab:

    # ks neutral "So, back once again to the light, Nozomi."
    ks neutral "Bien, de vuelta una vez más a la luz, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5194
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a9f5ce71:

    # ks "Back to watching those patterns we talked about." with dissolve
    ks "Una vez más observa esos patrones de los que hablamos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5195
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f3a5f971:

    # n "{size=16}Yeah...{/size}"
    n "{size=16}Seh...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5197
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_01d335dc:

    # ks "Just calmly letting those light spots hit your eyes."
    ks "Solo deja que esos puntos de luz pasen por tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5199
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d9585db7:

    # ks "Putting all your attention on the light as you feel yourself becoming more and more relaxed. More and more sleepy..."
    ks "Poniendo toda tu atención en la luz y sintiéndote más y más relajada. Sintiendo más y más sueño..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5204
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_19825faa:

    # ks smile "Just letting your consciousness drift effortlessly away as you stare... that's right."
    ks smile "Deja que tu consciencia se esfume mientras observas... eso es."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5206
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7c73f19c:

    # "Ah, she's already dropping fast. Maybe this is as far as I need to go with the light."
    "Ah, sí que está cayendo rápido. Tal vez ya no haga falta seguir usando la linterna a partir de este punto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5208
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6a546351:

    # ks "And while you're in this nice, relaxed state of trance, consciousness fading, you'll find that your subconscious is still listening attentively to my voice."
    ks "Y mientras estás en este agradable y relajado estado de trance, y tu consciencia se desvanece, notarás que tu subconsciente sigue escuchando atentamente mi voz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5213
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f9a8619e:

    # "Is this better than the other times we've done this?" with dissolve
    "¿Está mejor que las otras veces que lo hicimos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5214
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_63ad6d32:

    # "I didn't impress on her the need to \"sleep\", so her heavily glazed eyes are staring impotently ahead between slow, infrequent blinking."
    "No le di la necesidad de \"dormir\", así que sus vidriosos ojos miran impotentes hacia adelante entre lentos e infrecuentes parpadeos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5215
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1901cca6:

    # "She just looks so out completely of it, even after only a few sweeps of the light."
    "Luce completamente perdida, incluso después de solo unos pocos deslices de la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5390
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7b584a6e:

    # "I put a hand to the back of my head and sigh. I was sort of expecting this from her."
    "Me llevo una mano a la nuca y suspiro. Creo que no esperaba otra cosa de ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5396
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f0fc2287:

    # "I sigh inwardly. Is that what she thinks of me? Still?"
    "Suspiro para mis adentros. ¿Es eso lo que piensa de mí? ¿Aún?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5400
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fef6ff23:

    # "I can't let it slide. Not anymore."
    "No puedo dejarlo pasar. Ya no."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5851
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a37c4e90:

    # n "Sorry... I'm not being fair to you."
    n "Lo siento... No estoy siendo justa contigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5479
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b8a68e1b:

    # n neutral_right "It's just all a bit much, you know?" with dissolve
    n neutral_right "Es que todo esto es demasiado, ¿sabes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5410
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c9cd772b:

    # "I sigh. Openly this time."
    "Suspiro. En el exterior esta vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5431
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a135fa07:

    # ks "If you think about it, it'd make our experiments a lot easier if we could say we're doing it as part of an official project."
    ks "Si lo piensas, sería mucho más fácil hacer nuestros experimentos si pudieras decir que los estamos haciendo como parte de un proyecto oficial."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5433
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_13941fd3:

    # n side sad_closed "Maybe... B-but still, what's everyone at school going to think?" with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Tal vez... P-pero, aun así, ¿qué pensarán todos en la escuela?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5434
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_81623ce7:

    # ks frown "I mean, you're the class rep and you'd be helping one of your classmates for the sake of the school..."
    ks frown "Bueno, eres la representante de clase y estarías ayudando a uno de tus compañeros y apoyando la escuela."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5435
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c10813a8:

    # "Ugh, she's doing it again. But I'll push through."
    "Aj. Lo está haciendo otra vez. Pero tal vez sí logre convencerla."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-07-25 11:51

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4961
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_eac4c7b9:

    # "Just then, Nozomi falls back onto her bed and holds the penlight up in front of her."
    "Entonces, Nozomi cae de espaldas sobre su cama y sujeta la linterna frente a ella."
# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4984
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3a2d613a:

    # "She sighs and holds the penlight up to her face again." with dissolve
    "Suspira y alza la linterna frente a su rostro una vez más." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5435
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b705d346:

    # "Nozomi looks to me and puts a finger to her lips as she hops off her bed."
    "Nozomi me mira con un dedo en sus labios, saltando de la cama."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5064
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_028ddbe3:

    # "She then hurriedly stuffs the penlight back in her desk drawer before sliding it shut and looking to the door." with dissolve
    "Luego se apresura a ocultar la linterna de regreso en su cajón y lo cierra de un azote mientras mira hacia la puerta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5275
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a8466bb1:

    # ks "Yeah. I tried not to take you as deep as the other times, although you still seemed pretty far gone to me."
    ks "Sí. Intenté no llevarte tan profundo como antes, aunque para mí aun así lucías bastante absorta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5656
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_59bc63e0:

    # "Nozomi gets up from the bed and takes a deep breath while slowly running a hand through her hair."
    "Nozomi se levanta de la cama y respira hondo, pasando lentamente una mano por su cabello."

# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-07-30 11:01

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5376
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5254aec1:

    # ks smile "Uh, I'm going to help her out. Okay, Atsuko?" with dissolve
    ks smile "Em, voy a ayudarla. ¿De acuerdo, Atsuko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5381
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5c655262:

    # "All I gotta do is show a little confidence. Like I know what I'm doing..." with dissolve
    "Solo debo mostrar un poco de confianza. Como si supiera lo que esoy haciendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5383
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a91d6230:

    # ks smile "Nozomi, can you sit down on the bed please?"
    ks smile "Nozomi, ¿podrías sentarte en la cama, por favor?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5389
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_983d8eb5:

    # "Nevertheless, Nozomi does as I ask while her concerned mother sits down with her."
    "No obstante, Nozomi hace lo que le pido mientras que su preocupada madre se sienta junto a ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5390
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b4143cd8:

    # ks casual smile "Okay, now look at me."
    ks casual smile "Muy bien, ahora mírame."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5391
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_453c1a1a:

    # "I point to my eye as I say this and Nozomi awkwardly meets my gaze, not knowing what else to do."
    "Señalo mis ojos al decirlo y Nozomi me mira tímidamente, sin saber qué más hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5392
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_faaac878:

    # ks "Now, do you mind if I take your hand?"
    ks "Ahora, ¿te molesta si tomo tu mano?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5394
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5eb8e071:

    # n "{cps=15}I... I don't- {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    n "{cps=15}N-... no sé-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5395
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_07ab03ae:

    # ks "{cps=20}Now just focus on me. {w=0.5}Just relax and focus and- {/cps}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=20}Ahora enfócate en mí. {w=0.5}Relájate y concéntrate y- {/cps}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5401
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6c802e18:

    # extend "SLEEP!{w=0.5} Deep asleep, Nozomi."
    extend "¡DUERME!{w=0.5} Duerme profundamente, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5402
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_66984135:

    # "While she confused herself trying to answer me, I sharply tugged down on her arm and gave her a short, snappy and easy-to understand command."
    "Mientras se confundía al intentar responderme, tiré bruscamente de su brazo y le di una orden corta, rápida y fácil de entender."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5403
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_98d9e898:

    # "It's a command her befuddled mind was all too eager to latch onto, and I have to keep the relief from showing on my face as I watch her slump back down into trance."
    "Una orden a la que su aturdida mente estuvo más que dispuesta a aferrarse, y debo evitar que el alivio se me note en la cara al mirarla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5405
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f2f69b6e:

    # "But man, I'm so glad that worked."
    "Pero cielos, cuánto me alegra que funcionara."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5411
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9b4eef75:

    # ks "Very good. And now that you're back here, deeply hypnotized, I need you to let go of the suggestion I made to you." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Y ahora que una vez más estás profundamente hipnotizada, quiero que dejes ir la sugestión que te di." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5421
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_93159cb1:

    # "Nozomi's eyelids flicker as she begins to wake, watched all the while by her mother who has been concernedly observing us the whole time."
    "Nozomi alza sus temblantes párpados, observada en todo momento por su madre, quien con angustia no nos ha quitado los ojos de encima desde que empezamos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:5423
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_97728a8e:

    # n "{cps=15}Kyou... that was- {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    n "{cps=15}Kyou... eso fue- {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-10-15 22:51

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1987
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_00bbd78e:

    # "I wake up the next morning bright and early."
    "Despierto muy temprano a la mañana siguiente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1988
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0751cc5c:

    # "Normally I'm one for lying in, but the mixture of anxiety and excitement in my chest kept me from getting too much sleep."
    "Usualmente prefiero dormir hasta tarde, pero la mezcla de ansiedad y emoción en mi pecho me mantiene despierto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1990
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf838210:

    # "Besides, as the doorbell ringing downstairs reminds me, I have a busy day today..."
    "Además, al oír el timbre en el piso de abajo, sé que tendré un día muy ocupado..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1998
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_153c3d51:

    # "Heading downstairs, I open the door for my guest and she steps wordlessly inside, a quiet smile on her face."
    "Tras bajar las escaleras, le abro la puerta a mi invitada quien entra a la sala con una tranquila sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1999
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ec1f8244:

    # ks casual sigh "Damn, that was quick. I only messaged you like, five minutes ago."
    ks casual sigh "Diablos, qué rápido. Te escribí como hace cinco minutos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2000
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2fded262:

    # h "..."
    h "..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2001
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b37aae5:

    # ks "I thought I'd at least have time to shower first, but here you are."
    ks "Creí que al menos tendría tiempo de ducharme, pero aquí estás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2002
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2fded262_1:

    # h "..."
    h "..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2003
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0fd9b453:

    # ks smile "And I see you've gotten a lot better at shutting off your human routines when you don't need them."
    ks smile "Y veo que has mejorado mucho en apagar tus procesos humanos cuando no los necesitas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2004
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2fded262_2:

    # h "..."
    h "..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2005
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_68e361b6:

    # "Yeah, this [hypno6] has definitely internalized my programming more since the last time she was here. Better than I thought [p_they] would."
    "Sí, mi [hypno6!t!l] definitivamente ha internalizado más la programación que le di desde la última vez que estuvo aquí. Mejor de lo que esperaba."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2006
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4536d366:

    # "That only makes me more confident about [p_them] passing the test I have planned."
    "Eso me hace confiar aún más en que pasará la prueba que tengo planeada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2007
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d4db4eea:

    # ks neutral "Anyway, I don't need you for anything today. Me and the other [hypno6] can handle Sayori by ourselves, so having you there would just overcomplicate things."
    ks neutral "Como sea, no te necesito para nada hoy. Mi otr[genero_ao] [hypno6!t!l] y yo podemos manejar a Sayori solos, así que tenerte ahí solo complicaría las cosas de más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2008
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6caab416:

    # ks "I just wanted to pull you away from your prep for that tennis tournament you have going. See how you'd react."
    ks "Solo quería sacarte de tu entrenamiento para ese torneo de tenis que vas a jugar. Ver cómo reaccionarías."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2009
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_28230d67:

    # "It's just then that I reach out and tug the collar of the tennis uniform [p_they]'s wearing."
    "En ese momento me acerco a tomar entre mis dedos el cuello del uniforme de tenis que lleva puesto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2010
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cb2a503b:

    # ks "You were about to head for the tennis courts, weren't you?"
    ks "Ibas camino a las canchas de tenis, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2011
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_afe3e7ce:

    # h "Yes, Kyou. I'm s'posed to meet Risa there so we can train for the inter-school tennis tournament tomorrow. But then I got your instruction to come here."
    h "Sí, Kyou. Se supone que vea a Risa ahí para que podamos entrenar para el torneo de tenis interescolar de mañana. Pero luego recibí tu instrucción de venir aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2012
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_57d7d1c6:

    # "I frown a little. Should've realized someone would be expecting her there."
    "Frunzo un poco el ceño. Debí saber que alguien la estaría esperando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2013
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1811527a:

    # ks frown "Who's Risa?"
    ks frown "¿Quién es Risa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2014
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4974382b:

    # h "She's my friend. We're hitting partners at the tennis club."
    h "Es mi amiga. Somos compañeras de tiro en el club de tenis."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2015
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_992fe2d5:

    # ks "And do you have Risa's number?"
    ks "¿Y tienes el número de Risa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2016
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5290d621:

    # h "Yes."
    h "Sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2017
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_34edc8f9:

    # ks "Alright, call her now. Tell her you've been held up and you don't know how long you'll be."
    ks "Muy bien. Llámala ahora. Dile que algo se presentó y que no sabes cuánto vas a tardar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2018
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d0e78564:

    # "I've barely finished speaking before Hiroko pulls her phone from out of her sports bag."
    "Apenas termino de hablar, Hiroko saca su teléfono de su bolsa deportiva."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2019
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_248e1ac3:

    # h tennis_headhold2 neutral_side "..." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 neutral_side "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2020
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_83281756:

    # h surprised_side "Hey, Risa? I've been held up and I dunno how long I'll be." with dissolve
    h surprised_side "¿Hola, Risa? Algo se presentó y no sé cuánto voy a tardar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2021
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ea3f26b4:

    # h irritated "Yeah, it fuckin' sucks... Eh, don't ask why, okay? 's kinda personal." with dissolve
    h irritated "Sí, qué cagada... Eh, no preguntes por qué, ¿sí? Es un tanto personal." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2022
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d0f778d4:

    # h nervous_side "Thanks, 'Ris. I'll be there soon as I can, yeah?" with dissolve
    h nervous_side "Gracias, 'Ris. Estaré ahí tan pronto como pueda, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2023
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c0f0dcd1:

    # h happy "'Kay, love ya! Bye!" with dissolve
    h happy "Bien, ¡te quiero! ¡Adiós!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2025
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c24fee3e:

    # "Hiroko taps the phone to end the call and in an instant [p_their] demeanor shifts back to its default as [p_they] quietly puts the phone away." with dissolve
    "Hiroko toca la pantalla de su teléfono para terminar la llamada y en un instante regresa a su modo predeterminado y guarda su teléfono." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2061
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_14478f60:

    # ks neutral "Great. Now follow me..."
    ks neutral "Genial. Ahora sígueme..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2065
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ea24b036:

    # ks casual "You see all those manga books on the shelves there, [hypno6]?"
    ks casual "¿Ves todos esos libros de manga en los estantes de ahí, [hypno6!t!l]?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2067
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_92a1904c:

    # "As [p_they] enters the room with me, her eyes immediately swivel to where I point and she smiles blanky as she responds." with dissolve
    "Tras entrar a la habitación conmigo, dirige inmediatamente su mirada a donde señalo, y responde con una sonrisa vacía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2068
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_afd1de02:

    # h smile_side "Yes, Kyou." with dissolve
    h smile_side "Sí, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2071
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f08dfe2a:

    # ks "Good. Now when I tell you to, I want you to carry out the following instructions until I tell you to stop."
    ks "Bien. Ahora, cuando te indique, quiero que ejecutes las siguientes instrucciones hasta que te diga que te detengas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2073
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e0b0efb7:

    # ks "First, I want you to move all these mangas on the shelves to the coffee table in my living room downstairs." with dissolve
    ks "Primero, quiero que lleves todos esos mangas de los estantes a la mesa de centro que hay en mi sala en el piso de abajo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2074
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8426d18c:

    # ks "You will do this by picking one book off the shelf at a time, at random, taking it downstairs and repeating until these shelves are completely empty."
    ks "Lo harás tomando un libro del estante a la vez, al azar, llevándolo abajo hasta que estos estantes estén completamente vacíos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2075
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_55dcc0b0:

    # ks "Next, take one of the mangas you left in the living room and put it BACK on these shelves, making sure to arrange the books in alphabetical order."
    ks "Después, toma uno de los mangas que dejaste en la sala y ponlo DE REGRESO en estos estantes, asegurándote de acomodarlos en orden alfabético."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2076
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_711e1129:

    # ks "When you're done, you're to send me a text message reading \"[hypno2]\"."
    ks "Cuando hayas terminado, me enviarás un mensaje con el texto \"[hypno2!t]\"."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2077
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a0dcc7ef:

    # ks "Once you've sent the text, repeat these instructions from the beginning. Understand, [hypno6]?"
    ks "Una vez hayas enviado el texto, repetirás estas instrucciones desde el comienzo. ¿Entendido, [hypno6!t!l]?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2078
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b901d24d:

    # h "Yes, Kyou."
    h "Sí, Kyou."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2079
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_212d61a3:

    # "I let out a little chuckle at the [hypno6]'s immediate and easy compliance. No human alive would willingly do something this fucking stupid and repetitive."
    "Me río ligeramente de la respuesta inmediata y obediente que muestra [el] [hypno6!t!l]. Ningún humano en la Tierra accedería a hacer una mierda tan estúpida y repetitiva."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2080
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b8a01936:

    # "Before I hacked Hiroko's programming, [p_they] would've been positively murderous at the suggestion [p_they] do anything for me instead of train for tomorrow's big event."
    "Antes de hackear la programación de Hiroko, me habría querido matar por solo sugerir la idea de que hiciera algo por mí en lugar entrenar para su gran evento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2081
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_92cb73b0:

    # "So assigning this task is a great way to reinforce Hiroko's new programming and confirm that [p_their] systems have been completely taken over by my own code."
    "Por lo que asumo que esta tarea es una gran reafirmación de la nueva programación de Hiroko que confirmará que mi código se ha apoderado por completo de su sistema."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2082
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a9d82de:

    # ks "Good, [hypno6]. Now carry out my instructions. [hypno3]."
    ks "Bien, [hypno6!t!l]. Ahora ejecuta mis instrucciones. [hypno3!t]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2085
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_424329d9:

    # "With my first [hypno6] taken care of for the morning, I step into the shower and start to think about what's to come."
    "Habiéndome encargado de mi primer[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], entro a la ducha y me pongo a pensar en lo que está por ocurrir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2087
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4f73b6b3:

    # "It's still pretty early, but I need to get to Nozomi's house as soon as I can, before Sayori shows up."
    "Aún es bastante temprano, pero debo ir a casa de Nozomi tan pronto como pueda, antes de que Sayori llegue."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2146
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9ff70506:

    # "Then I can check in with the other [hypno6]; make doubly sure [p_they]'s operating in accordance with last night's deep programming session."
    "Entonces podré revisar a mi otr[genero_ao] [hypno6!t!l]; cerciorarme de que esté operando conforme a la profunda programación de anoche."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2089
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_157faf53:

    # "I'm gonna need [p_them] working properly if I'm to take care of Sayori before the day's out..."
    "Necesito que funcione adecuadamente si voy a encargarme de Sayori para el final del día..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2093
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f9e7595c:

    # "Alright, I'll just grab my keys and head out. And take a quick look at my manga collection."
    "Muy bien, ahora tomaré mis llaves y saldré. No sin antes darle un vistazo a mi colección de manga."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2094
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f215edec:

    # "There must be a couple dozen books missing, having been taken from varying places with no rhyme or reason..."
    "Deberían faltarle un par de docenas de libros, sacados de distintos lugares sin patrón y sin razón..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2096
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_28e7cfe0:

    # "Just then, Hiroko pads into the room and starts to crouch down in front of the shelves." with dissolve
    "En ese momento, Hiroko entra a la habitación y se agacha frente a los estantes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2097
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_68e09ff1:

    # ks casual "Ah, Hiroko, stop what you're doing for a moment."
    ks casual "Ah, Hiroko, detén lo que estás haciendo por un momento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2099
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b48c3ca4:

    # "She'd completely blanked me before I addressed her, but now she stands and turns to look straight at me." with dissolve
    "Me ignoraba por completo antes de que le hablara, pero ahora está de pie mirándome directamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2100
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a22577b7:

    # ks smile "I left my dirty laundry on the bathroom floor. Go pick it up and put it in the washing machine downstairs."
    ks smile "Dejé mi ropa sucia en el piso del baño. Levántala y métela en la lavadora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2101
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_353291da:

    # ks "When you're done, resume your previous instructions. Okay, [hypno6]?"
    ks "Cuando hayas terminado, reanuda tus instrucciones anteriores. ¿De acuerdo, [hypno6!t!l]?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2102
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9eac8445:

    # h smile "Okay, Kyou." with dissolve
    h smile "De acuerdo, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2104
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4ecb1090:

    # "[p_they!c] turns on [p_their] heel and walks back out towards the bathroom, and I pick up the keys from my desk, confident about leaving [p_them] in the house unsupervised..." with dissolve
    "Se da media vuelta y vuelve a bajar las escaleras camino al baño, mientras yo tomo las llaves de mi escritorio, confiando en que puedo dejarl[genero_ao] en la casa sin supervisión..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2106
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5008d8f9:

    # "... Damn, maybe I should've had Hiroko doing domestic service work the whole time instead of that stupid bullshit assignment I gave [p_them]?"
    "... Diablos, ¿tal vez habría sido mejor ponerl[genero_ao] a hacer servicio doméstico en lugar de esa estúpida tarea de mierda que le di?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2107
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b3a85f93:

    # "Something for next time maybe. If I can deal with Sayori first."
    "Será para la próxima, supongo. Si es que puedo hacerme cargo de Sayori primero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2108
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7581f9ab:

    # "Yeah, Sayori. I can't get excited about my [hypno6]s right now. I need to focus."
    "Sí, Sayori. No puedo emocionarme demasiado por mis [hypno6!t!l]s ahora. Debo concentrarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2109
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d4f39654:

    # "If this doesn't go down perfectly I could be in big trouble..."
    "Si esto no sale a la perfección, podría meterme en serios problemas..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2137
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e6a42ee2:

    # "Nozomi is waiting to greet me at the door when I arrive at her place."
    "Nozomi está esperando en la puerta para recibirme en su morada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2140
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1b399fab:

    # "I notice the flat manner in which the [hypno6] greets me immediately."
    "Noto inmediatamente el modo plano en que [el] [hypno6!t!l] me saluda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2141
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_66966641:

    # "Just like Hiroko, Nozomi defaults to [p_their] robotic state when alone or if [p_they]'s just with me. So this can only mean we're currently alone in this house."
    "Al igual que Hiroko, Nozomi permanece por defecto en su estado robótico cuando está sol[genero_ao] o si solo está conmigo. Eso solo puede significar que estamos solos en esta casa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2219
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6c4300a8:

    # "It's just then that I feel my phone buzz from a received text message..."
    "En ese momento siento mi teléfono vibrar con un mensaje recibido..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2221
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4442b8c1:

    # ks "Ah, no. She couldn't tear herself away from her tennis practice. You know how she is."
    ks "Ah, no. Tuvo que ir a su práctica de tenis. Ya sabes cómo es."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2222
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_14287d32:

    # s casual_handup "Hmm. Alright then. Now, I believe the two of you are going to enlighten me on what I have been out of the loop on." with dissolve
    s casual_handup "Mmm. Bien, entonces. Ahora, me parece que ustedes dos planean iluminarme con lo que me he perdido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2234
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_99ad62b2:

    # s irritated "And... you could not have simply told me this at any time before now? I'm sorry, Nozomi, but I don't understand why we needed to do this here." with dissolve
    s irritated "Y… ¿no pudieron simplemente haberme dicho eso cuando fuera? Perdóname, Nozomi, pero no entiendo por qué tenemos que hacer esto aquí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2235
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b295e1c4:

    # s casual_folded "You all made it seem much more complicated than what you are now telling me." with dissolve
    s casual_folded "Lo hicieron sonar mucho más complicado que lo que me están diciendo ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2237
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2b7fcf32:

    # s annoyed_right "Which was?" with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "¿La cual fue?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2242
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5efcdffa:

    # s casual_handup "And what would be so complicated about it? You shone it in her face as some kind of prank, yes?" with dissolve
    s casual_handup "¿Y qué tendría eso de complicado? La encendiste en su cara como alguna clase de broma, ¿cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2250
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_35eae3ff:

    # s casual_folded "But what of yours and Hiroko's sudden quietude and... compliance?" with dissolve
    s casual_folded "Pero ¿qué hay de ese súbito sosiego tuyo y de Hiroko y su… complacencia?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2252
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4ae6bee6:

    # s rolleyes "I mean, how do we go from not wanting to speak to Kyou on Monday, being scared of him by Tuesday..." with dissolve
    s rolleyes "Lo que quiero decir es: ¿Cómo es que pasamos de no querer hablar con Kyou el lunes, tenerle miedo el martes…" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2253
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b9ac5b08:

    # s annoyed "Angrily confronting him by Thursday, to having him home and hanging on his every word by Saturday?" with dissolve
    s annoyed "... enfrentarlo iracundamente el jueves, a invitarlo a casa y atender cada palabra de lo que dice el sábado?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2254
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cb595c2a:

    # s casual_handup concerned "That is an odd progression is it not?" with dissolve
    s casual_handup concerned "Es una progresión extraña, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2259
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8289269c:

    # s casual "Tired? Nozomi, it is mid-morning. Are you getting enough sleep?" with dissolve
    s casual "¿Cansada? Nozomi, estamos en plena mañana. ¿Estás durmiendo lo suficiente?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2427
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_db2e00c2:

    # nm neutral "Well... could I speak to you before you go?" with dissolve
    nm neutral "Pues... ¿podría hablar contigo antes de que te vayas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2446
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3606af66:

    # nm neutral "But there are only a few people she genuinely trusts enough to bring any closer than that." with dissolve
    nm neutral "Pero hay muy pocas personas en las que genuinamente confía lo suficiente para dejar que se acerquen más que eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2448
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7e8c5c71:

    # nm happy "But I know, I know, you have places to be and you're having to listen to this old woman's natter. I won't keep you any longer today." with dissolve
    nm happy "Pero ya sé, ya sé, tienes lugares adonde ir y aquí te tengo escuchando el parloteo de está doña. Ya no voy a entretenerte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2451
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_269b2e02:

    # nm happy "Good! I hope to see you again, Kyou. You're welcome in this house anytime." with dissolve
    nm happy "¡Bien! Espero volver a verte, Kyou. Eres bienvenido en esta casa cuando sea." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2460
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5244d001:

    # s concerned "Having to accept that I am, as you say... a [hypno6]." with dissolve
    s concerned "Tener que aceptar que soy, como dices... un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2463
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b704979a:

    # s casual_handup surprised_right "It is so outlandish, yet somehow I accept it completely." with dissolve
    s casual_handup surprised_right "Es tan estrafalario, y sin embargo lo acepto completamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2468
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b25f6582:

    # s casual sleep "So I apologize for questioning your authority, Kyou. You are my programmer after all." with dissolve
    s casual sleep "Así que me disculpo por cuestionar tu autoridad, Kyou. Eres mi programador, después de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2473
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_76e53f8f:

    # ks sigh "Oh my god... What am I doing, Sayori?"
    ks sigh "Oh, Dios mío... ¿qué estoy haciendo, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2474
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf390c15:

    # s concerned_right "You... are leading me to your home, Kyou." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Estás... guiándome a tu casa, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2475
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b9cc260c:

    # ks "No, I mean... fuck, what am I DOING?!"
    ks "No, digo... ¡carajo, ¿qué estoy HACIENDO?!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2476
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_663d7e3f:

    # s casual_handup "I am sorry, but it seems my limitations as a [hypno6] prevent me from drawing a distinction between this question and your last one." with dissolve
    s casual_handup "Me disculpo, pero parece que mis limitaciones como [hypno6!t!l] me impiden hallar una distinción entre esta pregunta y la anterior." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2477
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_761771ec:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "So although I have processed that you require a different response, I can only supply an identical answer." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Por lo que, si bien proceso que requieres una respuesta diferente, no puedo proveer más que una contestación idéntica." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2479
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_891de8d7:

    # ks angry "Sayori, no, you're NOT a [hypno6]! NONE of you are!" with dissolve
    ks angry "Sayori, no, ¡NO eres un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] ¡NINGUNA de ustedes lo es!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2480
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7c488431:

    # ks "You're real girls from my class that I fucked with just because I could. Just to see how far I could go with you all. Like you were some fucking science project."
    ks "Son chicas de verdad de mi clase a las que jodí solo porque podía. Solo por ver qué tan lejos podía llegar con ustedes. Como si fueran un puto proyecto se ciencias."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2481
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_df9617ca:

    # ks "And let's face it, I've already got my answer: I can go as far as I want!"
    ks "Y afrontémoslo, ya tengo mi respuesta: ¡puedo ir tan lejos como quiera!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2482
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_db8984ac:

    # s casual surprised_right "Kyou, I... I do not know how to process this information. But if I were truly human then I would find your confession... frightening." with dissolve
    s casual surprised_right "Kyou, no... no sé cómo procesar esta información. Pero si en verdad fuese humana, tu confesión me parecería... atemorizante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2483
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d43ed11c:

    # ks frown "Yeah... I'm a little scared of myself right now."
    ks frown "Sí... siento algo de miedo de mí mismo ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2491
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_614ce976:

    # ks "I haven't been kind to you. Or to Nozomi and especially not to Hiroko. Not to any of you. And you didn't deserve any of this. No one does..."
    ks "No he sido amable contigo. Ni con Nozomi, ni mucho menos con Hiroko. Con ninguna de ustedes. Y no se merecían nada de esto. Nadie lo merece..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2494
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_69c19daa:

    # "For a while it seems like time stands still while my mind opens up to the horrors of what I've done to these girls." with dissolve
    "Por un momento parece que el tiempo se detiene mientras mi mente se abre a los horrores de lo que les he hecho a estas chicas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2495
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_23311345:

    # "Even now, Sayori doesn't scream or run like a normal woman would on hearing any of this."
    "Incluso ahora, Sayori no grita ni sale corriendo como lo haría una mujer normal al oír todo esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2496
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_98838f5c:

    # "Instead, her expression is filled with concern at her programmer breaking down in front of her. Unable to do anything but follow my lead."
    "En vez de eso, su expresión se llena con preocupación hacia su programador quebrándose ante ella. Incapaz de hacer más que seguir mi dirección."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2497
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_916e4338:

    # "Because after just a few short minutes under my penlight she truly thinks she's a [hypno6] now, just like the rest of them."
    "Pues tras solo unos cortos minutos bajo mi linterna, cree verdaderamente que es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], igual que las otras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2498
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c0a73d2e:

    # "How the fuck was this supposed to go, Kyou? Were you gonna keep them like this for thir entire lives?"
    "¿Qué carajos se suponía que ocurriera, Kyou? ¿Ibas a tenerlas así por el resto de sus vidas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2499
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6c769920:

    # "Just pretend this shit is fine and no one in their lives would notice?"
    "¿Fingir que esta mierda está bien y nadie en sus vidas se daría cuenta?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2500
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2f22eee2:

    # ks sigh "Haaah.... h-haaaah...."
    ks sigh "Aaaah.... a-aaaah...."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2501
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_547117e1:

    # "It takes a few breaths, but eventually I can feel the cogs of my brain begin to turn once more as I try to form some kind of plan."
    "Tomo bastante aire y eventualmente vuelvo a sentir los engranajes girando en mi cabeza, intentando formar alguna especie de plan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2502
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_86400a67:

    # ks neutral "Alright... we're still going home, Sayori. Follow me."
    ks neutral "Muy bien... aún iremos a casa, Sayori. Sígueme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2503
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b50a93af:

    # s casual_handup "Of course." with dissolve
    s casual_handup "Desde luego." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2507
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_28ff25f3:

    # "My mind continues to work amidst the dread I feel, as I lead my silent companion to my door..."
    "Mi mente continúa trabajando a pesar del terror que siento, mientras llevo a mi silenciosa acompañante hasta mi puerta..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2509
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_298dd0e5:

    # ks casual "Here, head inside. I think I know what I'm going to do."
    ks casual "Es aquí, entra. Creo que sé qué es lo que haré."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2514
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_db76ee8d:

    # "Yeah. I'll send Nozomi a text; get her to come here as soon as she can."
    "Sí. Le enviaré un mensaje a Nozomi; que venga tan pronto como pueda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2515
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2dadc5a1:

    # "This dread feeling... I don't think it's ever gonna leave me for as long as I live."
    "Esta sensación de terror... no creo que desaparezca por el resto de mi existencia."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2516
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_95cd20d8:

    # "But it'll ease, if I give these girls their lives back."
    "Pero se aliviará un poco si les devuelvo a estas chicas sus vidas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2517
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f8a3019f:

    # ks casual frown "Alright, so... I think I know what to do."
    ks casual frown "Muy bien, pues... creo que sé qué hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2521
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b4985ba5:

    # "Just then there's a quiet padding of socked feet as Hiroko descends the staircase and calmly joins us in the living room." with dissolve
    "De pronto se escuchan los suaves pasos de Hiroko quien baja tranquilamente las escaleras y se nos une en la sala." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2522
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4123dbef:

    # ks sigh "Ah shit, Hiroko..."
    ks sigh "Ah, mierda, Hiroko..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2525
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8e75a3cf:

    # "Pulling out my phone, I quickly take a peek at my missed messages, just as I hear a gentle thud of a book dropping on my coffee table."
    "Saco mi teléfono y doy un vistazo rápido a mis mensajes sin leer, mientras escucho un libro desplomarse en mi mesa de centro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2526
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2081639f:

    # "{color=FF89AB}[hypno2]\n[hypno2]\n[hypno2]{/color}"
    "{color=FF89AB}[hypno2!t]\n[hypno2!t]\n[hypno2!t]{/color}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2527
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dde43d84:

    # "{color=FF89AB}[hypno2]\n[hypno2]{/color}"
    "{color=FF89AB}[hypno2!t]\n[hypno2!t]{/color}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2529
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_eaeeb990:

    # s casual_handup surprised "Hiroko? I thought you were at tennis practice?" with dissolve
    s casual_handup surprised "¿Hiroko? Creí que estabas en práctica de tenis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2530
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e232e3cb:

    # "This girl has been up and down those stairs literally hundreds of times. She must be completely worn out by now, no matter how hard she tries to hide it."
    "Esta chica ha bajado y subido las escaleras literalmente cientos de veces. Debe estar completamente agotada, sin importar cuánto intente ocultarlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2511
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7343f236:

    # ks surprised "Hiroko, stop! That's enough!"
    ks surprised "¡Hiroko, para! ¡Ya es suficiente!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2533
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fc2f8d9d:

    # "Having turned around to head up the stairs yet again, Hiroko ceases and turns back to face me with that quiet, eerie smile of hers." with dissolve
    "Habiéndose dado la vuelta para subir de nuevo las escaleras, Hiroko se detiene y se gira para mirarme con esa tranquila y espeluznante sonrisa suya." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2535
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11ba295f:

    # "At least for a moment, until she registers we have company." with dissolve
    "Al menos por un momento, hasta que se da cuenta de que tenemos compañía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2536
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5910d9f3:

    # h tennis_headhold2 nervous_side "S-Sayori? Uh, hi?" with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 nervous_side "¿S-Sayori? Eh, ¿hola?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2537
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9bdc6d2f:

    # "She sure passed my test alright. As if I needed another reminder of how badly I messed her up."
    "Pasó mi prueba sin duda. Como si necesitara otro recordatorio de cuánto la afecté."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2540
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f057471e:

    # ks sigh "Relax, both of you. You don't need to hide that you're \"[hypno6]\"s around each other. I hurt you both just the same." with dissolve
    ks sigh "Relájense las dos. No necesitan ocultar que son \"[hypno6!t!l]s\" frente a la otra. Les hice el mismo daño a ambas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2541
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bb4101e5:

    # h tennis smile "Oh... yes, Kyou. I will shut down my human mode then 'cuz I'm super low on energy." with dissolve
    h tennis smile "Oh... sí, Kyou. Apagaré mi modo humano porque estoy superbaja de energía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2542
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c367cc86:

    # ks "Yeah, you do that. You just have to listen to me, because I'm gonna do another deep programming session on both of you."
    ks "Sí, has eso. Porque les haré otra profunda sesión de programación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2543
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4207e2cc:

    # ks "And then Nozomi too, when she gets here..."
    ks "Y luego a Nozomi también, cuando llegue aquí..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2545
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4378bafa:

    # "I take a deep breath as I steel myself for what I need to do." with dissolve
    "Respiro profundo, armándome de valor para lo que debo hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2546
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_77dd4a7a:

    # ks neutral "But first I'm gonna say a few things. Just for my own sanity; get these thoughts out into the open and see if they still make any sense at all."
    ks neutral "Pero antes diré un par de cosas. Solo por mi propia cordura; diré estas ideas en voz alta para ver si aún tienen un mínimo de sentido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2549
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9b50de1c:

    # ks "So, uh... l-like, you're not gonna remember any of what I'm going to say, but I won't get another chance after, so I just wanna tell you how sorry I am for everything."
    ks "Pues, eh... e-este, no van a recordar nada de lo que voy a decir, pero no tendré otra oportunidad, así que solo quiero decirles cuánto lo siento por todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2550
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d4d5bdc1:

    # ks "Not just for what I've done to you. But for what I need to do to you now in order to set you free."
    ks "No solo por lo que les he hecho. Sino también por lo que debo hacer para poder liberarlas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2551
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bf78dadb:

    # ks "Because I know I can't just blank your memories of the past few days, tell you you're human beings again and expect it all to work out. It's gone too far for that."
    ks "Porque sé que no puedo simplemente borrar sus recuerdos de los últimos días, decirles que son seres humanos otra vez y esperar que todo salga bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2552
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fdf45e16:

    # ks "And if I just removed the [hypno6] programming from your heads and brought you back to reality... Man, I don't wanna know what would happen if I did that."
    ks "Y si solo removiera la programación de [hypno6!t!l] de sus cabezas y las trajera de vuelta a la realidad... Caray, no quiero saber qué pasaría si hago eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2553
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_595a30c6:

    # ks "So... I'm not gonna suggest that you're not [hypno6]s anymore, but I'll push that part of your identities all the way back, in the deepest, darkest corners of your minds."
    ks "Así que... no les diré que ya no son [hypno6!t!l]s, sino que voy a sepultar esa parte de sus identidades en lo más profundo y recóndito de sus mentes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2554
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5e28a279:

    # ks "I'll suggest the damage I did by hacking your programming will be repaired and that you'll be oblivious to your \"true\" natures once more."
    ks "Les diré que el daño que les hice al hackear su programación estará reparado y no tendrán idea de sus \"verdaderas\" naturalezas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2555
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90624832:

    # ks "As far as you'll be consciously aware you'll consider yourselves normal human beings exactly as you were."
    ks "En cuanto a ustedes concernirá conscientemente, se considerarán humanas normales exactamente como eran antes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2557
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_88603ba5:

    # ks "But if anything happens, anything at all, where you need to recall these last days of your lives while you were running under my programming..."
    ks "Pero si algo ocurre, cualquier cosa que les exija recordar estos últimos días de su vida mientras corrían mi programación..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2558
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_69b6de6d:

    # ks "W-well, you'll be able to process those times effortlessly without discomfort, without ever feeling something was out of place."
    ks "B-bueno, serán capaces de procesar esos momentos fácilmente y sin incomodidad, sin sentir que nada estuvo nunca fuera de lugar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2559
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6e3145ca:

    # ks "To your inner [hypno6] selves, you'll accept that these events were simply the cause of a rare glitch in your programming, never to be repeated."
    ks "En cuanto a sus [hypno6!t!l]s intern[genero_ao]s, aceptarán que estos eventos fueron simplemente la causa de ese extraño glitch en su programación, que nunca se repetirá."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2560
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_99c1ea93:

    # ks "That should allow you to live your lives as you were before..."
    ks "Eso debería permitirles vivir sus vidas como antes..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2561
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2c6cd6ca:

    # "I nod to myself. It seems right to me. As right as it can be."
    "Asiento para mí mismo. Me parece bien. Tan bien como puede estar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2563
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_855b249c:

    # "So let's end this."
    "Ahora terminemos con esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2564
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_991ebbaf:

    # k "Power down..."
    k "Apagar ahora..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2565
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_15fc8c88:

    # "AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's where I have to end things for now."
    "NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Y aquí lo debo dejar por ahora."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2566
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6b669766:

    # "Hoping I can complete an epilogue for next time and finish this story path in time for the next early access release!"
    "¡Espero poder completar un epílogo para la próxima y terminar esta línea para el siguiente acceso anticipado!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2567
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0ce858e9:

    # "TO BE CONTINUED!"
    "¡CONTINUARÁ!"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-10-26 22:42

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2453
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3264d8b4:

    # "I can't quiet that voice anymore."
    "Ya no puedo callar esa voz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2475
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_888cd1e1:

    # "Even now, after hearing all of this, Sayori doesn't scream or run like a normal woman would."
    "Incluso ahora, después de oír todo eso, Sayori no grita ni corre como una mujer normal."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2478
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3af2c682:

    # "How the fuck was this supposed to go, Kyou? Were you gonna keep them like this forever?"
    "¿Qué carajos se suponía que ocurriera, Kyou? ¿Ibas a tenerlas así para siempre?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2479
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_53cfc074:

    # "Just pretend this shit is fine and no one in their lives would notice anything amiss?"
    "¿Fingir que esta mierda está bien y que nadie en sus vidas notaría nada extraño?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2496
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f4b371f1:

    # "But it'll ease, if I give all these girls their lives back."
    "Pero se aliviará un poco si les devuelvo a estas chicas sus vidas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2497
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f36e2e58:

    # ks casual frown "Alright, so... here's what I'm gonna do."
    ks casual frown "Muy bien, pues... esto es lo que haré."


# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2540
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d7ce736a:

    # ks "W-well, you'll be able to process those times effortlessly without discomfort, without ever feeling something truly terrible had happened to you."
    ks "B-bueno, serán capaces de procesar esos momentos fácilmente y sin incomodidad, sin sentir nunca que nada horrible les ocurrió."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2543
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_52bcf4dd:

    # "I nod to myself. It seems right to me. At least, as right as it can be."
    "Asiento para mis adentros. Me parece bien. Al menos, tan bien como me es posible."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2547
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f6572367:

    # k "Okay, girls. Let's get you powered down..."
    k "Muy bien, chicas. Ahora voy a apagarlas..."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2021-11-30 09:30

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1482
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_37f15feb:

    # ks frown "After I spent this week brainwashing your friends into becoming my devoted groupies I had to re-examine those feelings."
    ks frown " Luego de pasar esta semana lavándoles el cerebro a tus amigas para convertirlas en mis fanáticas devotas, tuve que reexaminar esos sentimientos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1486
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_899f158e:

    # ks neutral "When it comes down to it, my feelings about you haven't changed so much that I've stopped wanting you. Far from it."
    ks neutral "Al final del día, mis sentimientos por ti no han cambiado tanto como para dejar de quererte. Ni de cerca."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1487
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5ac10906:

    # ks "I know I could make anyone love me with this penlight in my hand. After what it's done to you three there's no doubt in my mind about that."
    ks "Sé que puedo hacer que quien sea me ame con la linterna que tengo en mi mano. Tras lo que les hizo a ustedes tres, no me queda rastro de duda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1488
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f0ee80ba:

    # ks "And... sure, I could find someone better looking and make her mine. But what would be the point? She wouldn't mean anything to me."
    ks "Y... claro, podría encontrar a alguien más atractiva y hacerla mía. Pero ¿qué caso tendría? No significaría nada para mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1489
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb40f95b:

    # ks "But you, Nozomi. I've had my eyes on you for so long, but more than that... you're the reason for all of this."
    ks "Pero tú, Nozomi. He tenido mis ojos en ti por tanto tiempo, y lo que es más... tú eres la razón de todo esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1490
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_39aeca8f:

    # ks "Were it not for you, I never would've had these ideas by myself. Never would've followed through..."
    ks "De no ser por ti, nunca habría tenido estas ideas yo solo. Nunca las habría seguido..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1491
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_66dc0e24:

    # ks "I need you, Nozomi. I did all of this for you."
    ks "Te necesito, Nozomi. Hice todo esto por ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1492
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_02e19788:

    # "I watch as Nozomi's lower lip quivers. Her mind, foggy as it'll be from about a dozen active hypnotic suggestions, must be trying so hard to work for her."
    "El labio inferior de Nozomi se estremece. A su mente, nebulosa por casi una docena de activas sugestiones hipnóticas, debe estarle costando funcionar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1487
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2586c1f6:

    # n "A-and do you think that's... love, Kyou? This... this obsession?" with dissolve
    n "¿Y-y tú crees que eso es... amor, Kyou? Esta... ¿esta obsesión?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1494
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_058d5dbc:

    # n "We all knew there was something dangerous about you. The way you wouldn't leave us alone for all these years. There just had to be."
    n "Sabíamos que había algo peligroso en ti. Viendo cómo no nos dejabas en paz por tantos años. Sabíamos que no traerías nada bueno."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1495
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_151dcb00:

    # n "We didn't know what to do about you; the teachers wouldn't listen, but..."
    n "No sabíamos qué hacer contigo; los profesores no escuchaban, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1496
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_afbdaed2:

    # n sleeptalk "But I never could've imagined that you'd do something like this." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Pero nunca me pude imaginar que harías algo como esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1497
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_39af7bdf:

    # n "It shouldn't be possible. It... it shouldn't..."
    n "No debería ser posible. No... debería..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1499
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_50f04021:

    # "I scoff at her, shaking my head."
    "Me mofo de ella, sacudiendo la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1501
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2c252a1a:

    # ks frown "Maybe if you gave me a chance before then none of this would've happened." with dissolve
    ks frown "Tal vez si me hubieras dado una oportunidad antes, nada de esto habría pasado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1502
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cd7defa0:

    # ks "You never even TRIED to talk to me. None of you did."
    ks "Nunca INTENTASTE siquiera hablarme. Ninguna lo hizo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1506
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_190203db:

    # ks "I don't know if what I feel for you now is love or whatever, Nozomi. It doesn't matter anymore. We're past all that."
    ks "No sé si lo que siento por ti ahora es amor o qué-sé-yo, Nozomi. Eso ya no importa. Eso quedó atrás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1507
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_297ad131:

    # ks "You'll all be trying a lot harder for me from now on."
    ks "Todas se esforzarán mucho más de ahora en adelante."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1509
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6f0b6111:

    # "Nozomi, drained as she is on my couch, lets out a hollow chuckle."
    "Nozomi, agotada en mi sofá, libera una risita vacía."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1511
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b85551b8:

    # n sleeptalk "You can brainwash us all you want with that light. Make us say and do whatever your sick mind can think of to make you feel better..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Puedes lavarnos el cerebro tanto como quieras con esa luz. Hacernos decir y hacer lo que tu enferma mente crea que te hará sentir mejor..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1512
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_447dcc6a:

    # n "But nothing is making you do these things that you're doing. These... horrible things."
    n "Pero nada te obliga a hacer lo que estás haciendo... Estas... atrocidades."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1513
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_23f2844a:

    # n "This is what you are, Kyou. You'll always know you're a monster."
    n "Esto es lo que eres, Kyou. Siempre sabrás que eres un monstruo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1514
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f85597ae:

    # n sleepy "{cps=15}And that we were always right to be afraid of you-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    n sleepy "{cps=15}Y que siempre tuvimos razón al temerte-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1516
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_168ab416:

    # ks "Sleep, Nozomi."
    ks "Duerme, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1517
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ae6411a0:

    # n sleeptalk "N-n..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "N-n..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1519
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a363a074:

    # ks "You know you can't resist, Nozomi. You've been in various states of hypnosis all day long."
    ks "Sabes que no puedes resistirte, Nozomi. Has estado en varios estados de hipnosis todo el día."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1521
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_25a15ba7:

    # ks "So just sleep and let those nasty thoughts of yours slip away..." with dissolve
    ks "Así que duerme y deja que esos desagradables pensamientos se esfumen..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1522
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_688313c4:

    # "I try to keep a calmness to my voice as I take her back down fully into trance, but... goddamn, she got to me."
    "Intento guardar tranquilidad en mi voz al sumergirla por completo en trance, pero... maldita sea, creo que sí me alteró."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1523
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b3028f14:

    # "But so what if this makes me a monster? Or a creep? Or any of the other vile shit you and the others have thought about me?"
    "Pero ¿y qué si soy un monstruo? ¿O un bicho raro? ¿O todas esas mierdas que tú y las otras han pensado de mí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1524
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f649cddc:

    # "You all pushed me to this. And now I'll make sure you never say those kinds of things to me again."
    "Ustedes me orillaron a esto. Y ahora me aseguraré de que nunca vuelvan a decirme esa clase de cosas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1525
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cf4340e2:

    # ks neutral "That's right, Nozomi. Dropping so deep into hypnosis. Loving how good and easy it feels to go so deep for me."
    ks neutral "Eso es, Nozomi. Cae muy profundo en hipnosis. Sabiendo lo bien que se siente caer tan profundo por mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1526
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4c8e246b:

    # ks "And now that you're back into this nice, deep state for me, I..."
    ks "Y ahora que estás de vuelta en este agradable y profundo estado, quiero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1527
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_71f736ac:

    # "... This is it. This is what it's all come down to."
    "... Es la hora. Todo lo que hice culmina aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1528
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5e12dd5d:

    # ks "I..."
    ks "Quiero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1529
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d549bb46:

    # "I'm hesitating? Why?"
    "¿Estoy dudando? ¿Por qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1530
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_75be7d46:

    # ks "I want you to..."
    ks "Quiero que..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1531
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c03a5169:

    # "I know what I'm doing to them all is terrible, even if they kinda brought this on themselves. I've made my peace with that."
    "Sé que lo que les estoy haciendo es terrible, incluso si se lo buscaron. Ya hice las paces con eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1532
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d91fd130:

    # "And all I need are a few more words before Nozomi will be exactly the girl I want her to be. That's what I wanted all along, right?"
    "Y solo necesito unas cuantas palabras más para que Nozomi sea exactamente la chica que quiero que sea. Eso es lo que siempre quise, ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1533
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6546ea20:

    # "Even if it's a lie. Even if it makes me some kind of monster. If that's what it takes to make her mine..."
    "Incluso si es una mentira. Incluso si me vuelve una especie de monstruo. Si eso es lo que hace falta para que sea mía..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1536
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f8c73623:

    # ks "I want you to think back to our conversation from several days ago."
    ks "Quiero que pienses en la conversación que tuvimos hace varios días."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1537
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d94cc758:

    # "No more second-guessing myself. I've already thought all of this through. And I've already come this far."
    "Basta de vacilación. Ya pensé bien en todo esto. Y ya llegué tan lejos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1538
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_479048e2:

    # ks "Do you remember, Nozomi? How nice and relaxing and safe it feels to consider being in a relationship with me?"
    ks "¿Recuerdas, Nozomi? ¿Lo agradable y relajante y seguro que se siente considerar estar en una relación conmigo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1539
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1fdb935b:

    # n sleeptalk "I don't... it doesn't feel..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "No... no se sien-..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1540
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_91d20a80:

    # "It's time to finish what I started."
    "Es tiempo de terminar lo que empecé."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1542
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_69b69dc5:

    # ks "Doesn't feel right? But there's no denying how deeply relaxed you're feeling right now, is there?" with dissolve
    ks "¿No se siente correcto? Pero no puedes negar lo profundamente relajada que te sientes ahora, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1543
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c99b4577:

    # n sleeptalk "No..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "No..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1545
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_06241af7:

    # ks "So it follows that if you're as completely relaxed as this, then you must also be feeling safe... right?" with dissolve
    ks "Y si estás tan relajada, significa que también te sientes segura, ¿cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1546
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cf7077b7:

    # n sleeptalk "... Right." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "... Cierto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1548
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4e3dbccb:

    # ks "You're relaxed and safe and feeling right... and now you're considering a relationship with me. There's no stopping it. It's so natural to think about it now." with dissolve
    ks "Estás relajada y segura y te sientes muy bien... y ahora estás considerando estar en una relación conmigo. No se puede evitar. Es perfectamente natural pensarlo ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1549
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d95ac86c:

    # ks "That's right, you're thinking about a relationship, and you're weighing it against all those negative feelings that you have about me."
    ks "Eso es, estás pensando en una relación, pero te hacen dudar esos sentimientos negativos que tienes hacia mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1550
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e5c689a6:

    # ks "But the more you think about a relationship with me, the more natural it feels. And the more natural it feels, the more right it becomes to want a relationship with me..."
    ks "Pero entre más piensas en una relación conmigo, más natural se siente. Y entre más natural se siente, más correcto se vuelve estar en una relación conmigo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1551
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0aa7ea33:

    # ks "And the more right it becomes, the less reasonable it must be to have such negative feelings about me."
    ks "Y entre más correcto se vuelve, menos sentido debe tener conservar esos sentimientos negativos sobre mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1552
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1ff73f65:

    # ks "After all, you do want to become my girlfriend now... don't you, Nozomi?"
    ks "Después de todo, tú quieres convertirte en mi novia... ¿no es así, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1553
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8a448b12:

    # n sleeptalk "Y-... yes..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "S-... sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1555
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_076d58ea:

    # ks "So it makes no sense to hold on to those negative feelings you have about me. Does it?" with dissolve
    ks "Por lo que no tiene sentido aferrarte a esos sentimientos negativos que tienes por mí. ¿O sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1556
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c99b4577_1:

    # n sleeptalk "No..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "No..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1558
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fa101044:

    # ks "No it doesn't. Not when we know you want to become my girlfriend." with dissolve
    ks "No, no tiene sentido. No cuando sabes que quieres convertirte en mi novia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1559
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d74c4388:

    # ks "So let go of them, Nozomi. It must be so easy to let go of all that negativity you have towards me. All that resentment. All that hate."
    ks "Así que déjalos ir, Nozomi. Será muy fácil dejar ir toda esa negatividad que tienes hacia mí. Todo ese resentimiento. Todo ese odio."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1560
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_57ffdf53:

    # ks "{cps=15}Very easy to let it all vanish from your mind... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=15}Muy fácil dejar que todo se esfume de tu mente... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1562
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90f55a53:

    # extend "now, Nozomi. All gone."
    extend "ya, Nozomi. Se ha ido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1563
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6df5af98:

    # ks "And now, in a few moments it will be time to wake you up completely, embracing everything that you were told."
    ks "Y ahora, en unos momentos será hora de que despiertes por completo, abrazando todo lo que te he dicho."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1564
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4d31882d:

    # ks "Once you do, you will find that you can speak and move with complete freedom once again."
    ks "Y cuando lo hagas, notarás que, una vez más, puedes hablar y moverte con completa libertad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1571
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7655f7a9:

    # "AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's all we have time for I'm afraid ;_;"
    "NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Y se nos acabó el tiempo, me temo ;_;"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1572
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c12c4c42:

    # "This is another alternate path that I've struggled so much more than I thought I would going in..."
    "Esta es otra ruta alternativa que fue mucho más difícil de lo que pensé..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1573
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_886c960d:

    # "... To the point where it might have been better to have simply written it out of the game x.x"
    "... Tanto así que tal vez habría sido mejor simplemente cortarla del juego x.x"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1574
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9c67b5ab:

    # "I mean, we already know Kyou sees Nozomi as an opponent to be conquered now, not so much as a love interest anymore."
    "Vaya, ya todos sabemos que Kyou ve a Nozomi como un oponente al cual conquistar, ya no tanto como un interés amoroso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1575
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5344cd8c:

    # "Is there really much point in exporing an ending where Kyou makes Nozomi a slightly more privileged kind of minion as his enslaved girlfriend, compared to the others?"
    "¿De verdad tiene caso exponer un final en el que Kyou vuelve a Nozomi una secuaz ligeramente más privilegiada que las otras al ser su novia esclava?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1576
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_97ec9388:

    # "Well, maybe I'll work something out for next time..."
    "Bueno, tal vez se me ocurra algo para la próxima..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1577
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a00cf8c4:

    # "TO BE CONTINUED..."
    "CONTINUARÁ..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1685
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4d31882d_1:

    # ks "Once you do, you will find that you can speak and move with complete freedom once again."
    ks "Y cuando lo hagas, notarás que, una vez más, puedes hablar y moverte con completa libertad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1686
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c1eb1bc3_1:

    # ks "Waking up on a count of five, Nozomi."
    ks "Despierta a la cuenta de cinco, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1687
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_261e1d24_1:

    # ks "One, two... Taking a deep breath, feeling energy slowly return to you."
    ks "Uno, dos… Respira profundo, siente la energía volver a ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1688
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_50eed1f9_1:

    # ks "Three, four... Beginning to blink. Feeling your head become clearer; thoughts returning."
    ks "Tres, cuatro… Comienzas a parpadear. Siente cómo tu cabeza se aclara; tus pensamientos regresan."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1690
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_956ce66c_1:

    # ks "And five... wide awake, Nozomi."
    ks "Y cinco… despierta, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1691
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_afadbc11_1:

    # n sleepy "Mmn..." with dissolve
    n sleepy "Mmn…" with dissolve

