    # ks "Wide awake and alert. Welcome back."
    ks "Despierta y alerta. Bienvenida de vuelta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8111
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_394457b2:

    # "Akiko frowns as she looks to me. For a moment it seemed as if she was confused as to why I said that to her." with dissolve
    "Akiko me mira frunciendo el ceño. Por un momento lucía confundida al escucharme decir eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8112
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_51effa35:

    # a "You... wait, you mean it worked?"
    a "Tú... espera, ¿o sea que sí funcionó?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8113
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ada952b0:

    # ks "You seem surprised."
    ks "Pareces sorprendida."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8114
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d0d9025a:

    # "She holds my gaze for a moment before a quiet smile spreads across her lips."
    "Me mira a los ojos por un momento y luego una sonrisa se dibuja en sus labios."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8116
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_7a7d92ca:

    # a "... Yeah, I guess I am." with dissolve
    a "... Sí, supongo que lo estoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8117
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_d66fa768:

    # a "I was trying to focus on saying the letters and staring at that tree picture above the television, just like you wanted."
    a "Intentaba concentrarme en decir las letras y mirar la pintura del árbol sobre el televisor, como me pediste."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8119
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_e9b27fde:

    # a "And I don't know... I guess my eyes were feeling a little strained from all that staring. And I heard you saying some things while I was doing that." with dissolve
    a "Y no sé... supongo que mis ojos se sentían un poco tensos de tanto mirar. Y te oí diciendo cosas mientras hacía eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8121
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_902fb6d9:

    # a "I didn't know what to make of it, so I just kept saying the letters. Only all of a sudden I saw this light pass across my eyes and then..."
    a "No sabía qué pensar, así que simplemente seguí diciendo las letras. Hasta que, de pronto, la luz pasó por mis ojos y entonces..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8123
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_0c5fbd8b:

    # "She purses her lips for a moment." with dissolve
    "Frunce los labios por un momento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8124
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ea9e295a:

    # a "And then it's like I suddenly understood."
    a "Es como si hubiera entendido de repente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8125
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_46e3a17a:

    # "So the light from my penlight really did make a difference. At the very least it accelerated the process of putting her into trance, just as I suspected."
    "Así que la luz de mi linterna realmente hizo la diferencia. Por lo menos aceleró el proceso de ponerla en trance, tal como sospechaba."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8126
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_8ca25b82:

    # "Maybe if I had longer. Maybe if I'd asked her to repeat the alphabet exercise again, she might have begun to fall into trance without my light."
    "Tal vez si hubiera tenido más tiempo. Tal vez si le hubiera pedido repetir el ejercicio del alfabeto, habría empezado a caer en trance sin la linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8129
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ab292060:

    # a "So that's what hypnosis feels like..." with dissolve
    a "Conque así se siente la hipnosis..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8130
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_aeb0ade3:

    # "But I'll have time to think on this later."
    "Pero ya tendré tiempo de pensar en eso después."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8131
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_01f91a9f:

    # ks "Yeah. What do you think?"
    ks "Sí. ¿Qué te parece?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8132
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_ba065a67:

    # "Right now I need to focus on Akiko and her immediate needs."
    "Ahora mismo debo concentrarme en Akiko y sus necesidades inmediatas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8134
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_8de39e0f:

    # a "It's interesting~" with dissolve
    a "Es interesante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8135
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_728a1745:

    # a "If I had to compare it to something, it's a little like when I'm meditating. Except this felt a lot more... pleasant? Somehow?"
    a "Si tuviera que compararlo con algo, es parecido a cuando estoy meditando. Excepto que mucho más... ¿placentero? ¿Podría decir?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8136
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_43b72252:

    # ks "Would you like to experience it again? We still need to try that re-induction trigger we agreed on."
    ks "¿Te gustaría experimentarlo otra vez? Aún nos falta probar el ancla de reinducción que acordamos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8138
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_c2216ec8:

    # a "Oh... right, do you think that will work?" with dissolve
    a "Oh... cierto, ¿crees que vaya a funcionar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8141
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_0662831c:

    # a "It seems a little far-fetched to put someone back into hypnosis right..."
    a "Suena un tanto descabellado poner a alguien de vuelta en hipnosis instan-..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8144
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_433e87f5:

    # a "R-right away..."
    a "I-instantánea-...{w=1.0} mente..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8145
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_de9e04c7:

    # "With a chuckle, I hold up my phone with a rotating black spiral pattern displaying on its large OLED screen."
    "Riendo, alzo mi teléfono, desplegando un patrón de espiral giratoria color negro en su gran pantalla OLED."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8146
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_65348588:

    # "This was the app I was looking for a few minutes ago. Just a simple thing made just for a novelty purpose."
    "Esta es la aplicación que estaba buscando. Una cosilla simple hecha por la novedad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8147
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_847ffa45:

    # "But for Akiko in this moment, it may be more than just a novelty..."
    "Pero para Akiko en este momento, puede que sea más que solo una novedad..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8148
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_91ee803d:

    # ks "Just keep staring into the spiral, Akiko. Let it relax you and take you deeper."
    ks "Solo observa la espiral, Akiko. Deja que te relaje y te lleve más profundo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8151
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_f430bfb4:

    # ks "Deeper... that's right."
    ks "Más profundo... Eso es."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8197
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_08b5b065:

    # a "Eee..."
    a "E..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8200
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_615d209b:

    # ks "Allowing it all to fall away."
    ks "Deja que todo se esfume."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8202
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_37cc5e0b:

    # ks "As you drop irresistibly into..."
    ks "No hace falta resistir... Simplemente..."
