# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7148
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_20f7b38e:

    # "The next morning comes after a restless night's sleep."
    "La mañana siguiente llega tras una noche de poco descanso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7150
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ef9827a5:

    # "I can't stay in bed, not with this anxious feeling wracking my whole body."
    "No puedo quedarme en la cama, no con esta sensación de ansiedad azotando mi cuerpo entero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7152
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f2c20b66:

    # "But I got all morning to kill before the big day I have ahead of me..."
    "Pero tengo toda la mañana libre antes del gran día que me espera..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7159
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a9d67429:

    # "It takes far too long for the afternoon to roll around."
    "Siento que pasa una eternidad antes de que llegue la tarde."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7160
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cbff0225:

    # "Maybe I'm going to be earlier than Nozomi wanted, but I couldn't take waiting around in the house any more. This is driving me crazy."
    "Tal vez llego más temprano de lo que Nozomi quería, pero no soportaba seguir esperando en mi casa. Esto me está volviendo loco."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7161
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4b75ba81:

    # "I can't settle down until I've set things straight with Sayori."
    "No puedo descansar hasta que haya arreglado las cosas con Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7162
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f055f8cd:

    # "But... huh, you know, it's funny. The only reason any of this happened in the first place was because I wanted to get closer to Nozomi."
    "Pero... vaya, ¿sabes?, es gracioso. La única razón por la que esto ocurrió en primer lugar es porque quería acercarme a Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7163
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_094e7fed:

    # "In a roundabout way I've sort of achieved that, getting invited to her house and all. Even if it's still not exactly how I'd have wanted it."
    "De forma indirecta parece que lo conseguí; me invitó a su casa y todo. Aunque no fuera exactamente como hubiera querido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7165
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_19139bbb:

    # "Well anyway, I'll just turn in to this street here and... is this really the place?"
    "Bueno, en fin, solo doy la vuelta en esta calle y... ¿este es el lugar correcto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7166
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6f67d4cc:

    # "I check the note Nozomi gave me... this is the address, alright."
    "Reviso la nota que Nozomi me dio... esta es la dirección, sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7168
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3cd9b0fa:

    # "Looks pretty nice. Nozomi must live well if her family can afford a house like this."
    "Luce muy lindo. Nozomi debe vivir bien si su familia puede pagar un lugar así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7169
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_990eed15:

    # "Assuming this IS her house and not her idea of giving me the run around."
    "Asumiendo que SÍ sea su casa y no una treta para hacerme perder el tiempo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7171
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_17d08f46:

    # "Ugh, I'll put that thought out of my head and just press the doorbell..."
    "Ay, mejor me saco ese pensamiento de la cabeza y solo toco el timbre..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7178
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6b6d342f:

    # nm "... Hello?"
    nm "... ¿Hola?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7179
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b848f034:

    # "Instead of Nozomi, I'm greeted by an older woman at the door. She looks about forty I guess?"
    "En vez de Nozomi, me recibe una mujer mayor en la puerta. Parece tener ¿unos cuarenta, más o menos?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7180
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f35ee54d:

    # ks casual confused "Uh... h-hey."
    ks casual confused "Eh... ho-hola."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7181
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2e1ec8b2:

    # "Now I feel awkward. Did Nozomi really send me to some stranger's house? I really wouldn't put it past her with the way she was to me yesterday."
    "Ahora me siento incómodo. ¿Acaso Nozomi me mandó a la casa de una extraña? No me sorprendería con la forma en que me estaba tratando ayer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7182
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_57f7d1a6:

    # nm smile "Is there something I can help you with?" with dissolve
    nm smile "¿Puedo ayudarte en algo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7183
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1d8ce0b2:

    # "Although whoever she is, she seems friendly. Maybe..."
    "Aunque sea quien sea, parece amable. Tal vez..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7184
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9844263a:

    # ks "I... y-yeah, I was looking for Nozomi? N-Nozomi Akemi?"
    ks "Eh... s-sí, ¿estaba buscando a Nozomi? ¿N-Nozomi Akemi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7185
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_129b0bec:

    # nm surprised "OH!" with vpunch
    nm surprised "¡OH!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7186
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_749df013:

    # ks surprised "... W-what?"
    ks surprised "... ¿Qu-qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7187
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0b7407d4:

    # nm laugh "Ahaha, I'm sorry! I'm just surprised, that's all." with dissolve
    nm laugh "¡Ajaja, lo siento! Es que estoy sorprendida, es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7188
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d0d83b25:

    # nm smile "When my daughter told me she was having another person over for her study group I wasn't expecting a boy~" with dissolve
    nm smile "Cuando mi hija me dijo que vendría una persona más para su grupo de estudio, no me esperaba que fuera un muchacho." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7189
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b869fa09:

    # ks confused "I... I see."
    ks confused "Ya... ya veo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7190
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0cfcaf09:

    # "... Right. This is Nozomi's mother. Why the hell did I not realize that sooner?"
    "... Cierto. Es la madre de Nozomi. ¿Por qué diablos no me di cuenta antes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7192
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7abc57e0:

    # nm happy "Oh, but where are my manners? I'm Atsuko; nice to meet another classmate of Nozomi's~" with dissolve
    nm happy "Oh, pero ¿dónde están mis modales? Soy Atsuko; un gusto conocer a otro compañero de Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7194
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8f5c152c:

    # ks smile "I'm... Kyou. Kyou Koyama. Nice to meet you too."
    ks smile "Soy... Kyou. Kyou Koyama. Gusto en conocerla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7204
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8a73a9ac:

    # "Man, I am not used to talking to older people. It's not like I get much practice with my own folks."
    "Cielos, no estoy acostumbrado a hablar con gente mayor. No tengo mucha práctica que digamos con mis viejos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7205
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6ecb397f:

    # nm "I wonder why she's not here to greet you."
    nm "Me pregunto por qué no vino a recibirte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7206
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7cdc0e4b:

    # ks casual smile "Oh... w-well, I guess she's that deep into her books, huh?"
    ks casual smile "Oh... b-bueno, supongo que está muy inmersa en sus libros, ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7207
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5b0fb9b8:

    # "More like she's not that keen to see me... But I think I'll keep her mom oblivious to that fact."
    "Más bien no está muy emocionada de verme... Pero mejor que su mamá no sepa eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7209
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e2829a61:

    # nm happy "Mhmhm, you might be right. That Sayori must have her working hard!" with dissolve
    nm happy "Jijiji, tal vez tengas razón. ¡Esa Sayori debe tenerla trabajando duro!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7210
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f8234fc0:

    # "Huh? Sayori's already here? And here's me thinking I was way early."
    "¿Oh? ¿Sayori ya está aquí? Y yo que pensaba que yo había llegado temprano."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7211
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_73b41ce1:

    # nm laugh "I just hope you know what you've let yourself in for, young man~" with dissolve
    nm laugh "Solo espero que sepas en qué te estás metiendo, jovencito." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7212
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9df2e79d:

    # ks confused "Hm? W-what do you mean?"
    ks confused "¿Mm? ¿Qu-qué quiere decir?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7214
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1008af28:

    # "Just then, Nozomi's mother shoots me a somewhat curious expression." with dissolve
    "En ese momento, la madre de Nozomi me muestra una expresión un tanto curiosa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7215
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0a622393:

    # nm happy "Oh, nothing~ Anyway, I should let you get to it; you didn't come here to listen to some old lady natter." with dissolve
    nm happy "Oh, nada. En fin, ya no te entretengo; no viniste aquí para escuchar el parloteo de esta doña." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7216
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d9ce2e2e:

    # "It's not on her face for long before the smiles are back. But I bet she knows Sayori's study habits as much as anyone in my class."
    "No dura mucho tiempo en su rostro antes de regresar a su sonrisa. Pero apuesto a que conoce los hábitos de estudio de Sayori tanto como cualquiera en mi clase."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7217
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2a027d6d:

    # nm smile "So go right on upstairs. Nozomi's room is the second on the left." with dissolve
    nm smile "Así que sube las escaleras. La habitación de Nozomi es la segunda a la izquierda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7218
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_301ea576:

    # ks smile "Ah, okay. Thanks."
    ks smile "Ah, muy bien. Gracias."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7219
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6e29f7ab:

    # "Even she must think Sayori needs to let her hair down once in a while..."
    "Hasta ella debe pensar que Sayori tiene que relajarse de vez en cuando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7225
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a58e8639:

    # "Anyway, I head up the stairs and... okay, second on the left she said."
    "Como sea, subo las escaleras y... muy bien, dijo que la segunda a la izquierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7228
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5911ccec:

    # "Let's do this..."
    "Hagamos esto..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7229
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ee831f0d:

    # n "Um, come on in!"
    n "Em, ¡pasa!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7233
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_14e9efd2:

    # "I open the door to find myself in a spacious-looking bedroom."
    "Abro la puerta para encontrarme una habitación espaciosa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7235
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d101b364:

    # "It's a little disorganized, with some board game boxes stashed in a corner and some open textbooks laid out on the floor."
    "Está un poco desordenada, con cajas de juegos de mesa apiladas en la esquina y libros de texto abiertos en el suelo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7236
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d01418e6:

    # "Presumably those books are only there to support the lie that we're here to study for school. I doubt we're going to be doing any of that today."
    "Supongo que esos libros solo están ahí para sostener la mentira de que vinimos a estudiar. Dudo que hagamos nada de eso hoy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7238
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0837e7f2:

    # n "Hello, Kyou. Close the door behind you, please." with dissolve
    n "Hola, Kyou. Por favor, cierra la puerta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7239
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_00427fb7:

    # "Right. I'm just distracting myself here. I've got some convincing to do."
    "Claro. Solo me estoy distrayendo. Vine aquí para hablar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7240
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2c433f6f:

    # ks casual neutral "Uh, yeah. Hey, guys."
    ks casual neutral "Eh, sí. Hola, chicas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7244
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_733f1f26:

    # "As I hastily pull the door closed I notice Sayori, who... well, she's still not looking great I gotta say." with dissolve
    "Cerrando apresuradamente la puerta, noto a Sayori, quien... bueno, sigue sin verse muy bien, he de decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7245
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9175b8e7:

    # n sigh "Yeah... hi." with dissolve
    n sigh "Sí... hola." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7246
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_872bb82f:

    # "I guess this is what Mrs. Akemi was getting at just now."
    "Supongo que de esto hablaba la Sra. Akemi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7247
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a3dbc301:

    # ks neutral "S-so... uhh..."
    ks neutral "P-pues... eeh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7249
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a2d19c6f:

    # "But, man, where to begin. I want to talk to Sayori, but she's still not even looking at me." with dissolve
    "Pero, cielos, ¿por dónde empezar? Quiero hablar con Sayori, pero sigue sin siquiera mirarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7251
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_992ea18e:

    # n side frown "Okay, Kyou... I think you need to start by apologizing." with dissolve
    n side frown "Bien, Kyou... creo de debes empezar por disculparte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7252
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_95a959ac:

    # "Nozomi on the other hand is staring daggers right into my very soul."
    "Nozomi, por otro lado, me clava la mirada como dagas en mi alma."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7253
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8e0cd159:

    # ks confused "A... apologizing?"
    ks confused "¿Di-... disculparme?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7255
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_92df5dda:

    # n irritated "I mean, what the hell where you thinking the other night?" with dissolve
    n irritated "Digo, ¿qué diablos estabas pensando la otra noche?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7256
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bb89234f:

    # n front2 frown "Sayori told me you hypnotized her into thinking she had a... a personality switch? Do you have any idea how dangerous that is?" with dissolve
    n front2 frown "Sayori me contó que la hipnotizaste y la hiciste creer que tenía una... ¿una personalidad alterna? ¿Tienes idea de lo peligroso que es eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7257
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_50f90fce:

    # n irritated "And what's more you just LEFT her like that?" with dissolve
    n irritated "Y, lo que es más, ¿la DEJASTE así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7258
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9d2666fc:

    # "Yeah Nozomi, you're not wrong but goddamn, I don't need you to tell me how I fucked up."
    "Sí, Nozomi, no te equivocas, pero maldita sea, no necesito que me digas cuánto la cagué."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7259
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cb28cfd9:

    # ks frown "Look, I KNOW, okay? But how was I supposed to know she'd react like this?"
    ks frown "Mira, ya lo SÉ, ¿de acuerdo? Pero ¿cómo iba a saber yo que reaccionaría así?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7260
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_872fc849:

    # n side frown "You don't. You don't know how anyone will take a hypnotic suggestion which is why you always need to be careful." with dissolve
    n side frown "No lo sabías. No sabes cómo reaccionará nadie a una sugestión hipnótica y por eso siempre debes ser cuidadoso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7261
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_aa9bc811:

    # n frown_side "The most important thing for any hypnotist is to ensure the comfort and safety of their hypnotee." with dissolve
    n frown_side "Lo más importante para cualquier hipnotista es procurar el confort y la seguridad del hipnotizado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7262
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_991efc3d:

    # n frown "Did you know that, Mr. Does-Hypnosis-For-A-Hobby?" with dissolve
    n frown "¿Sabías eso, Sr. Hago-Hipnosis-Como-Pasatiempo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7263
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9a273996:

    # ks "Ugh..."
    ks "Ay..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7264
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0aa3e4e5:

    # n irritated "God. This stuff isn't just a party trick to impress people. It can leave lasting consequences. It can effect people in very real and powerful ways." with dissolve
    n irritated "Dios. Esto no es un simple truco para impresionar gente. Puede dejar consecuencias duraderas. Puede afectar a la gente de formas reales y muy fuertes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7265
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b8cfac25:

    # n frown "You remember Satoshi? That guy who hypnotized me at the culture fest last year? He understood that. He made sure we were all okay at the end of his show." with dissolve
    n frown "¿Te acuerdas de Satoshi? ¿El chico que me hipnotizó en el festival cultural el año pasado? Él entendía eso. Se aseguró de que todos estuviéramos bien al final de su acto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7266
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f12d3258:

    # n front2 "Every hypnotist, whether an amateur or an experienced professional should understand that." with dissolve
    n front2 "Todo hipnotista, así sea amateur o un profesional experimentado, debería entender eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7277
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_58e394e4:

    # n determined "And you had BETTER understand that now!" with dissolve
    n determined "¡Y más te VALE que lo entiendas ahora!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7278
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5d74cec9:

    # ks "{cps=15}Nozomi- {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=15}Nozomi- {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7279
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_15024ee8:

    # n angry "{cps=20}So the least you can do is get on your hands and knees and give her a {/cps}{nw}" with dissolve
    n angry "{cps=20}Así que lo menos que puedes hacer es ponerte sobre tus manos y rodillas y darle una {/cps}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7280
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_47dc6468:

    # extend "FUCKING apology for what you put her through, do you hear me?" with vpunch
    extend "PUTA disculpa por lo que la hiciste pasar, ¿me escuchaste?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7281
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9cd2e668:

    # "I can feel my body tense up and... Christ, I had no idea she could even get this pissed."
    "Puedo sentir mi cuerpo tensarse y... Dios, no tenía idea de que ella pudiera enojarse tanto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7283
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4622faca:

    # "My mouth hangs open as my mind races. I want to defend myself. Tell her she's blowing things out of proportion; that nothing I did deserves her raging at me like this." with dissolve
    "Me quedo boquiabierto y mi mente se acelera. Quiero defenderme. Decirle que está sacando las cosas de proporción; que nada de lo que hice merece esta ira." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7286
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6803fcf5:

    # "... But I almost feel drawn out of my own body as instead I find myself turning to Sayori and bowing my head." with dissolve
    "... Pero casi me siento fuera de mi propio cuerpo, volteando en dirección a Sayori e inclinando la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7291
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bb5abd4a:

    # ks sad "Look, Sayori I... I'm really sorry about all this." with dissolve
    ks sad "Mira, Sayori yo... realmente lamento todo esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7293
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a20643e9:

    # "And the words just fall out of my mouth."
    "Y las palabras simplemente salen de mi boca."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7294
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_65fb24cc:

    # ks "I just got excited for what we were doing and... a-and yeah, I got in over my head. It was pretty reckless."
    ks "Me emocioné por lo que estábamos haciendo y... y-y sí, no pensé claramente. Fue muy irresponsable."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7295
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7778e0d8:

    # ks "But I want to do right by you. I know you're afraid of me, but you have to believe I never meant to hurt you. I want to fix this."
    ks "Pero quiero hacer las cosas bien. Sé que me tienes miedo, pero tienes que creerme cuando digo que no era mi intención hacerte daño. Quiero arreglar esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7296
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f8a22e3f:

    # ks "S-so... will you forgive me?"
    ks "A-así que... ¿podrías perdonarme?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7297
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e1554201:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7298
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_692d3f98:

    # s casual_handup sleeptalk "Kyou... I..." with dissolve
    s casual_handup sleeptalk "Kyou... yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7299
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_eff0b843:

    # "I begin to raise my head once more, and my spine tenses as Sayori finally begins speaking to me."
    "Comienzo a alzar la cabeza, y siento tensión en la columna cuando Sayori finalmente empieza a hablarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7300
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e154191f:

    # s concerned_right "I do fear you, it is true." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Sí te tengo miedo, eso es verdad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7301
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_51691b30:

    # s concerned "Ever since my first hypnosis session I have been left with an unsettling feeling that something was not right. That my own mind was being influenced in ways I could not fathom." with dissolve
    s concerned "Desde mi primera sesión de hipnosis, he tenido la inquietante sensación de que algo no anda bien, y mi mente era influenciada de formas fuera de mi comprensión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7302
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ace6d508:

    # s neutral_right "At first it was enough to put such anxieties down to my own lack of knowledge in the matter, especially after the explanations you offered me." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Al principio bastaba atribuir tales ansiedades a mi propia falta de conocimiento sobre el tema, especialmente después de la explicación que me ofreciste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7303
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0e28972d:

    # s sleep "My intense experience could simply be put down to my high aptitude as a hypnotic subject. No more, no less." with dissolve
    s sleep "Mi intensa experiencia podía simplemente ser el resultado de mi alta aptitud como sujeto hipnótico. Ni más, ni menos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7304
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9bb771c5:

    # s neutral_right "But that changed with my second session with you. When that session ended not in your home, but in our classroom a full day later." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Pero eso cambió con mi segunda sesión contigo. Cuando dicha sesión concluyó no en tu morada, sino en nuestro salón un día entero después." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7305
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6f71ff69:

    # s casual surprised_right "If you can truly exert such a level of control over my thoughts and actions that I can in essence be two completely separate people with compartmentalized memories?" with dissolve
    s casual surprised_right "Si puedes ejercer tal control sobre mis pensamientos y acciones que puedo, en esencia, ser dos personas diferentes con memorias compartimentadas..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7306
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_23a0f08d:

    # s concerned_right "I cannot begin to describe how terrifying that is to me." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Ni siquiera puedo comenzar a describir el terror que eso me infunde." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7308
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a6877ad1:

    # ks "Sayori..."
    ks "Sayori..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7309
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d69a3057:

    # s casual_folded sleeptalk "But at the same time, I can accept that you truly meant me no harm. That your recklessness was borne of academic curiosity and ego as opposed to outright malice." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleeptalk "Pero a la misma vez, puedo aceptar que no tuviste la intención de dañar. Que tu negligencia fue fruto de la curiosidad académica y el ego, en lugar de malicia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7310
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_19477302:

    # s smile_right "So... I accept your apology. And I hope we can work ourselves to a resolution." with dissolve
    s smile_right "Y por lo tanto... acepto tu disculpa. Y espero que logremos encontrar una resolución." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7312
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_85172105:

    # "I feel a little wave of relief wash over me as I smile at her."
    "Siento una pequeña ola de alivio pasar sobre mí, y le sonrío."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7313
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f3651c1c:

    # ks smile "Yeah. Me too, Sayori."
    ks smile "Sí. Yo también, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7315
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_de9df2ec:

    # s casual_handup smile "So with all that said, perhaps it is time we got down to business?" with dissolve
    s casual_handup smile "Así que, dicho todo eso, ¿tal vez sea hora de lidiar con el tema en cuestión?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7316
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0b318dad:

    # n frown "Not until he gets on his hands and knees!" with dissolve
    n frown "¡No hasta verlo de manos y rodillas!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7317
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_090a334c:

    # ks sigh "Oh, come on!"
    ks sigh "¡Oh, vamos!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7318
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9774cbdb:

    # s casual happy "Mhmhmhmhmh~" with dissolve
    s casual happy "Jijijijiji." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7319
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bd9c6ad8:

    # "And man, if she's laughing again I know things are going to be alright."
    "Y cielos, si está riendo otra vez, sé que las cosas estarán bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7321
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_499ab339:

    # s smirk "I think we can overlook that little indiscrection, Nozomi. You can stand down now." with dissolve
    s smirk "Creo que podemos pasar por alto esa pequeña indiscreción, Nozomi. Ya puedes relajarte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7322
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9ea5f17b:

    # n pout "Hmpth, if you say so. But I'm not letting him off the hook just yet." with dissolve
    n pout "Bah, si tú lo dices. Pero no se saldrá de esta tan fácilmente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7325
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a08bf142:

    # "Just then, Sayori smiles as she places a hand gently on Nozomi's shoulder." with dissolve
    "En ese momento, Sayori sonríe y coloca una mano gentilmente en el hombro de Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7326
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_723a430c:

    # s "Thank you. I appreciate everything you are doing for me."
    s "Gracias. Aprecio todo lo que estás haciendo por mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7327
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_dfa9fb29:

    # n neutral_side "Hm? O-Oh, it's nothing. Really." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "¿Mm? O-oh, no es nada. De veras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7328
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3404cecb:

    # s neutral "You can hardly call organizing this little get-together in your own home nothing. Not to mention your perspective on my predicament has been invaluable." with dissolve
    s neutral "Yo no diría que organizar esta reunión en tu casa no es nada. Sin mencionar que tu perspectiva ante mi predicamento ha sido invaluable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7329
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b5d192de:

    # s sleep "I was at a complete loss, but with your help I am actually beginning to feel optimistic about reaching a satisfactory conclusion to this mess." with dissolve
    s sleep "Estaba completamente perdida, pero con tu ayuda, empiezo a sentirme optimista respecto a llevar este desastre a una satisfactoria conclusión." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7330
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_09e6fa01:

    # s smile "So thank you. Truly." with dissolve
    s smile "Así que gracias. En verdad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7331
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bbd87dfd:

    # "Yeah... I can really feel the tension start to diffuse from the room."
    "Sí... Puedo sentir la tensión menguarse en la habitación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7332
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_432b0d64:

    # n happy blush "Aw... honestly, I'm really glad you wanted my help. It's nice being able to do something for you for a change." with dissolve
    n happy blush "Ay... honestamente, me alegra mucho que quisieras mi ayuda. Es lindo poder yo hacer algo por ti para variar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7333
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d9fd4238:

    # "Everything's going to be fine. I KNOW I can fix this."
    "Todo estará bien. SÉ que puedo arreglar esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7334
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1f46a11c:

    # n smile_side "So... a-anyway, let's talk about why we're here, okay?" with dissolve
    n smile_side "Bien... e-en fin, hablemos de por qué estamos aquí, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7336
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_af58ea50:

    # s smile_right "Yes. Let's." with dissolve
    s smile_right "Sí. Hagamos eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7340
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4c9d675b:

    # "They then turn to me, and I can see in their expressions that it's finally time for us all to talk about this like adults." with dissolve
    "Luego voltean hacia mí, y puedo ver por su expresión que al fin es tiempo de hablar de esto como adultos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7341
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_befbe572:

    # n front2 neutral "Alright, so Sayori filled me in about what's been happening to her, and it definitely sounds like she's in the upper category of extremely hypnotizeable people." with dissolve
    n front2 neutral "Muy bien, pues Sayori me puso al tanto sobre lo que le ha estado pasando, y definitivamente suena a que está en la más alta categoría de gente extremadamente hipnotizable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7342
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a99942b2:

    # n surprised "But even so, it's pretty wild that you managed to effect her so completely with just two short hypnosis sessions!" with dissolve
    n surprised "Pero, aun así, ¡es una locura que lograras afectarla tanto con solo dos sesiones cortas de hipnosis!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7343
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d1f30e87:

    # n sigh "I don't think I'd have believed it if it was anyone other than Sayori telling me that." with dissolve
    n sigh "No creo haberlo creído si no hubiera sido Sayori quien me lo contó." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7415
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6c922f01:

    # "Still, there's something that bothers me about what they're saying."
    "Aun así, hay algo que me molesta sobre lo que han estado diciendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7346
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e7d96b65:

    # s casual_folded sleep "And I would have shared your skepticism. But I am certain that Kyou's hypnosis is effecting me in a way that appears no different from literal mind control, insane as that sounds." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep "Y yo habría compartido tu escepticismo." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep "Pero tengo certeza de que la hipnosis de Kyou me está afectando de forma que no parece distinta a control mental literal, por disparatado que suene." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7347
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e9829884:

    # ks confused "Are you really so sure you can't resist those hypnotic suggestions, Sayori?"
    ks confused "¿Estás tan segura de que no puedes resistir esas sugestiones hipnóticas, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7349
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b6efe1c0:

    # s neutral_right "Do you have any reason to doubt me?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "¿Tienes alguna razón para dudar de mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7350
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_34c644cb:

    # ks "Well I mean..."
    ks "Bueno, pues..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7351
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e10212fe:

    # "I gesture to Sayori's face, as sunken as it is."
    "Señalo con un gesto el fatigado rostro de Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7352
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_78aa08bc:

    # ks "Sure looks to me like you haven't been sleeping right."
    ks "Parece que no has estado durmiendo muy bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7353
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7e9fed05:

    # ks "You're both focused on the personality switch, but if you're not sleeping again then doesn't that mean you've been ignoring the first suggestion I made to you?"
    ks "Se están enfocando en el cambio de personalidad, pero si otra vez no estás durmiendo, ¿qué no significa que has estado ignorando la primera sugestión que te hice?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7355
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f205a84a:

    # "To that, Sayori simply shakes her head." with dissolve
    "Ante eso, Sayori simplemente sacude la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7356
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_41ba2443:

    # s neutral_right "I am afraid not. The contradiction you cite is trivially explained." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Me temo que no. La explicación a la contradicción que señalas es trivial." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7358
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_05e70076:

    # s casual "The hypnotic complusion you placed to empty my mind and fall asleep was predicated on the assumption that I would choose to go to bed." with dissolve
    s casual "El impulso hipnótico que implantaste de vaciar mi mente y caer dormida fue predicado bajo la suposición de que elegiría irme a la cama." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7359
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fbc32f7c:

    # s concerned_right "But since I awoke in our classroom the other day I remained awake deep into the night while I attempted to research my condition." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Pero desde que desperté en nuestro salón el otro día, permanecí despierta hasta tarde en la noche en mis intentos de investigar mi condición." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7360
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4f9d990c:

    # s sleeptalk "Turning in for the night was the last thing on my mind." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Una noche de descanso era lo último en mi mente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7361
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cc74a9fe:

    # n side sad_closed "Oh gosh, please don't tell me you haven't slept in two days, Sayori." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Oh, cielos, por favor no me digas que no has dormido en dos días." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7362
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_679963db:

    # s casual_handup concerned "I will not. Eventually even I had to admit defeat." with dissolve
    s casual_handup concerned "Descuida. Eventualmente incluso yo tuve que admitir la derrota." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7364
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8189aa04:

    # s concerned_right "And when I finally settled into bed, my eyes immediately fell closed and all the worries of the night vanished without trace." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Y cuando finalmente me posé sobre mi cama, mis ojos se cerraron inmediatamente y todas las preocupaciones de la noche se desvanecieron sin dejar rastro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7365
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_48c779b3:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "Were it not for the fact I had set an alarm to wake me in time for school the next morning I would have surely suffered a repeat of my earlier truancy." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "De no haber sido porque dejé una alarma para despertarme a tiempo para la escuela a la mañana siguiente, seguramente habría repetido mi ausentismo anterior." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7366
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fd927833:

    # s concerned_right "So you see, Kyou, your hypnotic suggestions are both working exactly as you instructed." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Así que, como vez, Kyou, ambas sugestiones hipnóticas están funcionando exactamente como instruiste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7367
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3db45fd0:

    # s casual_folded sleep "If any of us were hoping my adverse reaction to your mental meddling would put a stop to these compulsions it is sadly misplaced." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep "Si alguno de nosotros esperaba que mi reacción adversa a tu intromisión mental pondría alto a estos impulsos, tristemente no fue así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7368
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_de40c04e:

    # ks neutral "I... I see."
    ks neutral "Ya... ya veo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7369
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_517a50a7:

    # "Well, I guess I can't be surprised that Sayori found an extremely... Sayori way of shooting down my theory."
    "Bueno, supongo que no debe sorprenderme que Sayori encontrara una forma tan... Sayori de refutar mi teoría."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7370
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cf8b309d:

    # s neutral "I get the impression that the two of you are still not fully comprehending the effects upon my mind, even if you do believe me." with dissolve
    s neutral "Tengo la impresión de que aún no comprenden completamente los efectos sobre mi mente, incluso si me creen." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7371
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_569d1042:

    # n neutral_side "Yeah, it's... it's a little hard to wrap my head around it to be honest." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Sí, es... es un poco difícil de entender, si soy honesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7372
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3ddb6e29:

    # "Sayori nods slowly... then starts to look at me with purpose."
    "Sayori asiente lentamente... luego mira hacia mí con propósito."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7373
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4304787f:

    # s frown_right "... I believe a demonstration is in order." with dissolve
    s frown_right "... Considero que una demostración sería apropiada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7375
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_720ec734:

    # ks confused "Huh?" with dissolve
    ks confused "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7376
