    ks neutral "[alt_name]... conviértete en Sayori otra vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8212
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ddf3d138:

    # s casual surprised_right "I need to... huh?" with dissolve
    s casual surprised_right "¿Que me... eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8213
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_97f81603:

    # "The pair of us watch cautiously as \"[alt_name]\" seems to space out, her eyes looking to refocus in a manner that makes her look absolutely befuddled."
    "Ambos observamos con cuidado cómo \"[alt_name]\" parece aturdirse por un momento y sus ojos buscan reenfocarse de tal forma que luce absolutamente desconcertada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8214
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_20c18449:

    # n "Please tell me you're back to normal, [alt_name]."
    n "Por favor dime que ya volviste a la normalidad, [alt_name]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8215
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_81fac232:

    # s surprised "I... \"[alt_name]\"?" with dissolve
    s surprised "Vol-... ¿\"[alt_name]\"?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8216
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d384be2b:

    # n irritated "Ugh, I mean..." with dissolve
    n irritated "Ayy, digo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8218
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_007c7e3b:

    # s casual_handup "Nozomi? What..." with dissolve
    s casual_handup "¿Nozomi? ¿Qué...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8220
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ed827381:

    # s panicked "Haaah, wh-what, where am I? This is..." with dissolve
    s panicked "Aaah, ¿qu-que, dónde estoy? ¿Este es...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8227
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ed24a5f4:

    # "We can both see the panic in her eyes now, and Nozomi throws her arms around her in a frantic bid to calm her friend." with dissolve
    "Ambos podemos ver el pánico en sus ojos, y Nozomi la toma en sus brazos en un frenético intento por calmar a su amiga." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8228
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b45e89e0:

    # n "S-Sayori no, it's okay! Please don't freak out!"
    n "¡S-Sayori, no, todo está bien! ¡Por favor, no te asustes!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8229
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c79e47d5:

    # s casual sleepy "But... what am I doing here? I don't..." with dissolve
    s casual sleepy "Pero... ¿qué estoy haciendo aquí? No sé..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8230
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2c062696:

    # n sad_side "We messed up and I'm sorry, but you're safe now." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Metimos la pata y lo siento, pero ya estás a salvo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8231
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1ca3fe74:

    # ks sigh "We'll explain everything..."
    ks sigh "Te explicaremos todo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8233
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9e656e06:

    # "Sayori didn't make too much of a scene this time, thanks to Nozomi reassuring her."
    "Sayori no hizo una escena tan grande esta vez, gracias a que Nozomi estaba para reconfortarla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8234
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_adeaaa15:

    # "Either that or she's starting to get used to waking up like this..."
    "Eso o empieza a acostumbrarse a despertar así..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8235
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2d126214:

    # "Anyway, Nozomi and I started to explain everything that happened since the moment I triggered her in Nozomi's room."
    "Como sea, Nozomi y yo nos pusimos a explicar todo lo que pasó desde el momento en que dije el ancla en la habitación de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8242
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7bc931a9:

    # "She starts to frown at us as she continues to listen. A frown that only seems to deepen the more we tell her."
    "Ella empieza a fruncir el ceño mientras nos escucha. Y ese ceño solo se frunce más y más entre más contamos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8243
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3bd12cb4:

    # "Man, I still can't imagine how much of a headscrew this has got to be for her."
    "Caray, aún no me puedo ni imaginar lo desorientador que esto debe ser para ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8276
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_53af9813:

    # n "... And er, that's when Kyou said \"become Sayori\" to finally bring you back."
    n "... Y em, entonces Kyou dijo \"conviértete en Sayori\" para finalmente traerte de vuelta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8246
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e1554201_1:

    # s "..."
    s "..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8247
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_65f1deb9:

    # n sad_closed "Ahhh... p-please stop looking at us like that." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Aaah... p-por favor, deja de mirarnos así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8248
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ca74b182:

    # s casual_folded irritated "..." with dissolve
    s casual_folded irritated "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8249
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_32e7361d:

    # n front sigh "I... l-look, I told Kyou to change you back right after we confirmed what you wanted. He's the reason things got out of hand like this." with dissolve
    n front sigh "Eh... m-mira, yo le dije a Kyou que te devolviera a la normalidad justo después de confirmar lo que querías. Él es la razón por la que todo se salió de control." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8250
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3aac2566:

    # "Ugh, really Nozomi? You're trying to pin this all on me so you don't look bad in front of Sayori? I thought you were better than that."
    "Aj, ¿en serio, Nozomi? ¿Me vas a echar toda la culpa a mí para no verte mal delante de Sayori? Creí que eras mejor que esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8251
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e630f192:

    # ks casual sigh "Hey, I was going to until your mom walked in. I was trying not to make a scene!"
    ks casual sigh "Oye, iba a hacerlo hasta que tu mamá entró. ¡Intentaba no hacer una escena!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8252
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_50293125:

    # n front2 frown "Yes, great job, Kyou. Sayori lied to her dad and led us on a wild goose chase thanks to you, how's that for not making a scene?" with dissolve
    n front2 frown "Sí, gran trabajo, Kyou. Sayori le mintió a su papá y nos llevó a una alocada cacería gracias a ti. ¿Una escena? ¡No, qué va!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8253
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d48f35f2:

    # ks frown "I don't know, Nozomi, maybe if you hadn't yelled at me your mom wouldn't have come to check on us in the first place."
    ks frown "No lo sé, Nozomi, tal vez si no me hubieras gritado, tu mamá no habría venido a revisarnos en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8254
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b7cc3d91:

    # n determined "Ooh, don't you turn it around on me. We're only in this mess because you were too much of a coward to just say the thing." with dissolve
    n determined "Uh, no trates de darle la vuelta a esto. Solo estamos en este desastre porque fuiste demasiado cobarde para decir la frase." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8255
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_389f85db:

    # ks angry "I was thinking about Sayori the whole time! But what about you? You wanted her to have a freakout in front of your mom? You think that would've been good for her?"
    ks angry "¡Estuve pensando en Sayori todo el tiempo! Pero ¿y tú qué? ¿Querías que entrara en pánico delante de tu mamá? ¿Crees que eso habría sido bueno para ella?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8256
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_40ca1763:

    # n angry "Bullcrap! You were the one who said we could keep this whole thing a secret from Sayori the minute things turned sour! You weren't thinking about her well-being at all!" with dissolve
    n angry "¡No digas estupideces! ¡Tú fuiste el que dijo que no le contaríamos nada a Sayori desde el primer instante que las cosas salieron mal!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8257
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a2b3d204:

    # s frown_right "Enough." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Suficiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8259
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4492531e:

    # "Oh. Right, I guess I got a little carried away in the moment. But one word from Sayori is enough to silence us both." with dissolve
    "Oh. Cierto. Supongo que me dejé llevar por el momento. Pero una sola palabra de Sayori es basta para silenciarnos a ambos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8260
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6d020993:

    # s casual irritated "Now... I am still trying to process all of this, and I admit that I am feeling a certain amount of resentment towards the pair of you at this moment." with dissolve
    s casual irritated "Bien... aún intento procesar todo esto, y admito que siento cierta cantidad de resentimiento hacia ambos en este momento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8261
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cfbca9be:

    # s sleeptalk "But perhaps I share some responsibility in thinking we could run a controlled experiment such as this without consequence." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Pero quizá yo comparto algo de la responsabilidad por pensar que podríamos hacer un experimento controlado como este sin consecuencias." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8262
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_befbf5d6:

    # n side sad_side "Sayori..." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Sayori..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8263
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8b6d50c4:

    # s casual_handup concerned_right "I see no value in pointing fingers. What's done is done. And besides, as humiliating as this experience has been, we..." with dissolve
    s casual_handup concerned_right "No veo objeto en señalar culpables. Lo hecho hecho está. Y además, por humillante que haya sido esta experiencia, hemos..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8264
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7e10fcb8:

    # s concerned "Well, we have proven everything I set out to prove with this little exercise, have we not?" with dissolve
    s concerned "Bueno, hemos probado todo lo que buscaba probar con esta pequeña vivencia, ¿no les parece?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8265
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_92ef3f34:

    # "I can only nod glumly in agreement."
    "No puedo más que asentir cabizbajo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8266
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b2dc532c:

    # ks sad "Yeah. From the second I told you to swap personalities you really couldn't help yourself. It was just like before."
    ks sad "Sí. Desde el instante en que te dije que cambiaras de personalidad no pudiste hacer nada para evitarlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8269
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_09d97542:

    # ks "A person acting out a hypnotic suggestion should always be able to break out of it if they really didn't want to do it. If it was causing them pain in some way." with dissolve
    ks "Una persona siguiendo una sugestión hipnótica debería siempre ser capaz de librarse de ella si no quiere seguirla. Si la hace sufrir de alguna manera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8270
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bfeb9548:

    # ks "But it's like a switch flips in your brain and suddenly you really are like two different people with your own priorities and even your own separate memories."
    ks "Pero es como si un interruptor se moviera en tu cabeza y de repente fueras dos personas diferentes con sus propias prioridades e incluso memorias separadas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8271
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_42cf1819:

    # n sad_side "It doesn't matter if you're extremely hypnotizeable, there's no way this should be happening to you, Sayori. I really don't understand it at all." with dissolve
    n sad_side "No importa si eres extremadamente hipnotizable, esto no debería estarte pasando, Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8272
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ce27889c:

    # n sad_closed "It's like something out of a thriller novel, but there's no denying what happened. I can hardly imagine how scary this all is for you." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Es como algo salido de una novela de suspenso, pero es innegable lo que ocurrió. No puedo ni imaginar lo aterrador que esto debe ser para ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8273
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_11c62b93:

    # "Sayori sighs wearily as she runs a hand through her hair."
    "Sayori suelta un desgastado suspiro, pasando una mano por su cabello."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8274
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bf7bd910:

    # s casual sleeptalk "Indeed. Now I believe you truly understand the situation I am faced with, and why it needs to stop today." with dissolve
    s casual sleeptalk "Efectivamente. Ahora me parece que en verdad entienden la situación que estoy enfrentando, y por qué debe parar hoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8275
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_73aaf40b:

    # s sleep "I am exhausted mentally. Physically. My head feels as if it is being pulled in two different directions and I am just barely holding everything together." with dissolve
    s sleep "Estoy exhausta, mental y físicamente. Siento que mi ser ha estado siendo jalado en dos direcciones distintas y apenas puedo mantenerme íntegra." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8276
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_54885110:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "I... I cannot continue to live like this." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "No... no puedo continuar viviendo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8277
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a78a10af_1:

    # n sad_side "Yeah..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8279
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d9bb93cc:

    # "The three of us just stand there for a moment, sharing awkward looks amidst the bright lights and frivolous sounds from all around us." with dissolve
    "Los tres simplemente nos quedamos aquí parados por un momento, intercambiando miradas incómodas entre las luces brillantes y frívolos sonidos a nuestro alrededor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8280
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_08666e85:

    # "It's like this whole arcade is trying to drive our gloom out of here, and it can hardly be doing Sayori's state of mind much good."
    "Es como si todo el arcade intentara llevarse nuestra melancolía, y dudo que le esté haciendo bien al estado mental de Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8281
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bed653ed:

    # "I mean, there could hardly be a less appropriate place for this kind of situation."
    "Digo, no puedo pensar en un lugar menos apropiado para esta clase de situación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8282
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7cbaba51:

    # n smile_side "Hey, Sayori? Let's head home." with dissolve
    n smile_side "¿Ey, Sayori? Vámonos a casa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8283
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_41bdf1b3:

    # s concerned "Hm?" with dissolve
    s concerned "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8284
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9f59fd76:

    # n happy "Yeah. Let's get you away from all of this and we'll figure out how to get you back to normal together, okay?" with dissolve
    n happy "Sí. Hay que alejarte de todo esto y buscaremos la forma de arreglarte juntos, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8285
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2522b8bb:

    # s casual_folded "Well. Actually..." with dissolve
    s casual_folded "Bueno. De hecho..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8287
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_10779fee:

    # "Just then, Sayori turns herself towards the fighting game cabinet that \"[alt_name]\" was playing on when we found her." with dissolve
    "En ese momento, Sayori volta a ver la cabina del juego de pelea en el que \"[alt_name]\" estaba jugando cuando la encontramos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8288
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0549ed20:

    # s neutral "It is just that I am starting to find this environment comforting. Nostalgic, even." with dissolve
    s neutral "Es solo que este ambiente empieza a resultarme reconfortante. Nostálgico, incluso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8289
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_612ef5f8:

    # n surprised_side "Huh?" with dissolve
    n surprised_side "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8321
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4967c731:

    # "Her hand wanders over the surface of the cabinet, rubbing her fingers across the buttons as she gazes at its screen."
    "Su mano se desliza lentamente por la cabina, frotando los botones con sus dedos mientras mira la pantalla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8291
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4ba1e4d2:

    # s "So I was wondering..."
    s "Me estaba preguntando..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8292
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_efcb89e0:

    # s concerned_right "... Do either of you play?" with dissolve
    s concerned_right "... ¿Alguno de ustedes quiere jugar?" with dissolve
