# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8283
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1542c3f2:

    # n front2 frown "Yes, great job, Kyou. Sayori led us on a wild goose chase thanks to you, how's that for not making a scene?" with dissolve
    n front2 frown "Sí, gran trabajo, Kyou. Sayori nos llevó a una alocada cacería gracias a ti. ¿Una escena? ¡No, qué va!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8306
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cc7fb299:

    # s sleep "I am exhausted mentally. Physically. My head feels as if it is being pulled in two entirely different directions and I am just barely holding everything together." with dissolve
    s sleep "Estoy exhausta, mental y físicamente. Siento que mi cabeza ha estado siendo jalada en dos direcciones distintas y apenas puedo mantenerme íntegra." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8433
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_84e67410:

    # k "Oh, come on!"
    k "¡Oh, vamos!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8332
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b664720d:

    # "I smack the control stick in frustration as the fighting game cabinet shouts \"K.O.\" at me, as if to mock me personally."
    "Azoto la palanca de los controles con frustración, escuchando la cabina gritar \"K.O.\" como si se burlara personalmente de mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8334
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6e4129e6:

    # s smirk_right "Heh. I was under the impression that you were good at this sort of game, Kyou? Was I mistaken?" with dissolve
    s smirk_right "Je. Yo me imaginaba que eras bueno en esta clase de juegos, Kyou. ¿Mi suposición fue errónea?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8335
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_92feccc6:

    # "After that last round I'm feeling a little of what that other guy must have felt playing \"[alt_name]\" when we found her."
    "Tras ese último round, estoy sintiendo un poco de lo que aquel sujeto debió sentir jugando contra \"[alt_name]\" cuando la encontramos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8439
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c06a5fde:

    # k "Yeah well, I'm out of practice and I don't play this series so whatever." with dissolve
    k "Sí, bueno, estoy fuera de práctica, y yo no juego esta serie. ¿Qué más da?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8338
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2125f71b:

    # "Sayori simply chuckles as she taps her finger against the coin slot of the machine." with dissolve
    "Sayori simplemente se ríe, golpeteando con el dedo la ranura para monedas de la máquina." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8339
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_72212db2:

