translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_15aba208:

    # ks "I figured it'd help people fixate on the light so they'd find it easier to stay focused while I was talking them into trance."
    ks "Me imaginé que ayudaría a las personas a enfocarse en la luz para concentrarse más fácilmente mientras las guío al trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8521
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3c143b49:

    # s sleeptalk "Yes. And from my own experience of being under that light I can only conclude that your modifications are having the effect you intended." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Sí. Y por mi experiencia siendo sometida a esa luz solo puedo concluir que tus modificaciones han tenido el efecto deseado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8522
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_72f4e16f:

    # s neutral_right "You have mentioned before that I appeared to gasp in awe shortly after exposure. Its effect upon me was immediate and powerful." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Mencionaste anteriormente que emití un jadeo de asombro justo después de la exposición. Su efecto en mí fue inmediato y poderoso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8523
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_702f26fe:

    # s casual_handup irritated "So powerful in fact, that we cannot rule out the possibility that it effected large-scale changes in my brain chemistry." with dissolve
    s casual_handup irritated "Tan poderoso, de hecho, que no puedo descartar la posibilidad de que haya efectuado cambios a gran escala en mi química cerebral." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8524
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8905c648:

    # s frown_right "Changes that have had me acting on suggestions well beyond the bounds of what should be possible via hypnosis." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Cambios que me hicieron actuar conforme a sugestiones más allá de los límites de lo que debería ser posible mediante hipnosis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8525
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b96b5d8f:

    # n side sad_side "Sayori, you're... Are you saying what I think you're saying?" with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Sayori, estás... ¿estás diciendo lo que creo que estás diciendo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8526
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c2377a0d:

    # n sad "Kyou made a mind control device? But that's..." with dissolve
    n sad "¿Kyou creó un dispositivo de control mental? Pero eso es..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8527
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_875f3843:

    # "Sayori lets out a weary sigh. She knows how crazy she has to sound, but..."
    "Sayori deja salir un fatigado suspiro. Sabe lo loca que debe estar sonando, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8528
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9d664fb5:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "As I said, in the absence of any rational explanation we must entertain the impossible." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Como dije, en ausencia de cualquier explicación racional, debemos sospechar de lo imposible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8529
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_65d37e3d:

    # "Can I really... control minds? With my penlight?"
    "¿En serio puedo... controlar mentes? ¿Con mi linterna?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8530
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_66783d81:

    # s concerned_right "And if I am correct, then that penlight is both the cause of, and solution to my predicament." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Y si estoy en lo correcto, esa linterna es tanto la causa como la solución a mi predicamento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8531
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_702d3c0e:

    # "It's so fucking crazy to even think about, but I have to admit Sayori's starting to convince me."
    "Tan solo pensarlo parece una puta locura, pero debo admitir que Sayori empieza a convencerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8532
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_899498b1:

    # s casual "After all, if one can effect such drastic changes to a person's mind with that device alone, then it should be no trouble at all to use it to reverse those same changes." with dissolve
    s casual "Después de todo, si se pueden efectuar cambios tan drásticos en la mente de una persona solo con ese dispositivo, no debería ser un problema revertirlos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8533
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1e3ba5a3:

    # n neutral_side "So you're saying Kyou should hypnotize you with that penlight again? Only this time he lifts the suggestion that you have a split personality?" with dissolve
    n neutral_side "¿Estás diciendo que Kyou debería hipnotizarte con esa linterna otra vez? ¿Solo que esta vez elimine la sugestión de la personalidad doble?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8534
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_46c52cd7:

    # "I could really use this thing on Sayori, maybe anyone, and I could get them to do anything I wanted? Think anything I wanted?"
    "¿De verdad podría usar esta cosa en Sayori, tal vez en cualquiera, y lograr que haga lo que yo quiera? ¿Que pensara lo que yo quiera?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8535
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_721b4644:

    # s casual_folded sleep "Actually... what I am about to propose is something you could say is... a little reckless." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep "En realidad... lo que estaba por proponer es algo que se podría decir que es... un poco osado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8536
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5ab08757:

    # n sad_side "Reckless?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Osado?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8537
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0089636c:

    # "I'm not even sure how I feel about that."
    "Ni siquiera sé qué sentir al respecto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8538
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a733127d:

    # s concerned "Perhaps my alter ego is rubbing off on me more than I thought. Still, I believe it could resolve my predicament while simultaneously proving this ridiculous hypothesis of mine." with dissolve
    s concerned "Tal vez sea mi alter ego contagiándome su actitud un poco. Sin embargo, creo que podría resolver mi predicamento y simultáneamente probar mi ridícula hipótesis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8539
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_05e5ed49:

    # n neutral_side "So what are you thinking?" with dissolve
    n neutral_side "¿Y qué es eso que estás pensando?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8544
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bc9e8164:

    # "But before I can gather my thoughts I'm starting to wonder about that look Sayori's suddenly giving me." with dissolve
    "Pero antes de poder reflexionar, comienza a extrañarme esa mirada que Sayori me está poniendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8545
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_dc4b2569_4:

    # ks confused "What?"
    ks confused "¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8546
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7248e324:

    # s casual_handup "Kyou... how would you feel about me using the penlight on you?" with dissolve
    s casual_handup "Kyou... ¿qué opinas de la idea de que yo use la linterna en ti?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8548
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e55f794d:

    # ks surprised "WHAT?!" with vpunch
    ks surprised "¡¿QUÉ?!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8549
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c801e447:

    # "And now my head's all over the place. Did I just hear her right?"
    "Y ahora ni siquiera sé qué pensar. ¿Acaso la escuché bien?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8550
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0cbfc911:

    # n sad_side "You want to hypnotize Kyou with that penlight of his? After telling us how you think it's a mind control device?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Quieres hipnotizar a Kyou con su linterna? ¿Después de decirnos que crees que es un dispositivo de control mental?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8551
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c6b434b4:

    # s concerned "Correct." with dissolve
    s concerned "Correcto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8552
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6c354561:

    # "I just... what?"
    "Eh... ¿qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8553
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7b0fd45c:

    # ks frown "Seriously? No one in their right mind's going to be able to go into trance after hearing that kind of talk."
    ks frown "¿Sayori? Nadie en su sano juicio sería capaz de entrar en trance después de escucharte decir esas cosas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8554
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a4f7a80e:

    # n sad_closed "I have to agree. At least not in this sort of context." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "En eso concuerdo. Al menos no en este contexto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8555
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_89ef7e2b:

    # ks confused "Is there a GOOD context for this kind of talk?"
    ks confused "¿Existe algún BUEN contexto para decir esas cosas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8556
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e43e6bd9:

    # n sad blush "O-oh, um, well..." with dissolve
    n sad blush "O-oh, em, bueno..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8557
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f18d5d32:

    # n front sigh "L-look, that's not important. I'm agreeing with you, aren't I?" with dissolve
    n front sigh "M-mira, eso no es lo importante. Te estoy dando la razón, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8559
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1fcd3f15:

    # s casual_folded sleep "It is as impossible a proposition as could be." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep "Es una propuesta que no podría ser más imposible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8560
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f61dd61a:

    # s neutral_right "You would naturally have a high level of anxiety over falling into hypnosis. To say nothing of the fact that I have no practical experience with the subject." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Naturalmente sentirías una gran ansiedad respecto a caer en hipnosis. Sin mencionar el hecho de que no tengo experiencia práctica en el tema." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8562
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cbcea1ce:

    # s frown_right "And that is what makes it the perfect way to test my hypothesis." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Y eso lo vuelve el método perfecto para poner a prueba mi hipótesis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8563
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c197c613:

    # "If she's that convinced my penlight is somehow this kind of all-powerful mind control device, I guess I can't argue with her there."
    "Si está tan convencida de que mi linterna es alguna clase de dispositivo de control mental todopoderoso, supongo que no puedo discutir eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8564
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_65192b83:

    # s casual_handup "So how about it, Kyou?" with dissolve
    s casual_handup "Entonces, ¿qué opinas, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8565
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_922ae109:

    # "Maybe this penlight I've constructed really is that special. But then, why would I ever subject myself to it knowing that?"
    "Tal vez esta linterna que construí sí es así de especial. Pero entonces, ¿por qué me sometería a ella sabiendo eso?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8566
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bf5a704f:

    # s neutral "Perhaps it is too much to ask of of you, but..." with dissolve
    s neutral "Tal vez sea demasiado pedir, pero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8567
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_46df1149:

    # "And what is Sayori even hoping to get out of this? She really wants to prove her hypothesis that bad?"
    "¿Y qué piensa Sayori conseguir con esto? ¿Tanto desea probar su hipótesis?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8568
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_54123873:

    # s concerned_right "... Would you consent to such an experiment?" with dissolve
    s concerned_right "... ¿Consentirías a tal experimento?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8569
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6bd3c3b5:

    # "Is this her way of getting some kind of revenge for what I've put her through?"
    "¿Es su forma de obtener alguna especie de venganza por lo que la he hecho pasar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8570
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e160dce7:

    # s "Please, Kyou. Tell me what you are thinking."
    s "Por favor, Kyou. Dime qué estás pensando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8571
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3f2082a8:

    # "Not to mention, if this penlight of mine really is all that, how could I seriously consider giving it up to anybody?"
    "Sin mencionar que, si mi linterna en serio es así, ¿cómo podría considerar dársela a alguien?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8572
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0c9dff7c:

    # "So I'll..."
    "Entonces voy a..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8575
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_aecc7376:

    # ks neutral "Alright. Let's do it."
    ks neutral "Muy bien. Hagámoslo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8576
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2c525edd:

    # "For all the doubts I've got in my head, there's at least a couple of things I know for sure."
    "Por más dudas que tenga en mi cabeza, hay al menos un par de cosas de las que estoy seguro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8577
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5ae3003b:

    # n surprised "Huh? You're serious?" with dissolve
    n surprised "¿Eh? ¿En serio?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8578
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_517a5404:

    # "I was the one who got Sayori in this mess. If I hadn't sent her away that night thinking she was that other person, maybe we could've avoided this whole situation."
    "Fui yo quien metió a Sayori en este desastre. Si no la hubiera mandado a casa esa noche mientras pensaba que era otra persona, tal vez habríamos evitado esta situación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8579
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_863d7ff0:

    # s smile_right "Then I will thank you for granting me this second indulgence. You will not regret this." with dissolve
    s smile_right "Entonces, una vez más, te agradezco por concederme esto. No te arrepentirás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8580
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a194155b:

    # "She's been through a lot in these past few days and she's had every reason to doubt me."
    "Ha pasado por mucho estos días, y tiene mil razones para dudar de mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8582
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3018fa57:

    # "But despite everything, she... she really does seem to respect me." with dissolve
    "Pero a pesar de todo, de... de verdad parece respetarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8583
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_798a5f6a:

    # n side happy "Well... a-alright then! So, back to mine then?" with dissolve
    n side happy "Bien... ¡d-de acuerdo! Entonces, ¿volvemos a mi casa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8585
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9d91c5a5:

    # "Sayori isn't just some cold, overly-serious study fiend. There's also a genuine warmness to her."
    "Sayori no es solo una fría y excesivamente seria compañera de estudio. Hay calidez de verdad en ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8586
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c954a0c5:

    # "And if today has shown me anything, it's that she definitely has a playful side even when she isn't \"[alt_name]\"."
    "Y si algo aprendí este día, es que definitivamente tiene un lado juguetón incluso cuando no es \"[alt_name]\"."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8588
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2e7137d6:

    # "I want to be someone worthy of her respect."
    "Quiero ser alguien digno de ese respeto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8635
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c0545a31:

    # "So at long last, we find ourselves heading back to Nozomi's house."
    "Así que, finalmente, nos encontramos camino de regreso a casa de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8640
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e64c7915:

    # n "Um, Sayori? We might have a little bit of a problem." with dissolve
    n "Em, ¿Sayori? Puede que tengamos un problemita." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8641
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_276b3646:

    # "I'd be lying if I said I wasn't anxious about this whole thing, but I'm not going back on my word now."
    "Estaría mintiendo si dijera que no me pone nervioso todo esto, pero no faltaré a mi palabra."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8642
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0efea7b1:

    # s neutral "Oh? And what is that?" with dissolve
    s neutral "¿Oh? ¿Qué cosa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8643
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a92a22ee:

    # "I do trust Sayori to know what she's doing, all things considered."
    "Confío en que Sayori sabe lo que hace, a pesar de todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8644
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9571914e:

    # n irritated "Well thinking back, mom noticed how odd you were being at lunch; talking about wanting to play games instead of studying and such." with dissolve
    n irritated "Bueno, ahora que recuerdo, mamá notó lo extraño que estabas actuando mientras almorzábamos; hablando de querer jugar en lugar de estudiar y así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8645
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e58b4b90:

    # s casual_handup sleep "Hmm... understood." with dissolve
    s casual_handup sleep "Mmm... comprendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8646
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c752c0f0:

    # n sad_side "Not to mention she thinks you left because of a family emergency or something..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Sin mencionar que cree que te fuiste por alguna emergencia familiar o algo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8649
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6fdc5c00:

    # ks casual confused "Do we have to do this at your place, Nozomi? My house isn't that far, and it'll be empty." with dissolve
    ks casual confused "¿Tenemos que hacer esto en tu casa, Nozomi? La mía no está muy lejos, y no habrá nadie." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8650
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e270b150:

    # n sad "Your place? I don't know..." with dissolve
    n sad "¿Tu casa? No lo sé..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8652
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2ed7b877:

    # "Just then, Sayori let out an audible yawn as she puts a hand to her mouth." with dissolve
    "En ese momento, Sayori deja salir un audible bostezo, llevándose una mano a la boca." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8653
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9e3c0f32:

    # s "As preferable as that may be, I can barely walk another step."
    s "Por preferible que eso sea, apenas puedo poner un pie frente al otro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8654
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_45b126cf:

    # n sad_closed "Gosh, Sayori, I don't know how you're even standing." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Cielos, Sayori, no sé cómo te mantienes de pie." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8655
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_06a4d0c7:

    # s sleeptalk "Mmh. Admittedly I could have done without my alter ego running me ragged. Regardless, I shall persist." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Mmm. Ciertamente sería bueno que mi alter ego no hubiese agotado toda mi batería. Aun así, he de persistir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8657
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_05a78e26:

    # s neutral "Besides, I believe I can manage the... Atsuko situation." with dissolve
    s neutral "Además, creo que puedo manejar la... situación Atsuko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8665
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_54c71e2c:

    # "Her decision made, the three of us roll up to the front door of Nozomi's house and see ourselves inside."
    "Habiendo tomado su decisión, los tres pasamos por la puerta delantera y entramos a la sala de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8666
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1044ee8b:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: And this is where I'll have to leave things for now, I'm afraid. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTROA: Y aquí tendré que dejarlo por ahora, me temo. ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8667
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0fbcedc6:

    # "(( Writing this thing has been a lot tougher than I thought, so I'm going to take a break to focus on another part of the story for the next update. ))"
    "(( Escribir esto ha sido mucho más difícil de lo que pensé, así que voy a tomarme un descanso y concentrarme en otra parte de la historia en la próxima actualización. ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8668
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a3577976:

    # "(( In the meantime, feel free to read the tiny bit of rough outlining I did for the next scene or stay tuned for the continuation of this story path coming... soonish ^^; ))"
    "(( Mientras tanto, disfruten esta pizca de bosquejo que hice para la siguiente escena o manténganse en sintonía para ver la continuación que vendrá... más o menos pronto. ^^; "

