# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1489
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_835bdb39:

    # ks "But you, Nozomi. It's like I said, I studied hypnosis because of you. I made this penlight of mine for you."
    ks "Pero tú, Nozomi. Como dije, estudié hipnosis gracias a ti. Hice esta linterna para ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1493
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4c799707:

    # "I then make a point of gesturing to Hiroko and Sayori, grinning stupidly by my side."
    "Y entonces hago un gesto señalando a Hiroko y Sayori, sonriendo estúpidamente a mi lado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1494
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ffccb365:

    # ks "You're the reason for all of this. I did it all for you, so that's why..."
    ks "Tú eres la razón de todo esto. Lo hice todo por ti, y es por eso..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1495
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_00926027:

    # ks "... That's why I need you to love me, Nozomi Akemi."
    ks "... Es por eso que necesito que me ames, Nozomi Akemi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1499
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5a654480:

    # n "We didn't know what to do about you; no one else would listen to us, but..."
    n "No sabíamos qué hacer contigo; nadie más nos escuchaba, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1518
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1d1c9bde:

    # n "No matter what happens with us, you'll always know the truth."
    n "Sin importar lo que ocurra con nosotras, tú siempre sabrás la verdad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1519
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_30e5efbc:

    # n sleepy "{cps=15}You'll always know you're a monster-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    n sleepy "{cps=15}Siempre sabrás que eres un monstruo-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1525
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e8c751ca:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. You can't resist me; you know you've been in and out of my hypnosis all day long. You know how good this feels."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. No puedes resistirte a mí; sabes que has estado entrando y saliendo de mi hipnosis todo el día. Sabes lo bien que se siente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1528
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9fb12336:

    # ks "So just sleep, let all the tension out of your body and let yourself fall even deeper for me..." with dissolve
    ks "Así que duerme, deja que toda la tensión salga de tu cuerpo y cae aún más profundo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1532
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_15585a0a:

    # ks neutral "Dropping so deep, Nozomi. So much deeper into hypnosis. Feeling so good, finding it so easy to go deep for me."
    ks neutral "Muy, muy profundo, Nozomi. Cae profundo en este estado de hipnosis. Se siente muy bien y muy fácil caer ante mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1533
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_128536d8:

    # ks "And now that you're back into this nice, deep state of trance for me, I..."
    ks "Y ahora que estás de regreso en este agradable y profundo estado de trance, quiero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1555
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4c07bd3b:

    # ks "You're relaxed around me. Feeling safe and comfortable. So it's only natural if you find yourself considering how you really feel about me." with dissolve
    ks "Estar junto a mí te relaja. Te sientes a salvo y cómoda. Así que es natural que empieces a reconsiderar lo que sientes por mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1557
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cd2c55ac:

    # ks "If I can make you feel this good, then maybe it's not so strange if you find yourself becoming attracted to me. Find yourself wanting a relationship with me."
    ks "Si puedo hacerte sentir así de bien, tal vez no sea tan raro que empieces a sentirte atraída por mí, o que quieras una relación conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1558
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d37b71ce:

    # n sleeptalk "Urrh..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Eeeh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1560
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a09c3664:

    # ks "There's no stopping it. It's so natural to think about it now." with dissolve
    ks "No hay nada que lo detenga. Es natural pensar en eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1562
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_aa56d3e9:

    # ks "The more you consider starting a relationship with me, the more natural it feels. And the more natural it feels, the more right it becomes to want a relationship with me..."
    ks "Entre más consideras el estar en una relación conmigo, más natural se siente. Y entre más natural se siente, más sientes que es lo correcto..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1563
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a157bae:

    # ks "And the more right it becomes, the more you realize that you love me, Nozomi."
    ks "Y al saber que es lo correcto, te das cuenta de que me amas, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1564
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2ed1f7a2:

    # ks "You are experiencing such a deep feeling of love for me now... and I want you to accept that feeling."
    ks "Experimentas un profundo sentimiento de amor por mí... y quiero que aceptes ese sentimiento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1565
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_eee36705:

    # ks "You can do that for me, can't you, Nozomi?"
    ks "Puedes hacer eso por mí, ¿no es así, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1566
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4f272972:

    # n sleeptalk "I..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1567
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c40dc756:

    # n "Y-... yes..."
    n "S-... sí..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1569
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6d8481e1:

    # ks "That's good. You're doing so well, accepting these feelings. Allowing that love for me to grow in your heart. Allowing it to become your truth." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Haces muy bien en aceptar esos sentimientos. Deja que ese amor por mí crezca en tu corazón. Deja que se vuelva tu verdad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1570
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0460beb7:

    # ks "Because the truth is that you love me more than anything in the world. There is no one that you value more than me. Nothing you wouldn't do to make me happy."
    ks "Porque la verdad es que me amas más que a nada en el mundo. No hay nadie a quien valores más que a mí. Nada que no harías para hacerme feliz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1572
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7a583931:

    # ks "So it's only natural that you would want to become my girlfriend now... right, Nozomi?"
    ks "Así que es natural que ahora quieras ser mi novia... ¿cierto, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1573
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_90ee992c:

    # n sleeptalk "Right... I want to become... your girlfriend..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Cierto... quiero ser... tu novia..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1575
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3b7b68fd:

    # ks "Wonderful. So now, in a few moments I'm going to wake you from this deep state of trance and you're going to want to act on your new truth." with dissolve
    ks "Maravilloso. Y ahora, en unos momentos voy a despertarte de este estado de trance y actuarás conforme a tu nueva verdad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1576
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_97bd0e2c:

    # ks "And once you do, you will find that you can speak and move with complete freedom once again."
    ks "Y cuando lo hagas, notarás que una vez más puedes hablar y moverte con completa libertad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1594
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e06da99b:

    # "I look down on her, watching as her eyelids pull themselves open to register the sight that greets her."
    "La observo desde arriba, viendo cómo sus ojos se abren y registra la imagen que le da la bienvenida a su nueva realidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1595
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ce7f5142:

    # n surprised "K... Kyou?" with dissolve
    n surprised "¿K... Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1596
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_65a4c7f5:

    # "The sight of someone she's no doubt starting to feel very differently about."
    "La imagen de alguien por quien sin duda ahora tiene sentimientos completamente diferentes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1597
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c8deec55:

    # ks smile "That's me. Now what was that you were saying about me just now?"
    ks smile "Ese soy yo. Entonces, ¿qué estabas diciendo de mí hace un momento?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1599
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ecaad30b:

    # n front sleepy "What I was... what I was... s-saying?" with dissolve
    n front sleepy "¿Lo que estaba... estaba... d-diciendo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1600
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d98369ed:

    # ks smirk "Something about me being a monster, right?"
    ks smirk "Algo sobre que soy un monstruo, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1601
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4dd4e015:

    # "Nozomi's eyelids start to flicker violently as her sleepy mind continues its return to clarity, remembering the conversation we were just having."
    "Los párpados de Nozomi tiemblan con furor mientras su adormecida mente continúa su regreso a la claridad, recordando la conversación que estábamos teniendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1603
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_94709fe0:

    # "I can almost see the gears shifting in her mind, as she tries to reconcile the things she said with the desire I forced upon her." with dissolve
    "Casi puedo ver los engranes girando en su mente, intentando reconciliar las cosas que dijo con el deseo que forcé en su ser." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1605
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9fee577f:

    # n sleeptalk "O-oh... oh, that..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "O-oh... oh, eso..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1608
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a0ae82b5:

    # ks "You're having second thoughts now, aren't you?"
    ks "Ahora lo estás reconsiderando, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1612
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_509d751e:

    # n "K-Kyou, I... I know what I said." with dissolve
    n "K-Kyou, sé... sé lo que dije." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1613
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b092a56f:

    # n concerned "What you've done to me and my friends is wrong. It's so... so wrong." with dissolve
    n concerned "Lo que me hiciste a mí y a mis amigas es terrible. Es... realmente terrible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1614
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a4a05937:

    # n sleep "But it's okay. If it's you, it's okay." with dissolve
    n sleep "Pero está bien. Si eres tú, está bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1888
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_96687e22:

    # n neutral "When I think about everything you did. Knowing you learned hypnosis and did all these diabolical things just so you could have me..." with dissolve
    n neutral "Cuando pienso en todo lo que hiciste. Sabiendo que aprendiste hipnosis e hiciste todas estas cosas diabólicas solo para poder tenerme..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1616
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8d8d588e:

    # n smile blush "It's... it's actually kind of... romantic." with dissolve
    n smile blush "Es... de hecho, un tanto... romántico." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1608
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_50ced3a4:

    # n "Don't you think?"
    n "¿No lo crees?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1618
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_07b67f67:

    # "Nozomi bats her eyelids coquettishly as she takes a quiet step towards me."
    "Nozomi pestañea coquetamente, dando en silencio un paso hacia mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1619
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_50fa451b:

    # "And I grin triumphantly as I move to hold the small of her back and look into those beautiful brown eyes of hers."
    "Y yo, con una sonrisa triunfante, pongo mi mano en su espalda y miro directo a sus hermosos ojos cafés."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1619
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dcb3724d:

    # ks casual smirk "Just tell me what I really want to hear."
    ks casual smirk "Solo dime lo que quiero escuchar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1620
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e564932b:

    # n chuckle "Mhmhmhm..." with dissolve
    n chuckle "Jejejeje..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1623
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f2e4a20e:

    # n happy "I-I love you, Kyou! I can't help it, I love you so much, so please..." with dissolve
    n happy "¡T-te amo, Kyou! No puedo evitarlo, te amo muchísimo, así que por favor..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1624
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0a6eaa9c:

    # n laugh "Please make me your girlfriend!" with dissolve
    n laugh "¡Por favor, hazme tu novia!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1626
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_be53301f:

    # "I answer with a kiss of those invitingly soft lips while I hear my two fangirls squeeing mindlessly behind us." with dissolve
    "Respondo con un beso en sus suabes labios mientras escucho a mis fanáticas dar un chillido de alegría detrás de nosotros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1627
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2978e7bd:

    # "She moans and embraces me fully, and in an instant all those years of rejection and pain at her hands feel like they've been swept away by just this one moment."
    "Ella gime y me abraza, y en un instante todos esos años de rechazo y dolor a manos suyas parecen desvanecerse solo con este momento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1628
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_29aa70ab:

    # "Nozomi... you're mine at last."
    "Nozomi... finalmente eres mía."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1630
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_773ef001:

    # "And I'll never let you go..."
    "Y jamás te dejaré ir..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8529
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_955062b0:

    # s panicked "E-eeep!" with vpunch
    s panicked "¡A-ayyy!" with vpunch
# TODO: Translation updated at 2023-03-29 09:27

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1272
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7c46bc00:

    # ks "That's why you'll find yourself unable to raise your voice beyond a normal speaking volume, and it's why you can't move a muscle from where you are now."
    ks "Es por eso que no podrás elevar el volumen de tu voz más de lo normal, ni podrás mover un solo músculo de donde estás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1273
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ed4c8f5c:

    # ks "You know I'm not going to hurt you anyway, Nozomi. We're just going to have a nice little chat."
    ks "De todos modos, sabes que no voy a hacerte daño, Nozomi. Simplemente tendremos una pequeña charla."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1274
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e96d9861:

    # ks "So just relax and don't worry about a thing. You're perfectly safe here."
    ks "Así que relájate y no te preocupes por nada. Estás perfectamente segura aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1482
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e5211a1d:

    # "I then make a point of gesturing to Hiroko and Sayori, who grin stupidly as they register my attention."
    "Y entonces hago un gesto señalando a Hiroko y Sayori, quienes sonríen estúpidamente a mi lado al registrar mi atención."



# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1504
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b024ef78:

    # "Nozomi, drained as she is on the floor, lets out a hollow chuckle."
    "Nozomi, agotada en el suelo, suelta una risa vacía."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1511
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9bc007c8:

    # n "{cps=15}You'll always know you're a monster-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    n "{cps=15}Siempre sabrás que eres un monstruo-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1582
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_209409bc:

    # n sleepy "A-ahhh..." with dissolve
    n sleepy "A-aaah..." with dissolve



# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1615
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_16add1cc:

    # "Nozomi bats her eyelids coquettishly as she picks herself up from the floor before taking a quiet step towards me."
    "Nozomi pestañea coquetamente, levantándose del suelo y luego dando en silencio un paso hacia mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1625
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_586b3bac:

    # "I answer with a kiss of those invitingly soft lips while I hear my two fangirls squeeing mindlessly beside us." with dissolve
    "Respondo con un beso en sus suabes labios mientras escucho a mis fanáticas dar un chillido de alegría junto a nosotros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1725
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8f3f2c22:

    # n sleepy "A- aaah..." with dissolve
    n sleepy "A- aaah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1745
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4f4cf1e6:

    # "I smirk as I step back from her to take a seat on the couch while Nozomi, her breath heavy with a newfound sense of elation, scrambles to her feet."
    "Sonriente, doy un paso atrás para sentarme en el sofá, mientras que Nozomi, respirando fuertemente con su nuevo sentido de elación, se pone temblorosamente de pie."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1748
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f50ddddd:

    # "She takes an eager step towards me, only for me to halt her giddy advance with a raised hand."
    "Da un anhelante paso hacia mí, solo para que yo detenga su vertiginoso avance alzando una mano."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1749
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_af876b25:

    # n smile "K-Kyou?" with dissolve
    n smile "¿K-Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1750
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c3af3d90:

    # "Time to put this groupie in her proper place."
    "Hora de poner a esta admiradora en su lugar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1837
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_130e7fa8:

    # "Think it's time I made a speech."
    "Creo que es hora de dar un discurso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:10094
translate spanish Day6_Redemption_4eff391c:

    # "Akiko and I enjoy the moment in silence before she makes a move to leave and I walk her to the door."
    "Akiko y yo disfrutamos el momento en silencio, y posteriormente ella se da la vuelta para salir y yo la acompaño a la puerta."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2023-04-29 10:18

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6387
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7b5c1113:

    # "Not to mention... Nozomi."
    "Sin mencionar lo de... Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6388
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7d2c77d0:

    # "How am I going to break it to her that I hypnotized Nozomi again?"
    "¿Cómo voy a explicarle que hipnoticé a Nozomi otra vez?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6717
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9661c81d:

    # ks "I'm fine putting you back to how you were, Sayori, but what you're asking me to do, I..."
    ks "No tengo problemas con dejarte como estabas, Sayori, pero lo que me estas pidiendo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6718
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_92fa04b4:

    # ks "I just can't, okay?"
    ks "Simplemente no puedo, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6720
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4ac419a7_1:

    # s alert_annoyed_right "Kyou, I want you to think about what you are saying." with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed_right "Kyou, quiero que pienses en lo que estás diciendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6722
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_232bb7b2_1:

    # s "If you refuse to do this, you put us all in danger."
    s "Si te reúsas a hacer esto, nos pones a todos en peligro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6723
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b842b50a:

    # "I can't help but shake my head at what I'm hearing."
    "No puedo evitar sacudir la cabeza ante lo que estoy escuchando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6724
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5141a801:

    # ks frown "Look, I know it can be dangerous. I *know* that, okay? I didn't realize before how dangerous hypnosis can be."
    ks frown "Mira, sé que puede ser peligrosa. Lo *sé*, ¿de acuerdo? No me di cuenta antes de cuán peligrosa la hipnosis puede ser."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6725
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_fc14f13d:

    # ks "But I've learned from our time together. I know I have to be more careful about the things I say to a hypnotized subject, especially if I can get them as deep into it as with you."
    ks "Pero he aprendido de nuestro tiempo juntos. Sé que debo tener cuidado con lo que le digo a un sujeto hipnotizado, sobre todo si puedo llevarlo tan profundo como a ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6726
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4b37fcfd:

    # ks "I can really hurt people with my penlight, no doubt about that. But so long as I'm careful I can do so much good for people too."
    ks "Puedo hacerle daño a la gente con mi linterna, de eso no hay duda. Pero siempre y cuando sea cuidadoso, puedo hacerle mucho bien a la gente también."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6727
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4073407f:

    # ks "My hypnosis made you think you lost control of yourself, but with the right words I could have you feeling on top of the world. So don't tell me to throw it all away."
    ks "Mi hipnosis te hizo creer que perdiste el control de ti misma, pero con más cuidado
, podría hacerte sentir en la cima del mundo. No me pidas echarlo a la basura."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6728
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c0a036ec:

    # ks "Don't tell me I have to give this all up just because I made a mistake."
    ks "No me digas que tengo que renunciar a todo esto solo porque cometí un error."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6730
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b6617681:

    # "Sayori scoffs at me as she shakes her head disdainfully." with dissolve
    "Sayori resopla, sacudiendo la cabeza con desdén." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6731
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_390f2a57:

    # s "Unbelievable. The arrogance on you that you think you can handle such a wild and dangerous phenomenon you don't fully comprehend."
    s "Inconcebible. Tal es tu arrogancia que crees que puedes manejar un fenómeno tan peligroso que escapa de tu comprensión."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6739
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0fd9237e:

    # ks "You saw how it worked on Nozomi didn't you? I put her into trance with the penlight, took her out again and she didn't suffer for it at all."
    ks "Ya viste cómo funcionó en Nozomi, ¿no? La puse en trance con la linterna, la volví a sacar, y no sufrió en lo más mínimo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6740
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bdf9a4de:

    # ks "She even seemed to enjoy it, didn't she?"
    ks "Hasta pareció disfrutarlo, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6742
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ceb597b4:

    # s "You... Kyou, do not insult my intelligence by trying to convince me our experiment with Nozomi and my own experience are directly comparable." with dissolve
    s "Kyou... no insultes mi inteligencia intentando convencerme de que nuestro experimento con Nozomi y mi propia experiencia son directamente comparables." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6743
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b4177427:

    # ks "Of course they are! I hypnotized Nozomi and I..."
    ks "¡Claro que lo son! Hipnoticé a Nozomi y..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6744
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9691d504:

    # "Oh... right."
    "Oh... cierto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6745
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ce88b70a:

    # s "You... what?"
    s "Y... ¿qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6746
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7d621546:

    # ks confused "I- I..."
    ks confused "E-este..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6747
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1bed8835:

    # "In the heat of it all I forgot Sayori doesn't know what went down after she left me and Nozomi in the study club room."
    "En el calor del momento, olvidé que Sayori no sabe lo que ocurrió después de que nos dejó a Nozomi y a mí en el salón del club de estudio."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6749
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_aa5834fb:

    # s "You and Nozomi... you..." with dissolve
    s "Tú y Nozomi... tú..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6750
