    n neutral_side "O de cansancio. ¿Quieres que te sostenga o puedes mantenerte de pie por tu cuenta?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8907
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_032ea1bc:

    # "As Sayori sluggishly disentangles herself from Nozomi's embrace, she looks to me expectantly..." with dissolve
    "Desenredándose perezosamente de los brazos de Nozomi, Sayori me mira con expectativa..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8910
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8a51dce9:

    # "... And without a second thought I take the penlight from my pocket and hand it over."
    "... Y sin pensarlo dos veces, tomo la linterna de mi bolsillo y se la doy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8911
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_932d4638:

    # ks casual sigh "Yeah, let's do what we came here to do, I guess."
    ks casual sigh "Sí, hagamos lo que vinimos a hacer, supongo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8912
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b0d20b0e:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: Okay, gonna outline the rest of this story before I work on the dialogue. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Muy bien, voy a bosquejar el resto de la historia antes de trabajar en el diálogo. ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8913
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b3776ceb:

    # "(( As ever, feel free to read on to see what's in store or await the next update~ )"
    "(( Como siempre, siéntase libre de leer lo que hay disponible o esperar hasta la próxima actualización ))"
    "(( Tener en cuenta, sin embargo, que el bosquejo no está traducido al español. ))"
# TODO: Translation updated at 2023-06-18 21:32

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7234
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c390ad73:

    # "And all this business with Sayori *is* bringing us together. In a weird, roundabout kind of way."
    "Y todo este asunto con Sayori *sí* nos está uniendo. Aunque sea de una manera un tanto extraña y dando algunas vueltas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7235
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_da1cd5a8:

    # "Not really the way I'd have planned it, but I guess I'll take it..."
    "No es exactamente como lo había planeado, pero supongo que algo es algo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7417
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0a7902d1:

    # s casual_folded sleep "And I would have shared your skepticism. But there is no doubt in my mind that Kyou's hypnosis has had an effect on me beyond what should be possible." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep "Y yo habría compartido tu escepticismo. Pero no me cabe duda de que la hipnosis de Kyou ha tenido un efecto en mí más allá de lo que debería ser posible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7418
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_75417297:

    # "Because I look at Sayori now, and... yeah."
    "Porque miro a Sayori ahora, y... sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7419
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a9ec3cf9:

    # s neutral_right "It appears more consistent with being subject to many extended sessions of deep hypnotic conditioning from a highly-trained hypnotist, with my full knowledge and consent." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Parece más consistente con múltiples sesiones extendidas de profundo acondicionamiento con un hipnotista altamente entrenado, con mi conocimiento y consentimiento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7421
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b58aeb15:

    # "Something doesn't add up."
    "Algo no cuadra."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7422
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c84c2976:

    # s concerned_right "And as such, I am certain I have no ability to resist it." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Y como tal, puedo decir con certeza que no tengo la habilidad de resistirla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7426
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_94224c01:

    # s neutral_right "Why? Do you have any reason to doubt me?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "¿Por qué? ¿Tienes alguna razón para dudar de mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7599
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bf822b86_1:

    # s "... Kyou?" with dissolve
    s "... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7648
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6cc33d96:

    # "Because yeah, she doesn't seem to remember anything."
    "Porque sí, parece que no recuerda nada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7752
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4a4b1caf:

    # ks sigh "{size=16}I don't like this any more than you do but it'll be over soon, I promise.{/size}"
    ks sigh "{size=16}No me gusta esto más que a ti, pero terminará pronto, lo prometo.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7893
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_316d4012:

    # "I notice Nozomi casting a wary look to the happy friend in question..." with dissolve
    "Noto a Nozomi lanzarle una cautelosa mirada a la alegre amiga en cuestión..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7973
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b4e9b007:

    # nm smile_side "Hmm. Well, maybe a little mental break would do you some good if you feel you need it, dear." with dissolve
    nm smile_side "Mmm. Bueno, tal vez un pequeño descanso mental sería bueno para ti si sientes que lo necesitas, cariño." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8240
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_61121cd6:

    # n sad_side "So I just thought she might have said something to you? Something about the kind of person she was before senior high?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "Así que pensé que ¿tal vez te dijo algo? ¿Algo sobre la clase de persona que era antes de preparatoria?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8626
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6f746fb1:

    # s concerned "What happened to me should be impossible by our understanding of how hypnosis works." with dissolve
    s concerned "Lo que me pasó debería ser imposible con base en nuestro conocimiento sobre el funcionamiento de la hipnosis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8627
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_34579237:

    # s frown_right "Therefore, we have little choice but to indulge in some... shall we say, extremely out of the box thinking." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Por ello, no tenemos más opción que permitirnos pensar... digamos, extremadamente fuera de la caja." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8630
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_34e97eab:

    # s casual_folded "First, we need to talk more about your penlight." with dissolve
    s casual_folded "Primero que nada, debemos hablar un poco más de tu pluma linterna." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8647
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6fd4a22f:

    # "Sayori lets out a weary sigh as she gives Nozomi a knowing nod."
    "Sayori, dejando escapar un cansado suspiro, le asiente a Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8648
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_80942159:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "Impossible. It is a ridiculous statement to make in all seriousness. Yet it is exactly the explanation I put forth to you both." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Imposible. Una afirmación seriamente ridícula. Y sin embargo, es exactamente la explicación que presento ante ustedes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8650
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b4b244af:

    # "I mean sure, what happened to her is pretty damn crazy, I'll admit, but..."
    "Digo, claro, lo que le ocurrió fue una maldita locura, debo admitirlo, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8652
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d1d497d8:

    # ks confused "You're serious? You think I've been altering your brain chemistry and controlling your mind with..." with dissolve
    ks confused "¿Hablas en serio? ¿Crees que he estado alterando tu química cerebral y controlando tu mente con..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8655
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ac7acab2:

    # ks "... with this?"
    ks "... con esto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8656
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d6b3f66f:

    # "Taking the penlight from my pocket, I hold it up in the air for both to see in all its mundane glory."
    "Sacando la linterna de mi bolsillo, la sostengo en el aire para que ambas la vean en toda su mundana gloria."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8657
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_22fdfd26:

    # s concerned_right "I do. And if I am correct, then that penlight is both the cause of, and solution to my predicament." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "En efecto. Y si estoy en lo correcto, entonces esa linterna es tanto la causa como la solución a mi predicamento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8658
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_43c26241:

    # "I'm proud of the modifications I made to it. I was sure it'd help induce a trance state just like I planned, but the very idea it could do what she's saying?"
    "Estoy orgulloso de las modificaciones que le hice. Estaba seguro de que ayudaría a inducir un estado de trance como planeé, pero ¿la sola idea de que pudiera hacer lo que dice?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8660
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cf2b5b02:

    # ks "Sayori, there's out of the box thinking and there's completely nuts. And this is completely fucking nuts, you know that, right?"
    ks "Sayori, existe pensar fuera de la caja y luego está la locura. Y esto es una puta locura, lo sabes, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8661
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a0e562a0:

    # "I don't believe it. I CAN'T believe it."
    "No lo creo. No PUEDO creerlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8662
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d8c6698a:

    # "If there's anything that makes sense here at all it's more like..."
    "Si hay algo que tenga sentido, sería más bien..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8663
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8b9f6367:

    # n sad_closed "I-I'm sorry but Kyou's right. This is insanity." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "L-lo siento, pero Kyou tiene razón. Eso suena muy inverosímil." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8664
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2c5ee77a:

    # s concerned "There has been little sanity in what has happened to me. Is it really so far-fetched given what we have witnessed today?" with dissolve
    s concerned "Poca verosimilitud ha habido en lo que me ha estado sucediendo. ¿Es realmente tan descabellado dado lo que presenciamos hoy?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8666
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e750e01b:

    # n sad_side "I know, I just... gosh, I think we're still coming to terms with how hypnotically suggestible you really are." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Lo sé, es que... cielos, creo que aún estamos asimilando lo hipnóticamente sugestionable que eres." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8667
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a5656b97:

    # n neutral_side "Sayori, you're so sharp-witted, and I know when there's something you want to focus on you'll never let go." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Sayori, eres muy perspicaz, y sé que cuando hay algo en lo que te quieres concentrar, no quitas el dedo del renglón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8668
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_804e5fa2:

    # n sad "If Kyou even halfway knows what he's doing with hypnosis, using a light designed to catch your attention?" with dissolve
    n sad "Si Kyou siquiera parcialmente sabe lo que hace con la hipnosis, usando una luz diseñada para captar la atención..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8669
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c99ccfc7:

    # n neutral_side "Maybe that's all it takes to unlock the boundless potential of your mind to do virtually anything, just like we've seen." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "... Tal vez eso sea todo lo que haga falta para desbloquear el ilimitado potencial de tu mente para hacer virtualmente cualquier cosa, tal como vimos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8670
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9363b71a:

    # n neutral_side "Your mind is just that capable of doing all these wild and wonderful and... yes, kinda scary things." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Tu mente simplemente es así de capaz de hacer todas estas cosas tan locas y maravillosas y... sí, un tanto aterradoras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8671
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ea8ac62a:

    # n sad_closed "I don't think it's the penlight that's special, Sayori." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Yo no creo que sea la linterna la que es especial, Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8672
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_97f7a462:

    # n sad_side "... You are." with dissolve
    n sad_side "... Eres tú." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8673
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_beca9ef7:

    # "Yeah. That's pretty much what I was going to say."
    "Sí. Eso es básicamente lo que iba a decir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8674
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_396d4b4f:

    # s casual_folded sleeptalk_concerned "Ah..." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleeptalk_concerned "Ah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8675
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e10d5132:

    # "But to all that, Sayori just draws out another laboured sigh as her head lowers to the floor."
    "Pero en respuesta a todo eso, Sayori simplemente suelta otro exhausto suspiro, agachando la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8676
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_17e9756e:

    # s concerned "I... suppose I should feel flattered. But no, I do not believe there is anything special about me, Nozomi." with dissolve
    s concerned "Supongo... que debería sentirme alagada. Pero no, yo no creo que haya nada de especial en mí, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8677
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_05711726:

    # s sleeptalk "All that you see of me, I have had to work damned hard to attain; I am no genius." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Todo lo que ves en mí, tengo que trabajar increíblemente duro para obtenerlo; no soy ningún genio." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8678
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_03eeeea4:

    # s concerned_right "So... Look, I do not ask that you believe me. Just that you humor me for a while; I believe I am owed that much." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Así que... Mira, no les pido que me crean. Solo que me permitan poner esto a prueba; creo que es lo menos que pueden hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8679
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_15db920b:

    # "I let out a little sigh of my own this time. So she's that set on this theory of hers, huh?"
    "Ahora es mi turno de soltar un pequeño suspiro. Conque así de aferrada está a su teoría, ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8680
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2ad3b777:

    # ks neutral "Alright... so what now?"
    ks neutral "Muy bien... entonces, ¿qué hacemos ahora?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8686
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_33910a35:

    # s casual "Well, I believe we can all agree your penlight and its unique properties are a likely culprit in facilitating these drastic changes upon me." with dissolve
    s casual "Bueno, me parece que todos podemos estar de acuerdo en que la linterna y sus propiedades únicas son un posible culpable de facilitar estos cambios drásticos en mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8687
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ba6e8542:

    # s neutral_right "So it stands to reason that in order to reverse those changes, you could simply apply it in the same manner as before." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Así que resulta razonable que, para revertir dichos cambios, podrías simplemente utilizarla del mismo modo que antes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8695
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ebc0ceb1:

    # s casual_folded sleep "Actually... what I am about to propose is something you could say is... a little reckless, given my opinion on the matter." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleep "De hecho... lo que estoy por proponer es algo que podrían considerar... un tanto osado, dada mi opinión en el tema." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8703
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ba123576:

    # "... I'm starting to wonder about that look Sayori's suddenly giving me." with dissolve
    "... Comienza a generarme preguntas esa mirada que Sayori me está dando de repente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8714
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2504870f:

    # ks confused "Is there a *good* context for this kind of talk?"
    ks confused "¿Existe algún *buen* contexto para decir esas cosas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8813
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3dce8826:

    # s "I... think I would prefer to finish this here and now if it is all the same to you."
    s "Creo... que preferiría terminar con esto aquí y ahora si no les importa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8865
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cc4ddfc4:

    # n smile_side "Oh... y-yeah. How silly of us." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Oh... s-sí. Qué tontos somos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8867
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bc10cfc5:

    # s casual_folded laugh "So I had to skip the class after all and my, what a delightfully whimsical day this has been! It is like no one is of a mind to do any boring work today~" with dissolve
    s casual_folded laugh "Así que tuve que saltarme la clase después de todo y ¡cielos, qué día tan encantador y fantástico ha sido el de hoy! Parece que nadie tiene apetito de aburrido trabajo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8869
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_18711128:

    # s casual_handup sleeptalk_concerned "So I... aawwwnnn... I will laze it up with my friends a while longer and catch the next class when it is time." with dissolve
    s casual_handup sleeptalk_concerned "Así que... uuuaaaa... holgazanearé con mis amigos un rato más y me aseguraré de asistir a la clase siguiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8872
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_41136445:

    # s smile "I just hope that he will not be too upset with me if he discovers my tardiness." with dissolve
    s smile "Solo espero que no esté muy molesto conmigo si descubre mi inasistencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8880
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fb086c84:

    # nm happy "Well he won't hear about it from me~" with dissolve
    nm happy "Bueno, no escuchará nada de mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8883
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_69698faf:

    # nm smile_side "Anyway I'll let you all get on. It's been lovely to see you again, Sayori." with dissolve
    nm smile_side "En fin, dejaré que se diviertan. Ha sido encantador volver a verte, Sayori." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8884
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c42a2e94:

    # "Maybe she doesn't actually give a shit. It's not like Sayori's *her* daughter, after all."
    "Tal vez en realidad no le importa una mierda. No es que Sayori sea *su* hija, después de todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8885
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f6b4b9d8:

    # s casual smile "Likewise, Atsuko. Thank you for understanding." with dissolve
    s casual smile "Igual a usted, Atsuko. Gracias por entender." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8944
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_26905610:

    # s sleeptalk noblush "I will live. Let us just leave it at that." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk noblush "Viviré. Dejémoslo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8945
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_391dc832:

    # "Still, Sayori simply shakes her head dismissively before turning to face me as her expression becomes serious."
    "Aun así, Sayori simplemente sacude la cabeza despectivamente para luego voltear a verme con una expresión más seria."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8946
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0b28170d:

    # s casual_handup frown_right "Besides, we do not have much time so let us get down to business." with dissolve
    s casual_handup frown_right "Además, no gozamos de mucho tiempo, así que comencemos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8948
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a7bbe933:

    # "Right. The very reason we came here is buried in my pants pocket as I move to grasp it in my hand." with dissolve
    "Cierto. La razón por la que estamos aquí está guardada en el bolsillo de mi pantalón, encima del cual ahora pongo mi mano." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8952
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fd7d0ed2:

    # s concerned_right "Are you... having second thoughts, perchance?" with dissolve
    s concerned_right "¿Estás... dudando ahora, quizás?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8953
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_07e77b98:

    # "All my hard work and determination is instilled in this device. A device that Sayori strongly believes can control minds and I..."
    "Todo mi arduo trabajo y determinación están plasmados en este dispositivo que Sayori cree fuertemente que puede controlar mentes y yo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8957
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_514e9da6:

    # "... and I simply smile as I pass it over to her waiting hands." with dissolve
    "... y yo simplemente sonrío y lo pongo en sus manos abiertas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8958
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_34e97e9f:

    # ks casual smile "No, it's fine. Let's do what we came here to do."
    ks casual smile "No, descuida. Hagamos lo que vinimos a hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8959
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_44df7877:

    # "After all, I already made my decision at the arcade and Sayori's been through enough as it is."
    "Después de todo, ya tomé mi decisión en el arcade y Sayori ya pasó por suficiente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8960
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7ec4938e:

    # "And besides, it's not like she can actually control my mind with this thing."
    "Además, no es como si realmente pudiera controlar mi mente con esa cosa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8961
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d7dd9fc5:

    # s "Very well. Then Kyou, I would like you to lay down on the bed and we can get started."
    s "Muy bien, Entonces, Kyou, quisiera que te recuestes en la cama y podemos comenzar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8962
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6de00524:

    # "... Right?"
    "... ¿Verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8964
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1ce784ce:

    # s concerned "Uh, if that is okay with you, Nozomi?" with dissolve
    s concerned "Eh, ¿si eso no te causa molestia, Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8965
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_69373eef:

    # n surprised "Oh, sure. Go ahead, Kyou." with dissolve
    n surprised "Oh, claro. Adelante, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8974
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8c80a1d7:

    # "Nozomi steps aside and, with a glance at them both, I do as I'm asked."
    "Nozomi se hace a un lado y, dándoles una mirada a ambas, hago lo que se me pide."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9018
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_90b8c3da:

    # "Sure feels odd, setting myself up like this. I never expected anyone would try hypnotizing me, and I sure didn't think I'd want anyone to."
    "Sí que se siente raro ponerme en esta posición. Nunca esperé que nadie intentara hipnotizarme, y definitivamente nunca pensé que querría que alguien lo hiciera."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9023
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9f43b4ca:

    # n neutral_side "So, um... what's the plan, Sayori? Do you know what you're doing?"
    n neutral_side "Entonces, em... ¿cuál es el plan, Sayori? ¿Sabes lo que estás haciendo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9020
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fa2963a3:

    # "And man, Nozomi's bed feels way softer than mine."
    "Y vaya, la cama de Nozomi se siente mucho más suabe que la mía."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9021
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_96fea898:

    # s smile "This is very much out of my realm of experience, but... yes. Sort of." with dissolve
    s smile "Esto ciertamente escapa mi experiencia, pero sí. Algo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9022
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_006cf68c:

    # "Kinda smells nicer too..."
    "Creo que también huele mejor..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9029
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b3b00acd:

    # n smile_side "Okay well, I don't want to disturb you two so I'll just stand over here. Let me know if you need me for anything, okay?"
    n smile_side "De acuerdo, no quiero molestarlos así que solo me pararé aquí. Dime si me necesitas por cualquier cosa, ¿sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9025
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_98cc2e06:

    # "But as pleasant as this feels, I know I can't get distracted."
    "Pero por placentero que sea, sé que no puedo distraerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9032
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4701afad:

    # s "Thank you, Nozomi. There is something we should discuss soon but for now, I would like you to observe us." with dissolve
    s "Gracias, Nozomi. Hay algo que tendremos que discutir pronto, pero por ahora, quisiera que nos observes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9027
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d6b0a70f:

    # "Sayori's standing over me now; my penlight held aloft as she begins to address me."
    "Sayori está ahora sobre mí; con mi linterna en el aire, comienza a hablarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9028
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_32c2c64f:

    # s smile_right "So Kyou, I shall attempt to hypnotize you with this penlight and, should I succeed, will aim to resolve the situation as we discussed." with dissolve
    s smile_right "Entonces, Kyou, intentaré hipnotizarte con esta linterna y, de tener éxito, buscaré resolver la situación como discutimos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9029
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7c51fb7b:

    # "Resolve it by controlling my mind? That's what she means, right?"
    "¿Resolverla controlando mi mente? Eso es lo que quiere decir, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9031
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d71b6cf2:

    # s neutral_right "In the process of doing so, I will prove or disprove conclusively that this form of hypnosis you created is capable of surpassing the human will." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "En el proceso, demostraré o desmentiré de manera conclusiva que este método de hipnosis que creaste es capaz de sobrepasar el libre albedrio humano." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9032
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f8c21f09:

    # "And I'm really going to let her try it..."
    "Y en serio voy a dejarla intentarlo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9033
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4779097e:

    # s neutral "Should all go according to my plan, neither I nor anyone else will live in fear of this phenomenon ever again. I will \"fix\" this, as you so desired this morning." with dissolve
    s neutral "Si todo va de acuerdo al plan, ni yo ni nadie más volverá a vivir con miedo de este fenómeno. Voy a \"arreglar\" esto, como deseabas esta mañana." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9034
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8c7dc9fa:

    # s neutral_right "And you do still desire such an outcome, correct?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Y ese continúa siendo tu deseo, ¿correcto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9046
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_929fc005:

    # ks casual confused "Well... yeah. I wouldn't be doing this if I didn't, right?"
    ks casual confused "Pues... sí. No estaría haciendo esto si no, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9039
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6ab55251:

    # "Sayori notes my response and nods, seeming to regard me with all the coolness of a doctor assessing a patient."
    "Sayori asiente ante mi respuesta, aparentemente dirigiéndose a mí con toda la calma de una doctora atendiendo a un paciente."


# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9049
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b7ba69ec:

    # s "Now... {w=1.0}{nw}"
    s "Ahora... {w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9052
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f2e4b245:

    # extend "{cps=10}awwwnn...{/cps}"
    extend "{cps=10}uuaaa...{/cps}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9041
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_895808ab:

    # "At least until she yawned again. Makes me wonder which of us is gonna fall asleep first..."
    "Al menos hasta que vuelve a bostezar. Me hace preguntarme quién de los dos se dormirá primero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9043
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_deb6084d:

    # s neutral_right "Now I feel I should warn you that you may experience some discomfort during the process. But please do not worry. I can guarantee no harm will come to you." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Ahora debo advertirte que puede que experimentes algo de incomodidad durante el proceso. Pero, por favor, no te preocupes. Te garantizo que no sufrirás ningún daño." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9044
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_97269238:

    # "And now she sounds like... damn, why am I feeling like a guinea pig in an unethical experiment all of a sudden?"
    "Y ahora suena como... diablos, ¿por qué me siento como un conejillo de indias en un experimento antiético de repente?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9045
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_70f076bf:

    # s smirk_right "Ehehe... Does my prattle make you anxious? Good. Keep that feeling as we begin..." with dissolve
    s smirk_right "Ejeje... ¿mis palabras te ponen nervioso? Bien. Conserva ese sentimiento mientras comenzamos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9047
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e799a1cd:

    # "Before I can utter a retort, Sayori flips the switch of the penlight and I'm immediately blasted by a flash of its light..."
    "Antes de poder pronunciar una respuesta, Sayori mueve el interruptor de la linterna e inmediatamente me azota un destello de su luz..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9049
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7e299f91:

    # s surprised_right "As I recall, the technique is for me to pass the beam back and forth like so." with dissolve
    s surprised_right "Por lo que recuerdo, la técnica consiste en pasar el haz de un lado a otro justo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9051
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_892c81c0:

    # "She flashes the light in my eyes a second time and I'm already seeing a dazzling array of spots and patterns."
    "Desliza la luz por mis ojos por segunda vez e inmediatamente me deslumbra una gama de puntos y patrones."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9052
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_521bef30:

    # s "And for you to simply listen to me. For you to focus on this captivating little creation of yours."
    s "Y que simplemente me escuches. Que te enfoques en esta cautivante creación tuya."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9054
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_97b0d849:

    # "I mean, it shouldn't surprise me. I'm the one who put them there, and yet..."
    "Digo, no debería sorprenderme. Fui yo quien los puso ahí, y sin embargo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9055
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6f012257:

    # s smile_right "And it is captivating, is it not? Simply take it all in." with dissolve
    s smile_right "Y sí que es cautivante, ¿no lo crees? Simplemente aprécialo con detenimiento." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9056
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_396290ac:

    # "And yet I can't help but wonder about them."
    "Y sin embargo no puedo evitar sentir curiosidad sobre ellos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9060
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bb86bb4b:

    # s "Fully immerse yourself in the warm glow of the light."
    s "Sumérgete por completo en el cálido brillo de la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9063
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b9d70315:

    # s "Allow yourself to see every detail it impresses upon you."
    s "Déjate llevar y mira cada detalle que se genera ante ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9064
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fb7dbe52:

    # "This is what made Sayori go so deep into trance and accept that she could become a different person?"
    "¿Esto es lo que hizo que Sayori callera tan profundo en trance y aceptara que podía convertirse en otra persona?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9067
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7dc5cb40:

    # s "Let it consume your every thought, and..."
    s "Deja que consuma todo pensamiento, y..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9070
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8237f76b:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "Awww... become your entire focus now." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Uuaaa... se vuelva el centro de toda tu atención." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9071
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f65963bc:

    # "This is... uhh, what was I even thinking about? Well, never mind."
    "Esto es... emm... ¿en qué estaba pensando? Bueno, ¿qué importa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9074
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_388093d5:

    # s sleeptalk "Becoming so focused upon this light, that you may notice you are becoming tired. You may find yourself wanting to blink more and more."
    s sleeptalk "Y te concentras tanto en esta luz que puede que notes que empiezas a sentirte cansado. Puede que quieras parpadear más y más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9075
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e18835eb:

    # "I need to focus. Even though it's... hard..."
    "Debo concentrarme. Aunque sea... difícil..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9079
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8893529f:

    # s "And that's only natural. It's natural to feel so tired when one is so completely focused as you are."
    s "Y eso es natural. Es natural sentirte así de cansado cuando te concentras completamente en algo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9081
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e9440781:

    # "It's hard... to keep my eyes open."
    "Es difícil... mantener los ojos abiertos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9085
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4d616552:

    # s "Feeling more and more tired, every time you blink."
    s "Te sientes más y más cansado, cada vez que parpadeas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9086
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_64ae7f60:

    # "Hard to... think..."
    "Difícil... pensar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9090
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9bcd1fd1:

    # s "And... mrrrn, with every blink you make, as you become more and more... t-tired, you will naturally wonder how good it would feel..."
    s "Y... mmnn, con cada parpadeo, al sentirte más y más... c-cansado, naturalmente te preguntarás lo bien que se sentiría... "

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9094
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5097c3f7:

    # s "... if you were to simply keep those tired eyelids closed."
    s "... si sencillamente mantuvieras esos cansados ojos cerrados."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9096
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9964e9b1:

    # s "Feeling good. Feeling relaxed. Feeling ready to let your every conscious thought go..."
    s "Te sientes bien. Te sientes relajado. Te sientes listo para dejar ir todos tus pensamientos conscientes..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9099
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_da0bb9b6:

    # s "Now. Sleep."
    s "Ahora. Duerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9107
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_14b92c76:

    # s "-nd Now. Thoughts returning, Kyou. Come back to us."
    s "-ora. Tus pensamientos regresan, Kyou. Vuelve con nosotras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9108
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b74df06e:

    # "I find myself drawing a deep, shuddered breath as I suddenly find myself standing over..."
    "Respiro profunda y temblorosamente, encontrándome repentinamente de pie."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9110
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_023540a4:

    # ks casual confused "S-Sayori? What...?"
    ks casual confused "¿S-Sayori? ¿Qué...?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9111
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d9f7f634:

    # "I'm standing? When did I get off the bed? I was just lying there while Sayori was..."
    "¿Estoy de pie? ¿Cuándo me levanté de la cama? Estaba ahí acostado mientras Sayori estaba..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9112
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ced46c04:

    # n neutral_right "Well he certainly doesn't seem to remember, does he?" with dissolve
    n neutral_right "Bueno, ciertamente no parece recordar, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9113
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c5329a20:

    # "While she was hypnotizing me... right."
    "Mientras estaba hipnotizándome... cierto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9114
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fdee4bad:

    # s casual_folded "Indeed. Kyou, could you confirm to us that you have no recollection of the last twenty minutes?" with dissolve
    s casual_folded "En efecto. Kyou, ¿puedes confirmarnos que no tienes memoria de los últimos veinte minutos?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9116
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e8110bb8:

    # ks confused "T-twenty minutes? What?" with dissolve
    ks confused "¿V-veinte minutos? ¿Qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9117
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fad85eca:

    # "{cps=15}I gotta scratch my head here and... {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"
    "{cps=15}Me rasco la cabeza y... {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9120
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b00d496d:

    # ks surprised "Hah!"
    ks surprised "¡Ah!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9121
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_73490b0a:

    # "I just tapped myself on the head with... with my penlight? When did I get this back?"
    "Me acabo de tocar la cabeza con... ¿con mi linterna? ¿Cuándo recuperé esto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9124
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2949536b:

    # n concerned "Kyou? Calm down, okay? It's fine if you don't remember." with dissolve
    n concerned "¿Kyou? Cálmate, ¿sí? Está bien si no recuerdas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9125
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bb3ce617:

    # s concerned_right "Better than fine, actually. Everything appears to be proceeding exactly as I expected." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Mejor que bien, de hecho. Todo aparenta haber procedido exactamente como esperaba." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9126
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_94291e51:

    # "Holding my head in one hand, I sigh and nod as I recall what Sayori was trying to prove with me."
    "Con una mano en la cabeza, suspiro y asiento, recordando lo que Sayori intentaba demostrar conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9127
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7162b2c7:

    # s "That fear you feel? The realization that you lost your entire sense of agency that defies all rational explanation?"
    s "¿Ese miedo que sientes? ¿El descubrimiento de que perdiste enteramente tu sentido de agencia, desafiando toda explicación racional?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9128
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a2fa1af6:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "Believe me, I am familiar." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Créeme, estoy familiarizada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9129
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_85aae6e6:

    # "Man, I don't know if I'm afraid like she thinks I am, but if that's what it feels like to be hypnotized? It's a little freaky, that's for sure."
    "Caray, no sé si estoy tan asustado como cree que estoy, pero si así es como se siente ser hipnotizado, sí es un tanto inquietante, no lo voy a negar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9131
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a12cf0a1:

    # ks sigh "Yeah... So what the hell happened just now?"
    ks sigh "Seh... ¿Y qué fue lo que acaba de pasar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9134
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3e001c98:

    # "The pair of them exchange looks like they're barely able to explain to themselves what they've just seen, let alone to me." with dissolve
    "El par intercambia miradas como si apenas pudieran comprender ellas mismas lo que acaban de ver, ya ni hablemos de explicármelo a mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9135
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d7425aeb:

    # "But eventually it's Nozomi who clears her throat as she begins to answer me."
    "Pero eventualmente es Nozomi quien se aclara la garganta y comienza a responderme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9166
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4b5fa80e:

    # n sad "Okay well, when Sayori and I were sure you were deep in trance, she gave you some instructions to take the penlight and hypnotize her just like you did before." with dissolve
    n sad "De acuerdo, pues, cuando Sayori y yo estábamos seguras de que estabas en un profundo trance, te dio instrucciones de tomar la linterna e hipnotizarla como hiciste antes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9171
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_64c87773:

    # n "And that when you did, you'd remove the sleeping and personality-switching suggestions you gave her \"to the best of your ability\" before waking her up and..." with dissolve
    n "Y que cuando lo hicieras, removerías las sugestiones de sueño y cambio de personalidad que le diste \"como te sea posible\" antes de despertarla y..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9143
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e8495914:

    # s casual_handup "And awaiting further instructions, yes." with dissolve
    s casual_handup "Y luego esperaras por subsecuentes instrucciones, sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9144
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_44690b0b:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "Oh my god, Kyou, you should have seen yourself. It was like watching some kind of robot running a program." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Oh, por Dios, Kyou, debiste haberte visto. Fue como ver alguna especie de robot ejecutando un programa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9145
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_64c521bc:

    # n shocked "The moment Sayori clicked her fingers you snatched the penlight back and you just... you just did it! You didn't even hesitate for a second!" with dissolve
    n shocked "¡Tan pronto Sayori chasqueó los dedos, le arrebataste la linterna y... lo hiciste así como así! ¡No dudaste ni por un segundo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9146
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1186d3b0:

    # ks confused "I... seriously?!"
    ks confused "Yo... ¡¿en serio?!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9147
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3d777f92:

    # "Okay, this all just got even freakier, I'll admit."
    "De acuerdo, esto se puso todavía más inquietante, lo admito."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9149
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f4a864ea:

    # n "Yeah. It was kind of incredible watching you from the sidelines. A hypnotized hypnotist..." with dissolve
    n "Sí. Fue un tanto increíble verlos desde aquí. Un hipnotista hipnotizado..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9150
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cb0eec01:

    # "That really happened? I have no reason to think either of them could be lying."
    "¿Eso en serio pasó? No tengo razón para creer que alguna de ellas pudiera estar mintiendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:8901
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f7cd5685:

    # n sad_closed "I've never seen anything like it." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Nunca había visto nada así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9152
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7b23ec20:

    # "And yet, I'm not entirely sure I can accept it."
    "Y aun así, no estoy del todo seguro de poder aceptarlo."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2023-06-29 18:15

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9131
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3340005e:

    # "While she was trying to hypnotize me... right."
    "Mientras estaba intentando hipnotizarme... cierto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9143
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_34eb7150:

    # s concerned_right "Indeed. You were asked to forget, after all." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "En efecto. Se te instruyó que olvidaras, después de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9144
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_76b9fb97:

    # "Holding my head in one hand, I sigh as I recall what Sayori was trying to prove with me."
    "Con una mano en la cabeza, suspiro, recordando lo que Sayori estaba intentando probar conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9145
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1614eaf4:

    # ks "So... you did it? You actually hypnotized me?"
    ks "O sea que... ¿lo hiciste? ¿En verdad me hipnotizaste?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9148
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_a20068f1:

    # "Sayori simply smiles triumphantly, as if I needed more evidence for my eyes." with dissolve
    "Sayori simplemente sonríe triunfante, como si necesitara más evidencia ante mis ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9155
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_397b57d5:

    # s "It appears everything is proceeding exactly as I hoped. You really don't remember a thing, do you?" with dissolve
    s "Todo aparenta haber procedido exactamente como esperaba. En serio no recuerdas nada, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9177
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7b89633c:

    # "Whoa, is this what it feels like to be hypnotized? It's a little freaky, that's for sure."
    "Guau, ¿así se siente ser hipnotizado? Sí es un poco inquietante, no lo voy a negar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9179
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_44cb5af9:

    # n "Yeah. It was kind of incredible watching you from the sidelines. A hypnotized hypnotist performing on the very person who hypnotized them..." with dissolve
    n "Sí. Fue un tanto increíble verlos de cerca. Un hipnotista hipnotizado actuando sobre la misma persona que lo hipnotizó..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9181
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_3dbe3103:

    # "That really happened? I did all that under hypnosis?"
    "¿Eso en serio pasó? ¿Hice todo eso bajo hipnosis?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9183
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_63766b51:

    # "Gotta admit, I'm having a hard time wrapping my head around this..."
    "Debo admitir que me está costando asimilar la idea..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9190
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fc907751:

    # s casual "I can see that you are not entirely believing of Nozomi's account. And to be fair, I was not conscious to witness it myself." with dissolve
    s casual "Puedo ver que no le das crédito completamente a al testimonio de Nozomi. Y para ser justos, yo misma no estuve consciente para presenciar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9198
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4f833fef:

    # s neutral_right "But proving it, Kyou, is a simple matter. You have only to say two words and we can erase all doubt right here and now." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Pero probarlo, Kyou, será trivial. Simplemente debes decir tres palabras que borrarán toda duda aquí y ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9199
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_37d827eb:

    # s frown_right "And I am anxious to reach a resolution. So let us prove it together." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Y ansío alcanzar una resolución. Así que probémoslo juntos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9201
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c53a3731:

    # "I nod as I realize what she means."
    "Asiento con la cabeza, dándome cuenta de a qué se refiere."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9203
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d70de823:

    # ks "You want me to say it?" with dissolve
    ks "¿Quieres que lo diga?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9204
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_564f1351:

    # "That phrase. The one that left her so afraid of me since that day..."
    "Esa frase. La que le causó tanto temor de mí desde aquel día..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9205
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2fc4ee99:

    # s casual_folded "I want you to say it." with dissolve
    s casual_folded "Quiero que lo digas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9208
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_aa333db1:

    # "The one that's caused so much trouble... I take a deep breath, steeling myself before..."
    "La que ha causado tantos problemas... tomo aire, armándome de valor para luego..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9210
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_21377dbe:

    # ks "... Become [alt_name]."
    ks "... Conviértete en [alt_name]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9211
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ca69dfe4:

    # "Before I allow the dreaded phrase to leave my lips for Sayori to hear clear and true."
    "Para luego dejar que la temida frase salga de mis labios y llegue fuerte y claro a los oídos de Sayori."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9195
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5754602f:

    # s "..." with dissolve
    s "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9214
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_99963892:

    # s casual surprised_right "Hah..." with dissolve
    s casual surprised_right "Ah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9215
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2c3e5420:

    # n sad_side "Hah? Sayori, what happened?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Ah? Sayori, ¿qué pasó?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9216
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9fdd7558:

    # s casual_folded "Nothing..." with dissolve
    s casual_folded "Nada..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9218
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_074d1962:

    # "Sayori holds a hand to her cheek as she begins to giggle with relief."
    "Sayori se lleva una mano a la mejilla, riendo de alivio."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9219
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c6444f49:

    # s casual_handup laugh "Ahahaha, nothing has happened!" with dissolve
    s casual_handup laugh "¡Ajajaja, no pasó nada!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9220
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0e2e0362:

    # s happy "My mind is clear and Kyou's words have no longer hold power over me, I am certain." with dissolve
    s happy "Mi mente está limpia y las palabras de Kyou ya no tienen poder sobre mí, tengo certeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9221
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_44505fef:

    # "I release the breath I was holding as I witness the delight in Sayori's face. A delight that I know she, not \"[alt_name]\", is expressing."
    "Dejo salir el aliento que estaba sosteniendo, viendo el deleite en el rostro de Sayori. Un deleite que sé que ella, no \"[alt_name]\", está expresando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9222
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1addb705:

    # n sad_closed "Oh, thank goodness. When you got so excited I was fearing the worst." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Oh, gracias al cielo. Cuando te emocionaste, por un momento temí lo peor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9223
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b395a22d:

    # "But then that means..."
    "Pero eso significa..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9224
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_34fa874e:

    # s pout "Oh come now, Nozomi. Do you really consider me such a stick in the mud?" with dissolve
    s pout "Oh, vamos, Nozomi. ¿En verdad me consideras tan falta de vida?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9225
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0b29e374:

    # "That means I really was hypnotized into doing all that?"
    "¿Eso significa que sí fui hipnotizado e hice todo eso?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9226
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6c6f929b:

    # n happy "Eheh, sorry. But I'm really not used to seeing you like this." with dissolve
    n happy "Jeje, lo siento. Pero en serio no estoy acostumbrada a verte así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9227
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_73697c45:

    # n smile_side "At least not until today, with the arcade and the, um..." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Al menos no hasta hoy, con el arcade y la, em..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9228
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fe99ddeb:

    # "I hypnotized Sayori just now, with my penlight, and I don't remember a single thing?"
    "¿Acabo de hipnotizar a Sayori, con mi linterna, y no me acuerdo de nada?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9229
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0c3c46df:

    # n laugh "And the play-acting downstairs, ahahaha~" with dissolve
    n laugh "Y la actuación que diste ahí abajo, ajajaja." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9231
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e9f56f49:

    # s rolleyes "Urrgh, now why on earth did you bring that up?" with dissolve
    s rolleyes "Ayyy, ¿por qué tuviste que mencionarlo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9224
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_9bc7a34a:

    # n smile_side "Oh gosh, I could've sworn mom thought you'd gone crazy back there."
    n smile_side "Oh, cielos, podría haber jurado que mamá pensó que te habías vuelto loca."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9235
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1d54173e:

    # "Sayori, with nothing more than a penlight and a meagre understanding of hypnosis was able to perform a feat just as incredible as mine when I hypnotized her."
    "Sayori, sin nada más que una pluma linterna y un escaso entendimiento de la hipnosis, fue capaz de realizar una proeza tan increíble como la mía cuando la hipnoticé."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9237
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_163cc7ae:

    # s casual_handup sleeptalk "Yes... I fear I may never be able to look your mother in the eye ever again." with dissolve
    s casual_handup sleeptalk "Sí... Temo que tal vez nunca pueda volver a ver a tu madre a los ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9239
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_391202a3:

    # "That's... what does this mean? Don't tell me she's right about my penlight being a mind control device."
    "Eso... ¿qué significa eso? No me digas que tiene razón y mi linterna es un dispositivo de control mental."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9231
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_57f4744f:

    # n sad_closed "Oh Sayori no, don't think like that."
    n sad_closed "Oh, Sayori, no, no pienses así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9242
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_4236b06e:

    # "That's just... that's just nuts. It's too absurd to even think about."
    "Pero eso... esto no tiene sentido. Es demasiado absurdo para siquiera pensarlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9243
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_340538cc:

    # s casual happy "Mrrrnn... what have I become..." with dissolve
    s casual happy "Mmmnn... ¿en qué me he convertido?..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9241
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_20b22146:

    # n "Ehehe come on, you. Snap out of it~"
    n "Jejeje, vamos. No seas dramática."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9250
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5da88342:

    # "Nozomi moves to hug her friend, and as they chuckle together with fondness I'm left shaking my head."
    "Nozomi abraza a su amiga, y mientras ríen con cariño, no puedo evitar sacudir la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9243
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_55ac26e1:

    # ks casual confused "I don't believe it..."
    ks casual confused "No lo creo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9258
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_dbc0eaa8:

    # n "Hm? What don't you believe?" with dissolve
    n "¿Mm? ¿Qué es lo que no crees?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9259
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2c48b366:

    # "There's a rational explanation for all of this."
    "Hay una explicación racional para todo esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9260
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_941c8ec9:

    # ks neutral "Look, it's great that you feel in control of yourself again. That was always the main thing about doing all this."
    ks neutral "Mira, es estupendo que te sientas en control de ti misma otra vez. Ese era el objetivo de todo esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9261
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_f455b706:

    # ks "But Sayori, if this is supposed to prove this penlight is literally controlling our minds I really don't see how."
    ks "Pero, Sayori, si esto se supone que sea prueba de que esta linterna literalmente está controlando nuestras mentes, de verdad no veo cómo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9263
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_48d32ceb:

    # n sad_closed "Oh, Kyou..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Oh, Kyou..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9264
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fd75f45d:

    # "Yeah, you sigh all you want. That doesn't change the facts."
    "Sí, suspiren todo lo que quieran. Eso no cambia los hechos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9265
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c08b1cd8:

    # ks frown "What? It's just the truth."
    ks frown "¿Qué? Es la verdad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9267
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_81234489:

    # n frown "Sayori managed to hypnotize you so deeply that you were basically hers to command and you don't even remember her doing it." with dissolve
    n frown "Sayori logró hipnotizarte tan profundamente que básicamente estabas bajo sus órdenes y ni siquiera lo recuerdas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9268
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0c7c137b:

    # n frown_side "She did it despite barely knowing anything about the process, not to mention the fact you'd never been hypnotized before." with dissolve
    n frown_side "Lo hizo a pesar de no saber casi nada del proceso, sin mencionar el hecho de que nunca antes habías sido hipnotizado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9272
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_c420b2c0:

    # n "The only thing she had was your penlight!" with dissolve
    n "¡Lo único que tenía era tu linterna!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9273
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_024f7850:

    # ks frown "\"Hers to command\"? That's a little dramatic, don't you think?"
    ks frown "¿\"Bajo sus órdenes\"? Un poco dramático, ¿no crees?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9274
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_020f3d43:

    # n irritated "Look, do you really think she could've had that kind of sway over you if that penlight wasn't as dangerous as she said it is?" with dissolve
    n irritated "Mira, ¿en serio crees que habría podido tener esa clase de influencia sobre ti si esa linterna no fuera tan peligrosa como dijo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9276
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d895614e:

    # ks sigh "Hey, it might be enough to convince you, but that really only proves one thing." with dissolve
    ks sigh "Oye, tal vez sea suficiente para convencerte a ti, pero eso solo prueba una cosa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9277
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_1627f0fb:

    # n frown "And that is?" with dissolve
    n frown "¿Qué cosa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9278
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0f053b68:

    # "I fold my arms and draw a breath through my nose."
    "Me cruzo de brazos e inhalo por la nariz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9279
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_eb8074eb:

    # "It's a little embarrassing to admit, but it's the only rationalization that makes any goddamned sense."
    "Es un poco vergonzoso admitirlo, pero es la única racionalización que tiene el más mínimo maldito sentido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9280
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2bfcf1c9:

    # ks sigh "Well, turns out I'm just as easy to hypnotize as Sayori. We're both in that top category of super-suggestible people."
    ks sigh "Bueno, resulta que soy tan fácil de hipnotizar como Sayori. Ambos somos personas supersugestionables de alta categoría."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9282
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_cab6827d:

    # n "Oh, for the love of..." with dissolve
    n "Oh, por el amor de..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9283
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_30edc0f4:

    # n frown "Do you really think you're *both* so hypnotically suggestible that you'll go along with anything a hypnotist tells you? How likely do you think that is?" with dissolve
    n frown "¿En serio crees que *ambos* son tan hipnóticamente sugestionables que harán lo que sea que les diga un hipnotista? ¿Qué tan probable es eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9284
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_19cc8338:

    # ks frown "More likely than some cheap penlight being able to control minds like it was out of some hokey thriller novel, that's for sure."
    ks frown "Más probable que una linterna barata capaz de controlar mentes como si viniera de una novela de suspenso, eso seguro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9288
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_944a4c3b:

    # n "Oooh, you... " with dissolve
    n "Oooh, pero si..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9281
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bf6786d6:

    # n determined "After everything we've seen today you're still not convinced? I can't believe you're being so stubborn." with dissolve
    n determined "Después de todo lo que hemos visto hoy, ¿aún no estás convencido? No puedo creer que seas tan obstinado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9290
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e09a630f:

    # s casual_folded frown_right "Be that as it may, I will concede that you have a point, Kyou." with dissolve
    s casual_folded frown_right "Sea como fuere, he de conceder que tienes un punto, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9291
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_2ba66ce6:

    # n sigh "Ugh, maybe. But still..." with dissolve
    n sigh "Ay, tal vez. Pero aun así..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9292
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_e8602488:

    # s neutral "It is fine. An extraordinary claim such as mine requires extraordinary evidence, after all." with dissolve
    s neutral "Está bien. Una afirmación extraordinaria tal como la mía requiere evidencia extraordinaria, después de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9286
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ca18bd2c:

    # s sleep "So let us entertain that you and I both possess an extreme level of affinity for entering a hypnotic state and absorbing suggestions into our subconscious." with dissolve
    s sleep "Así que supongamos que ambos tenemos una extrema afinidad para entrar a un trance hipnótico y absorber sugestiones en nuestro subconsciente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9297
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b608e834:

    # s neutral_right "Just as you have asserted that I wished on some level for the behaviours you effected on me via hypnosis, the same could be said for you." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Así como propusiste que yo deseé en cierto grado el comportamiento que causaste en mí vía hipnosis, lo mismo podría decirse de ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9298
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b8442930:

    # s concerned_right "After all, you were sincere in your desire to fix my situation, were you not?" with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Al fin y al cabo, fuiste sincero en tu deseo de arreglar mi situación, ¿no es así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9299
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_97967074:

    # ks neutral "Well, yeah. Of course I was."
    ks neutral "Pues, sí. Claro que sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9300
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_831b7ae2:

    # s casual neutral "If we were to assume your level of hypnotic suggestibility is comparable to mine, then it follows you would have little issue in carrying out the behaviours I impressed upon you." with dissolve
    s casual neutral "Si asumimos que tu nivel de sugestionabilidad es comparable al mío, es razonable que no tendrías problemas en adoptar los comportamientos que implanté en ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9301
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8331bd71:

    # s neutral_right "It is not \"mind control\" to persuade you to do something you were already predisposed to doing." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "No es \"control mental\" persuadirte a hacer algo que ya estabas predispuesto a hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9302
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_25e8ba01:

    # ks "Exactly. That's exactly my point."
    ks "Exacto. Eso es justo lo que intento decir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9321
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_fb889bfb:

    # "I hold the penlight up to look at it once again."
    "Alzo mi linterna para mirarla una vez más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9322
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_6bf708bb:

    # "This small, unassuming, cheap little penlight that only differs from any other because of a few insignificant little markings I added to the bulb and the lens."
    "Esta pequeña, aburrida y barata linternita que solo difiere de cualquier otra por unas cuantas marcas insignificantes que les añadí al foco y la lente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9323
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_7159ac0d:

    # "The light's great at catching the attention, no doubt about that, but to imagine I could use it to alter brain chemistry? Override the human will into doing anything I wanted?"
    "La luz es excelente capturando la atención, sí, pero ¿imaginar que pudiera usarla para alterar la química cerebral? ¿Sobrescribir la voluntad humana a mi antojo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9327
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d823ad6b:

    # n "So I guess now is the moment of truth, huh, Sayori?" with dissolve
    n "Entonces creo que es el momento de la verdad, ¿eh, Sayori?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9328
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_febe70c9:

    # "It's impossible."
    "Es imposible."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9329
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_aca7c97d:

    # s concerned "I-indeed. It's time..." with dissolve
    s concerned "E-en efecto. Es el momento..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9330
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_bf23b2e9:

    # "My eyes drift from the penlight to notice the girls looking to each other with an expression I can't quite understand."
    "Mis ojos se mueven de la linterna a las chicas que se miran con una expresión que no entiendo del todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9331
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_d0cad353:

    # "For some reason it makes me a little anxious."
    "Por alguna razón, me pone nervioso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9323
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_37a92dc7:

    # ks confused "What do you mean? What are you talking about?"
    ks confused "¿A qué se refieren? ¿De qué hablan?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9334
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_df0e3783:

    # s casual_handup frown_right "... Break the penlight, Kyou." with dissolve
    s casual_handup frown_right "... Rompe la linterna, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9336
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_33c5a1e3:

    # "Before I can say anything I'm stunned by the sight of these two hands in front of me."
    "Antes de poder decir nada, veo atónito un par de manos frente a mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9337
