# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9433
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_8d2e9354:

    # "Another voice interjects, startling the three of us as we look around to see none other than..." with dissolve
    "Otra voz se manifiesta, haciendo a los tres sobresaltarnos y voltear para ver a nada menos que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9439
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_ac5c398f:

    # nm sleep "I know, I know, I shouldn't eavesdrop..." with dissolve
    nm sleep "Lo sé, lo sé, no debería espiar..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9440
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_5d74f6ff:

    # "Oh geez, how long has she been listening to us? Did she have her ear pressed to the door this whole time or what?"
    "Oh, cielos, ¿cuánto tiempo lleva escuchándonos? ¿Tenía la oreja contra la puerta todo este tiempo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9442
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_0b1bea59:

    # nm neutral_side "And it's like I said before; you three are grown-ups. You don't need an overbearing busy-body like me poking my nose into everything." with dissolve
    nm neutral_side "Y como dije antes, los tres son adultos. No necesitan a una entrometida prepotente como yo metiendo sus narices en todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9443
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_27adeeb8:

    # nm "But I'm sorry, I've been worrying all morning and, hand on my heart, I don't think I can let this be."
    nm "Pero lo siento, llevo toda la mañana preocupada y, con la mano en el corazón, no creo poder ignorar esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9444
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Alter_Switch_b222201a:

    # n "W-what do you mean?"
    n "¿Q-qué quieres decir?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9445
