translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_851c23cc:

    # "Just as I suspected, triggering her post-hypnotic suggestion to stay calm over and over left her mind floating in and out of a half-tranced state."
    "Tal como sospechaba, activar su sugestión posthipnótica para permanecer calmada una y otra vez hizo que su mente estuviera entrando y saliendo de un estado de semi-trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9644
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_ba8776ca:

    # ks neutral "Aaaallll the way down now. Falling into a deep, relaxing sleep. Hearing only my voice. Listening only to my suggestions."
    ks neutral "Muuuuyyyy profundo. Déjate caer en un profundo y relajante sueño. Escuchando solamente mi voz. Escuchando solamente mis sugestiones."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9645
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_d8647830:

    # "And with a little encouragement, that reeling mind of hers fell right back into a trance that seems every bit as deep as the ones I subjected her to with my penlight."
    "Y con un pequeño empujón, su mente tambaleante cayó directamente de regreso a un trance que parece tan profundo como aquellos que le induje con mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9646
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_ff73dfb1:

