    # "Hell, this barely counts as me getting revenge; I'm practically doing you a favour here."
    "Vaya, esto apenas si contará como venganza; prácticamente te estoy haciendo un favor."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9706
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_a15dc3e1:

    # h sleeptalk "Yeah... polite an'... courteous..." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Sí... educada y... cortés..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9708
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_28817c88:

    # ks "Wonderful. Now on a count of five, you're going to awaken from this hypnotic trance, feeling fully refreshed and accepting everything you were told." with dissolve
    ks "Maravilloso. Y ahora, a la cuenta de cinco, despertarás de este trance hipnótico, sintiéndote fresca y aceptando todo lo que te dije." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9709
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_70c1a16e:

    # ks "So one, two... slowly regaining consciousness, beginning to feel the wind on your face."
    ks "En uno, dos... recuperas lentamente la consciencia, comenzando a sentir el viento en tu rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9710
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_d0fe4470:

    # ks "Three, taking a nice deep breath... four, feeling your eyelids begin to open and..."
    ks "Tres, respira profundo... cuatro, siente cómo tus párpados comienzan a abrirse y..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9713
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_8e8bac69:

    # ks "Five, wide awake and fully refreshed." with dissolve
    ks "Cinco, despierta, fresca y alerta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9714
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_3573474e:

    # h "{size=16}Mmmnh...{/size}"
    h "{size=16}Mmmnn...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9716
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_fd29c99d:

    # "Hiroko's eyes begin to glimmer in the moonlight as she awakens before my eyes."
    "Los ojos de Hiroko brillan bajo la luz de la luna al despertar ante mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9717
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_ebdc6813:

    # "And just as she seems to regain her senses, I pull my penlight from out of my pocket in front of her as I flash her a confident grin."
    "Y justo cuando parece volver en sí, saco la linterna de mi bolsillo con una confiada sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9718
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_3493edbe:

    # ks smirk "Glad you decided to be reasonable after all, Hiroko."
    ks smirk "Me alegra que al final decidieras ser razonable, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9720
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_0be4bf48:

    # h "Huhhh...?" with dissolve
    h "¿Eeeeh...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9722
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_24e5e38a:

    # "It takes her a moment, but as I wiggle my penlight in front of her eyes a polite smile beings to spread across her lips as she realizes what I'm getting at." with dissolve
    "Le toma un momento, pero cuando meneo la linterna frente a sus ojos, una sonrisa cortés se dibuja en sus labios al darse cuenta de lo que quiero decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9723
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_4e7e96ad:

    # h "Ohh... yeah, no problem."
    h "Ooh... sí, no hay problema."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:10972
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_ea786fa6:

    # "And I'm pleased to note that there's not a hint of irritation to be found in those eyes that now look to me with an unfamiliar kindness."
    "Y me complace notar que no hay ni un rastro de irritación en esos ojos que ahora me miran con una inusual amabilidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9726
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_dcc34fc6:

    # h "We're square now anyways, so it's totally reasonable to give it back~" with dissolve
    h "Al fin y al cabo ya estamos a mano, así que es completamente razonable devolverla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9727
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_c204f578:

    # "I was sure that this would work, but witnessing her demeanor shift before my eyes is immensely gratifying all the same."
    "No tenía duda de que iba a funcionar, pero presenciar su cambio de comportamiento con mis propios ojos no deja de ser inmensamente gratificante."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9728
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_e6b9c218:

    # ks "Heh, glad to hear it. You really ran me ragged today, you little pipsqueak."
    ks "Je, me alegra oír eso. Sí que me tuviste dando vueltas todo el día, pequeña mequetrefe."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9730
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_7bd7ba05:

    # h "Ehehehe. H'yeah, thanks for putting up with me today. You really were a big help." with dissolve
    h "Ejejeje. Seh, gracias por aguantarme hoy. Me ayudaste mucho." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9732
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_886e043f:

    # "Yeah, I don't think she'll be menacing anyone for a while."
    "Sí, no creo que vaya a ser una amenaza para nadie por un tiempo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9733
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_9654ee29:

    # ks smile "Sure. Anyway, I'm gonna head out. Be nice to everyone at the tourney tomorrow, alright?"
    ks smile "Desde luego. En fin, yo ya me voy. Sé amable con todos en el torneo de mañana, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9735
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_aebeca93:

    # h "Yeah I will, but... Kyou?" with dissolve
    h "Por supuesto, pero... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9736
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_dfa106a6:

    # ks neutral "What is it?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué ocurre?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9738
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_53841f8b:

    # h "Does that mean you ain't coming? I kinda wanted you to watch me play." with dissolve
    h "¿Eso significa que no vas a venir? Tenía ganas de que me vieras jugar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9739
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_bcf6ea18:

    # "Huh? She wants me to..."
    "¿Eh? ¿Quiere que yo...?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9741
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_6685738c:

    # ks "Uhhh..."
    ks "Eeeh..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9742
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_4383e483:

    # "... Well, she would say that wouldn't she?"
    "... Bueno, o eso dice, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9744
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_a8fef634:

    # h "Y'know, just saying. You helped me a ton, so... it'd be cool if I can show you what all this was for." with dissolve
    h "Ya sabes, solo digo. Me ayudaste un montón, así que... sería genial poder mostrarte los resultados de todo esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9745
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_6928e481:

    # "It'd be the polite thing to say to someone who's been helping your ass all week."
    "Sería una descortesía no invitar a alguien que te estuvo ayudando toda la jodida semana."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9747
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_701b042a:

    # h "Plus, Nozo's throwing a lil' party for me afterward. Thought you might wanna come celebrate with us." with dissolve
    h "Además, Nozo dará una pequeña fiesta al final. Pensé que querrías venir a celebrar con nosotras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9748
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_7b6a29f0:

    # "There's... There's just no way she'd be saying any of this to me were it not for that."
    "Ella... ella nunca me diría esto si no fuera por eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9749
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_a5606484:

    # ks "Yeah, I... wasn't planning to, Hiroko."
    ks "Sí, no... no planeaba ir, Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9750
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_db591e46:

    # "And man, I wish she didn't bring up Nozomi. Just thinking about her face again is making my skin crawl."
    "Y caray, ojalá no hubiera mencionado a Nozomi. Solo pensar en su rostro hace que se me erice la piel."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9752
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_d8fc0647:

    # h "Suit yourself. But if you change your mind, you know where to find us~" with dissolve
    h "Como quieras. Pero si cambias de opinión, ya sabes dónde encontrarnos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9755
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_6631c6d9:

    # "Hiroko really did a number on my brain the other night, no doubt about that."
    "Hiroko de verdad logró tener un efecto en mi cerebro la otra noche, de eso no hay duda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9756
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_b8d16b45:

    # "I mean, that's why I couldn't let her keep the penlight a moment longer, right?"
    "Digo, es precisamente por eso que no podía dejarla conservar la linterna ni un segundo más, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9791
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_736c256b:

    # "There's no way I could let her keep something that can alter a person's very perceptions of reality whether they want it or not."
    "De ninguna manera puedo dejarla conservar algo que puede alterar la percepción de la realidad de una persona así lo quiera o no."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9794
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_356355ae:

    # "A device that stretches the boundaries of hypnosis beyond what anyone thought possible?"
    "¿Un dispositivo que estira los límites de la hipnosis más allá de lo que nadie creyó posible?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9795
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_f6b49a72:

    # "I can't let her have this again. No one else can have it."
    "No puedo dejar que vuelva a tener esto. Nadie más puede tenerlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9796
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_7c9acc04:

    # "No one else can be allowed to... to use it."
    "No puedo permitir que nadie más la... la use."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9797
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_e5a73182:

    # "Should I have even used it again, knowing what I know now?"
    "¿Debería haberla usado yo otra vez, sabiendo lo que sé ahora?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9802
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_326dcac1:

    # "Maybe Hiroko had it coming after all the shit she's put me and others through. She's a bully, that much I know for sure."
    "Puede que Hiroko se lo haya buscado después de la mierda por la que me hizo pasar. Es una brabucona, de eso estoy seguro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9803
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_25ab246a:

    # "But forcing her to fix herself with this thing? I have to admit it's a little messed up that I did that to her."
    "Pero ¿obligarla a arreglarse usando esta cosa? Debo admitir que no se siente del todo bien haberle hecho eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9804
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_3ebcce4c:

    # "I won't leave her like that for long. A week maybe, then I'll meet up with her again, lift that suggestion from her head and..."
    "No la dejaré así mucho tiempo. Una semana, tal vez, luego me volveré a reunir con ella, le quitaré esa sugestión de la cabeza y..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9806
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_91288474:

    # "... And then what? She'll see it was for her own good? Is that how I see it playing out?"
    "... ¿Y luego qué? ¿Verá que fue por su propio bien? ¿De verdad puedo esperar que eso pase?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9807
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_bd7255da:

    # "I'd have to put another suggestion in her head just to stop her from lashing out at me."
    "Tendré que poner otra sugestión en su cabeza para evitar que se abalance contra mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9808
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_bab94846:

    # "It'd be a permanent change to her reality, one she didn't want, but I don't think I'd have a choice."
    "Será un cambio permanente a su realidad, uno que ella no quería, pero no creo tener otra opción."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9809
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_832c4731:

    # "... Hell, what if NONE of this is permanent? I've started to believe it is, but the truth is I just don't know how much my penlight is doing to our minds."
    "... Es más, ¿qué tal si NADA de esto es permanente? He estado asumiendo que lo es, pero la verdad es que no sé qué tanto mi linterna les está haciendo a nuestras mentes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9810
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_517b0439:

    # "It's only been a few days since we hypnotized each other. But if it really doesn't last, then..."
    "Solo han pasado algunos días desde que nos hipnotizamos. Pero si en realidad no perdura, entonces..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9811
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_ef2d6c62:

    # "Then I'll stop seeing Nozomi as ugly, and Hiroko will realize what I did to her one way or another."
    "Entonces dejaré de ver fea a Nozomi, y Hiroko se dará cuenta de lo que le hice de una forma u otra."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:9814
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_Penlight_49474b33:

    # "One thing's for sure, I have to keep my guard up..."
    "Una cosa es segura, no puedo bajar la guardia..."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2024-05-01 13:39

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:42
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f2047e5c:

    # n smile "So where are we doing this? In there? {w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    n smile "¿Y en dónde lo haremos? ¿Por ahí? {w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:450
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_1be878fc_1:

    # n side irritated "To say nothing of all the times I caught you leering at me from afar when you thought you were being discreet." with dissolve
    n side irritated "Sin mencionar todas las veces que te atrapé viéndome a la distancia cuando pensabas que estabas siendo discreto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:127
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_1dbac321:

    # s irritated "If there is any attraction to be discussed here, it is distinctly of the one-sided and voyeuristic sort." with dissolve
    s irritated "Si hay alguna atracción de la qué discutir, es distintivamente del tipo unidireccional y voyerista." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:133
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_a33fd6c4:

    # s sleeptalk "She has lost her spirit. Her determination. Her drive to succeed." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Ha perdido su espíritu. Su determinación. Su impulso de victoria." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:154
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_70ecb270:

    # s casual_folded irritated "Okay Kyou, that is enough. I don't understand what you did to my friends exactly, but I know I'm getting dumber just listening to your self-serving justifications." with dissolve
    s casual_folded irritated "bien, Kyou, suficiente. No sé qué les hiciste a mis amigas exactamente, pero sí que me vuelvo más tonta al escuchar tus autocomplacientes justificaciones." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:161
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_44bc48b1:

    # "... As ridiculous as this talk of \"brainwashing\" is, it's obvious Nozomi believes what she's saying."
    "... Por ridícula que sea toda esta charla sobre \"lavado de cerebro\", es obvio que Nozomi sí cree lo que está diciendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:162
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_79c916f1:

    # "So what the hell is happening here? Some deep repression? Or regret about going along with me?"
    "Entonces ¿qué diablos está pasando aquí? ¿Alguna clase de represión profunda? ¿O arrepentimiento de lo que hizo conmigo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:169
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_bd793da2:

    # s frown_right "So here is what needs to happen. We all pay Hiroko a visit, you... hypnotize her again, or whatever it is you did, and you bring her back to how she was." with dissolve
    s frown_right "Pues esto es lo que tiene que pasar. Le hacemos todos una visita a Hiroko, tú la... hipnotizas de nuevo, o lo que sea que hayas hecho, y la regresas a la normalidad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:171
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_9b4fa239:

    # ks confused "Eh... n-now hold on a second. Let me think..."
    ks confused "Eh... e-esperen un segundo. Déjenme pensar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:172
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_31ebb319:

    # "And Hiroko didn't truly want to be helped either? But if that's true, why did any of this happen at all?"
    "¿Y Hiroko tampoco quería que la ayudara? Pero si ese es el caso, ¿cómo pudo pasar todo esto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:173
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_b22a6bed:

    # n determined "What's there to think about, Kyou? You hurt us, and you need to own that." with dissolve
    n determined "¿Qué es lo que hay que pensar, Kyou? Nos hiciste daño, y tienes que hacerte responsable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:174
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_4d1db176:

    # "I hypnotized them. They were hypnotized, I'm sure of it. And they were totally willing to go along with everything I told them. Everything."
    "Las hipnoticé. Estaban hipnotizadas, de eso estoy seguro. Y definitivamente estaban dispuestas a hacer todo lo que les dije. Todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:175
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_731d9b4b:

    # ks "Y-yeah... okay, maybe. But I..."
    ks "S-sí... de acuerdo, tal vez. Pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:176
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_9598a3fa:

    # "But they really want nothing to do with me? Is that the truth of it?"
    "Pero ¿en serio no quieren tener nada que ver conmigo? ¿Es esa la verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:177
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_3aa5e228:

    # s casual_handup irritated "There is nothing to think about. Either you resolve the situation with Hiroko or we take matters into our own hands." with dissolve
    s casual_handup irritated "No hay nada en qué pensar. O resuelves esta situación con Hiroko, o tomaremos el asunto en nuestras propias manos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:178
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_987b4e30:

    # "I don't understand any of this. But one thing's becoming very clear to me..."
    "No entiendo nada de esto. Pero una cosa sí me está quedando clara..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:182
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_70b65a25:

    # s annoyed "What you have done is unnatural. The person we know as Hiroko doesn't exist right now. Why don't you understand?" with dissolve
    s annoyed "Lo que has hecho es antinatural. La persona que conocemos como Hiroko no existe en estos momentos. ¿Por qué no lo entiendes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:193
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_d12e04cc:

    # n "You're right. And he must have documented what he's been doing with us, right?" with dissolve
    n "Tienes razón. Y debe tener documentado lo que ha estado haciendo con nosotras, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:194
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_97703ad7:

    # "This whole situation is getting wildly out of hand."
    "Toda esta situación se está saliendo de control."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:195
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_8c9c99d2:

    # s frown "Indeed. In any case, we need to start taking pictures." with dissolve
    s frown "Efectivamente. En cualquier caso, debemos comenzar a tomar fotografías." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:196
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_cb7a2fe0:

    # "I gotta dial things back, and fast."
    "Debo calmar las cosas, y rápido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:197
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_1c220ed2:

    # ks surprised "S-seriously, just calm down, both of you! Do you really think I'm some kind of criminal?"
    ks surprised "¡E-en serio, solo cálmense las dos! ¿De verdad creen que soy alguna clase de criminal?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:199
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_327b7635:

    # n frown "Kyou, you abused us. You cornered us when we were vulnerable and you forced us to go along with your own twisted desires." with dissolve
    n frown "Kyou, abusaste de nosotras. Nos acorralaste cuando estábamos vulnerables y nos obligaste a complacer tus propios retorcidos deseos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:200
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_9ab0ff14:

    # "My own... twisted desires? So that's what she really thinks of me?"
    "¿Mis propios... retorcidos deseos? ¿Eso es en serio lo que piensa de mí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:203
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_0a83c2bd:

    # n "I don't know if we could convince a court of law, even with all this evidence, but don't you dare tell me you didn't know what you were doing." with dissolve
    n "No sé si podremos convencer a una corte, incluso con toda esta evidencia, pero no te atrevas a decirme que no sabías lo que estabas haciendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:204
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_282572c7:

    # "So deep down in her heart, there... there really is nothing."
    "Así que en el fondo de su corazón, realmente... realmente no hay nada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:206
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_bebe940d:

    # "That's the truth of it all, huh?"
    "Conque esa es la verdad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:207
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_6f4d2b29:

    # ks "N-Nozomi, I swear I didn't know! I thought you... you..."
    ks "¡N-Nozomi, juro que no sabía! Creí que a ti... a ti..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:208
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_016189f9:

    # s casual_folded irritated "To even think you could pretend ignorance at a time like this. You contemptible sleaze." with dissolve
    s casual_folded irritated "Ni creas que puedes fingir ignorancia en un momento así, sórdido despreciable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:209
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_91e42f94:

    # ks "I thought you'd LIKE all of this!"
    ks "¡Creí que a ti esto te GUSTARÍA!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:211
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f7d0ee65:

    # n "You thought I'd... {w=1.0}{nw}"
    n "¿Creíste que me... {w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:215
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_ad816716:

    # extend "w-what on earth?"
    extend "qu-qué cosa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:216
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_2952eea5:

    # n angry "{cps=15}O-of all the-{w=0.5}{/cps}{nw}" with dissolve
