# game/Kyou 6.rpy:515
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_c0caf992:

    # h confused "She wants to get into med school, don't she? She'll never make it if she don't give it everything she's got." with dissolve
    h confused "Quiere entrar a la escuela de medicina, ¿no? Nunca lo logrará si no da todo lo que tiene." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:632
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_7884532c:

    # ks "I have never seen you that way before."
    ks "Nunca antes te había visto así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:641
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_0ce9ad28_1:

    # ks "That I could be someone who could... who could make you feel that way again."
    ks "Que podría ser yo... quien pudiera hacerte sentir así otra vez."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:648
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_03043c02:

    # "I can't imagine the look on my face is any less incredulous as Hiroko's right now. But Nozomi..."
    "Dudo que la expresión en mi rostro sea menos incrédula que la de Hiroko. Pero, Nozomi..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:649
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_303acfa0_1:

    # "You get why I did this, right?"
    "Entiendes por qué hice esto, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:653
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_e3612dc7:

    # n side sad_side "So on that day, you just walked up to me and went about hypnotizing me without my consent. Because you thought I'd be into it?" with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Conque ese día, simplemente caminaste hasta mí y te pusiste a hipnotizarme sin mi consentimiento. ¿Ya que creíste que me gustaría?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:656
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_a0e7dc3f_1:

    # n sad_closed "I still can't remember clearly, but I can imagine what I must have thought when I saw you like that." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Aún no lo recuerdo con claridad, pero puedo imaginar lo que debí pensar cuando te vi así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:659
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_0b997403_1:

    # n "For you to approach me in such a manner? I must have been terrified thinking about what you were going to do." with dissolve
    n "¿Verte acercarte de esa manera? Debí haber estado aterrada pensando qué es lo que ibas a hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:660
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_397b040e_1:

    # n concerned "I think under those circumstances, it would've been easy for my mind to withdraw into itself and just accept whatever you told me, just so I'd be safe from you." with dissolve
    n concerned "Creo que, en esas circunstancias, habría sido fácil para mi mente retraerse y simplemente aceptar lo que sea que me dijeras solo para estar a salvo de ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:662
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_dde83573_1:

    # "My mind races as I try to search my own memories of that day..."
    "Mi mente se acelera intentando rememorar lo que ocurrió ese día..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:664
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_63217bd6_1:

    # "She... she seemed more annoyed than anything. She even told me so when I had her under."
    "Lucía... lucía molesta, más que nada. Incluso me lo dijo mientras estaba hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:665
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_a9675775_1:

    # "But now she's saying she was scared? How could she possibly be scared of someone like me?"
    "Pero ¿ahora dice que estaba asustada? ¿Cómo podría asustarla alguien como yo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:666
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_a7b4c1bd:

    # ks confused "Nozomi I'd never-{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks confused "Nozomi, yo nunca haría-{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:669
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_0b788d63_1:

    # n irritated "It didn't matter how many times we rebuffed you over the years. You only ever thought about what it would take to make me want you, huh." with dissolve
    n irritated "Poco importó cuántas veces te rechazamos durante estos años. Lo único en lo que pensabas era qué haría falta para que yo te quisiera, ¿o no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:671
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_0d5ad18d_1:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "You never thought how scary that made you to me." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Nunca pensaste en el miedo que me causabas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:675
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_0029d8d1:

    # ns casual concerned "Or to Sayori. You got your hooks into her the same way, right?"
    ns casual concerned "A mí y a Sayori. Le clavaste tus garras a ella también, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:676
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_719d703d_1:

    # ns "I can just picture you backing her into a corner, with all the unearned self-confidence you got from pulling that trick on me."
    ns "Puedo imaginarte acorralándola, con toda la inmerecida confianza que obtuviste después de haber jugado ese truco conmigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:677
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_63863e6f_1:

    # ns "I'll bet you felt you were doing everything right when you \"convinced\" her to see things your way."
    ns "Apuesto a que pensaste que estabas haciendo todo bien cuando la \"convenciste\" de ver las cosas a tu manera."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:681
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_ec32bf75_1:

    # n "You see, Kyou, you learned the basics of hypnosis. How to capture a person's attention with deliberate and authoritive words and actions." with dissolve
    n "Verás, Kyou, aprendiste las bases de la hipnosis. Cómo capturar la atención de una persona con palabras y acciones deliberadas y autoritativas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:682
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_f14e06a2_1:

    # n sad "And you convinced yourself that was enough. That this obsession you have with me... was enough." with dissolve
    n sad "Y te convenciste de que eso era suficiente. De que esta obsesión que tienes conmigo... era suficiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:683
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_abf8d641_1:

    # n sad_closed "You're not some calculating mastermind trying to brainwash us all. I guess it's a little insane to think that was the case." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "No eres una mente maestra calculadora intentando lavarnos el cerebro. Supongo que pensar en eso es algo disparatado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:685
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_2f9c320e_1:

    # n front2 sleeptalk_concerned "No, you're just a dangerous fool who dabbled in something you learned but never cared to understand. And we've had to suffer for it." with dissolve
    n front2 sleeptalk_concerned "No, solo eres un obtuso peligroso que incursionó en algo que aprendió pero nunca se molestó en comprender. Y nosotras tuvimos que sufrir por eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:686
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_1a3435b6:

    # ks "Uh... w-well..."
    ks "Eh... p-pues..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:687
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_7eed6cd0_1:

    # n sleep_concerned "I'm not sure which is scarier, to be quite honest with you." with dissolve
    n sleep_concerned "No estoy segura de cuál da más miedo, siendo sincera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:688
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_82a1be69_1:

    # n pain "But you can't do this to us anymore, Kyou. You understand?" with dissolve
    n pain "Pero no puedes seguir haciéndonos esto, Kyou. ¿Lo entiendes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:689
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_8d972a75_1:

    # n cry "I NEED you to understand! It doesn't matter if I like hypnosis, you can't just do this kind of thing to me, or to anyone!" with dissolve
    n cry "¡NECESITO que lo entiendas! No importa si me gusta la hipnosis, ¡no puedes seguirme haciendo esta clase de cosas, ni a mí ni a nadie!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:690
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_32c5e7ef_1:

    # "So what she's saying is... I was right about her."
    "O sea que lo que está diciendo es... que tenía razón respecto a ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:691
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_cca084f5:

    # h casual_headhold nervous_side "H-hey, what about Sayori? He's gotta fix her, don't he?" with dissolve
    h casual_headhold nervous_side "O-oye, ¿y qué hay de Sayori? La tiene que arreglar, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:692
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_e937356a_1:

    # "I was right about her liking hypnosis. I was right about it being the key to making her notice me."
    "Tenía razón, sí le gusta la hipnosis. Tenía razón al creer que sería la clave para que me notara."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:694
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_80d0f6d9:

    # n "No... n-no, he doesn't know what he's doing. I don't think he even understands what he did to us." with dissolve
    n "No... n-no, él no sabe lo que hace. No creo que siquiera entienda lo que nos hizo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:695
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_5323cf81_1:

    # "But all I did was make her fear me. She'll never even look at me again after today."
    "Pero lo único que hice fue lograr que me tema. Ni siquiera volteará a verme después de hoy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:696
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_5c2aee70:

    # h sad_side "So then..." with dissolve
    h sad_side "Entonces..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:697
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_545aaafc_1:

    # n sad_side "I can put her in touch with a real hypnotherapist, it'll be okay." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Puedo ponerla en contacto con un verdadero hipnoterapeuta, eso debe ayudarla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:698
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_cd6898be_1:

    # "I blew it. I blew it big time, huh."
    "Lo eché a perder. Lo arruiné por completo, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:699
