# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6770
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0a684d88:

    # "How am I going to break it to her that I hypnotized Nozomi again? Somehow I don't think she'll take it well."
    "¿Cómo voy a explicarle que hipnoticé a Nozomi otra vez? No creo que se lo tome bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6771
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_79ae034b:

    # "... Maybe it's better if I don't bring it up. At least not today."
    "... Tal vez sea mejor no mencionarlo. Al menos no hoy."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6772
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e5bdbd02:

    # "{cps=20}We have more important things to talk about after all, and- {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    "{cps=20}Al fin y al cabo, tenemos cosas más importantes de las que hablar, y- {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6934
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_68429745:

    # ks frown "Listen... Sayori..."
    ks frown "Escucha, Sayori..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:6935
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f4adee5e:

    # ks "I'm fine putting you back to how you were, but what you're asking me to do, it's..."
    ks "No tengo problemas con dejarte como estabas, pero lo que me estás pidiendo es..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7102
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_37e372dc:

    # ks "Okay, listen... Sayori..."
    ks "De acuerdo, escucha... Sayori..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7103
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c19fc5c1:

    # ks "I'm fine putting you back to how you were, but what you're asking me to do, I..."
    ks "No tengo problemas con dejarte como estabas, pero lo que me estás pidiendo es..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7112
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e91b6f21:

    # ks "I can really hurt people with my penlight; I get that. But so long as I'm careful I can do so much good for people too."
    ks "Puedo hacerle daño a la gente con mi linterna; lo entiendo. Pero siempre y cuando sea cuidadoso, puedo hacerle mucho bien a la gente también."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7117
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_abde693e:

    # s "Unbelievable. The arrogance on you that you think you can handle such a wild and dangerous phenomenon you barely comprehend."
    s "Inconcebible. Tal es tu arrogancia que crees que puedes manejar un fenómeno tan peligroso que escapa de tu comprensión."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7127
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_172865b1:

    # ks "Of course they are! I hypnotized Nozomi and all that happened was..."
    ks "¡Claro que lo son! Hipnoticé a Nozomi y lo único que pasó fue..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7130
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a500a92d:

    # s "Was... what?"
    s "Fue... ¿qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7131
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8269a1e6:

    # ks confused "I- I, uh..."
    ks confused "E-eh, este..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7132
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c2a53c88:

    # "Dammit. I didn't mean to let it slip about what went down after she left me and Nozomi in the study club room."
    "Maldita sea. No quería que se me escapara lo que pasó después de que nos dejó a mí y a Nozomi en la sala del club de estudio."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7139
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b1103167:

    # "And from the look in her eyes, it's clear she's already figured out what I left unsaid." with dissolve
    "Y por la mirada en sus ojos, está claro que ya descifró lo que estaba a punto de decir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7140
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_97129a46:

    # "This really wasn't a good time to bring this up."
    "Este no era un buen momento para mencionarlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7142
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_894ba24f:

    # "... Well, I knew we'd have to deal with this sooner or later. Guess we're ripping the band-aid off now."
    "... Bueno, sabía que tendríamos que lidiar con esto tarde o temprano. Supongo que vamos a arrancar la curita."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7145
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_577ad382:

    # s "Do you take me for a fool? You *know* how dangerous that contraption of yours has been!" with dissolve
    s "¿Me tomas por una tonta? ¡Tú *sabes* lo peligroso que ha sido ese dispositivo tuyo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7146
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ed20e57b:

    # s "As if our experiment wasn't reckless enough. Why would you even consider using such a thing on her a second time?"
    s "Como si nuestro experimento no hubiera sido ya lo suficientemente imprudente. ¿Cómo se te pasó por la cabeza usar esa cosa en ella una segunda ocasión?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7149
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_aad3a671:

    # s "The stupidity boggles my mind, it really does." with dissolve
    s "Tal estupidez simplemente me deja estupefacta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7155
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3c2e140b:

    # s "YOU knew better than to involve her in this any more than we had to! You gave your WORD you would not!" with dissolve
    s "¡TÚ sabías bien por qué era mala idea involucrarla más de lo necesario! ¡Diste tu PALABRA de que no lo harías!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7156
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_58f97608:

    # s "So spare me your frivolous excuses!"
    s "¡Así que ahórrame tus frívolas excusas!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7160
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cd164fc1:

    # "Sayori begins to pace furiously around my room while my breath quickens."
    "Sayori comienza a dar vueltas por la habitación mientras su respiración se acelera con la ira."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7161
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_971c3080:

    # "But even as I panic I know one thing for sure: I can't back down now."
    "Pero incluso en este pánico, hay una cosa de la que estoy seguro: No puedo echarme para atrás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7163
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5b6e9dda:

    # ks casual angry "I... It was YOUR idea to bring Nozomi, remember? And besides, I didn't pressure her or bring it up or anything!"
    ks casual angry "Fue... fue TU idea traer a Nozomi, ¿recuerdas? ¡Y además, no la presioné ni lo propuse ni nada!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7164
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4216276f:

    # ks "SHE made the choice! She WANTED to do it all on her own!"
    ks "¡ELLA tomó la decisión! ¡Ella misma QUERÍA hacerlo!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7165
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_400f7dc7:

    # s alert_irritated "Oh nonono, don't you DARE push your responsibility on to her. As though she could've had any idea of the danger she was subjecting herself to!" with dissolve
    s alert_irritated "Oh, nonono, no te ATREVAS a pasarle a ella la responsabilidad. ¡Como si pudiera haber tenido idea del peligro al que se estaba sometiendo!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7166
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d35e19a5:

    # ks "I didn't... for fuck's sake, Sayori, I didn't put her in danger! I gave her a simple suggestion and I made sure to undo it before I let her leave."
    ks "No la... ¡la puta madre, Sayori, no la puse en ningún peligro! Le di una sugestión simple y me aseguré de deshacerla antes de dejarla ir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7167
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_53dce6c2:

    # ks "All I did was make her happy. I was so fucking careful with her, and..."
    ks "Todo lo que hice fue hacerla feliz. Tuve todo el puto cuidado del mundo, y..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7168
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_43cc29a9:

    # ks "B-besides, what did you expect me to do? Tell her to fuck off?"
    ks "A-además, ¿qué esperabas que hiciera? ¿Mandarla al carajo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7169
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ed5dad12:

    # s casual alert_angry_right "YES! If that is what it would take!" with dissolve
    s casual alert_angry_right "¡SÍ! ¡Si eso era lo que hacía falta!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7170
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e1f79a9c:

    # "Just hearing that is... it's making my chest tighten, like I can hardly breathe."
    "Solo escuchar esto... hace que me apriete el pecho, como si me costara respirar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7171
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_04c9fbf2:

    # s casual_handup alert_irritated "Dammit. I should have known better than to trust either of you to keep a cool head." with dissolve
    s casual_handup alert_irritated "Maldición. Debí saber que no podía confiar en que ustedes dos mantuvieran la cabeza fría." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7172
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b21a994b:

    # "After all we've been through, she really doesn't trust me."
    "Después de todo por lo que hemos pasado, de verdad no confía en mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7173
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5484ca92:

    # s alert_annoyed_right "You need to do better, Kyou. Do you hear me?" with dissolve
    s alert_annoyed_right "Necesitas hacer las cosas mejor, Kyou. ¿Me oyes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7174
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cd1b59d5:

    # "I can't deal with this."
    "No puedo lidiar con esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7175
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b6ca4315:

    # s alert_angry_right "The next time she approaches you for another hypnosis session, you MUST shut her down! I will brook no debate on this!" with dissolve
    s alert_angry_right "¡La próxima vez que te pida otra sesión de hipnosis, DEBES rechazarla! ¡Esto no está a discusión!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7177
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1ac045dc:

    # "I can't deal with... her."
    "No puedo lidiar con... ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7178
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4e6501de:

    # s casual "She may beg, or threaten but no matter what you... Kyou?" with dissolve
    s casual "Te podrá rogar, o amenazar, pero sin importar qué... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7180
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ffc3f6b0:

    # "I don't care what it takes..."
    "No me importa lo que haga falta..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7181
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_56945191:

    # s "Kyou, have you listened to a damn word I said?"
    s "¿Kyou, siquiera me estás escuchando?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7182
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f76af0d9:

    # ks neutral "... Become [alt_name]."
    ks neutral "... Conviértete en [alt_name]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7184
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1cb9778d:

    # s casual alert_panicked_right "Y-YOU...{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    s casual alert_panicked_right "A-AH...{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7186
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_72e87d84_1:

    # extend casual alert_surprised_right ""
    extend casual alert_surprised_right ""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7187
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_45b9f890:

    # "... I just need her gone."
    "... Necesito que se vaya."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7188
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_40dc88a2:

    # s "... Kyou? What on earth is the matter? You're looking a little pale."
    s "... ¿Kyou? ¿Qué te sucede? Luces algo pálido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7189
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a416cf65:

    # ks "O-oh, it's..."
    ks "O-oh, es que..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7190
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_973b7984:

    # "It was almost automatic, the way I just uttered those words."
    "Fue casi automática la forma en que pronuncié esas palabras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7193
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4adc5fec:

    # ks "It's nothing. Don't worry about it, [alt_name]."
    ks "No es nada. No te preocupes por eso, [alt_name]."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7195
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ac0b4db4:

    # "But now that I have, there's no going back."
    "Pero ahora que lo hice, no hay marcha atrás."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7196
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6af933ff:

    # s casual_handup alert_happy "Mhmhmh, well if you say so~" with dissolve
    s casual_handup alert_happy "Jijiji, bueno, si tú lo dices." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7197
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8de36488:

    # "I give the changed girl a smile as I try to compose myself for what I must do."
    "Le ofrezco a la chica cambiada una sonrisa mientras intento prepararme para lo que debo hacer."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7198
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_439122fe:

    # ks smile "Anyway, I was just thinking..."
    ks smile "En fin, estaba pensando..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7201
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e2724e9b:

    # s alert_giggle "About what?" with dissolve
    s alert_giggle "¿Sobre qué?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7202
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d8e31afb_1:

    # ks "Right. Well..."
    ks "Bueno. Pues..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7205
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_85ef2d08:

    # "I take my penlight from out of my pocket and lock eyes with Sayori's carefree doppelganger."
    "Saco la linterna de mi bolsillo y miro a la despreocupada doble de Sayori a los ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7207
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9747b1d8:

    # ks "While I have you here, I thought we could have another hypnosis session together. You don't mind, do you?"
    ks "Ya que estás aquí, se me ocurrió que podríamos tener otra sesión de hipnosis juntos. No te molesta, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7208
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e2e35bba:

    # "\"[alt_name]\" looks to the penlight in my hand, then to me, before letting out a cheerful giggle."
    "\"[alt_name]\" mira la linterna en mi mano, luego a mí, para luego soltar una alegre risita."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7210
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9d4964e4:

    # s alert_laugh "Oh, is that all? Well, I'm game if you are~" with dissolve
    s alert_laugh "Oh, ¿eso es todo? Bueno, yo me apunto si tú te apuntas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7216
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5160e9c3:

    # "Gesturing to the couch, I steel myself as \"[alt_name]\" goes to get comfortable."
    "Luego de invitarla a sentarse con un ademán, suelto un suspiro viendo a \"[alt_name]\" acomodarse."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7218
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_41993c56:

    # s "So what did you want to try this time?" with dissolve
    s "¿Y qué querías intentar esta vez?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7219
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4e1f41fc:

    # ks casual "I, uh... I thought I could try to drop you into trance faster. Get some practice in for the culture fest, you know?"
    ks casual "Eh... quería intentar hacerte caer en trance más rápido. Practicar un poco para el festival cultural."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7222
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0a2f6f95:

    # s "Alright~ Well, I'm ready when you are, Kyou!" with dissolve
    s "Muy bien. ¡Pues, lista cuando tú lo estés, Kyou!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7223
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_74fe7912_1:

    # "It's clear to me that \"[alt_name]\" has absolutely no memory of anything we've done since the last time she was active."
    "Me queda claro que \"[alt_name]\" no tiene ningún recuerdo de lo que hemos hecho desde la última vez que estuvo activa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7224
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_59d466d9:

    # "I don't think there can be any denying that Sayori was right about the hold these suggestions of mine have on her."
    "Creo que no se puede negar que Sayori tenía razón sobre el control que mis sugestiones tienen sobre ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7228
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_55274b8d_1:

    # ks "Very good Sayo-, uh, [alt_name]. Nice and relaxed now, as you look up at the light for me."
    ks "Muy bien Sayo-, eh, [alt_name]. Ahora relájate y observa la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7229
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d11ab2d9:

    # "So I'll make a few more suggestions. But it'll be alright, Sayori..."
    "Así que haré algunas sugestiones más. Pero, todo estará bien, Sayori..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7233
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cd2cf1c0_1:

    # ks "Finding it so easy, so natural, to let yourself sink into the couch. To allow my light to sweep over your face."
    ks "Es tan fácil, tan natural simplemente hundirte en el sofá. Permitir que mi luz se deslice por tu rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7234
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bf6ad57a:

    # "You won't need to worry about me, or Nozomi or even yourself any longer."
    "Ya no tendrás que preocuparte por mí, ni por Nozomi, ni siquiera por ti misma."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7236
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3e4f1af0_1:

    # ks neutral "Very good. Just letting the light take you down. Letting your eyelids become heavy. Knowing deep down how sleepy it makes you to watch the light."
    ks neutral "Muy bien. Deja que la luz te lleve. Deja que tus párpados se pongan pesados. Sabiendo en el fondo cuánto sueño te da observar la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7237
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ff63f3ea:

    # "With this penlight of mine I'll... I'll make things right with everybody."
    "Con esta linterna que tengo en mis manos voy a... voy a hacer las cosas bien con todos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7239
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9da1b970_1:

    # ks "Very natural, very right it is, to stare and sink further."
    ks "Es muy natural, muy correcto mirar y dejarte llevar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7241
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9d58e6d7_1:

    # ks "And if you need to relax even deeper, letting those tired, heavy eyelids close... that's okay."
    ks "Y si necesitas relajarte más profundamente dejando que esos pesados párpados se cierren... puedes hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7244
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_16e1cfef_1:

    # ks "Letting them close..." with dissolve
    ks "Deja que se cierren..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7246
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_511debc7_1:

    # ks "Dropping so quickly, [alt_name]. So deeply."
    ks "Y caerás muy rápido, [alt_name]. Muy profundo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7248
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ce573a4d_1:

    # ks "And sleep."
    ks "Y duerme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7250
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2e1bae4a_1:

    # ks "Feeling so good as your conscious mind falls deep asleep, [alt_name]." with dissolve
    ks "Se siente muy bien dejar que tu mente consciente se quede profundamente dormida, [alt_name]." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7251
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_87e94a28_1:

    # "I breathe a little sigh. So far so good." with dissolve
    "Dejo salir un suspiro. De momento, todo bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7252
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_68cbad21_1:

    # ks "Now, [alt_name], as you remain so deeply asleep, I want you to remember that this is not who you truly are."
    ks "Y ahora, [alt_name], que estás profundamente dormida, quiero que recuerdes que esta no es quien eres en realidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7253
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_95622ee6_1:

    # ks "You need to become Sayori again, while still remaining in this deep, completely relaxed state of trance."
    ks "Conviértete en Sayori una vez más, permaneciendo en este profundo y completamente relajado estado de trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7254
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2d11e6d7_1:

    # ks "You can do that can't you... Sayori?"
    ks "Puedes hacer eso, ¿verdad... Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7257
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_73735ab1_1:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "I-I... yes..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "S-... sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7259
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b4e0fca4:

    # ks "That's... that's great, Sayori. I knew you could do it." with dissolve
    ks "G-... grandioso, Sayori. Sabía que podrías hacerlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7260
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6c4b9c89_1:

    # "I take a moment to pause, as I collect myself for what I'm about to do..."
    "Hago una pequeña pausa, armándome de valor para lo que estoy a punto de hacer..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7261
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cfe37577_1:

    # ks "And now that you are, once again, Sayori I want you to do something else for me."
    ks "Y ahora que eres nuevamente Sayori, quiero que hagas algo por mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7262
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cb78b6d6_1:

    # ks "This time, I need you to accept that [alt_name] no longer exists as a part of you."
    ks "Esta vez quiero que aceptes que [alt_name] ya no forma parte de ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7263
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9ac4ed39_2:

    # ks "[alt_name] is no more, and the words \"become [alt_name]\" will no longer have any special effect on you if you hear me or anyone else say it."
    ks "[alt_name] ya no existe, y las palabras \"Conviértete en [alt_name]\" ya no tienen ningún efecto especial en ti al escucharme a mí o a quien sea decirlas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7264
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ae3b8afe_2:

    # ks "Also... you will no longer be compelled to blank your mind completely when you try to sleep at night. What you do when you try to sleep is entirely up to you again."
    ks "Además... ya no estarás obligada a vaciar por completo tu mente al intentar dormir por las noches. Lo que hagas al intentar dormir, una vez más, depende enteramente de ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7265
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ebce5f4e_1:

    # ks "In fact, anything I may have suggested to you in trance will immediately and effortlessly fade from your mind."
    ks "De hecho, cualquier sugestión que pudiera haberte dado mientras estabas en trance se desvanecerá al instante de tu mente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7266
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_976d3e97_1:

    # ks "None of the suggestions I made previously will influence your behaviour or thinking in any way."
    ks "Ninguna de las sugestiones que creé previamente influirá de ninguna manera en tu comportamiento o tu pensamiento."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7267
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6cbdd3cd_2:

    # ks "Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "Comprendes, ¿Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7269
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2c76e08e_2:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Yes..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7270
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6575aa96:

    # "That's right. I gave you what you came here for. Honor your wishes."
    "Eso es. Te di lo que buscabas. Honré tus deseos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7271
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_09a820e4:

    # "I won't interfere with your life's work or whatever."
    "No interferiré con el trabajo de tu vida o lo que sea."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7273
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e99d8bce_1:

    # ks "That's great, Sayori. Completely free of my suggestions, just feeling so good. So relaxed... so ready to accept new suggestions..." with dissolve
    ks "Grandioso, Sayori. Completamente libre de mis sugestiones, te sientes muy bien. Muy relajada... y lista para aceptar nuevas sugestiones..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7274
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9dea423a:

    # "I could never do anything terrible to you."
    "Nunca podría hacerte nada terrible."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7275
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_74fe96fc:

    # ks "Isn't that right, Sayori?"
    ks "¿No es así, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7277
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5a4d21ad:

    # s alert_sleeptalk "Yes... Ready to accept new suggestions..." with dissolve
    s alert_sleeptalk "Sí... Lista para aceptar nuevas sugestiones..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7279
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e32df393:

    # "But I can't let you interfere with what I'm doing here. I'm sure you'll understand." with dissolve
    "No puedo dejar que interfieras con lo que estoy haciendo aquí. Sé que lo entenderás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7280
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_15836ab9:

    # ks "That's right. So now I need you to accept that when I wake you from this state of hypnosis, you will find that you no longer care about my penlight."
    ks "Eso es. Y ahora, quiero que aceptes que cuando te despierte de este estado de hipnosis, notarás que ya no te importa mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7281
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bb50bb18:

    # ks "You will no longer feel any concern or curiosity about my hypnosis, or about what me and Nozomi are doing."
    ks "No sentirás ninguna preocupación ni curiosidad por mi hipnosis, ni por lo que Nozomi y yo hacemos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7282
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_294646d0:

    # ks "Instead, you will find yourself completely content to carry on as you were. Understand, Sayori?"
    ks "En vez de eso, preferirás simplemente volver a lo que solías hacer. ¿Entiendes, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:7286
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5012396e:

    # s "Uh... uh-huh. I understand..."
    s "Eh... ajá. Entiendo..."
# TODO: Translation updated at 2024-08-23 10:15

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2595
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_228fa330:

    # "Yeah, Sayori. I can't get excited about Nozomi or my [hypno6] right now. I need to focus."
    "Sí, Sayori. No puedo emocionarme demasiado por Nozomi ni mi [hypno6!t!l] ahora. Debo concentrarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2716
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_450eb24d:

    # n "Hey, sweetie~"
    n "Hola, cariño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2718
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_58e98ab8:

    # "We embrace as I step inside, but she seems to notice the tension in my body immediately." with dissolve
    "Al entrar me recibe con un abrazo, pero parece notar inmediatamente la tensión en mi cuerpo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2719
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1cba40ca:

    # n "Are you worried about today?"
    n "¿Estas preocupado por lo de hoy?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2720
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d8e887e0:

    # ks casual "Yeah. Of course I am."
    ks casual "Sí. Desde luego que sí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2722
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f5564bb1:

    # "And to that, Nozomi musters another smile as she pecks me on the lips." with dissolve
    "Y en respuesta a eso, Nozomi me ofrece otra sonrisa y un besito en los labios." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2723
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c06cfb07:

    # n smile "Everything's going to be fine. As long as we have each other, we'll be okay." with dissolve
    n smile "Todo estará bien. Siempre y cuando nos tengamos el uno al otro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2724
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e3f772ef:

    # "I have to admit, having Nozomi so completely in my corner now is giving me at least a little confidence that I can pull this off."
    "Debo admitir que tener a Nozomi completamente de mi lado ahora me da al menos un poco de confianza en que puedo lograr esto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2725
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a7e9a38a:

    # ks smile "Yeah. Maybe you're right. So do you want to take this to your room?"
    ks smile "Sí. Tal vez tengas razón. Entonces, ¿quieres llevar esto a tu habitación?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2726
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a1ed0203:

    # n side sad_side "Uh... yes. Sure, that makes sense." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Eh... sí. Claro, tiene sentido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2727
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e794b7c9:

    # ks "What?"
    ks "¿Qué?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2728
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c4da24ab:

    # n smile "N-nothing. I just never invited a guy in there before and..." with dissolve
    n smile "N-nada. Es solo que nunca he invitado a un chico ahí antes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2729
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a3aa4280:

    # n laugh "R-really, it's nothing! Come on~" with dissolve
    n laugh "¡N-no es nada! Adelante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2731
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f900badf:

    # "And on that slightly weird note, she turns and heads upstairs while I follow behind."
    "Dejándome un tanto extrañado, se da la vuelta y sube las escaleras mientras la sigo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2735
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b109b159:

    # "Leading me to..."
    "Llevándome a..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2736
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_50401ab3:

    # n chuckle "U-um, here we are!" with dissolve
    n chuckle "E-em, ¡henos aquí!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2737
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f0f6e6cd:

    # "... Wait, this is what her room looks like?"
    "... Espera, ¿así es como luce su habitación?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2738
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9e140e7b:

    # n neutral_right "Sorry about the mess..." with dissolve
    n neutral_right "Perdona el desorden..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2739
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b340beeb:

    # ks casual "Uh, yeah..."
    ks casual "Eh, claro..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2740
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_aa176e2d:

    # "As I look around the floor, I notice all sorts of discarded clothing and board game paraphernalia scattered everywhere."
    "Mirando el suelo, noto toda clase de ropa y parafernalia de juegos de mesa regados por todos lados."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2741
