# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2996
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_adc400d5:

    # s concerned "I... it would seem so." with dissolve
    s concerned "Eh... eso parece." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2997
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_cfb28d39:

    # "I'm almost home free. All I have to do now is bring Sayori back to my place and finish what I started on her."
    "Ya casi tengo todo asegurado. Lo único que tengo que hacer es llevar a Sayori a mi casa y terminar lo que empecé con ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2998
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_97614d43:

    # n sad_side "Did you know Hiroko's a [hypno6] too? Have you both been secretly monitoring me this whole time? Why?" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¿Sabías que Hiroko es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] también? ¿Las dos han estado monitoreándome en secreto todo este tiempo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2999
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0f929cf7:

    # s sleeptalk "Nozomi, this all feels so completely new to me. So I am sorry, but I have no memory about any of this." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Nozomi, todo esto es completamente nuevo para mí. Así que lo siento, pero no tengo recuerdos de nada de esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3000
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b37307ab:

    # s casual_folded sleeptalk_concerned "To discover such a thing about myself. Living a lie. No, not even living at all... I cannot begin to describe how frightening that is to me." with dissolve
    s casual_folded sleeptalk_concerned "Descubrir algo así de mí misma. Vivir una mentira. No, ni siquiera vivir... No puedo ni describir lo aterrador que esto es para mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3001
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f172ef4e:

    # "I'll be able to tinker with her and Hiroko's robotized brains to my heart's content, and with my loving new girlfriend at my side."
    "Podré retocar su robotizado cerebro así como el de Hiroko tanto como desee, y con mi amorosa nueva novia a mi lado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3002
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6665d5c8:

    # s concerned "But please believe this: I truly meant you no harm. And I have always considered you a friend. I'm sure Hiroko is... built the same." with dissolve
    s concerned "Pero por favor créeme cuando digo esto: Nunca tuve intenciones de causar ningún daño. Y siempre te he considerado mi amiga. Apuesto a que Hiroko... opera igual." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3003
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_249293ee:

    # n irritated "Ugh. I remember now; Hiroko was the one who introduced us. It's all starting to make sense..." with dissolve
    n irritated "Ay. Ahora lo recuerdo; Hiroko fue quien nos presentó. Todo comienza a tener sentido..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3004
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e0f97268:

    # n sad "But there's still a few things that confuse me... Kyou?" with dissolve
    n sad "Pero aún hay un par de cosas que me confunden... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3005
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3d02436e:

    # ks casual neutral "Hm?"
    ks casual neutral "¿Mm?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3006
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_adc4383d:

    # "Nozomi calling my name takes me out of my musings for a moment."
    "Escuchar a Nozomi decir mi nombre me saca por un momento de mis reflexiones."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3007
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5b7b37ce:

    # n front2 neutral_left "I couldn't help but notice, this... hack you did on her? Flashing your penlight in her eyes and such? Well..." with dissolve
    n front2 neutral_left "No pude evitar notar que ese... ¿hackeo que le hiciste? ¿Con la luz de tu linterna en sus ojos y eso? Pues..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3008
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fcff33f5:

    # ks confused "Well?"
    ks confused "¿Pues?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3009
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_98dcf3af:

    # n shocked "It looked exactly like you were doing with me! Wasn't that just hypnosis?" with dissolve
    n shocked "¡Lucía exactamente igual a lo que hiciste conmigo! ¿No fue eso tan solo hipnosis?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3012
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb75668b:

    # "I scratch the back of my head awkwardly at the question." with dissolve
    "Me rasco incómodamente la cabeza ante la pregunta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3013
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_33ab66a2:

    # ks "Ah, y-yeah... you see..."
    ks "Ah, s-sí... verás..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3014
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4ef566f2:

    # "Of course it's exactly like that. Sayori's not really a..."
    "Por supuesto que es exactamente igual. Sayori no es realmente un[genero_a]..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3015
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_9f20ec10:

    # "Damn, whether she's infatuated with me or not I feel like I need to come up with an explanation pronto."
    "Demonios, así esté apasionada conmigo o no, debo inventarme una explicación de inmediato."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3016
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_80fcc746:

    # ks sigh "The light effects her... optic sensors and temporarily shorts them, which allows me to slip my own commands into her system and break her original programming."
    ks sigh "La luz afecta sus... sensores ópticos y genera un corto circuito temporal que me permite introducir mis propios comandos a su sistema y romper su programación original."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3017
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a4456211:

    # ks "And yeah, my method of hacking a [hypno6] like this one is a lot like performing hypnosis on a human, but it's different."
    ks "Y sí, mi método para hackear un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] así es muy similar a practicar hipnosis en un humano, pero es diferente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3018
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e2755c49:

    # n side sad "Different how?" with dissolve
    n side sad "¿En qué es diferente?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3019
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_38ddef32:

    # ks neutral "Different in that... well, humans have free will, right?"
    ks neutral "Diferente en que... bueno, lo humanos tienen libre albedrío, ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3020
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e484bcd3:

    # ks "Hypnosis can effect people like you, but only if you let it. I might be able to hypnotize you, but I can never effect a change to you that you don't want."
    ks "La hipnosis puede afectar a la gente como tú, pero solo si lo permites. Podría hipnotizarte, pero nunca podría hacerte un cambio que tú no quieras."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3021
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f69154a5:

    # n sad_closed "That's right..." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Eso es cierto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3022
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5881d350:

    # ks "But this [hypno6] over here can only run on her programming."
    ks "Pero [el] [hypno6!t!l] que tienes a tu lado únicamente puede ejecutar programación."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3024
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3b371a58:

    # ks "Once I breached [p_their] defences with the light, [p_they] couldn't stop me from entering programming of my own." with dissolve
    ks "Una vez traspasé sus defensas con la luz, no pudo evitar que ingresara mi propia programación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3025
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8d5dc681:

    # ks "Sayori can't choose to ignore the code I put in. [p_they!c] can only follow the instructions [p_they]'s given because [hypno6]s have no free will."
    ks "Sayori no puede elegir ignorar el código que introduje. Solo puede seguir las instrucciones que se le dan porque l[genero_ao]s [hypno6!t!l] no tienen libre albedrío."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3026
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ba626c8b:

    # "I then turn my head towards the confused, anxious-looking girl to our left."
    "Luego volteo a ver a la confundida y visiblemente ansiosa chica a nuestra izquierda."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3027
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_74fe96fc:

    # ks "Isn't that right, Sayori?"
    ks "¿No es así, Sayori?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3028
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c9f88c31:

    # s casual surprised_right "I..." with dissolve
    s casual surprised_right "Yo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3029
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2960895f:

    # "Fortunately, I think I got enough into her head earlier that she'll respond the way I want her to."
    "Afortunadamente, creo que me metí lo suficiente en su cabeza como para que responda como quiero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3030
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_729f1935:

    # s sleepy "Yes, Kyou. That is correct." with dissolve
    s sleepy "Sí, Kyou. Es correcto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3031
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6ea589b6:

    # s concerned_right "As my programmer, I am compelled to process any instruction you give me." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Como mi programador, estoy obligada a procesar cualquier instrucción que me dé." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3032
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_485e83e1:

    # "And that response seems to placate Nozomi's curiosity."
    "Y esa respuesta parece aplacar la curiosidad de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3033
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d233f9c2:

    # n sad_closed "I see. I'm sorry, this is all still such a shock to me." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Ya veo. Lo siento, esto también es muy impactante para mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3035
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_11c74547:

    # n front2 concerned "Sayori and Hiroko were my only real friends, you know?" with dissolve
    n front2 concerned "Sayori y Hiroko eran mis únicas amigas verdaderas, ¿sabes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3036
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_4c53b596:

    # "But what she says next stirs something in me."
    "Pero lo que dice a continuación mueve algo dentro de mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3037
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_efa104ff:

    # ks confused "What? I thought you had tons of friends."
    ks confused "¿Qué? Creí que tenías muchos amigos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3038
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_96bf8de6:

    # n sleeptalk "Oh I'm acquainted with a lot of people, sure." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Oh, conozco a mucha gente, claro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3039
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2d466665:

    # "Seriously. She always seemed popular in class."
    "En serio. Siempre pareció popular en clase."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3040
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_484e9446:

    # n neutral_left "I hang out with some of our classmates. And I have my board game and karaoke nights with the literature club girls." with dissolve
    n neutral_left "Convivo con algunos de nuestros compañeros. Y tengo noches de juegos de mesa y karaoke con las chicas del club de literatura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3041
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7db67042:

    # "But these two girls are the only people she talks to?"
    "Pero ¿estas dos chicas son las únicas personas con las que habla?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3042
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7f677df6:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "It's... I don't know. I just have a hard time trusting people. There isn't really anyone I feel like I can trust outside of my own family." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Es... no sé. Me cuesta confiar en la gente. No hay realmente nadie en quien sienta que puedo confiar fuera de mi familia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3043
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_79db3465:

    # "And I'm turning them into mindless automatons to satisfy my own curiosity..."
    "Y las estoy convirtiendo en autómatas sin mente para satisfacer mi propia curiosidad..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3044
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f8d98a3d:

    # n concerned "No one else I can really open up to... except you, Kyou." with dissolve
    n concerned "Nadie más con quien pueda sentirme totalmente segura... excepto tú, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3072
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e8fc102e:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "You're all I have left, so..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Eres lo único que me queda, así que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3046
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1a768f06:

    # n cry "Please don't ever leave me!" with dissolve
    n cry "¡Por favor no me dejes!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3047
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e13f2118:

    # "((AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's where I'm leaving things for now, right around the point where Kyou will need to make the decision to turn back from this madness or fully commit. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Y ahí es donde lo dejaremos por ahora, justo en el punto en el que Kyou debe decidir entre darle marcha atrás a esta locura o comprometerse completamente. ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3048
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_caf9f069:

    # "(( I hope you've enjoyed this sub-path so far~ As ever, please leave any feedback you have on the usual channels. ))"
    "(( Espero que estén disfrutando esta sub-ruta hasta el momento. Como de costumbre, envíen cualquier retroalimentación por los canales de siempre. ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3049
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d9c5e22c:

    # "{size=40}TO BE CONTINUED... {/size}"
    "{size=40}CONTINUARÁ... {/size}"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2024-09-01 11:17

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2492
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb26d26d:

    # ks neutral "Anyway, I don't need you for anything today. Me and Nozomi can handle Sayori by ourselves, so having you there would just overcomplicate things."
    ks neutral "Como sea, no te necesito para nada hoy. Nozomi y yo podemos manejar a Sayori solos, así que tenerte ahí solo complicaría las cosas de más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2573
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_42fa363d:

    # "With my [hypno6] taken care of for the morning, I step into the shower and start to think about what's to come."
    "Habiéndome encargado de mi [hypno6!t!l], entro a la ducha y me pongo a pensar en lo que está por ocurrir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2579
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb7b1f4f:

    # "Then we can go over some last minute preparation."
    "Luego podemos hacer algunos preparativos de último minuto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2580
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_78e17830:

    # "We're both gonna need to be ready for anything if we're to take care of Sayori before the day's out..."
    "Ambos tendremos que estar listos para lo que sea si queremos encargarnos de Sayori para hoy..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2604
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_93629bc7:

    # "I only get one shot at this. If Sayori manages to escape me, if she realizes what I'm really doing?"
    "Solo tengo una oportunidad. Si Sayori se me logra escapar, si se da cuenta de lo que realmente estoy haciendo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2607
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8aded719:

    # "We only get one shot at this. If Sayori manages to escape us, if she realizes what I'm really doing?"
    "Solo tenemos una oportunidad. Si Sayori se nos logra escapar, si se da cuenta de lo que realmente estoy haciendo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2608
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ad8636ad:

    # "Well, I don't want to imagine what will happen to me..."
    "No me quiero ni imaginar lo que pasará conmigo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2765
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_602b5b27:

    # n rolleyes "She was a little annoying about the fact you're coming over. Like I said, you're the first guy I've invited and she kinda made a big deal about it." with dissolve
    n rolleyes "Se puso un poco fastidiosa cuando supo que tú vendrías. Como dije, eres el primer muchacho que he invitado e hizo un poco de alboroto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2805
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3c1248d6:

    # "As much as I've planned for this, I never actually figured out what exactly what I was going to say to her when this came up. I guess I'll just have to wing it."
    "Por mucho que planeé esto, nunca pensé en qué decirle exactamente cuando llegáramos a esto. Supongo que improvisaré."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:2877
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a80e47b6:

    # ks "Feeling so nice to not have to think for a while. Feeling so wonderful to let your eyelids droop, becoming sleepy under the light even as you focus on it for me."
    ks "Se siente tan bien no tener que pensar por un rato. Se siente tan maravilloso dejar que tus párpados caigan. Estar bajo esta luz te da tanto sueño, aunque te concentres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3043
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e96275c6:

    # "... Although all of this is bullshit, isn't it."
    "... Aunque toda esta mierda es una completa mentira, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3045
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_8c2a1d78:

    # "It didn't bother me before. I knew what my hypnosis was doing to these girls ever since I hypnotized Hiroko in that alley."
    "Antes no me había molestado. Sabía lo que mi hipnosis les estaba haciendo a estas chicas desde que hipnoticé a Hiroko en ese callejón."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3048
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_358f54e5:

    # "... Why is it starting to bother me now?"
    "... ¿Por qué me está molestando ahora?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3053
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_bc4346cc:

    # "I know I've gotten enough into this girl's head that she'll respond the way I want her to."
    "Sé que me metí lo suficiente en la cabeza de esta chica como para que responda como yo quiero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3055
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c6e4db81:

    # s sleepy "Yes, Kyou. That is correct. As a [hypno6], I cannot choose to ignore my code." with dissolve
    s sleepy "Sí, Kyou. Es correcto. Como [hypno6!t!l], no puedo elegir ignorar mi código." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3056
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dceedcc1:

    # s concerned_right "And as my programmer, I am compelled to process any instruction you give me." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Y como mi programador, estoy obligada a procesar cualquier instrucción que me des." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3057
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f1dcf59b:

    # "Her response seems to placate Nozomi's curiosity."
    "Su respuesta parece aplacar la curiosidad de Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3061
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5d897a6e:

    # "But then as I hear what she has to say next, I start to realize what's been nagging at me."
    "Pero luego, cuando escucho lo que dice a continuación, empiezo a darme cuenta de qué es lo que me estaba molestando."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3067
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_99dbd8ef:

    # "But the more I look back, the more I realize these two girls are the only people I ever saw her talk to. Like, *really* talk to."
    "Pero entre más me pongo a recordar, más me doy cuenta de que estas dos chicas son las únicas personas con las que la he visto hablar. *De verdad* hablar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3069
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ac764e0a:

    # "And I'm turning them both into mindless automatons to satisfy my own perverse curiosity."
    "Y las estoy convirtiendo a ambas en autómatas sin pensamientos para satisfacer mi propia perversa curiosidad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3071
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6f1b6a76:

    # "As if I wasn't getting cold feet about this shit already. Shit, my brain's doing flips right now."
    "Como si no estuviera dudando ya de esta mierda. Carajo, el cerebro me está dando vueltas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3073
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_aa355773:

    # "I have to... do something..."
    "Tengo que... hacer algo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3075
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f22ee34e:

    # "I have to..."
    "Tengo que..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3080
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d72fc775:

    # ks frown "Nozomi, come on. Get a hold of yourself!"
    ks frown "Nozomi, vamos. ¡Reacciona!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3081
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7785e003:

    # "No. This is no time for second-guessing myself. I gotta pull it together."
    "No. Este no es momento para bacilar. Tengo que ser decidido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3083
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1704964f:

    # n surprised "K-Kyou?" with dissolve
    n surprised "¿K-Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3084
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_dc724ba0:

    # "I need to follow through. I need to see this through to the end."
    "Debo seguir adelante. Debo continuar hasta el final."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3016
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ee5537db:

    # ks angry "Hiroko and Sayori aren't your friends! They were NEVER your friends! They're... they're dangerous automatons who'd betray you the second their masters send the signal!"
    ks angry "¡Hiroko y Sayori no son tus amigas! ¡NUNCA fueron tus amigas! Son... ¡autómatas peligrosos que te traicionarían tan pronto sus amos les enviaran una señal!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3086
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a9ba76da:

    # n frightened "But... t-they're still my..." with dissolve
    n frightened "Pero... a-aún son mis..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3087
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_66e5a3fc:

    # "So I will. I'll tell her what we both need to hear."
    "Y eso es lo que haré. Le diré lo que ambos necesitamos escuchar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3088
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7ddbf981:

    # ks "They're [hypno6!u]S, Nozomi! They don't care about you or anyone!"
    ks "¡Son [hypno6!t!u]S, Nozomi! ¡No les importas tú ni nadie!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3089
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c99a9eb7:

    # ks "Their whole lives were just a lie, a cover story made up by their creators. Whatever you think they feel for you? They don't. They don't feel a damn thing!"
    ks "Sus vidas enteras no fueron más que una mentira, una historia inventada por sus creadores. Lo que sea que creas que sienten por ti es falso. ¡No sienten nada!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3090
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_66fff196:

    # "And I'll comfort her, of course. I'll take her trembling hands in mine as I speak our new truth to her. A truth we both need to fully believe in."
    "Y la consolaré, por supuesto. Tomaré sus temblantes manos en las mías mientras le explico nuestra nueva realidad. Una realidad que ambos debemos creer con plenitud."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3091
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5e3f0e29:

    # ks sad "I'm sorry, Nozomi. I know it hurts, but you have to let go. But I promise you it'll be okay. We will be okay."
    ks sad "Lo siento, Nozomi. Sé que duele, pero tienes que irte. Mas te prometo que todo estará bien. Estaremos bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3093
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b426fa2e:

    # "We need to believe. For both our sakes." with dissolve
    "Debemos creer. Por el bien de ambos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3094
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a7ff42a7:

    # ks smile "I'm here for you. And I promise I'll never, ever leave you. Got it?"
    ks smile "Estoy aquí para ti. Y te prometo que nunca jamás te dejaré ir. ¿Entendido?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3096
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f9f159e5:

    # "I pull her in for a hug and my quivering new girlfriend throws her arms around me, choking down sobs." with dissolve
    "Tiro de ella para abrazarla, y mi nueva novia, estremeciéndose, me envuelve en sus brazos, aguantando el llanto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3097
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_745f09da:

    # n "Y-y-you're right. Thank you for saying that."
    n "T-t-tienes razón. Gracias por decir eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3098
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2537da4c:

    # n concerned "I'll be fine, Kyou. Just give me a little time." with dissolve
    n concerned "Estaré bien, Kyou. Solo dame algo de tiempo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3101
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_81a44f0b:

    # "As she sniffles, I notice Nozomi glance towards our silent companion, who gazes forlornly back at her." with dissolve
    "Sollozando, Nozomi voltea a ver a nuestra silenciosa acompañante, quien le devuelve la mirada con aflicción." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3102
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b240c0ab:

    # "Sayori has nothing to say to defend herself. No compulsion to flee, or attack us, or scream for help."
    "Sayori no tiene nada que decir en su defensa. No tiene ningún impulso por huir, atacarnos ni pedir auxilio."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3103
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_2f2c3356:

    # "After all, [p_they] really is just a recently-reprogrammed [hypno6] short on commands from [p_their] newly-appointed programmer."
    "Después de todo, no es más que un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] recién reprogramad[genero_ao] a quien le faltan comandos de su nuevo programador."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3105
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_5cdc4739:

    # "It's just the truth, right?" with dissolve
    "Esa es la realidad, ¿cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:3107
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b159617f:

    # n "Do what you have to, my love..."
    n "Haz lo que tengas que hacer..."

