# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4313
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_705a4c3f:

    # "Finally. It's the weekend..."
    "Finalmente. Llegó el fin de semana..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4314
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_55c3092b:

    # "Yesterday really dragged on since I last saw Akiko. But at least those girls didn't bother me again."
    "El día de ayer se sintió muy largo desde que me despedí de Akiko. Pero al menos esas chicas no me volvieron a molestar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4315
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8814abb4:

    # "All I've had to do is wait. Something I've had to do a ton these past couple nights."
    "Lo único que tuve que hacer fue esperar. Algo que he tenido que hacer mucho las últimas noches."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4319
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_c25cb1b4:

    # "But finally, after all these hours listlessly playing videogames and staring at the ceiling, my patience is about to be rewarded."
    "Pero finalmente, luego de varias horas de jugar videojuegos con desgano y quedarme mirando el techo, mi paciencia está por ser recompensada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4321
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_b7acc76c:

    # ks casual smile "Akiko?"
    ks casual smile "¿Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4323
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_bac277a7:

    # a "\"Errm... ehehehe~\""
    a "\"Emmm... ejejeje.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4324
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ede5a580:

    # ks smirk "... Nozomi?"
    ks smirk "... ¿Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4325
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_83881178:

    # a "\"Oh... oh gosh, that felt so empowering when you called me that.\""
    a "\"Oh... oh, Dios, oigo el nombre y tiemblo. Siento que me llena de poder.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4326
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7c7009c3:

    # a "\"... Say it again?\""
    a "\"... Dilo otra vez.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4327
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f112052c:

    # "I can't stop myself from letting out a hearty chuckle."
    "No puedo evitar soltar una risa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4328
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_23c1e651:

    # ks smile "Not until I see you. We're still on for today, right?"
    ks smile "No hasta que pueda verte. Sigue en pie lo de hoy, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4329
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5f2c5b86:

    # a "\"Oh, of course! I just wanted to say I might be held up a little while. They're taking longer with the last customer than I thought.\""
    a "\"¡Oh, por supuesto! Solo quería decir que tal vez llegue un poco tarde. Se están tardando más con la clienta anterior de lo que pensé.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4330
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f6d10b8b:

    # ks confused "\"Last customer\"? Where are you, exactly?"
    ks confused "¿\"La clienta anterior\"? ¿Dónde estás, exactamente?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4331
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_57492c83:

    # a "\"Y-you know... just some place, haha.\""
    a "\"Y-ya sabes... solo un lugar, jaja.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4332
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ca4f6c87:

    # "It was only a simple question, \"Nozomi\". What's made you so nervous, I wonder?"
    "Fue una pregunta simple, \"Nozomi\". ¿Qué te tiene tan nerviosa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4333
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_0b73f3bc:

    # a "\"A-anyway, so I'll meet you at 10:30. I hope that's okay?\""
    a "\"E-en fin, te veré a las 10:30. Espero que no haya problema.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4334
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_14e400e2:

    # ks smile "It's fine. I haven't even left the house yet."
    ks smile "No te preocupes. Ni siquiera he salido de la casa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4335
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_961a58fa:

    # a "\"That's great! S-see you soon, then, ehehehe~\""
    a "\"¡Genial! E-entonces, te veo pronto, ejejeje.\""

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4337
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3481d23a:

    # "Man, with how skittish she seemed, I'm not sure if I should be more excited to see her or just worried."
    "Caray, con lo escurridiza que está siendo, no estoy seguro de si debería estar emocionado o preocupado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4338
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ec40a51f:

    # "But I do like how she sounds now. She almost made me feel I was talking to... well, her."
    "Pero sí que me gusta cómo suena ahora. Casi me hizo sentir que estaba hablando con... bueno, ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4340
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ea908f20:

    # "It's a pleasant thought, and one that I keep in my head as I take my time walking into town."
    "Una idea agradable que permanece en mi cabeza mientras camino a la ciudad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4343
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_95282573:

    # "... Well, this is where we agreed to meet. Did she need even more time?"
    "... Bueno, este es nuestro punto de encuentro. ¿Aún necesita más tiempo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4344
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_85aba4bd:

    # "Is this just what girls are like? I guess I wouldn't know."
    "¿Así son todas las chicas? Supongo que no sé mucho al respecto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4345
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7406a1b4:

    # "But... she'll be here. I know she wouldn't let me down like this."
    "Pero... aquí estará. Sé que no me defraudaría así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4346
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_91931a57:

    # a "Kyou!"
    a "¡Kyou!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4347
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3873a71a:

    # "Almost on cue, I hear her voice carry out over the small crowds around me."
    "Y casi como si la hubiera invocado, escucho su voz entre las pequeñas multitudes que me rodean."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4348
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_b52070dd:

    # "And with a smile, I turn around..."
    "Y con una sonrisa, me doy la vuelta..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4352
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2cade0a3:

    # a "Ahahahaha... h-hi!"
    a "¡Ajajajaja... ho-hola!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4353
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_67e42227:

    # "... I am dimly aware of the lower half of my jaw detaching myself from the rest of it."
    "... Apenas noto cómo mi mandíbula inferior se desprende de la otra mitad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4354
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_337645cb:

    # a laugh_wink "S-s-... surprise!" with dissolve
    a laugh_wink "¡S-s-... sorpresa!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4355
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_774bea32:

    # "So the appointment she was talking about..."
    "O sea que la cita que mencionó que agendó..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4356
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7620a098:

    # ks casual surprised "Y-you just got that done?! That's..."
    ks casual surprised "¡¿T-te acabas de hacer eso?! Está..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4357
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_9d721195:

    # a happy "Mhm! Gosh, I was so nervous they wouldn't get the color just right, but the second I saw myself in the mirror I was just so..." with dissolve
    a happy "¡Mjm! Dios, temía tanto que no les quedara bien el color, pero en cuanto me miré al espejo, me puse tan..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4358
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2cc9fcbf:

    # a laugh "Aaaaaahhh~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a laugh " Aaaaaahhh. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4359
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_c311d652:

    # "She runs both her hands through her revitalized hair, now a delectable shade of brown, while my face recovers to form an admiring smile."
    "Desliza ambas manos por su revitalizado cabello, que ahora es de un deleitable tono marrón, mientras mi rostro se recupera y forma una sonrisa de admiración."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4360
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8f0e743b:

    # ks smile blush "It's perfect."
    ks smile blush "Está perfecto."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4361
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a9557a39:

    # "It really is uncanny how well she nailed it."
    "Es aterrador lo bien que lo replicó."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4362
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_76ea038e:

    # a casual_down3 laugh_open "It is, isn't it!" with dissolve
    a casual_down3 laugh_open "¡¿Verdad que sí?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4363
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8465f8e5:

    # "Even the fact she went through with something like this is..."
    "El solo hecho de que haya llevado a cabo algo así es..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4364
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ce90f984:

    # a smile_side "I actually thought about dyeing my hair the other day, right after restyling it? But I've never done it before and I didn't want to mess up." with dissolve
    a smile_side "De hecho pensé en teñirme el cabello el otro día, justo después del cambio de estilo. Pero nunca lo he hecho antes y no quería hacer un desastre." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4365
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_21c48bef:

    # a smile "So I booked an appointment online right there and then." with dissolve
    a smile "Así que puse una cita en línea en ese instante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4366
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_551fa099:

    # "Well, it's extraordinary."
    "Pues, es extraordinario."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4367
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_95765dd2:

    # a casual3 sigh -blush "Could you believe I was actually thinking about backing out of it the following morning?" with dissolve
    a casual3 sigh -blush "¿Puedes creer que estaba pensando en cancelarlo a la mañana siguiente?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4368
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_1a3532d4:

    # ks confused -blush "Oh, really?"
    ks confused -blush "Oh, ¿en serio?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4369
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f487e5d3:

    # a sad "Yeah. It seems ridiculous to think about now, right? I'm just glad you gave me the courage to go through with it." with dissolve
    a sad "Sí. Suena ridículo ahora, ¿verdad? Me alegra que me hayas dado el valor para hacerlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4370
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_101f1e8a:

    # "I mean, it's still Akiko underneath those beautiful locks, but... wow, she's really starting to pull it off."
    "Quiero decir, sigue siendo Akiko bajo esa bella cabellera, pero... guau, de verdad lo está consiguiendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4371
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_95eb9c9f:

    # ks smile blush "So what do you want to do now... Nozomi?"
    ks smile blush "¿Y qué quieres hacer ahora... Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4373
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_e632fc2d:

    # "To that, \"Nozomi\" simply runs a hand through her pretty hair once again as she smiles adorably at me." with dissolve
    "En respuesta, \"Nozomi\" simplemente pasa una mano por su lindo cabello una vez más, mostrándome una adorable sonrisa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4374
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5daa5319:

    # a happy "Mhmhmhm~ A-actually, I have one more appointment to keep if you don't mind?" with dissolve
    a happy "Jijiji. D-de hecho, tengo otro lugar al que ir si no te molesta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4375
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8625e7e4:

    # "She did mention a second appointment, now that I think of it."
    "Sí, mencionó una segunda cita, ahora que lo pienso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4376
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4e8853fa:

    # ks -blush "This close together? Maybe we should've met for lunch if your morning's so busy."
    ks -blush "¿Y los agendaste tan cerca uno del otro? Tal vez debimos mejor planear un almuerzo si tu mañana está tan ocupada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4377
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_05ce4628:

    # a laugh "O-oh no, ehehehe~" with dissolve
    a laugh "O-oh, no, ejejeje." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4378
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_73686414:

    # a smile "I, um... wanted you to be here for this." with dissolve
    a smile "Yo, em... quería que estuvieras aquí para esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4381
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_96695e3c:

    # "Intrigued, I let her lead me down the streets for a short distance before she stops outside a..."
    "Intrigado, dejo que me guíe por las calles, y tras caminar una corta distancia, se detiene afuera de una..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4386
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_471e60fe:

    # ks casual confused "Aki-... Nozomi, this is..." with dissolve
    ks casual confused "Aki-... Nozomi, esto es..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4387
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_07876f74:

    # a happy blush "Yeah! They have a same day service; I actually stopped by here on my way to the hairdressers." with dissolve
    a happy blush "¡Sí! Tienen servicio para el mismo día; de hecho, pasé por aquí de camino a la peluquería." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4388
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_e971409e:

    # a smile "Do you mind waiting outside? I shouldn't be long." with dissolve
    a smile "¿Te molesta esperar afuera? No debería tardar mucho." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4389
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f571bcd3:

    # "How could I refuse a smile as pure as that?"
    "¿Cómo puedo decirle que no a una sonrisa tan pura como esa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4390
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_12aa880a:

    # ks smile blush "Y-yeah, okay. I'm not going anywhere."
    ks smile blush "S-sí, de acuerdo. No me iré a ningún lado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4392
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5cd16baf:

    # "Not sure why I couldn't just walk in there with her, but if this is what she wants I'm not going to complain."
    "No sé por qué no pude simplemente entrar con ella, pero si eso es lo que quiere, no me voy a quejar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4393
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_68e380e0:

    # "The weather's certainly pleasant enough to wait, and it gives me time to process my shock."
    "El clima ciertamente es apto para esperar afuera, y me da tiempo para procesarlo todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4394
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8f7b5025:

    # "This is what I wanted, and... wow, she's really going all out today."
    "Esto es lo que quería, y... guau, realmente no está teniendo reparos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4395
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_83417f44:

    # "As if I wasn't excited already. But seeing just how far that girl's going to reinvent herself? And all because of me?"
    "Como si no estuviera de por sí emocionado. Pero ¿viendo lo lejos que está yendo esa chica para reinventarse? ¿Y todo debido a mí?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4396
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a669e443:

    # "It's stirring something in me, that's for sure..."
    "Está avivando algo en mí, de eso estoy seguro..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4398
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ff3931f8:

    # a "I'm back!"
    a "¡Ya volví!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4401
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_57486122:

    # "Yeah. I knew what she was up to the second she stopped us here, but..."
    "Sí. Sabía lo que planeaba en cuanto nos detuvimos aquí, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4402
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_30342da3:

    # ks surprised "How... how on earth?"
    ks surprised "¿Cómo... cómo es que...?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4403
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4c02328c:

    # "Those glasses..."
    "Esos anteojos..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4404
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_387aff7a:

    # ks "They're EXACTLY the same as hers!"
    ks "¡Son EXACTAMENTE iguales a los suyos!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4405
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5581822b:

    # a laugh_open "RIGHT?!" with dissolve
    a laugh_open "¡¿VERDAD?!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4406
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2a4bfd56:

    # a smile_side "I mean... gosh, I looked through their website last night to see if they had anything similar, but there they were! I couldn't believe it!" with dissolve
    a smile_side "Digo, Dios, revisé su sitio web anoche para ver si tenían algo similar, ¡pero ahí estaban! ¡No lo podía creer!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4407
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ad608675:

    # a happy "She must come here for her glasses too~" with dissolve
    a happy "Tal vez ella también compra sus anteojos aquí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4408
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_416d4964:

    # "She happily plays with them between her fingers as I watch, while they frame her face so perfectly."
    "La veo jugar alegremente con ellos entre sus dedos, mientras que enmarcan perfectamente su rostro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4409
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3f9d957a:

    # "Although as she does so, I find myself having to ask..."
    "Aunque debo preguntar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4410
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_d2639082:

    # ks confused "So, uh... all this must have set you back, right?"
    ks confused "Este, eh... ¿imagino que todo esto no fue muy barato?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4411
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7f5e37c5:

    # a smile "Mhm, a little. Especially with my prescription." with dissolve
    a smile "Mjm, sí costó un poco. Sobre todo con mi prescripción." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4412
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_20158fee:

    # a laugh "Between this and the hairdressers I'm basically flat broke!" with dissolve
    a laugh "¡Entre esto y la peluquería, estoy básicamente en la quiebra!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4413
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_03bff4aa:

    # "She says that in such a chipper manner."
    "Y lo dice con tanto regocijo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4414
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_65a76d99:

    # ks confused -blush "Oh... wow, I'm sorry about that."
    ks confused -blush "Oh... guau, perdón por eso."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4415
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ffecc065:

    # a confused -blush "Eh? Why apologize? You didn't march me out here and make me do this, did you?" with dissolve
    a confused -blush "¿Eh? ¿Por qué te disculpas? Tú no me trajiste acá y me obligaste a hacer esto, ¿o sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4416
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ef39b87f:

    # "I mean, honestly? I may as well have."
    "Pues, la verdad, algo así."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4417
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5675212e:

    # ks sigh "Well no, but..."
    ks sigh "Bueno, no, pero..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4418
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4498400a:

    # a smile "It's not about the money, Kyou. I'm not worried about that at all." with dissolve
    a smile "No se trata del dinero, Kyou. Eso no me preocupa ni un poco." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4420
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2fd45dfb:

    # a smile_side "When I saw myself back at the hairdressers I was squealing with happiness. But when I saw myself at the opticians just now? I was blinking back tears." with dissolve
    a smile_side "Cuando me vi en el espejo de la peluquería, estaba chirriando de alegría. Pero cuando me vi en la óptica, estaba aguantándome las lágrimas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4421
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_97412229:

    # a neutral_side "I guess I just... I just hadn't thought of myself as attractive for such a long time." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "Supongo que no... no me había considerado atractiva en tanto tiempo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4423
