    "Hago justo eso, y Nozomi cierra vertiginosamente la cortina mientras espero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4542
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_03278261:

    # "It's pretty exciting hearing her change right in front of me, with just this one piece of fabric protecting her modesty."
    "Es bastante emocionante oírla cambiarse delante de mí, con nada más que esta tela protegiendo su modestia."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4543
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_51e7095d:

    # "Man, this really does feel like I'm clothes shopping with my girlfriend."
    "Caray, de verdad siendo que estoy de compras con mi novia."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4544
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_c23def7c:

    # "Can't help but wonder how she thinks about all this. About us..."
    "No puedo evitar preguntarme qué siente sobre todo esto. Sobre nosotros..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4549
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5b685c54:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: Once again, we gotta use our imagination. Noziko isn't wearing undies (the only other outfit change I have for her right now), she's in a dress and it's sooo cute! ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTROA: Una vez más, hay que usar la imaginación. Noziko no está en ropa interior (el único otro atuendo que tengo para ella de momento), ¡sino en un lindísimo vestido! ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4550
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_c0fabc2f:

    # "((As for what it actually looks like, I haven't decided on a look yet. I might have a few options to poll the angelcakes members on my Discord, though. ))"
    "(( En cuanto a cómo luce realmente, aún no lo he decidido. Pero tal vez haya una votación para los miembros angelcakes en mi Discord. ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4551
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3e3a5121:

    # a "Ehehe, what do you think?"
    a "Ejeje, ¿qué opinas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4552
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7d283101:

    # ks casual smile blush "Oh... w-wow, that is stunning."
    ks casual smile blush "Oh... g-guau, está espectacular."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4553
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_36fd4287:

    # "I don't even have to think about it. I don't need to flatter her; she really does look fantastically feminine to my eyes."
    "Ni siquiera tengo que pensarlo. No necesito adularla; de verdad luce deslumbrantemente femenina ante mis ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4568
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4cd500a5:

    # a "Mm! I don't know for sure, but it does feel very Noz..."
    a "¡Mm! No lo sé con certeza, pero sí se siente muy Noz..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4555
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4cbde023:

    # "She pauses a second to clear her throat, before chirping assertively."
    "Hace una pausa para aclararse la garganta, para luego continuar asertivamente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4556
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fd0b4c45:

    # a smile "It does feel very me~" with dissolve
    a smile "Se siente muy yo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4557
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4f4b17f4:

    # ks "Yeah, Nozomi... it does."
    ks "Sí, Nozomi... estoy de acuerdo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4558
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2000b001:

    # "We just stand there in a moment's peace, while my eyes wander up and down her much improved appearance."
    "Nos quedamos un momento en silencio mientras mis ojos recorren su mejorada apariencia de arriba a abajo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4559
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5f102700:

    # a nozomi_b_up3 smile_side "S-so, um... I know you said you were going to buy me new clothes. But surely you didn't mean two outfits, right?" with dissolve
    a nozomi_b_up3 smile_side "P-pues, em... sé que dijiste que ibas a comprarme ropa nueva. Pero imagino que no quisiste decir dos atuendos, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4560
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_dc1664b3:

    # ks smile "Ah, yeah. We gotta get you some new shoes too."
    ks smile "Ah, sí, también necesitas zapatos nuevos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4561
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ca99d877:

    # a surprised "Huh?! Oh my gosh, really?" with dissolve
    a surprised "¡¿Eh?! Oh, por Dios, ¿de verdad?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4562
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7190e259:

    # "I grin as I nod at her once more."
    "Le asiento con una sonrisa una vez más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4563
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_426adf50:

    # ks "Gotta complete the look, right? We've already come this far."
    ks "Hay que completar el set, ¿verdad? Ya llegamos hasta aquí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4564
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_20194388:

    # a happy "Kyou, I... I'm speechless! You've been so generous to me practically since the day we met." with dissolve
    a happy "Kyou, yo... ¡no tengo palabras! Has sido tan generoso conmigo prácticamente desde que nos conocimos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4565
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8e06df9f:

    # "She and I share another moment's silence. But she's surely waiting on me to make a decision here."
    "Ella y yo compartimos otro momento de silencio. Pero seguro está esperando a que yo tome la decisión."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4566
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_c9a801f7:

    # "Just getting to wear anything that has the essence of Nozomi is a delight for her."
    "Tan solo poder usar algo que lleve la esencia de Nozomi es un deleite para ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4568
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_43b91644:

    # "So I've decided..." with dissolve
    "Así que mi decisión es..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4573
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3186a405:

    # "Akiko nods happily, as she moves to neatly assemble the other garments back in their hangers before picking up her old clothes and throwing them over her shoulder." with dissolve
    "Akiko asiente alegremente, luego devuelve las otras prendas a donde estaban colgadas y posteriormente pone su vieja ropa sobre su hombro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4576
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_815b00ea:

    # "Akiko nods happily."
    "Akiko asiente alegremente."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4577
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2a1447e2:

    # a "Okay, Kyou. Just give me a moment, I'm going to change back."
    a "Muy bien, Kyou. Solo dame un momento para volver a cambiarme."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4581
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_d8c1db46:

    # "She doesn't wait for my answer before pulling the curtains in front of me once more."
    "No espera a mi respuesta antes de volver a esconderse tras las cortinas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4583
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_6c583f14:

    # "Judging by the sounds she's making in there, I know I'm not going to be standing here much longer..."
    "A juzgar por los sonidos que está haciendo ahí, sé que no estaré parado aquí mucho tiempo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4588
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2ca1c6be:

    # a "All done~"
    a "Todo listo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4589
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2353c44e:

    # ks casual smile "Perfect. You look perfect, Nozomi."
    ks casual smile "Perfecto. Te ves perfecta, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4590
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_0044712e:

    # a happy blush "Ehehehe~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a happy blush "Ejejeje. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4591
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3e91f667:

    # a smile "Get the store clerk over here, okay? I want to wear these out." with dissolve
    a smile "Trae al empleado de la tienda, ¿puedes? Quiero llevármelo puesto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4594
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_62b05287:

    # "So Nozomi and I took our shopping spree to the shoe store."
    "Y luego Nozomi y yo continuamos nuestras compras en la tienda de zapatos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4595
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ba3bf3f5:

    # "We must've spent nearly an hour in there. But with her company it barely felt like any time at all."
    "Pasamos como una hora ahí. Pero con su compañía, sentí que no pasó nada de tiempo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4600
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_c277b2e0:

    # "Needless to say, my lovely companion looks pleased as punch when we stop at a nearby restaurant for lunch."
    "Sobra decir que mi adorable compañera luce más que complacida cuando nos detenemos en un restaurante cercano para almorzar."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4601
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_caf91928:

    # a smile "Well I don't know about you, but I'm just having the best day~" with dissolve
    a smile "Bueno, no sé tú, pero yo estoy teniendo el mejor día de todos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4602
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_6e878cdd:

    # ks casual smile "Yeah. It's been a lot of fun."
    ks casual smile "Sí. Ha sido muy divertido."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4604
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_68623d6c:

    # "I smile at her, and she lets out the cutest giggle." with dissolve
    "Le sonrío, y ella responde con una adorable risita." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4605
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ceb83c62:

    # a smile "I still have no idea what it is about you, you know? But it really does make me feel like everything's going to be okay when you're around." with dissolve
    a smile "Aún no sé qué es lo que hay en ti, ¿sabes? Pero en serio me hace sentir que todo estará bien cuando estás cerca." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4606
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5b6eb92c:

    # ks smile "Yeah. I feel the same way around you, Nozomi. Helps me forget..."
    ks smile "Sí. Yo me siento igual junto a ti, Nozomi. Me ayuda a olvidar..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4607
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_d0738384:

    # "... That you're not really Nozomi? Even though you sure look and act like her now?"
    "... ¿Que no eres realmente Nozomi? ¿A pesar de que ahora luzcas y actúes como ella?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4608
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_97600372:

    # ks "... Well, you know. And it sounds like you've been going through a rough patch of your own."
    ks "... Bueno, ya sabes. Y suena a que tú también has pasado por dificultades."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4609
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_5f8a9eab:

    # a neutral "Yeah. And don't even get me started on all the student council work." with dissolve
    a neutral "Sí. Ni me hagas empezar con todo el trabajo del consejo estudiantil." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4623
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2672afa8:

    # a "A few of the other members were complaining that we've fallen behind on our culture fest preparations since we started our talks."
    a "Algunos de los otros miembros se han quejado del atraso con los preparativos del festival cultural desde que empezamos nuestras charlas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4612
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3f5a5c3e:

    # a sad_side "We actually have a big sporting event tomorrow that I need to be there for, so after today I'll barely have any time to call my own until the festival's wrapped up." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Y de hecho tenemos un gran evento deportivo al que tengo que asistir mañana, después de hoy apenas tendré tiempo para mí hasta el festival." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4613
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_e7c74d47:

    # ks confused "Oh, really?"
    ks confused "Oh, ¿en serio?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4614
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fbce6c8e:

    # "That does surprise me. The culture fest's still a couple weeks away."
    "Eso sí que me sorprende. Aún faltan un par de semanas para el festival."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4615
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a6a1ca79:

    # a sad "Yeah. I might even get forced out of the president position if I don't step it up." with dissolve
    a sad "Sí. Puede que me saquen de la posición de presidenta si no acelero el ritmo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4616
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_dc386661:

    # "I didn't realize she was that snowed under."
    "No me había dado cuenta de que tenía tanto encima."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4617
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_aba6f4fa:

    # ks "What about our school lunch meets? Are we still on for those?"
    ks "¿Y qué hay de nuestras reuniones durante el almuerzo? ¿Eso sigue en pie?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4619
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_96916731:

    # a "Mhm, sure. Although we'll probably have to move out of the student council room; it's too disruptive to the others and it hasn't been fair to them." with dissolve
    a "Mjm, seguro. Aunque probablemente tendremos que hacerlo fuera de la sala del consejo estudiantil; es muy disruptivo para los demás y no ha sido justo para ellos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4620
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_12001599:

    # ks neutral "Right..."
    ks neutral "Cierto..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4621
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_841aa061:

    # "I knew this was all going a little too well."
    "Sabía que todo esto estaba yendo demasiado bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4623
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4a86b03f:

    # "But before I can say any more the student council president starts to break into another smile, as if to banish the unpleasant interlude from her mind." with dissolve
    "Pero antes de poder decir nada más, una sonrisa aparece en el rostro de la presidenta, como buscando borrar el desagradable interludio de mi mente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4624
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_1e980581:

    # a "Ehhh, b-but let's not get worked up about that right now~"
    a "Eeeh, p-pero no nos preocupemos por eso ahora mismo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4625
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3f739ce1:

    # "I sigh."
    "Suspiro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4626
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8e1aad18:

    # ks sigh "I'm trying, but... just when we were really getting to know each other, you know?"
    ks sigh "Lo intento, pero... justo cuando empezábamos a conocernos de verdad, ¿sabes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4628
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_109121c0:

    # ks "Nozomi, you're the only person I can even talk to around here. Hell, you're the only person I even want to be around." with dissolve
    ks "Nozomi, eres la única persona con la que puedo hablar por aquí. Es más, eres la única persona junto a la que quiero estar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4629
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_816ff475:

    # ks "Guess these next weeks are gonna suck for both of us, huh."
    ks "Supongo que las próximas semanas serán las peores para los dos, ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4630
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_b2437735:

    # a smile "It will. But it's only a few weeks, Kyou. We'll still be here." with dissolve
    a smile "Así parece. Pero son solo algunas semanas, Kyou. Seguiremos aquí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4631
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_645d0cdd:

    # "That sweet smile of hers she's showing me now. She's really nailed that expression from..."
    "Esa dulce sonrisa que me está mostrando ahora. De verdad le sale exactamente igual a la de..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4632
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_ae7a2a63:

    # a "And besides, I don't have any other plans for today. Do you?"
    a "Y además, no tengo ningún otro plan para hoy. ¿Y tú?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4633
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4a707da9:

    # "Well, that other girl."
    "Bueno, esa otra chica."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4634
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_24bccb53:

    # ks neutral "Well... no I don't."
    ks neutral "Este... no, ninguno."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4660
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_80d984dd:

    # a giggle "Hehe, right~ So let's give today our all, okay?" with dissolve
    a giggle "Jeje, ya veo. Entonces disfrutemos este día al máximo, ¿sí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4636
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_de8860ec:

    # "That smile gives me peace. It's surely the same, assured feeling that she's gotten from being around me."
    "Esa sonrisa me da paz. Seguramente es la misma sensación de seguridad que ella recibe al estar junto a mí."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4649
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_65f0af3a:

    # ks smile "Yeah. We can spend the whole day together if you want to, Nozomi." with dissolve
    ks smile "Sí. Tienes razón, podemos pasar el día entero juntos si eso quieres, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4638
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_80d1a94e:

    # "As long as we have each other, we're going to be all right."
    "Siempre y cuando nos tengamos el uno al otro, estaremos bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4639
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a96aa509:

    # ks "Because I sure as hell want to."
    ks "Porque yo definitivamente sí quiero."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4640
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f9c92691:

    # a laugh "Ahahaha, I was hoping you'd say that~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a laugh "Ajajaja, esperaba que dijeras eso. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4641
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a4c081bb:

    # a smile "And I know just the thing we could do, if you're up for it." with dissolve
    a smile "Y sé exactamente lo que podríamos hacer, si te parece." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4642
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_67e6052f:

    # ks smile "With you I'd be up for anything. Uh, so long as it's not too expensive; I think my wallet's running pretty dry too."
    ks smile "Contigo estoy dispuesto a lo que sea. Eh, siempre y cuando no sea muy costoso; creo que mi billetera está un poco seca también."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4643
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_14af3370:

    # a laugh_wink blush "Ehehe s-sorry. And you've already spoiled me so much today." with dissolve
    a laugh_wink blush "Ejeje, l-lo siento. Y ya me consentiste mucho hoy." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4644
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fa604440:

    # ks smile blush "It's fine. Y-you're worth it, Nozomi."
    ks smile blush "Descuida. T-tú lo vales, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4645
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_353c72f5:

    # ks "Just tell me, alright?"
    ks "Solo dímelo, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4646
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a41dd2fb:

    # a smile_side "Okay, well I was thinking..." with dissolve
    a smile_side "Está bien, pues, estaba pensando..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4647
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4d3a1ad5:

    # a happy "How do you feel about hitting the karaoke club after lunch?" with dissolve
    a happy "¿Qué te parecería ir al club del karaoke después de almorzar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4650
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_9b4fbfa8:

    # "((AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's all we have for now!))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: ¡Y eso es todo lo que tenemos por ahora! ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4651
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a5083e05:

    # "((Look forward to the next update where I'll be extending this storyline and adding some completed artwork for these scenes, including (I hope) those new outfits for Akiko.))"
    "(( Esperen con ansias la próxima actualización donde expandiré esta historia añadiendo algo de arte para estas escenas, incluyendo (espero) esos nuevos atuendos para Akiko. ))"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4652
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_48ee1faf:

    # "{size=30}TO BE CONTINUED... {/size}"
    "{size=30}CONTINUARÁ... {/size}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4669
translate spanish Day6_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9cea4648:

    # "That must be her at the door now."
    "Esa debe ser ella en la puerta."

