# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4448
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_cf3f9728:

    # ks smile blush "And let me be the first to tell you, Nozomi: You look absolutely gorgeous."
    ks smile blush " Y déjame ser el primero en decírtelo, Nozomi: Te ves absolutamente preciosa."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4520
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_b88e6c87:

    # "There's a momentary pause before Nozomi pulls the curtain back while I suck in a breath..."
    "Hay una pausa momentánea antes de que Nozomi abra la cortina mientras yo contengo el alitendo..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4526
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_97be4e44:

    # "My eyes take her all in, from head to toe and back again."
    "Mis ojos absorben su bella imagen de la cabeza a los pies."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4527
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_e424889d:

    # "Before me stands a woman now completely made over, happily modelling the clothes that apparently made up Nozomi's past self."
    "Ante mí se encuentra de pie una mujer completamente renovada, modelando felizmente los ropajes que al parecer Nozomi alguna vez vistió."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4549
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_79d7480e:

    # a shy_side "Well we can't say for sure, but... w-well, it is a pretty dress you have there..." with dissolve
    a shy_side "Pues, no podemos estar seguros, pero... b-bueno, ese que tienes ahí es un vestido lindo..." with dissolve

# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-05-21 19:06

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4622
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8e219234:

    # "She then lets out a sigh as her head slightly droops, and for a moment I'm forced to remember who it is I'm really talking to." with dissolve
    "Su cabeza decae ligeramente con un suspiro, y por un momento me veo obligado a recordar con quién estoy hablando realmente." with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-05-31 22:02

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:78
translate spanish Day6_NonCon_Kyou_b51b9e18:

    # n front2 determined "Do you think we're stupid, Kyou? I've known Hiroko since junior high, but even if I hadn't did you seriously think we'd not notice something amiss?" with dissolve
    n front2 determined "¿Crees que somos estúpidas, Kyou? He conocido a Hiroko desde que la secundaria, pero aun si fuera menos tiempo, ¿de verdad crees que no notaríamos que algo anda mal?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4686
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_af27e39f:

    # a "Oh... well, I was in my elementary school choir?" with dissolve
    a " Oh... bueno, yo estaba en el coro en primaria." with dissolve

# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-06-20 18:51

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4728
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2b2e0d24:

    # "It's good that she's learned from my old crush. But now I wonder... maybe Nozomi's been listening to her too much if she's taking everything she says about herself as gospel?"
    "Es bueno que aprendiera de la chica que solía gustarme. Pero ahora me pregunto... ¿no le estará prestando demasiada atención si se toma todo lo que le dice de sí misa como evangelio?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4729
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_6a0c5472:

    # ks neutral "Alright, get comfy on that couch. I want to try something."
    ks neutral "Muy bien, ponte cómoda en ese sofá. Quiero probar algo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4730
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_e0cb65a4:

    # a confused "Try something? Aren't we going to sing?" with dissolve
    a confused "¿Probar algo? ¿No íbamos a cantar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4731
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_6609667f:

    # ks smile "We will, soon. But how about we kick things off with a little hypnosis first?"
    ks smile "En un momento. Pero ¿qué tal un pequeño preámbulo con algo de hipnosis?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4736
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2fb42361:

    # "Nozomi's confusion gives way to a smile, as an excited purr seems to escape her lips." with dissolve
    "La confusión de Nozomi da paso a una sonrisa, y un ronroneo de emoción escapa de sus labios." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4737
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f089753c:

    # a "O-oh gosh, are you..."
    a "O-oh, Dios, ¿quieres...?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4738
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_16e882f2:

    # ks "Let me hypnotize you, Nozomi."
    ks "Déjame hipnotizarte, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4741
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_c77c2160:

    # "I sit beside her on the couch and produce my penlight from my pocket, and her eyes immediately swivel towards it as she giddily nods her consent." with dissolve
    "Me siento a su lado en el sofá, saco mi linterna del bolsillo, y sus ojos inmediatamente giran hacia ella, al darme su consentimiento asintiendo la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4742
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_4e9edfda:

    # a "Ahh, a-alright. Doing it here sounds like it'd be fun, actually~"
    a "Aah, m-muy bien. Suena divertido hacerlo aquí, de hecho."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4747
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_51ca5513:

    # k "I love that you get so excited for this stuff. Okay, now just look up and let the light hit you."
    k "Me encanta lo emocionada que esto te pone. De acuerdo, ahora mira hacia arriba y deja que la luz brille sobre ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4751
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fadf2917:

    # k "That's right, Nozomi. Just breathe, relax, and remember all that you felt before."
    k "Eso es, Nozomi. Solo respira, relájate y recuerda todo lo que sentiste antes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4754
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_0b9bdfcd:

    # k "Remembering how good it feels to watch the light dance before your eyes."
    k "Recuerda lo bien que se siente observar la luz danzar ante tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4760
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_e0db86df:

    # k "And how it draws you in so completely, as that pleasant, sleepy feeling washes over you."
    k "Y cómo te empieza a atraer, sintiendo esa placentera sensación de sueño extenderse dentro de ti."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4758
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_602e8ac3:

    # a "{size=16}Mmmm..."
    a "{size=16}Mmmm..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4765
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7d976b92:

    # k "Remembering how your eyelids become heavier, and heavier, with every sweep of the light."
    k "Recuerda cómo tus párpados se ponen más y más pesados con cada desliz de la luz."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4771
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_9a624aa6:

    # k "How sleepy it makes you feel."
    k "Cómo te hace sentir más y más sueño."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4775
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f948b0e8:

    # k "How deeply entranced it makes you."
    k "Cómo te hace caer en un profundo trance."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4781
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_55c56508:

    # k "How it all makes you want to close those heavy eyelids and..."
    k "Cómo te hace querer cerrar esos pesados párpados. Solo déjalos caer y..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4787
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_d10d4d5e:

    # k "Sleep. All the way down... that's right."
    k "Duerme. Muy profundo... eso es."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4776
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_7e047669:

    # "I have to smile as she adorably slumps her head gently against my shoulder as she falls."
    "Me provoca una sonrisa lo adorable que luce al dejar caer su cabeza gentilmente sobre mi hombro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4791
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_9329d310:

    # k "Falling so... so very deeply for me now, Nozomi. Becoming so completely, wonderfully hypnotized."
    k "Déjate caer muy... muy profundo, Nozomi. Sintiéndote completa y maravillosamente hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4778
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_bfa4d9df:

    # "Makes me want to fall silent for a few moments and just enjoy having her here. A sleeping beauty cuddled up so cozily by my side."
    "Me hace querer guardar silencio por unos momentos y simplemente disfrutar tenerla aquí. Una bella durmiente acurrucada cómodamente a mi lado."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4779
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_06aa86e1:

    # "I hope we get to enjoy many more moments like this, Nozomi. But now I need to correct you on a few... misconceptions you've been having."
    "Espero que podamos disfrutar muchos más momentos así, Nozomi. Pero ahora tengo que corregir un par de... ideas erróneas que has estado teniendo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4795
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_68b1f499:

    # k "And now that you're feeling so wonderfully hypnotized, now that you're completely focused on my voice... I want to talk to you about the person you admire most." with dissolve
    k "Y ahora que te sientes tan maravillosamente hipnotizada, ahora que estás totalmente enfocada en mi voz... quiero hablarte de la persona que más admiras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4796
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fee46c56:

    # k "And who is it you admire most?"
    k "¿Y quién es la persona que más admiras?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4782
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_3dcfef56:

    # a sleeptalk "Mmn, it's... it's Nozomi. Nozomi Akemi..." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "Mmn, es... es Nozomi. Nozomi Akemi..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4800
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_17729cc6:

    # k "That's right. Nozomi Akemi is the person you admire more than anyone in the world. So much that you want to be everything she is." with dissolve
    k "Así es. Nozomi Akemi es la persona que admiras más que a nadie en este mundo. Tanto que quieres ser todo lo que ella es." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4801
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_24d11b8a:

    # k "You've adopted the way she looks, the way she acts, the way she talks... you've even adopted her name."
    k "Has adoptado la forma en que luce, la forma en que actúa, la forma en que habla... incluso adoptaste su nombre."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4802
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_820a00cc:

    # k "It makes you feel so good to impersonate Nozomi, doesn't it?"
    k "Te hace sentir muy bien imitar a Nozomi, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4787
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fe5922a8:

    # a sleeptalk "Yes... feels so... good..." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "Sí... se siente muy... bien..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4806
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_55819097:

    # k "I know it does. And it's good that you feel so strongly about her. Nozomi is feminine perfection, and it's right that you try to meet that ideal. It makes you happy." with dissolve
    k "Yo sé que sí. Y es bueno que lo que sientas por ella sea tan fuerte. Nozomi es la perfección de la feminidad, y es bueno que sigas ese ideal. Te hace feliz." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4807
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f2921639:

    # k "And I don't want you to lose that feeling. It's good that you're becoming so much like Nozomi. It's good that you want to be so much like Nozomi."
    k "Y no quiero que pierdas ese sentimiento. Es bueno que te estés volviendo tan parecida a Nozomi. Es bueno que quieras ser como Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4808
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_6d3d8e52:

    # k "But that doesn't mean you always need to listen to Nozomi herself."
    k "Pero eso no quiere decir que siempre tengas que escuchar a la misma Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4793
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_b0027474:

    # "I watch as the girl's lips start to tremble as I introduce the idea to her; the doubt writing itself plainly even on her dormant features." with dissolve
    "Veo cómo los labios de la chica comienzan a temblar al introducirle la idea; la duda escrita con claridad incluso en su rostro durmiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4812
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2b85a326:

    # a "I... I-I don't...?" with dissolve
    a "¿No siempre... e-escucharla...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4814
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_99c73880:

    # k "Sometimes people lie to us when they want to spare our feelings. Sometimes we even lie to ourselves. And in that respect, Nozomi is no different to anyone else." with dissolve
    k "A veces la gente nos miente para no herir nuestros sentimientos. A veces incluso nos mentimos a nosotros mismos. Y en ese aspecto, Nozomi no es diferente a los demás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4816
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_666689eb:

    # k "Sometimes, it takes the people observing us to reveal the truth about who we really are. Understand?" with dissolve
    k "A veces hace falta que la gente nos observe para revelar la verdad de quiénes somos realmente. ¿Comprendes?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4798
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_d87e0679:

    # a sleeptalk "Ah... I... t-think so..." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "Ah... eso... c-creo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4820
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fc3e637c:

    # k "So keep that in mind when I talk to you about Nozomi." with dissolve
    k "Así que mantén eso en mente cuando te hable de Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4821
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_649565ad:

    # k "Sometimes, what I say about her is more truthful than what Nozomi has to say about herself."
    k "A veces lo que yo diga sobre ella es más veraz que lo que ella dice de sí misma."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4822
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_2125bc7b:

    # k "Let that thought sit deep in your mind. Let it inform how you think about Nozomi, and then awaken for me on a count of three."
    k "Deja que esa idea se asiente en lo profundo de tu mente. Deja que informe cómo piensas en Nozomi, y despierta a la cuenta de tres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4824
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_fba992bb:

    # k "Waking up nice and refreshed in one... two... three."
    k "Despierta fresca y contenta en uno... dos... tres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4805
