    # a drowsy "Mmmrrrrnn..." with dissolve
    a drowsy "Mmmmnnnnn..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4828
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_47020290:

    # "Damn, that sleepy expression of hers is gorgeous. She's gorgeous." with dissolve
    "Cielos, qué hermosa es su soñolienta expresión. Qué hermosa es esta chica." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4829
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_f2b0b38a:

    # k "Welcome back, Nozomi. Did you enjoy that?"
    k "Bienvenida de vuelta, Nozomi. ¿Qué te pareció?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4810
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_9471e4af:

    # "And I surely don't want to make her any less beautiful than she is now. Merely keep her on the right path to perfection." with dissolve
    "Y ciertamente no quiero hacerla menos bella de lo que es ahora. Simplemente la mantendré en el camino correcto a la perfección." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4811
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8f176dbe:

    # a "I did... gosh, you have such a way with words, Kyou~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}"
    a "Maravilloso... Dios, sí que eres bueno con las palabras, Kyou. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4812
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_200f6ad8:

    # "I certainly don't want her to stop moving forward with the ideal of becoming Nozomi. A little course correction is all she needs."
    "Ciertamente no quiero que deje de avanzar con el ideal de volverse Nozomi. Una pequeña corrección de curso es todo lo que necesitaba."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4835
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_8d82b5ed:

    # k "You just bring out the best in me, Nozomi. Now let's just forget about that silly idea of your idol not being able to sing."
    k "Eres tú quien saca lo mejor de mí, Nozomi. Ahora, ¿por qué no nos olvidamos de esta tonta idea de que tu ídolo no sabe cantar?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4814
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_44d87f0f:

    # a confused -blush "O-oh, are we still on that?" with dissolve
    a confused -blush "O-oh, ¿aún sigues con eso?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4838
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_80bd8eeb:

    # k "Forget about what she told you. We both know she sings like a goddamned angel."
    k "Olvídate de lo que te dijo. Ambos sabemos que ella canta como un maldito ángel."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4817
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_62885ea4:

    # a "Ehehe... Yeah, she absolutely does. She must've been messing with me." with dissolve
    a "Ejeje... Sí, definitivamente. Seguro solo estaba jugando conmigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4818
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_547fe4c2:

    # a smile_side "Mmm that's so like her, trying to downplay how perfect she is compared to the rest of us." with dissolve
    a smile_side "Mmm, típico de ella, intentando minimizar lo perfecta que es comparada al resto de nosotros." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4843
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_b0fc6dda:

    # k "Yeah. But you're not so bad yourself, Nozomi. And I'm sure you sing wonderfully, so what do you say about getting us started?"
    k "Sí. Pero tú tampoco estás tan mal, Nozomi. Estoy seguro de que tu canto es fabuloso, así que, ¿te parece si empezamos?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4823
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_b193e08a:

    # "Yeah. There's no need to over-react here, make a big deal out of this and risk spoiling our day out."
    "Sí. No hay por qué exaltarme, ahogarme en un vaso de agua y arriesgarme a arruinar nuestro día."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4824
translate spanish Day6_Villain2_Kyou_a2264fcb:

    # "As much as she idolizes Nozomi and no doubt hangs on her every word, I know she listens to me too."
    "Por mucho que idolatre a Nozomi y sin duda le preste atención a cada palabra que ella dice, sé que me escucha a mí también."

