# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1942
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a7732939:

    # ks sigh "Just... sleep, Nozomi."
    ks sigh "Solo... duerme, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1945
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_33f795ca:

    # n "..." with dissolve
    n "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1947
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e1bdfc25:

    # "I stare down at her as I compel her to lay dormant at my feet once more, and I let out a pained sigh."
    "Miro hacia abajo en su dirección una vez habiéndola obligado a yacer durmiente a mis pies, y suelto un acongojado suspiro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1948
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_b2f28ce1:

    # "All this time I've been contorting these girls to my will, forcing them to worship me beyond all reason so I could feel good about myself for once in my life."
    "Llevo todo este tiempo controlando a estas chicas a mi voluntad, forzándolas a venerarme más allá de todo raciocinio. Pude sentirme bien conmigo mismo por una vez en mi vida."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1949
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a2b53dce:

    # ks neutral "Dropping... dropping deeper, Nozomi..."
    ks neutral "Caes muy... muy profundo, Nozomi..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1950
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a6462c7e:

    # "All it took was a few words from this girl to take that feeling away? Seems she really got to me after all."
    "¿Y solo hicieron falta unas cuantas palabras de estas chicas para hacer ese sentimiento desaparecer? Creo que al final sí me afectó."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1951
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c230c7e2:

    # ks "Deeper into hypnosis. Letting everything but the sound of my voice fade from your consciousness once more."
    ks "Más profundo en este estado de hipnosis. Dejando que todo excepto el sonido de mi voz se esfume de tu consciencia una vez más."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1952
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_de711f3a:

    # "But now that she's completely at my mercy, right at the cusp of total victory, I'm really just going to... walk it all back? Forget all this ever happened?"
    "Pero ahora que está completamente a mi merced, justo en la cúspide de mi victoria total, ¿de verdad voy a... dar marcha atrás así nada más? ¿Olvidar que todo esto pasó?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1953
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_f4e44922:

    # ks "And now that you only hear my voice, I need you to listen very carefully..."
    ks "Y ahora que únicamente oyes mi voz, quiero que escuches atentamente..."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1954
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_a433a63b:

    # "Abandon everything I've accomplished?"
    "¿Abandonaré todo lo que logré?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1955
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6fa8e9d8:

    # ks "Because everything I tell you from this point on, you will accept as your absolute truth."
    ks "Porque todo lo que te diga desde este momento lo aceptarás como tu realidad absoluta."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1956
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_0de6ed34:

    # "All of this, my penlight, my year of hard work... it was for nothing?!"
    "Todo esto, mi pluma linterna, mi año de arduo trabajo... ¡¿fueron para nada?!"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1957
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_376f6732:

    # ks "First, you are going to forget every interaction you've had with me this past week, all the way back to when I first hypnotized you in our classroom."
    ks "Primero vas a olvidar cada interacción que tuviste conmigo la última semana, desde el momento en que te hipnoticé por primera vez en el salón."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1958
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_130fbdef:

    # ks "You will not recall a single thing that happened between us since that day. And that includes when Hiroko tried to drag you to karaoke."
    ks "No recordarás nada de lo que pasó entre nosotros desde ese día. Y eso incluye cuando Hiroko intentó arrastrarte al karaoke."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1959
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e7f884a7:

    # ks "As far as you're aware, none of that ever happened. Understand?"
    ks "En lo que a ti concierne, nada de eso pasó. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1961
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_c01da0da:

    # n "Yes... none of that... h-happened..." with dissolve
    n "Sí... nada de eso... p-pasó..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1963
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6eef1682:

    # ks "That's good. Every other suggestion I have made to you will disappear as soon as you wake from this state of trance. You only need to forget." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Las demás sugestiones que te he hecho desaparecerán tan pronto despiertes de este estado de trance. Solo debes olvidar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1964
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_875bfee9:

    # "So... undo this, huh? Do you really think I can just set the clock back on all of this, Nozomi? Because you're wrong."
    "Conque... deshacer esto, ¿eh? ¿De verdad crees que puedo simplemente retroceder el reloj, Nozomi? Porque te equivocas."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1965
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1ad9eafd:

    # "You made all that noise about quitting school. And I could make you and your friends forget that, sure. But your parents?"
    "Pegaste el grito en el cielo sobre dejar la escuela. Y podría hacerte a ti y a tus amigas olvidar eso, claro."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1966
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_84f68c0f:

    # "No, if I'm going to mend things with you all then I have no choice but to alter your realities."
    "No, si voy a enmendarlo todo, no tengo más opción que alterar sus realidades."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1967
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_1bd0c14a:

    # ks "Instead, what you'll remember about me this week is what I'm about to tell you."
    ks "En vez de eso, lo que recordarás sobre mí de esta semana es lo que estoy por contarte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1968
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_efab90c6:

    # "You don't mind, do you, girls?"
    "No les molesta, ¿o sí, chicas?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1969
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_ab9f7d41:

    # ks "Nozomi, when we met to clean the classroom that day, I did flash my penlight over your eyes and I did try to hypnotize you."
    ks "Nozomi, cuando nos juntamos para limpiar el salón ese día, sí encendí la luz de mi linterna sobre tus ojos e intenté hipnotizarte."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1970
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_13fd3faf:

    # ks "But it wasn't serious; it was just a dumb prank. It obviously didn't work, and we both knew it didn't work. But you felt scared all the same about what I did."
    ks "Pero no fue en serio; solo fue una tonta broma. Obviamente no funcionó, y ambos supimos que no funcionó. Pero de igual forma te asustó lo que hice."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1971
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_3678e39d:

    # ks "So you skipped school and wanted to leave because you couldn't think straight."
    ks "Así que faltaste a la escuela y quisiste irte porque no pensabas con claridad."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1972
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_6e6b7f03:

    # ks "You were going to go through with it, only Sayori called you this morning to say I wanted to apologize and talk things out with all of you."
    ks "De verdad pensabas dejar la escuela, pero Sayori te llamó esta mañana para decirte que quería disculparme y conversarlo con ustedes."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1973
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_d9125b16:

    # ks "Obviously you were worried about seeing me again, but Sayori convinced you that it was worth listening to what I had to say."
    ks "Obviamente te preocupaba volver a verme, pero Sayori te convenció de que valía la pena escuchar lo que tenía que decir."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1974
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_e08afa76:

    # ks "That's why you're all here in my house today. We talked things through, you accepted my apology, and now you no longer want to leave our school."
    ks "Y por eso todas están aquí en mi casa. Lo discutimos, aceptaste mi disculpa, y ya no quieres dejar la escuela."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1975
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_fb1b754d:

    # ks "When I wake you up from this state of trance, these will be the things you remember. Okay, Nozomi?"
    ks "Cuando te despierte de este estado de trance, todo eso será lo que recordarás. ¿Está bien, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1977
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_292c412e:

    # n "... Okay." with dissolve
    n "... Bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:1979
translate spanish Day6_Villain_Kyou_7c739106:

    # ks "Good. I want you to think only of these memories. Repeat them in your head over and over until I say it's time to wake..." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien. Quiero que pienses solo en estos recuerdos. Repítelos en tu cabeza una y otra vez hasta que sea hora de despertar..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4289
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_a65f14d6:

    # "I then turned my attention to the other girls, who had been watching me with those adoring yet vacant expressions this entire time."
    "Después de eso dirijo mi atención a las otras chicas, quienes me estuvieron observando de principio a fin con esos vacíos ojos de adoración."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4291
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_9d079861:

    # "And in no time at all I had them sat on the couch as I turned my penlight on them for one last time, and took an eraser to their memories..."
    "Y en un santiamén las senté en el sofá y usé mi linterna en ellas una última vez, pasando el borrador por sus memorias."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4300
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_ebd65177:

    # n "... So that's really all it was."
    n "... De modo que de eso se trataba todo."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4302
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_1df791c8:

    # "That lie I told Hiroko the other day is now a reality for all three of them."
    "Esa mentira que le conté a Hiroko el otro día es ahora una realidad para las tres."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4303
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_a47824eb:

    # n sleeptalk "Just a dumb prank..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Solo una tonta broma..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4304
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_09438669:

    # ks casual neutral "I tried to tell you, Nozomi. Did you honestly think it could've been anything else?"
    ks casual neutral "Traté de decírtelo, Nozomi. ¿De verdad pensaste que podría ser alguna otra cosa?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4308
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_b3535d28:

    # n "Well... I-I mean..." with dissolve
    n "Pues... b-bueno..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4310
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_323122b7:

    # "Hiroko awkwardly rubs the back of her head as Nozomi stumbles for an explanation." with dissolve
    "Hiroko se frota incómodamente la nuca mientras Nozomi balbucea, tratando de explicar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4311
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_6189a19a:

    # h confused_side "Like, let's be real Nozo; we totally get why you thought it was something worse." with dissolve
    h confused_side "O sea, la verdad, Nozo, sí entendemos por qué pensaste que era algo peor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4312
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_3a337d87:

    # h frown "Wouldn't even be the creepiest thing he's done, I reckon." with dissolve
    h frown "No sería lo más espeluznante que ha hecho, eso sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4313
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_2e57a3d1:

    # "I'm kinda missing her being my brainwashed idiot minion already."
    "Casi empiezo a extrañar la versión secuaz lavada del cerebro de ella."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4314
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_fd81a2cc:

    # s casual_handup sleeptalk "Now now, Hiroko, there is no need for that." with dissolve
    s casual_handup sleeptalk "Bien, Hiroko, eso no es necesario." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4316
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_39631855:

    # s concerned "He has explained everything to our satisfaction, has he not?" with dissolve
    s concerned "Nos ha dado una explicación satisfactoria para todo, ¿no es así?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4317
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_d2b328a6:

    # "But I'll have to save my regrets for later."
    "Pero mejor me guardo mis arrepentimientos para luego."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4319
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_1d656ff4:

    # h casual rolleyes "Uggh... I guess?" with dissolve
    h casual rolleyes "Ayy... ¿supongo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4320
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_664bd3b7:

    # "The main thing is, none of these girls have any idea of what I really did to them."
    "Lo importante ahora es que ninguna de estas chicas tiene idea de lo que realmente les hice."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4323
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_33e0a98d:

    # n "He has. So... I guess I owe you an apology too, Kyou." with dissolve
    n "Es cierto. Así que... supongo que yo también te debo una disculpa, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4326
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_720ec734:

    # ks confused "Huh?" with dissolve
    ks confused "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4327
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_4f940dc3:

    # n concerned "I feel like kind of an idiot for taking things this far; letting my imagination get the better of me." with dissolve
    n concerned "Me siento un poco idiota por haber llevado las cosas tan lejos; dejarme llevar por mi imaginación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4328
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_0e01436d:

    # "And you bet I'll be taking the truth of all this to my goddamned grave."
    "Y pueden apostar a que me llevaré la verdad de todo esto a mi maldita tumba."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4329
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_c602f94e:

    # ks frown "N-no, don't... worry about it. We're cool."
    ks frown "N-no, no te... preocupes por eso. Todo bien."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4330
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_7dea3f2d:

    # h casual_headhold2 frown_side "H'yeaaah, I dunno about that. So, are we done? Can we go now?" with dissolve
    h casual_headhold2 frown_side "Seeeeh, de eso no estoy tan segura. Pero bueno, ¿ya terminamos? ¿Nos podemos ir?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4333
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_c8710660:

    # n "Ahh, that's right! You have a tournament to prepare for and I've been keeping you away with my crap!" with dissolve
    n "¡Aah, es cierto! ¡Tienes un torneo para el que prepararte y yo te tengo aquí con mi desastre!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4334
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_79439498:

    # h sad_side "Geez, Nozo, don't be like that... But yeah, I seriously gotta make a move; I didn't even bring my tennis gear with me." with dissolve
    h sad_side "Caray, Nozo, no te pongas así... Pero sí, de verdad me tengo que ir; ni siquiera me traje mi equipo de tenis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4335
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_3570f591:

    # s smile "Go on, Hiroko. Get out of here." with dissolve
    s smile "Anda, Hiroko. Sal de aquí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4336
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_5cdd4931:

    # h casual_armup angry_side "Hey, you can't tell me what to do!" with dissolve
    h casual_armup angry_side "¡Oye, no puedes decirme que hacer!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4337
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_e23e7b2f:

    # n shocked_side "GO!" with dissolve
    n shocked_side "¡VE!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4338
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_8b2c176c:

    # h shocked_side "I'm going, I'm going!" with dissolve
    h shocked_side "¡Por eso digo que ya me voy!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4341
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_788598a2:

    # "So there's no going back now. I really did undo everything, just like Nozomi wanted." with dissolve
    "Pues ya no hay marcha atrás. De verdad deshice todo, tal como Nozomi quería." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4344
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_d1d151fa:

    # n "Honestly. If she chokes at that thing because of me I'll never forgive myself." with dissolve
    n "Juro que si lo echa a perder por mi culpa, nunca me lo perdonaré." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4345
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_8aa13b21:

    # "But I have to wonder... maybe this wasn't all for nothing."
    "Pero me pregunto... si tal vez me equivoco al creer que todo fue para nada."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4346
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_43c5acdd:

    # s casual concerned "Nozomi, you know she would be here no matter what. If she knew coming here would despoil her chance of a tennis career, she would still make the same choice." with dissolve
    s casual concerned "Nozomi, sabes que ella estaría aquí sin importar qué. Si supiera que venir aquí la despojaría de su oportunidad de una carrera en el tenis, su decisión sería la misma." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4347
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_105f9358:

    # s neutral "She would never blame you for something like this." with dissolve
    s neutral "Ella nunca te culparía por algo así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4348
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_69ed633a:

    # "Could I have really lived with what I'd done? Could I have even gotten away with it all in the end?"
    "¿Podría haber vivido con lo que habría hecho? ¿Podría siquiera haberme salido con la mía al final?"

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4349
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_0bc3329f:

    # n sad_closed "Yeah... I suppose you're right." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Sí... supongo que tienes razón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4350
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_dd79b2b6:

    # "I guess now I'll never know."
    "Ahora supongo que nunca lo sabré."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4352
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_3b913221:

    # s casual_handup smile "Anyway, I believe that concludes matters. And much like our firey friend, I have other places to be today." with dissolve
    s casual_handup smile "En fin, me parece que eso concluye nuestros asuntos. Y en semejanza a nuestra llameante amiga, tengo otros sitios a los que asistir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4353
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_197c8288:

    # n happy "Well... yeah, alright. Let's get out of here too~" with dissolve
    n happy "Bien... sí, de acuerdo. Salgamos de aquí también." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4354
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_6ff035a8:

    # "And... ugh, I gotta believe that's for the best."
    "Y... aj, he de creer que es para mejor."

# game/Kyou 6.rpy:4355
translate spanish Devotion_Reconsidered_8973ec4e:

